        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER ONE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Worst Birthday</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Not for the first time, an argument had broken out over breakfast at number four, Privet Drive. Mr Vernon Dursley had been woken in the early hours of the morning by a loud, hooting noise from his nephew Harry’s room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Third time this week!’ he roared across the table. ‘If you can’t control that owl, it’ll have to go!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried, yet again, to explain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She’s   <i class=\"calibre4\">bored, </i>’ he said. ‘She’s used to flying around outside. If I could just let her out at night …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do I look stupid?’ snarled Uncle Vernon, a bit of fried egg dangling from his bushy moustache. ‘I know what’ll happen if that owl’s let out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He exchanged dark looks with his wife, Petunia. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to argue back but his words were drowned by a long, loud belch from the Dursleys’ son, Dudley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I want more bacon.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s more in the frying pan, sweetums,’ said Aunt Petunia, turning misty eyes on her massive son. ‘We must feed you up while we’ve got the chance … I don’t like the sound of that school food …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nonsense, Petunia, I never went hungry when  <i class=\"calibre4\">I  </i> was at Smeltings,’ said Uncle Vernon heartily. ‘Dudley gets enough, don’t you, son?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley, who was so large his bottom drooped over either side of the kitchen chair, grinned and turned to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pass the frying pan.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve forgotten the magic word,’ said Harry irritably. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The effect of this simple sentence on the rest of the family was incredible: Dudley gasped and fell off his chair with a crash that shook the whole kitchen; Mrs Dursley gave a small scream and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>8 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">clapped her hands to her mouth; Mr Dursley jumped to his feet, veins throbbing in his temples. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I meant “please”!’ said Harry quickly. ‘I didn’t mean –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘WHAT HAVE I TOLD YOU,’ thundered his uncle, spraying spit over the table, ‘ABOUT SAYING THE M WORD IN OUR </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">HOUSE?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HOW DARE YOU THREATEN DUDLEY!’ roared Uncle Vernon, pounding the table with his fist. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I just –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I WARNED YOU! I WILL NOT TOLERATE MENTION OF </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">YOUR ABNORMALITY UNDER THIS ROOF!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared from his purple-faced uncle to his pale aunt, who was trying to heave Dudley to his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right,’ said Harry, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">all right</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon sat back down, breathing like a winded rhinoceros and watching Harry closely out of the corners of his small, sharp eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ever since Harry had come home for the summer holidays, Uncle Vernon had been treating him like a bomb that might go off at any moment, because Harry  <i class=\"calibre4\">wasn’t</i> a normal boy. As a matter of fact, he was as not normal as it is possible to be. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter was a wizard – a wizard fresh from his first year at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. And if the Dursleys were unhappy to have him back for the holidays, it was nothing to how Harry felt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He missed Hogwarts so much it was like having a constant stomach ache. He missed the castle, with its secret passageways and ghosts, his lessons (though perhaps not Snape, the Potions master), the post arriving by owl, eating banquets in the Great Hall, sleeping in his four-poster bed in the tower dormitory, visit-ing the gamekeeper, Hagrid, in his cabin in the grounds next to the Forbidden Forest and, especially, Quidditch, the most popular sport in the wizarding world (six tall goalposts, four flying balls and fourteen players on broomsticks). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All Harry’s spellbooks, his wand, robes, cauldron and top-of-the-range Nimbus Two Thousand broomstick had been locked in a cupboard under the stairs by Uncle Vernon the instant Harry had come home. What did the Dursleys care if Harry lost his place in the house Quidditch team because he hadn’t practised all sum-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Worst Birthday 9 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">mer?  What  was  it  to  the  Dursleys  if  Harry  went  back  to  school without any of his homework done? The Dursleys were what wizards called Muggles (not a drop of magical blood in their veins) and as far as they were concerned, having a wizard in the family was a matter of deepest shame. Uncle Vernon had even padlocked Harry’s owl, Hedwig, inside her cage, to stop her carrying messages to anyone in the wizarding world. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked nothing like the rest of the family. Uncle Vernon was large and neckless, with an enormous black moustache; Aunt Petunia was horse-faced and bony; Dudley was blond, pink and porky. Harry, on the other hand, was small and skinny, with brilliant green eyes and jet-black hair that was always untidy. He wore round glasses, and on his forehead was a thin, lightning-shaped scar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was this scar that made Harry so particularly unusual, even for a wizard. This scar was the only hint of Harry’s very mysterious past, of the reason he had been left on the Dursleys’ doorstep eleven years before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At the age of one, Harry had somehow survived a curse from the greatest dark sorcerer of all time, Lord Voldemort, whose name most witches and wizards still feared to speak. Harry’s parents had died in Voldemort’s attack, but Harry had escaped with his lightning scar, and somehow – nobody understood why – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Voldemort’s powers had been destroyed the instant he had failed to kill Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So Harry had been brought up by his dead mother’s sister and her husband. He had spent ten years with the Dursleys, never understanding why he kept making odd things happen without meaning to, believing the Dursleys’ story that he had got his scar in the car crash which had killed his parents. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then, exactly a year ago, Hogwarts had written to Harry, and the whole story had come out. Harry had taken up his place at wizard school, where he and his scar were famous … but now the school year was over, and he was back with the Dursleys for the summer, back to being treated like a dog that had rolled in something smelly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dursleys hadn’t even remembered that today happened to be Harry’s twelfth birthday. Of course, his hopes hadn’t been high; they’d never given him a proper present, let alone a cake – but to ignore it completely … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>10 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment, Uncle Vernon cleared his throat importantly and said, ‘Now, as we all know, today is a very important day.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up, hardly daring to believe it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This could well be the day I make the biggest deal of my career,’ said Uncle Vernon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went back to his toast. Of course, he thought bitterly, Uncle Vernon was talking about the stupid dinner party. He’d been talking of nothing else for a fortnight. Some rich builder and his wife were coming to dinner and Uncle Vernon was hoping to get a huge order from him (Uncle Vernon’s company made drills). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think we should run through the schedule one more time,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Uncle Vernon. ‘We should all be in position at eight o’clock. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Petunia, you will be –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In the lounge,’ said Aunt Petunia promptly, ‘waiting to welcome them graciously to our home.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good, good. And Dudley?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll be waiting to open the door.’ Dudley put on a foul, simper-ing smile. ‘May I take your coats, Mr and Mrs Mason?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’ll  <i class=\"calibre4\">love</i> him!’ cried Aunt Petunia rapturously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent, Dudley,’ said Uncle Vernon. Then he rounded on Harry. ‘And  <i class=\"calibre4\">you? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll be in my bedroom, making no noise and pretending I’m not there,’ said Harry tonelessly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Exactly,’ said Uncle Vernon nastily. ‘I will lead them into the lounge, introduce you, Petunia, and pour them drinks. At eight fifteen –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll announce dinner,’ said Aunt Petunia. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And Dudley, you’ll say –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘May I take you through to the dining room, Mrs Mason?’ said Dudley, offering his fat arm to an invisible woman. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My perfect little gentleman!’ sniffed Aunt Petunia. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And  <i class=\"calibre4\">you? </i>’ said Uncle Vernon viciously to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll be in my room, making no noise and pretending I’m not there,’ said Harry dully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Precisely. Now, we should aim to get in a few good compli-ments at dinner. Petunia, any ideas?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Vernon tells me you’re a  <i class=\"calibre4\">wonderful</i> golfer, Mr Mason …  <i class=\"calibre4\">Do</i> tell me where you bought your dress, Mrs Mason …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Perfect … Dudley?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How about: “We had to write an essay about our hero at </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Worst Birthday 11 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">school, Mr Mason, and  <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> wrote about  <i class=\"calibre4\">you. </i>” ’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This was too much for both Aunt Petunia and Harry. Aunt Petunia burst into tears and hugged her son, while Harry ducked under the table so they wouldn’t see him laughing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you, boy?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry fought to keep his face straight as he emerged. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll be in my room, making no noise and pretending I’m not there,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Too right you will,’ said Uncle Vernon forcefully. ‘The Masons don’t know anything about you and it’s going to stay that way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When dinner’s over, you take Mrs Mason back to the lounge for coffee, Petunia, and I’ll bring the subject round to drills. With any luck, I’ll have the deal signed and sealed before the  <i class=\"calibre4\">News at Ten. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We’ll be shopping for a holiday home in Majorca this time tomorrow.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t feel too excited about this. He didn’t think the Dursleys would like him any better in Majorca than they did in Privet Drive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right – I’m off into town to pick up the dinner jackets for Dudley and me. And  <i class=\"calibre4\">you, </i>’ he snarled at Harry, ‘you stay out of your aunt’s way while she’s cleaning.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry left through the back door. It was a brilliant, sunny day. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He crossed the lawn, slumped down on the garden bench and sang under his breath, ‘Happy birthday to me … happy birthday to me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No cards, no presents, and he would be spending the evening pretending not to exist. He gazed miserably into the hedge. He had never felt so lonely. More than anything else at Hogwarts, more even than playing Quidditch, Harry missed his best friends, Ron Weasley and Hermione Granger. They, however, didn’t seem to be missing him at all. Neither of them had written to him all summer, even though Ron had said he was going to ask Harry to come and stay. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Countless times, Harry had been on the point of unlocking Hedwig’s cage by magic and sending her to Ron and Hermione with a letter, but it wasn’t worth the risk. Underage wizards weren’t allowed to use magic outside school. Harry hadn’t told the Dursleys this; he knew it was only their terror that he might turn them all into dung beetles that stopped them locking  <i class=\"calibre4\">him</i> in the cupboard under the stairs with his wand and broomstick. For the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>12 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">first couple of weeks back, Harry had enjoyed muttering nonsense words under his breath and watching Dudley tearing out of the room as fast as his fat legs would carry him. But the long silence from Ron and Hermione had made Harry feel so cut off from the magical world that even taunting Dudley had lost its appeal – and now Ron and Hermione had forgotten his birthday. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What wouldn’t he give now for a message from Hogwarts? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">From any witch or wizard? He’d almost be glad of a sight of his arch-enemy, Draco Malfoy, just to be sure it hadn’t all been a dream … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Not that his whole year at Hogwarts had been fun. At the very end of last term, Harry had come face to face with none other than Lord Voldemort himself. Voldemort might be a ruin of his former self, but he was still terrifying, still cunning, still determined to regain power. Harry had slipped through Voldemort’s clutches for a second time, but it had been a narrow escape, and even now, weeks later, Harry kept waking in the night, drenched in cold sweat, wondering where Voldemort was now, remembering his livid face, his wide, mad eyes … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry suddenly sat bolt upright on the garden bench. He had been staring absent-mindedly into the hedge –  <i class=\"calibre4\">and the hedge was</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">staring back. </i> Two enormous green eyes had appeared among the leaves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jumped to his feet just as a jeering voice floated across the lawn. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know what day it is,’ sang Dudley, waddling towards him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The huge eyes blinked and vanished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry, not taking his eyes off the spot where they had been. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know what day it is,’ Dudley repeated, coming right up to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well done,’ said Harry. ‘So you’ve finally learned the days of the week.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Today’s your  <i class=\"calibre4\">birthday, </i>’ sneered Dudley. ‘How come you haven’t got any cards? Haven’t you even got friends at that freak place?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Better not let your mum hear you talking about my school,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Harry coolly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley hitched up his trousers, which were slipping down his fat bottom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why’re you staring at the hedge?’ he said suspiciously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Worst Birthday 13 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m trying to decide what would be the best spell to set it on fire,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley stumbled backwards at once, a look of panic on his fat face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You c-can’t – Dad told you you’re not to do m-magic – he said he’ll chuck you out of the house – and you haven’t got anywhere else to go – you haven’t got any  <i class=\"calibre4\">friends</i> to take you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Jiggery pokery! </i>’ said Harry in a fierce voice. ‘Hocus pocus … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">squiggly wiggly …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘MUUUUUUM!’ howled Dudley, tripping over his feet as he dashed back towards the house. ‘MUUUUM! He’s doing you know what!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry paid dearly for his moment of fun. As neither Dudley nor the hedge was in any way hurt, Aunt Petunia knew he hadn’t really done magic, but he still had to duck as she aimed a heavy blow at his head with the soapy frying pan. Then she gave him work to do, with the promise he wouldn’t eat again until he’d finished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">While Dudley lolled around watching and eating ice-creams, Harry cleaned the windows, washed the car, mowed the lawn, trimmed the flowerbeds, pruned and watered the roses and re-painted the garden bench. The sun blazed overhead, burning the back of his neck. Harry knew he shouldn’t have risen to Dudley’s bait, but Dudley had said the very thing Harry had been thinking himself … maybe he  <i class=\"calibre4\">didn’t</i> have any friends at Hogwarts … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wish they could see famous Harry Potter now,’ he thought sav-agely, as he spread manure on the flowerbeds, his back aching, sweat running down his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was half past seven in the evening when at last, exhausted, he heard Aunt Petunia calling him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get in here! And walk on the newspaper!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry moved gladly into the shade of the gleaming kitchen. On top of the fridge stood tonight’s pudding: a huge mound of whipped cream and sugared violets. A joint of roast pork was sizzling in the oven. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eat quickly! The Masons will be here soon!’ snapped Aunt Petunia, pointing to two slices of bread and a lump of cheese on the kitchen table. She was already wearing a salmon-pink cocktail dress. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry washed his hands and bolted down his pitiful supper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The moment he had finished, Aunt Petunia whisked away his </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>14 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">plate. ‘Upstairs! Hurry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As he passed the door to the living room, Harry caught a glimpse of Uncle Vernon and Dudley in bow-ties and dinner jackets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had only just reached the upstairs landing when the doorbell rang and Uncle Vernon’s furious face appeared at the foot of the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Remember, boy – one sound …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry crossed to his bedroom on tiptoe, slipped inside, closed the door and turned to collapse on his bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The trouble was, there was already someone sitting on it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TWO — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dobby’s Warning</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry managed not to shout out, but it was a close thing. The little creature on the bed had large, bat-like ears and bulging green eyes the size of tennis balls. Harry knew instantly that this was what had been watching him out of the garden hedge that morning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As they stared at each other, Harry heard Dudley’s voice from the hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘May I take your coats, Mr and Mrs Mason?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The creature slipped off the bed and bowed so low that the end of its long thin nose touched the carpet. Harry noticed that it was wearing what looked like an old pillowcase, with rips for arm and leg holes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – hello,’ said Harry nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter!’ said the creature, in a high-pitched voice Harry was sure would carry down the stairs. ‘So long has Dobby wanted to meet you, sir … Such an honour it is …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Th-thank you,’ said Harry, edging along the wall and sinking into his desk chair, next to Hedwig, who was asleep in her large cage. He wanted to ask, ‘What are you?’ but thought it would sound too rude, so instead he said, ‘Who are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby, sir. Just Dobby. Dobby the house-elf,’ said the creature. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – really?’ said Harry. ‘Er – I don’t want to be rude or anything, but – this isn’t a great time for me to have a house-elf in my bedroom.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia’s high, false laugh sounded from the living room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The elf hung his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not that I’m not pleased to meet you,’ said Harry quickly, ‘but, er, is there any particular reason you’re here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yes, sir,’ said Dobby earnestly. ‘Dobby has come to tell you, sir … it is difficult, sir … Dobby wonders where to begin …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>16 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit down,’ said Harry politely, pointing at the bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To his horror, the elf burst into tears – very noisy tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">S-sit down! </i>’ he wailed. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Never … never ever </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry thought he heard the voices downstairs falter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m  sorry,’  he  whispered,  ‘I  didn’t  mean  to  offend  you  or  anything.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Offend Dobby!’ choked the elf. ‘Dobby has  <i class=\"calibre4\">never </i> been asked to sit down by a wizard – like an  <i class=\"calibre4\">equal</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, trying to say ‘Shh!’ and look comforting at the same time, ushered Dobby back onto the bed where he sat hiccoughing, looking like a large and very ugly doll. At last he managed to control himself, and sat with his great eyes fixed on Harry in an expression of watery adoration. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can’t have met many decent wizards,’ said Harry, trying to cheer him up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby shook his head. Then, without warning, he leapt up and started banging his head furiously on the window, shouting, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Bad</i> Dobby!  <i class=\"calibre4\">Bad</i> Dobby!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t – what are you doing?’ Harry hissed, springing up and pulling Dobby back onto the bed. Hedwig had woken up with a particularly loud screech and was beating her wings wildly against the bars of her cage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby had to punish himself, sir,’ said the elf, who had gone slightly cross-eyed. ‘Dobby almost spoke ill of his family, sir …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your family?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The wizard family Dobby serves, sir … Dobby is a house-elf – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bound to serve one house and one family for ever …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do they know you’re here?’ asked Harry curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby shuddered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh no, sir, no … Dobby will have to punish himself most grievously for coming to see you, sir. Dobby will have to shut his ears in the oven door for this. If they ever knew, sir –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But won’t they notice if you shut your ears in the oven door?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby doubts it, sir. Dobby is always having to punish himself for something, sir. They lets Dobby get on with it, sir. Sometimes they reminds me to do extra punishments …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But why don’t you leave? Escape?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A house-elf must be set free, sir. And the family will never set Dobby free … Dobby will serve the family until he dies, sir …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Warning 17 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And I thought I was hard-done-by staying here for another four weeks,’ he said. ‘This makes the Dursleys sound almost human. Can’t anyone help you? Can’t I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Almost at once, Harry wished he hadn’t spoken. Dobby dissolved again into wails of gratitude. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please,’ Harry whispered frantically, ‘please be quiet. If the Dursleys hear anything, if they know you’re here …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter asks if he can help Dobby … Dobby has heard of your greatness, sir, but of your goodness, Dobby never knew …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who was feeling distinctly hot in the face, said, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Whatever you’ve heard about my greatness is a load of rubbish. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I’m not even top of my year at Hogwarts, that’s Hermione, she –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he stopped quickly, because thinking about Hermione was painful. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter is humble and modest,’ said Dobby reverently, his orb-like eyes aglow. ‘Harry Potter speaks not of his triumph over He Who Must Not Be Named.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Voldemort?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby clapped his hands over his bat ears and moaned, ‘Ah, speak not the name, sir! Speak not the name!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry,’ said Harry quickly. ‘I know lots of people don’t like it – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">my friend Ron …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stopped again. Thinking about Ron was painful, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby leaned towards Harry, his eyes wide as headlamps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby heard tell,’ he said hoarsely, ‘that Harry Potter met the Dark Lord for a second time, just weeks ago … that Harry Potter escaped  <i class=\"calibre4\">yet again. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry nodded and Dobby’s eyes suddenly shone with tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, sir,’ he gasped, dabbing his face with a corner of the grubby pillowcase he was wearing. ‘Harry Potter is valiant and bold! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He has braved so many dangers already! But Dobby has come to protect Harry Potter, to warn him, even if he  <i class=\"calibre4\">does</i> have to shut his ears in the oven door later …  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry Potter must not go back to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hogwarts. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a silence broken only by the chink of knives and forks from downstairs and the distant rumble of Uncle Vernon’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘W-what?’ Harry stammered. ‘But I’ve got to go back – term starts on September the first. It’s all that’s keeping me going. You don’t know what it’s like here. I don’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">belong</i> here. I belong in your </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>18 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">world – at Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, no, no,’ squeaked Dobby, shaking his head so hard his ears flapped. ‘Harry Potter must stay where he is safe. He is too great, too good, to lose. If Harry Potter goes back to Hogwarts, he will be in mortal danger.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why?’ said Harry in surprise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There is a plot, Harry Potter. A plot to make most terrible things happen at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry this year,’ whispered Dobby, suddenly trembling all over. ‘Dobby has known it for months, sir. Harry Potter must not put himself in peril. He is too important, sir!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What terrible things?’ said Harry at once. ‘Who’s plotting them?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby made a funny choking noise and then banged his head madly against the wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right!’ cried Harry, grabbing the elf’s arm to stop him. ‘You can’t say, I understand. But why are you warning  <i class=\"calibre4\">me? </i>’ A sudden, unpleasant thought struck him. ‘Hang on – this hasn’t got anything to do with Vol– sorry – with You Know Who, has it? You could just shake or nod,’ he added hastily, as Dobby’s head tilted worryingly close to the wall again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slowly, Dobby shook his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not – not  <i class=\"calibre4\">He Who Must Not Be Named, </i> sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Dobby’s eyes were wide and he seemed to be trying to give Harry a hint. Harry, however, was completely at sea. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He hasn’t got a brother, has he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby shook his head, his eyes wider than ever. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well then, I can’t think who else would have a chance of making horrible things happen at Hogwarts,’ said Harry. ‘I mean, there’s Dumbledore, for one thing – you know who Dumbledore is, don’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby bowed his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Albus Dumbledore is the greatest Headmaster Hogwarts has ever had. Dobby knows it, sir. Dobby has heard Dumbledore’s powers rival those of He Who Must Not Be Named at the height of his strength. But sir,’ Dobby’s voice dropped to an urgent whisper, ‘there are powers Dumbledore doesn’t … powers no decent wizard …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And before Harry could stop him, Dobby bounded off the bed, seized Harry’s desk lamp and started beating himself around the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Warning 19 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">head with ear-splitting yelps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A sudden silence fell downstairs. Two seconds later Harry, heart thudding madly, heard Uncle Vernon coming into the hall, calling, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dudley must have left his television on again, the little tyke!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quick! In the wardrobe!’ hissed Harry, stuffing Dobby in, shut-ting the door and flinging himself onto the bed just as the door handle turned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What – the –  <i class=\"calibre4\">devil</i> – are – you – doing?’ said Uncle Vernon through gritted teeth, his face horribly close to Harry’s. ‘You’ve just ruined the punchline of my Japanese-golfer joke … one more sound and you’ll wish you’d never been born, boy!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stomped flat-footed from the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Shaking, Harry let Dobby out of the wardrobe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See what it’s like here?’ he said. ‘See why I’ve got to go back to Hogwarts? It’s the only place I’ve got – well, I  <i class=\"calibre4\">think</i> I’ve got friends.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Friends who don’t even  <i class=\"calibre4\">write</i> to Harry Potter?’ said Dobby slyly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I expect they’ve just been – hang on,’ said Harry, frowning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How do  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> know my friends haven’t been writing to me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby shuffled his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter mustn’t be angry with Dobby – Dobby did it for the best …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Have you been stopping my letters? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby has them here, sir,’ said the elf. Stepping nimbly out of Harry’s reach, he pulled a thick wad of envelopes from the inside of the pillowcase he was wearing. Harry could make out Hermione’s neat writing, Ron’s untidy scrawl and even a scribble that looked as though it was from the Hogwarts gamekeeper, Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby blinked anxiously up at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter mustn’t be angry … Dobby hoped … if Harry Potter thought his friends had forgotten him … Harry Potter might not want to go back to school, sir …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wasn’t listening. He made a grab for the letters, but Dobby jumped out of reach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter will have them, sir, if he gives Dobby his word that he will not return to Hogwarts. Ah, sir, this is a danger you must not face! Say you won’t go back, sir!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry angrily. ‘Give me my friends’ letters!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>20 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then Harry Potter leaves Dobby no choice,’ said the elf sadly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before Harry could move, Dobby had darted to the bedroom door, pulled it open – and sprinted down the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mouth dry, stomach lurching, Harry sprang after him, trying not to make a sound. He jumped the last six stairs, landing cat-like on the hall carpet, looking around for Dobby. From the dining room he heard Uncle Vernon saying, ‘… tell Petunia that very funny story about those American plumbers, Mr Mason, she’s been dying to hear …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ran up the hall into the kitchen and felt his stomach disappear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia’s masterpiece of a pudding, the mountain of cream and sugared violets, was floating up near the ceiling. On top of a cupboard in the corner crouched Dobby. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ croaked Harry. ‘Please … they’ll kill me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter must say he’s not going back to school –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby … please …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Say it, sir …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby gave him a tragic look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then Dobby must do it, sir, for Harry Potter’s own good.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The pudding fell to the floor with a heart-stopping crash. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cream splattered the windows and walls as the dish shattered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a crack like a whip, Dobby vanished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There were screams from the dining room and Uncle Vernon burst into the kitchen to find Harry, rigid with shock, covered from head to foot in Aunt Petunia’s pudding. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At  first,  it  looked  as  though  Uncle  Vernon  would  manage  to gloss the whole thing over (‘Just our nephew – very disturbed – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">meeting strangers upsets him, so we kept him upstairs …’) He shooed the shocked Masons back into the dining room, promised Harry he would flay him to within an inch of his life when the Masons had left, and handed him a mop. Aunt Petunia dug some ice-cream out of the freezer and Harry, still shaking, started scrubbing the kitchen clean. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon might still have been able to make his deal – if it hadn’t been for the owl. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia was just handing round a box of after-dinner mints when a huge barn owl swooped through the dining room window, dropped a letter on Mrs Mason’s head and swooped out </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Warning 21 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">again. Mrs Mason screamed like a banshee and ran from the house, shouting about lunatics. Mr Mason stayed just long enough to tell the Dursleys that his wife was mortally afraid of birds of all shapes and sizes, and to ask whether this was their idea of a joke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood in the kitchen, clutching the mop for support as Uncle Vernon advanced on him, a demonic glint in his tiny eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Read it!’ he hissed evilly, brandishing the letter the owl had delivered. ‘Go on – read it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took it. It did not contain birthday greetings. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Mr Potter, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">We have received intelligence that a Hover Charm was used at</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">your place of residence this evening at twelve minutes past nine. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">As you know, underage wizards are not permitted to perform</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">spells outside school, and further spellwork on your part may</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">lead to expulsion from said school (Decree for the Reasonable</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Restriction of Underage sorcery, 1875, Paragraph C). </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">We would also ask you to remember that any magical activity</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">which risks notice by members of the non-magical community</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">(Muggles) is a serious offence, under section 13 of the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">International Confederation of Warlocks’ Statute of Secrecy. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Enjoy your holidays! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Yours sincerely, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Mafalda Hopkirk</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Improper Use of Magic Office</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Ministry of Magic</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up from the letter and gulped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You didn’t tell us you weren’t allowed to use magic outside school,’ said Uncle Vernon, a mad gleam dancing in his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Forgot to mention it … slipped your mind, I dare say …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was bearing down on Harry like a great bulldog, all his teeth bared. ‘Well, I’ve got news for you, boy … I’m locking you up … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you’re never going back to that school … never … and if you try and magic yourself out – they’ll expel you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And laughing like a maniac, he dragged Harry back upstairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon was as bad as his word. The following morning, he paid a man to fit bars on Harry’s window. He himself fitted the cat-flap in the bedroom door, so that small amounts of food could be pushed inside three times a day. They let Harry out to use the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>22 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bathroom morning and evening. Otherwise, he was locked in his room around the clock. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Three days later, the Dursleys were showing no sign of relenting and Harry couldn’t see any way out of his situation. He lay on his bed watching the sun sinking behind the bars on the window and wondered miserably what was going to happen to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What was the good of magicking himself out of his room if Hogwarts would expel him for doing it? Yet life at Privet Drive had reached an all-time low. Now the Dursleys knew they weren’t going to wake up as fruitbats, he had lost his only weapon. Dobby might have saved Harry from horrible happenings at Hogwarts, but the way things were going, he’d probably starve to death anyway. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The cat-flap rattled and Aunt Petunia’s hand appeared, pushing a bowl of tinned soup into the room. Harry, whose insides were aching with hunger, jumped off his bed and seized it. The soup was stone cold, but he drank half of it in one gulp. Then he crossed the room to Hedwig’s cage and tipped the soggy vegetables at the bottom of the bowl into her empty food tray. She ruffled her feathers and gave him a look of deep disgust. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s no good turning your beak up at it, that’s all we’ve got,’ said Harry grimly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He put the empty bowl back on the floor next to the cat-flap and lay back down on the bed, somehow even hungrier than he had been before the soup. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Supposing he was still alive in another four weeks, what would happen if he didn’t turn up at Hogwarts? Would someone be sent to see why he hadn’t come back? Would they be able to make the Dursleys let him go? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The room was growing dark. Exhausted, stomach rumbling, mind spinning over the same unanswerable questions, Harry fell into an uneasy sleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He dreamed that he was on show in a zoo, with a card reading </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Underage Wizard’ attached to his cage. People goggled through the bars at him as he lay, starving and weak, on a bed of straw. He saw Dobby’s face in the crowd and shouted out, asking for help, but Dobby called, ‘Harry Potter is safe there, sir!’ and vanished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then the Dursleys appeared and Dudley rattled the bars of the cage, laughing at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Warning 23 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop it,’ Harry muttered, as the rattling pounded in his sore head. ‘Leave me alone … cut it out … I’m trying to sleep …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He opened his eyes. Moonlight was shining through the bars on the window. And someone  <i class=\"calibre4\">was</i> goggling through the bars at him: a freckle-faced, red-haired, long-nosed someone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron Weasley was outside Harry’s window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER THREE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Burrow</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ron! </i>’ breathed Harry, creeping to the window and pushing it up so they could talk through the bars. ‘Ron, how did you – what the –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s mouth fell open as the full impact of what he was seeing hit him. Ron was leaning out of the back window of an old turquoise car, which was parked  <i class=\"calibre4\">in mid-air. </i> Grinning at Harry from the front seats were Fred and George, Ron’s elder twin brothers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s been going on?’ said Ron. ‘Why haven’t you been answering my letters? I’ve asked you to stay about twelve times, and then Dad came home and said you’d got an official warning for using magic in front of Muggles …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It wasn’t me – and how did he know?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He works for the Ministry,’ said Ron. ‘You  <i class=\"calibre4\">know</i> we’re not supposed to do spells outside school –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bit rich coming from you,’ said Harry, staring at the floating car. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, this doesn’t count,’ said Ron. ‘We’re only borrowing this, it’s Dad’s,  <i class=\"calibre4\">we</i> didn’t enchant it. But doing magic in front of those Muggles you live with …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I told you, I didn’t – but it’ll take too long to explain now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Look, can you explain to them at Hogwarts that the Dursleys have locked me up and won’t let me come back, and obviously I can’t magic myself out, because the Ministry’ll think that’s the second spell I’ve done in three days, so –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop  gibbering,’  said  Ron,  ‘we’ve  come  to  take  you  home  with us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you can’t magic me out either –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We don’t need to,’ said Ron, jerking his head towards the front seats and grinning. ‘You forget who I’ve got with me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Burrow 25 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tie that round the bars,’ said Fred, throwing the end of a rope to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If the Dursleys wake up, I’m dead,’ said Harry, as he tied the rope tightly around a bar and Fred revved up the car. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t worry,’ said Fred, ‘and stand back.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry moved back into the shadows next to Hedwig, who seemed to have realised how important this was and kept still and silent. The car revved louder and louder and suddenly, with a crunching noise, the bars were pulled clean out of the window as Fred drove straight up in the air – Harry ran back to the window to see the bars dangling a few feet above the ground. Panting, Ron hoisted them up into the car. Harry listened anxiously, but there was no sound from the Dursleys’ bedroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When the bars were safely in the back seat with Ron, Fred reversed as close as possible to Harry’s window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get in,’ Ron said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But all my Hogwarts stuff … my wand … my broomstick …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Locked in the cupboard under the stairs, and I can’t get out of this room –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No problem,’ said George from the front passenger seat. ‘Out of the way, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred and George climbed carefully through the window into Harry’s room. You had to hand it to them, thought Harry, as George took an ordinary hairpin from his pocket and started to pick the lock. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A lot of wizards think it’s a waste of time, knowing this sort of Muggle trick,’ said Fred, ‘but we feel they’re skills worth learning, even if they are a bit slow.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a small click and the door swung open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So – we’ll get your trunk – you grab anything you need from your room and hand it out to Ron,’ whispered George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Watch out for the bottom stair, it creaks,’ Harry whispered back, as the twins disappeared onto the dark landing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dashed around his room, collecting his things together and passing them out of the window to Ron. Then he went to help Fred and George heave his trunk up the stairs. Harry heard Uncle Vernon cough. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last, panting, they reached the landing, then carried the trunk through Harry’s room to the open window. Fred climbed </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>26 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">back into the car to pull with Ron, and Harry and George pushed from the bedroom side. Inch by inch, the trunk slid through the window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon coughed again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A bit more,’ panted Fred, who was pulling from inside the car, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘one good push …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and George threw their shoulders against the trunk and it slid out of the window into the back seat of the car. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK, let’s go,’ George whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But as Harry climbed onto the window-sill there came a sudden loud screech from behind him, followed immediately by the thunder of Uncle Vernon’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘THAT RUDDY OWL!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve forgotten Hedwig!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tore back across the room as the landing light clicked on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He snatched up Hedwig’s cage, dashed to the window and passed it out to Ron. He was scrambling back onto the chest of drawers when Uncle Vernon hammered on the unlocked door – and it crashed open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a split second, Uncle Vernon stood framed in the doorway; then he let out a bellow like an angry bull and dived at Harry, grabbing him by the ankle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron, Fred and George seized Harry’s arms and pulled as hard as they could. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Petunia!’ roared Uncle Vernon. ‘He’s getting away! HE’S </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">GETTING AWAY!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Weasleys gave a gigantic tug and Harry’s leg slid out of Uncle Vernon’s grasp. As soon as Harry was in the car and had slammed the door shut, Ron yelled, ‘Put your foot down, Fred!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and the car shot suddenly towards the moon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t believe it – he was free. He wound down the window, the night air whipping his hair, and looked back at the shrinking rooftops of Privet Drive. Uncle Vernon, Aunt Petunia and Dudley were all hanging, dumbstruck, out of Harry’s window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you next summer!’ Harry yelled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Weasleys roared with laughter and Harry settled back in his seat, grinning from ear to ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let Hedwig out,’ he told Ron, ‘she can fly behind us. She hasn’t had a chance to stretch her wings for ages.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">George handed the hairpin to Ron and a moment later, Hedwig </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Burrow 27 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">had soared joyfully out of the window to glide alongside them like a ghost. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So – what’s the story, Harry?’ said Ron impatiently. ‘What’s been happening?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry told them all about Dobby, the warning he’d given Harry and the fiasco of the violet pudding. There was a long shocked silence when he had finished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very fishy,’ said Fred finally. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Definitely dodgy,’ agreed George. ‘So he wouldn’t even tell you who’s supposed to be plotting all this stuff?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t think he could,’ said Harry. ‘I told you, every time he got close to letting something slip, he started banging his head against the wall.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He saw Fred and George look at each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What, you think he was lying to me?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Fred, ‘put it this way – house-elves have got powerful magic of their own, but they can’t usually use it without their masters’ permission. I reckon old Dobby was sent to stop you coming back to Hogwarts. Someone’s idea of a joke. Can you think of anyone at school with a grudge against you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry and Ron together, instantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Draco Malfoy,’ Harry explained. ‘He hates me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Draco Malfoy?’ said George, turning round. ‘Not Lucius Malfoy’s son?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Must be, it’s not a very common name, is it?’ said Harry. ‘Why?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve heard Dad talking about him,’ said George. ‘He was a big supporter of You Know Who.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And when You Know Who disappeared,’ said Fred, craning around to look at Harry, ‘Lucius Malfoy came back saying he’d never meant any of it. Load of dung – Dad reckons he was right in You Know Who’s inner circle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had heard these rumours about Malfoy’s family before, and they didn’t surprise him at all. Draco Malfoy made Dudley Dursley look like a kind, thoughtful and sensitive boy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know whether the Malfoys own a house-elf …’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, whoever owns him will be an old wizarding family, and they’ll be rich,’ said Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, Mum’s always wishing we had a house-elf to do the iron-ing,’ said George. ‘But all we’ve got is a lousy old ghoul in the attic </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>28 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and gnomes all over the garden. House-elves come with big old manors and castles and places like that, you wouldn’t catch one in our house …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was silent. Judging by the fact that Draco Malfoy usually had the best of everything, his family was rolling in wizard gold; he could just see Malfoy strutting around a large manor house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sending the family servant to stop Harry going back to Hogwarts also sounded exactly like the sort of thing Malfoy would do. Had Harry been stupid to take Dobby seriously? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m glad we came to get you, anyway,’ said Ron. ‘I was getting really worried when you didn’t answer any of my letters. I thought it was Errol’s fault at first –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s Errol?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Our owl. He’s ancient. It wouldn’t be the first time he’d collapsed on a delivery. So then I tried to borrow Hermes –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Who? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The owl Mum and Dad bought Percy when he was made a prefect,’ said Fred from the front. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Percy wouldn’t lend him to me,’ said Ron. ‘Said he needed him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Percy’s been acting very oddly this summer,’ said George, frowning. ‘And he  <i class=\"calibre4\">has</i> been sending a lot of letters and spending a load of time shut up in his room … I mean, there’s only so many times you can polish a prefect badge … You’re driving too far west, Fred,’ he added, pointing at a compass on the dashboard. Fred twiddled the steering wheel. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So, does your dad know you’ve got the car?’ said Harry, guess-ing the answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er, no,’ said Ron, ‘he had to work tonight. Hopefully we’ll be able to get it back in the garage without Mum noticing we flew it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What does your dad do at the Ministry of Magic, anyway?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He works in the most boring department,’ said Ron. ‘The Misuse of Muggle Artefacts Office.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The  <i class=\"calibre4\">what? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s all to do with bewitching things that are Muggle-made, you know, in case they end up back in a Muggle shop or house. Like, last year, some old witch died and her tea set was sold to an antiques shop. This Muggle woman bought it, took it home and tried to serve her friends tea in it. It was a nightmare – Dad was working overtime for weeks.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Burrow 29 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What happened?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The teapot went berserk and squirted boiling tea all over the place and one man ended up in hospital with the sugar tongs clamped to his nose. Dad was going frantic, it’s only him and an old warlock called Perkins in the office, and they had to do Memory Charms and all sorts to cover it up …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But your dad … this car …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred laughed. ‘Yeah, Dad’s mad about everything to do with Muggles, our shed’s full of Muggle stuff. He takes it apart, puts spells on it and puts it back together again. If he raided our house he’d have to put himself straight under arrest. It drives Mum mad.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s the main road,’ said George, peering down through the windscreen. ‘We’ll be there in ten minutes … just as well, it’s getting light …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A faint pinkish glow was visible along the horizon to the east. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred brought the car lower and Harry saw a dark patchwork of fields and clumps of trees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re a little way outside the village,’ said George. ‘Ottery St Catchpole …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lower and lower went the flying car. The edge of a brilliant red sun was now gleaming through the trees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Touchdown!’ said Fred as, with a slight bump, they hit the ground. They had landed next to a tumbledown garage in a small yard and Harry looked out for the first time at Ron’s house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It looked as though it had once been a large stone pigsty, but extra rooms had been added here and there until it was several storeys high and so crooked it looked as though it was held up by magic (which, Harry reminded himself, it probably was). Four or five chimneys were perched on top of the red roof. A lop-sided sign stuck in the ground near the entrance read ‘The Burrow’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Round the front door lay a jumble of wellington boots and a very rusty cauldron. Several fat brown chickens were pecking their way around the yard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not much,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">brilliant, </i>’ said Harry happily, thinking of Privet Drive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They got out of the car. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, we’ll go upstairs really quietly,’ said Fred, ‘and wait for Mum to call us for breakfast. Then Ron, you come bounding downstairs going, ‘Mum, look who turned up in the night!’ and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>30 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">she’ll be all pleased to see Harry and no one need ever know we flew the car.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Ron. ‘Come on, Harry, I sleep at the –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had gone a nasty greenish colour, his eyes fixed on the house. The other three wheeled around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley was marching across the yard, scattering chickens, and for a short, plump, kind-faced woman, it was remarkable how much she looked like a sabre-toothed tiger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ah</i>,’ said Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh dear,’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley came to a halt in front of them, her hands on her hips, staring from one guilty face to the next. She was wearing a flowered apron with a wand sticking out of the pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">So</i>,’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Morning, Mum,’ said George, in what he clearly thought was a jaunty, winning voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you any idea how worried I’ve been?’ said Mrs Weasley in a deadly whisper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry, Mum, but see, we had to –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All three of Mrs Weasley’s sons were taller than she was, but they cowered as her rage broke over them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Beds empty! No note! Car gone … could have crashed … out of my</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">mind with worry … did you care? … never, as long as I’ve lived … you</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">wait until your father gets home, we never had trouble like this from</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Bill or Charlie or Percy </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Perfect Percy,’ muttered Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘YOU COULD DO WITH TAKING A LEAF OUT OF PERCY’S </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">BOOK!’ yelled Mrs Weasley, prodding a finger in Fred’s chest. ‘You could have  <i class=\"calibre4\">died, </i> you could have been  <i class=\"calibre4\">seen, </i> you could have lost your father his  <i class=\"calibre4\">job</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It seemed to go on for hours. Mrs Weasley had shouted herself hoarse before she turned on Harry, who backed away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m very pleased to see you, Harry, dear,’ she said, ‘Come in and have some breakfast.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She turned and walked back into the house and Harry, after a nervous glance at Ron, who nodded encouragingly, followed her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The kitchen was small and rather cramped. There was a scrubbed wooden table and chairs in the middle and Harry sat down on the edge of his seat, looking around. He had never been in a wizard house before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Burrow 31 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The clock on the wall opposite him had only one hand and no numbers at all. Written around the edge were things like ‘Time to make tea’, ‘Time to feed the chickens’ and ‘You’re late’. Books were stacked three deep on the mantelpiece, books with titles like <i class=\"calibre4\">Charm Your Own Cheese, Enchantment in Baking</i> and  <i class=\"calibre4\">One Minute</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Feasts – It’s Magic! </i> And unless Harry’s ears were deceiving him, the old radio next to the sink had just announced that coming up was ‘Witching Hour, with the popular singing sorceress, Celestina Warbeck’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley was clattering around, cooking breakfast a little haphazardly, throwing dirty looks at her sons as she threw sausages into the frying pan. Every now and then she muttered things like ‘don’t know  <i class=\"calibre4\">what</i> you were thinking of’ and ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">never</i> would have believed it’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t blame  <i class=\"calibre4\">you, </i> dear,’ she assured Harry, tipping eight or nine sausages onto his plate. ‘Arthur and I have been worried about you, too. Just last night we were saying we’d come and get you ourselves if you hadn’t written back to Ron by Friday. But really’ (she was now adding three fried eggs to his plate), ‘flying an illegal car halfway across the country – anyone could have seen you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She flicked her wand casually at the washing-up in the sink, which began to clean itself, clinking gently in the background. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was  <i class=\"calibre4\">cloudy, </i> Mum!’ said Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You keep your mouth closed while you’re eating!’ Mrs Weasley snapped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They were starving him, Mum!’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you!’ said Mrs Weasley, but it was with a slightly softened expression that she started cutting Harry bread and buttering it for him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment, there was a diversion in the form of a small, red-headed figure in a long nightdress, who appeared in the kitchen, gave a small squeal, and ran out again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ginny,’ said Ron in an undertone to Harry. ‘My sister. She’s been talking about you all summer.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, she’ll be wanting your autograph, Harry,’ grinned Fred, but he caught his mother’s eye and bent his face over his plate without another word. Nothing more was said until all four plates were clean, which took a surprisingly short time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Blimey, I’m tired,’ yawned Fred, setting down his knife and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>32 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">fork at last. ‘I think I’ll go to bed and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You will not,’ snapped Mrs Weasley. ‘It’s your own fault you’ve been up all night. You’re going to de-gnome the garden for me, they’re getting completely out of hand again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Mum –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you two,’ she said, glaring at Ron and George. ‘You can go up to bed, dear,’ she added to Harry. ‘You didn’t ask them to fly that wretched car.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry, who felt wide awake, said quickly, ‘I’ll help Ron, I’ve never seen a de-gnoming –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s  very  sweet  of  you,  dear,  but  it’s  dull  work,’  said  Mrs Weasley. ‘Now, let’s see what Lockhart’s got to say on the subject.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And she pulled a heavy book from the stack on the mantelpiece. George groaned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mum, we know how to de-gnome a garden.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked at the cover of Mrs Weasley’s book. Written across it in fancy gold letters were the words:  <i class=\"calibre4\">Gilderoy Lockhart’s</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Guide to Household Pests. </i> There was a big photograph on the front of a very good-looking wizard with wavy blond hair and bright blue eyes. As always in the wizarding world, the photograph was moving; the wizard, who Harry supposed was Gilderoy Lockhart, kept winking cheekily up at them all. Mrs Weasley beamed down at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, he is marvellous,’ she said, ‘he knows his household pests, all right, it’s a wonderful book …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mum fancies him,’ said Fred, in a very audible whisper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be so ridiculous, Fred,’ said Mrs Weasley, her cheeks rather pink. ‘All right, if you think you know better than Lockhart, you can go and get on with it, and woe betide you if there’s a single gnome in that garden when I come out to inspect it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Yawning and grumbling, the Weasleys slouched outside with Harry behind them. The garden was large and, in Harry’s eyes, exactly what a garden should be. The Dursleys wouldn’t have liked it – there were plenty of weeds, and the grass needed cutting </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– but there were gnarled trees all around the walls, plants Harry had never seen spilling from every flowerbed and a big green pond full of frogs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Muggles have garden gnomes, too, you know,’ Harry told Ron as they crossed the lawn. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Burrow 33 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I’ve seen those things they think are gnomes,’ said Ron, bent double with his head in a peony bush. ‘Like fat little Father Christmases with fishing rods …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a violent scuffling noise, the peony bush shuddered and Ron straightened up. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">This</i> is a gnome,’ he said grimly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gerroff me! Gerroff me!’ squealed the gnome. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was certainly nothing like Father Christmas. It was small and leathery-looking, with a large, knobbly, bald head exactly like a potato. Ron held it at arm’s length as it kicked out at him with its horny little feet; he grasped it around the ankles and turned it upside-down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is what you have to do,’ he said. He raised the gnome above his head (‘Gerroff me!’) and started to swing it in great circles like a lasso. Seeing the shocked look on Harry’s face, Ron added, ‘It doesn’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">hurt</i> them – you’ve just got to make them really dizzy so they can’t find their way back to the gnomeholes.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He let go of the gnome’s ankles: it flew twenty feet into the air and landed with a thud in the field over the hedge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pitiful,’ said Fred. ‘I bet I can get mine beyond that stump.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry learned quickly not to feel too sorry for the gnomes. He decided just to drop the first one he caught over the hedge, but the gnome, sensing weakness, sank its razor-sharp teeth into Harry’s finger and he had a hard job shaking it off until – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wow, Harry – that must’ve been fifty feet …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The air was soon thick with flying gnomes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See, they’re not too bright,’ said George, seizing five or six gnomes at once. ‘The moment they know the de-gnoming’s going on they storm up to have a look. You’d think they’d have learned by now just to stay put.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Soon, the crowd of gnomes in the field started walking away in a straggling line, their little shoulders hunched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’ll be back,’ said Ron, as they watched the gnomes disappear into the hedge on the other side of the field. ‘They love it here … Dad’s too soft with them, he thinks they’re funny …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Just then, the front door slammed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s back!’ said George. ‘Dad’s home!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They hurried through the garden and back into the house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley was slumped in a kitchen chair with his glasses off and his eyes closed. He was a thin man, going bald, but the little hair he had was as red as any of his children’s. He was wearing </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>34 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">long green robes which were dusty and travel-worn. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What a night,’ he mumbled, groping for the teapot as they all sat down around him. ‘Nine raids. Nine! And old Mundungus Fletcher tried to put a hex on me when I had my back turned …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley took a long gulp of tea and sighed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Find anything, Dad?’ said Fred eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All I got were a few shrinking door-keys and a biting kettle,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">yawned Mr Weasley. ‘There was some pretty nasty stuff that wasn’t my department, though. Mortlake was taken away for questioning about some extremely odd ferrets, but that’s the Committee on Experimental Charms, thank goodness …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why would anyone bother making door-keys shrink?’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just Muggle-baiting,’ sighed Mr Weasley. ‘Sell them a key that keeps shrinking to nothing so they can never find it when they need it … Of course, it’s very hard to convict anyone because no Muggle would admit their key keeps shrinking – they’ll insist they just keep losing it. Bless them, they’ll go to any lengths to ignore magic, even if it’s staring them in the face … but the things our lot have taken to enchanting, you wouldn’t believe –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘LIKE CARS, FOR INSTANCE?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley had appeared, holding a long poker like a sword. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley’s eyes jerked open. He stared guiltily at his wife. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C-cars, Molly, dear?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, Arthur, cars,’ said Mrs Weasley, her eyes flashing. ‘Imagine a wizard buying a rusty old car and telling his wife all he wanted to do with it was take it apart to see how it worked, while  <i class=\"calibre4\">really</i> he was enchanting it to make it  <i class=\"calibre4\">fly. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley blinked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, dear, I think you’ll find that he would be quite within the law to do that, even if, er, he maybe would have done better to, um, tell his wife the truth … There’s a loophole in the law, you’ll find … as long as he wasn’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">intending</i> to fly the car, the fact that the car  <i class=\"calibre4\">could</i> fly wouldn’t –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Arthur Weasley, you made sure there was a loophole when you wrote that law!’ shouted Mrs Weasley. ‘Just so you could carry on tinkering with all that Muggle rubbish in your shed! And for your information, Harry arrived this morning in the car you weren’t intending to fly!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry?’ said Mr Weasley blankly. ‘Harry who?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Burrow 35 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked around, saw Harry and jumped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good Lord, is it Harry Potter? Very pleased to meet you, Ron’s told us so much about –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Your sons flew that car to Harry’s house and back last night! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">shouted Mrs Weasley. ‘What have you got to say about that, eh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you really?’ said Mr Weasley eagerly. ‘Did it go all right? I-I mean,’ he faltered, as sparks flew from Mrs Weasley’s eyes, ‘that-that was very wrong, boys – very wrong indeed …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s leave them to it,’ Ron muttered to Harry, as Mrs Weasley swelled like a bullfrog. ‘Come on, I’ll show you my bedroom.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They slipped out of the kitchen and down a narrow passageway to an uneven staircase, which zigzagged its way up through the house. On the third landing, a door stood ajar. Harry just caught sight of a pair of bright brown eyes staring at him before it closed with a snap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ginny,’ said Ron. ‘You don’t know how weird it is for her to be this shy, she never shuts up normally –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They climbed two more flights until they reached a door with peeling paint and a small plaque on it, saying ‘Ronald’s Room’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stepped in, his head almost touching the sloping ceiling, and blinked. It was like walking into a furnace: nearly everything in Ron’s room seemed to be a violent shade of orange: the bed-spread, the walls, even the ceiling. Then Harry realised that Ron had covered nearly every inch of the shabby wallpaper with posters of the same seven witches and wizards, all wearing bright orange robes, carrying broomsticks and waving energetically. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your Quidditch team?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Chudley Cannons,’ said Ron, pointing at the orange bed-spread, which was emblazoned with two giant black  <i class=\"calibre4\">Cs</i> and a speeding cannonball. ‘Ninth in the league.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s school spellbooks were stacked untidily in a corner, next to a pile of comics which all seemed to feature  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Adventures of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Martin Miggs, the Mad Muggle. </i> Ron’s magic wand was lying on top of a fish tank full of frogspawn on the window-sill, next to his fat grey rat, Scabbers, who was snoozing in a patch of sun. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stepped over a pack of Self-Shuffling playing cards on the floor and looked out of the tiny window. In the field far below he could see a gang of gnomes sneaking, one by one, back through the Weasleys’ hedge. Then he turned to look at Ron, who was watching him almost nervously, as though waiting for his opinion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>36 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s a bit small,’ said Ron quickly. ‘Not like that room you had with the Muggles. And I’m right underneath the ghoul in the attic, he’s always banging on the pipes and groaning …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry, grinning widely, said, ‘This is the best house I’ve ever been in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s ears went pink. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER FOUR — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">At Flourish and Blotts</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Life at The Burrow was as different as possible from life in Privet Drive. The Dursleys liked everything neat and ordered; the Weasleys’ house burst with the strange and unexpected. Harry got a shock the first time he looked in the mirror over the kitchen mantelpiece and it shouted, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Tuck your shirt in, scruffy! </i>’ The ghoul in the attic howled and dropped pipes whenever he felt things were getting too quiet, and small explosions from Fred and George’s bedroom were considered perfectly normal. What Harry found most unusual about life at Ron’s, however, wasn’t the talking mirror or the clanking ghoul: it was the fact that everybody there seemed to like him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley fussed over the state of his socks and tried to force him to eat fourth helpings at every meal. Mr Weasley liked Harry to sit next to him at the dinner table so that he could bombard him with questions about life with Muggles, asking him to explain how things like plugs and the postal service worked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Fascinating! </i>’ he would say, as Harry talked him through using a telephone. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ingenious, </i> really, how many ways Muggles have found of getting along without magic.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry heard from Hogwarts one sunny morning about a week after he had arrived at The Burrow. He and Ron went down to breakfast to find Mr and Mrs Weasley and Ginny already sitting at the kitchen table. The moment she saw Harry, Ginny accidentally knocked her porridge bowl to the floor with a loud clatter. Ginny seemed very prone to knocking things over whenever Harry entered a room. She dived under the table to retrieve the bowl and emerged with her face glowing like the setting sun. Pretending he hadn’t noticed this, Harry sat down and took the toast Mrs Weasley offered him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Letters from school,’ said Mr Weasley, passing Harry and Ron </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>38 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">identical envelopes of yellowish parchment, addressed in green ink. ‘Dumbledore already knows you’re here, Harry – doesn’t miss a trick, that man. You two’ve got them, too,’ he added, as Fred and George ambled in, still in their pyjamas. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a few minutes there was silence as they all read their letters. Harry’s told him to catch the Hogwarts Express as usual from King’s Cross station on September the first. There was also a list of the new books he’d need for the coming year. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Second-year students will require: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Standard Book of Spells, Grade 2</i> by Miranda Goshawk <i class=\"calibre4\">Break with a Banshee</i> by Gilderoy Lockhart <i class=\"calibre4\">Gadding with Ghouls</i> by Gilderoy Lockhart <i class=\"calibre4\">Holidays with Hags</i> by Gilderoy Lockhart <i class=\"calibre4\">Travels with Trolls</i> by Gilderoy Lockhart <i class=\"calibre4\">Voyages with Vampires</i> by Gilderoy Lockhart <i class=\"calibre4\">Wanderings with Werewolves</i> by Gilderoy Lockhart <i class=\"calibre4\">Year with the Yeti</i> by Gilderoy Lockhart Fred, who had finished his own list, peered over at Harry’s. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve been told to get all Lockhart’s books, too!’ he said. ‘The new Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher must be a fan – bet it’s a witch.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At this point, Fred caught his mother’s eye and quickly busied himself with the marmalade. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That lot won’t come cheap,’ said George, with a quick look at his parents. ‘Lockhart’s books are really expensive …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, we’ll manage,’ said Mrs Weasley, but she looked worried. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I expect we’ll be able to pick up a lot of Ginny’s things second-hand.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, are you starting at Hogwarts this year?’ Harry asked Ginny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She nodded, blushing to the roots of her flaming hair, and put her elbow in the butter dish. Fortunately no one saw this except Harry, because just then Ron’s elder brother Percy walked in. He was already dressed, his Hogwarts prefect badge pinned to his knitted tank top. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Morning, all,’ said Percy briskly. ‘Lovely day.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He sat down in the only remaining chair but leapt up again almost immediately, pulling from underneath him a moulting, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At Flourish and Blotts 39 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">grey feather duster – at least, that was what Harry thought it was, until he saw that it was breathing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Errol!’ said Ron, taking the limp owl from Percy and extracting a letter from under its wing. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Finally</i> – he’s got Hermione’s answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I wrote to her saying we were going to try and rescue you from the Dursleys.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He carried Errol to a perch just inside the back door and tried to stand him on it, but Errol flopped straight off again so Ron laid him on the draining board instead, muttering, ‘Pathetic.’ Then he ripped open Hermione’s letter and read it out loud: <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Ron, and Harry if you’re there,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">I hope everything went all right and that Harry is OK and</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">that you didn’t do anything illegal to get him out, Ron, because</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">that would get Harry into trouble, too. </i> I’ve  <i class=\"calibre4\">been really worried</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">and if Harry is all right, will you please let me know at once,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">but perhaps it </i> would   <i class=\"calibre4\">be better if you used a different owl,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">because I think another delivery might finish your one off. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I’m very busy with school work, of course</i> – ‘How can she be?’ said Ron in horror. ‘We’re on holiday!’ –  <i class=\"calibre4\">and we’re going</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">to London next Wednesday to buy my new books. Why don’t we</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">meet in Diagon Alley? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Let me know what’s happening as soon as you can, love from</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hermione. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, that fits in nicely, we can go and get all your things then, too,’ said Mrs Weasley, starting to clear the table. ‘What’re you all up to today?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron, Fred and George were planning to go up the hill to a small paddock the Weasleys owned. It was surrounded by trees that blocked it from view of the village below, meaning that they could practise Quidditch there, as long as they didn’t fly too high. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They couldn’t use real Quidditch balls, which would have been hard to explain if they had escaped and flown away over the village; instead they threw apples for each other to catch. They took it in turns to ride Harry’s Nimbus Two Thousand, which was easily the best broom; Ron’s old Shooting Star was often outstripped by passing butterflies. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Five minutes later they were marching up the hill, broomsticks over their shoulders. They had asked Percy if he wanted to join </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>40 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">them, but he had said he was busy. Harry had only seen Percy at meal-times so far; he stayed shut in his room the rest of the time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wish I knew what he was up to,’ said Fred, frowning. ‘He’s not himself. His exam results came the day before you did; twelve O.W.Ls and he hardly gloated at all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ordinary Wizarding Levels,’ George explained, seeing Harry’s puzzled look. ‘Bill got twelve, too. If we’re not careful, we’ll have another Head Boy in the family. I don’t think I could stand the shame.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Bill was the oldest Weasley brother. He and the next brother, Charlie, had already left Hogwarts. Harry had never met either of them, but knew that Charlie was in Romania, studying dragons, and Bill in Egypt, working for the wizards’ bank, Gringotts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno how Mum and Dad are going to afford all our school stuff this year,’ said George after a while. ‘Five sets of Lockhart books! And Ginny needs robes and a wand and everything …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry said nothing. He felt a bit awkward. Stored in an underground vault at Gringotts in London was a small fortune that his parents had left him. Of course, it was only in the wizarding world that he had money; you couldn’t use Galleons, Sickles and Knuts in Muggle shops. He had never mentioned his Gringotts bank account to the Dursleys; he didn’t think their horror of anything connected with magic would stretch to a large pile of gold. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley woke them all early the following Wednesday. After a quick half-a-dozen bacon sandwiches each, they pulled on their coats and Mrs Weasley took a flowerpot off the kitchen mantelpiece and peered inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re running low, Arthur,’ she sighed. ‘We’ll have to buy some more today … ah well, guests first! After you, Harry dear!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And she offered him the flowerpot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at them all watching him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘W-what am I supposed to do?’ he stammered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s never travelled by Floo powder,’ said Ron suddenly. ‘Sorry, Harry, I forgot.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never?’ said Mr Weasley. ‘But how did you get to Diagon Alley to buy your school things last year?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I went on the Underground –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Really?’ said Mr Weasley eagerly. ‘Were there  <i class=\"calibre4\">escapators? </i> How exactly –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At Flourish and Blotts 41 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not  <i class=\"calibre4\">now, </i> Arthur,’ said Mrs Weasley. ‘Floo powder’s a lot quick-er, dear, but goodness me, if you’ve never used it before –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’ll be all right, Mum,’ said Fred. ‘Harry, watch us first.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He took a pinch of glittering powder out of the flowerpot, stepped up to the fire and threw the powder into the flames. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a roar, the fire turned emerald green and rose higher than Fred, who stepped right into it, shouted, ‘Diagon Alley!’ and vanished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You must speak clearly, dear,’ Mrs Weasley told Harry, as George dipped his hand into the flowerpot. ‘And mind you get out at the right grate …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The right what?’ said Harry nervously, as the fire roared and whipped George out of sight too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, there are an awful lot of wizard fires to choose from, you know, but as long as you’ve spoken clearly –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’ll be fine, Molly, don’t fuss,’ said Mr Weasley, helping himself to Floo powder too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But dear, if he got lost, how would we ever explain to his aunt and uncle?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They wouldn’t mind,’ Harry reassured her. ‘Dudley would think it was a brilliant joke if I got lost up a chimney, don’t worry about that.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … all right … you go after Arthur,’ said Mrs Weasley. ‘Now, when you get into the fire, say where you’re going –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And keep your elbows tucked in,’ Ron advised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And your eyes shut,’ said Mrs Weasley. ‘The soot –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t fidget,’ said Ron. ‘Or you might well fall out of the wrong fireplace –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But don’t panic and get out too early, wait until you see Fred and George.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Trying hard to bear all this in mind, Harry took a pinch of Floo powder and walked to the edge of the fire. He took a deep breath, scattered the powder into the flames and stepped forward; the fire felt like a warm breeze; he opened his mouth and immediately swallowed a lot of hot ash. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D-Dia-gon Alley,’ he coughed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It  felt  as  though  he  was  being  sucked  down  a  giant  plug  hole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He seemed to be spinning very fast … the roaring in his ears was deafening … he tried to keep his eyes open but the whirl of green flames made him feel sick … something hard knocked his elbow </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>42 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and he tucked it in tightly, still spinning and spinning … now it felt as though cold hands were slapping his face … squinting through his glasses he saw a blurred stream of fireplaces and snatched glimpses of the rooms beyond … his bacon sandwiches were churning inside him … He closed his eyes again wishing it would stop, and then – he fell, face forward, onto cold stone and felt his glasses shatter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dizzy and bruised, covered in soot, he got gingerly to his feet, holding his broken glasses up to his eyes. He was quite alone, but <i class=\"calibre4\">where</i> he was, he had no idea. All he could tell was that he was standing in the stone fireplace of what looked like a large, dimly lit wizard’s shop – but nothing in here was ever likely to be on a Hogwarts school list. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A glass case nearby held a withered hand on a cushion, a blood-stained pack of cards and a staring glass eye. Evil-looking masks leered down from the walls, an assortment of human bones lay upon the counter and rusty, spiked instruments hung from the ceiling. Even worse, the dark, narrow street Harry could see through the dusty shop window was definitely not Diagon Alley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The sooner he got out of here, the better. Nose still stinging where it had hit the hearth, Harry made his way swiftly and silently towards the door, but before he’d got halfway towards it, two people appeared on the other side of the glass – and one of them was the very last person Harry wanted to meet when he was lost, covered in soot and wearing broken glasses: Draco Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked quickly around and spotted a large black cabinet to his left; he shot inside it and pulled the doors to, leaving a small crack to peer through. Seconds later, a bell clanged, and Malfoy stepped into the shop. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The man who followed could only be his father. He had the same pale, pointed face and identical cold grey eyes. Mr Malfoy crossed the shop, looking lazily at the items on display, and rang a bell on the counter before turning to his son and saying, ‘Touch nothing, Draco.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy, who had reached for the glass eye, said, ‘I thought you were going to buy me a present.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I said I would buy you a racing broom,’ said his father, drum-ming his fingers on the counter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the good of that if I’m not in the house team?’ said Malfoy, looking sulky and bad-tempered. ‘Harry Potter got a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At Flourish and Blotts 43 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nimbus Two Thousand last year. Special permission from Dumbledore so he could play for Gryffindor. He’s not even that good, it’s just because he’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">famous</i> … famous for having a stupid <i class=\"calibre4\">scar</i> on his forehead …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy bent down to examine a shelf full of skulls. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… everyone thinks he’s so  <i class=\"calibre4\">smart, </i> wonderful  <i class=\"calibre4\">Potter</i> with his  <i class=\"calibre4\">scar</i> and his  <i class=\"calibre4\">broomstick</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You have told me this at least a dozen times already,’ said Mr Malfoy, with a quelling look at his son, ‘and I would remind you that it is not – prudent – to appear less than fond of Harry Potter, not when most of our kind regard him as the hero who made the Dark Lord disappear – ah, Mr Borgin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A stooping man had appeared behind the counter, smoothing his greasy hair back from his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mr Malfoy, what a pleasure to see you again,’ said Mr Borgin in a voice as oily as his hair. ‘Delighted – and young Master Malfoy, too – charmed. How may I be of assistance? I must show you, just in today, and very reasonably priced –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not buying today, Mr Borgin, but selling,’ said Mr Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Selling?’ The smile faded slightly from Mr Borgin’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You have heard, of course, that the Ministry is conducting more raids,’ said Mr Malfoy, taking a roll of parchment from his inside pocket and unravelling it for Mr Borgin to read. ‘I have a few – ah – items at home that might embarrass me, if the Ministry were to call …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Borgin fixed a pince-nez to his nose and looked down the list. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Ministry wouldn’t presume to trouble you, sir, surely?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Malfoy’s lip curled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have not been visited yet. The name Malfoy still commands a certain respect, yet the Ministry grows ever more meddlesome. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There are rumours about a new Muggle Protection Act – no doubt that flea-bitten, Muggle-loving fool Arthur Weasley is behind it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt a hot surge of anger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– and as you see, certain of these poisons might make it  <i class=\"calibre4\">appear</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I understand, sir, of course,’ said Mr Borgin. ‘Let me see …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can I have  <i class=\"calibre4\">that? </i>’ interrupted Draco, pointing at the withered hand on its cushion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, the Hand of Glory!’ said Mr Borgin, abandoning Mr Malfoy’s list and scurrying over to Draco. ‘Insert a candle and it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>44 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">gives light only to the holder! Best friend of thieves and plunderers! Your son has fine taste, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I hope my son will amount to more than a thief or a plunderer, Borgin,’ said Mr Malfoy coldly and Mr Borgin said quickly, ‘No offence, sir, no offence meant –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Though if his school marks don’t pick up,’ said Mr Malfoy, more coldly still, ‘that may indeed be all he is fit for.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not my fault,’ retorted Draco. ‘The teachers all have favourites, that Hermione Granger –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I would have thought you’d be ashamed that a girl of no wizard family beat you in every exam,’ snapped Mr Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ha!’ said Harry under his breath, pleased to see Draco looking both abashed and angry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s the same all over,’ said Mr Borgin, in his oily voice. ‘Wizard blood is counting for less everywhere –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not with me,’ said Mr Malfoy, his long nostrils flaring. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, sir, nor with me, sir,’ said Mr Borgin, with a deep bow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In that case, perhaps we can return to my list,’ said Mr Malfoy shortly. ‘I am in something of a hurry, Borgin, I have important business elsewhere today.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They started to haggle. Harry watched nervously as Draco drew nearer and nearer to his hiding place, examining the objects for sale. He paused to examine a long coil of hangman’s rope and to read, smirking, the card propped on a magnificent necklace of opals:   <i class=\"calibre4\">Caution: Do Not Touch. Cursed – Has Claimed the Lives of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Nineteen Muggle Owners to Date. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Draco turned away and saw the cabinet right in front of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He walked forward … he stretched out his hand for the handle … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Done,’ said Mr Malfoy at the counter. ‘Come, Draco!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wiped his forehead on his sleeve as Draco turned away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good day to you, Mr Borgin, I’ll expect you at the manor tomorrow to pick up the goods.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The moment the door had closed, Mr Borgin dropped his oily manner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good day yourself,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Mister</i> Malfoy, and if the stories are true, you haven’t sold me half of what’s hidden in your  <i class=\"calibre4\">manor</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Muttering darkly, Mr Borgin disappeared into a back room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry waited for a minute in case he came back, then, quietly as he could, slipped out of the cabinet, past the glass cases and out of the shop door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At Flourish and Blotts 45 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Clutching his broken glasses to his face he stared around. He had emerged into a dingy alleyway that seemed to be made up entirely of shops devoted to the Dark Arts. The one he’d just left, Borgin and Burkes, looked like the largest, but opposite was a nasty window display of shrunken heads, and two doors down, a large cage was alive with gigantic black spiders. Two shabby-looking wizards were watching him from the shadow of a doorway, muttering to each other. Feeling jumpy, Harry set off, trying to hold his glasses on straight and hoping against hope he’d be able to find a way out of there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">An old wooden street sign hanging over a shop selling poisonous candles told him he was in Knockturn Alley. This didn’t help, as Harry had never heard of such a place. He supposed he hadn’t spoken clearly enough through his mouthful of ashes back in the Weasleys’ fire. Trying to stay calm, he wondered what to do. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not lost are you, my dear?’ said a voice in his ear, making him jump. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">An aged witch stood in front of him, holding a tray of what looked horribly like whole human fingernails. She leered at him, showing mossy teeth. Harry backed away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m fine, thanks,’ he said. ‘I’m just –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HARRY! What d’yeh think yer doin’ down there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s heart leapt. So did the witch; a load of fingernails cas-caded down over her feet and she cursed as the massive form of Hagrid, the Hogwarts gamekeeper, came striding towards them, beetle-black eyes flashing over his great bristling beard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid!’ Harry croaked in relief. ‘I was lost … Floo powder …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid seized Harry by the scruff of the neck and pulled him away from the witch, knocking the tray right out of her hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Her shrieks followed them all the way along the twisting alleyway out into bright sunlight. Harry saw a familiar, snow-white marble building in the distance: Gringotts bank. Hagrid had steered him right into Diagon Alley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yer  a  mess!’  said  Hagrid  gruffly,  brushing  soot  off  Harry  so forcefully he nearly knocked him into a barrel of dragon dung outside an apothecary’s. ‘Skulkin’ around Knockturn Alley, I dunno  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– dodgy place, Harry – don’ want no one ter see yeh down there –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I realised  <i class=\"calibre4\">that, </i>’ said Harry, ducking as Hagrid made to brush him off again. ‘I told you, I was lost – what were you doing down there, anyway?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>46 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> was lookin’ fer a Flesh-Eatin’ Slug Repellent,’ growled Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re ruinin’ the school cabbages. Yer not on yer own?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m staying with the Weasleys but we got separated,’ Harry explained. ‘I’ve got to go and find them …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They set off together down the street. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How come yeh never wrote back ter me?’ said Hagrid, as Harry jogged alongside him (he had to take three steps to every stride of Hagrid’s enormous boots). Harry explained all about Dobby and the Dursleys. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ruddy Muggles,’ growled Hagrid. ‘If I’d’ve known –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! Harry! Over here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up and saw Hermione Granger standing at the top of the white flight of steps to Gringotts. She ran down to meet them, her bushy brown hair flying behind her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What happened to your glasses? Hello, Hagrid … Oh, it’s <i class=\"calibre4\">wonderful</i> to see you two again … Are you coming into Gringotts, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As soon as I’ve found the Weasleys,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh won’t have long ter wait,’ grinned Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione looked around; sprinting up the crowded street were Ron, Fred, George, Percy and Mr Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ Mr Weasley panted. ‘We  <i class=\"calibre4\">hoped</i> you’d only gone one grate too far …’ He mopped his glistening bald patch. ‘Molly’s frantic – she’s coming now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where did you come out?’ Ron asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Knockturn Alley,’ said Hagrid grimly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Brilliant! </i>’ said Fred and George together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve never been allowed in,’ said Ron enviously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I should ruddy well think not,’ growled Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley now came galloping into view, her handbag swinging wildly in one hand, Ginny just clinging onto the other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Harry – oh, my dear – you could have been anywhere –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gasping for breath she pulled a large clothes brush out of her bag and began sweeping off the soot Hagrid hadn’t managed to beat away. Mr Weasley took Harry’s glasses, gave them a tap of his wand and returned them, good as new. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, gotta be off,’ said Hagrid, who was having his hand wrung by Mrs Weasley (‘Knockturn Alley! If you hadn’t found him, Hagrid!’). ‘See yer at Hogwarts!’ And he strode away, head and shoulders taller than anyone else in the packed street. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At Flourish and Blotts 47 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Guess who I saw in Borgin and Burkes?’ Harry asked Ron and Hermione as they climbed the Gringotts steps. ‘Malfoy and his father.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did Lucius Malfoy buy anything?’ said Mr Weasley sharply behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, he was selling.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So he’s worried,’ said Mr Weasley with grim satisfaction. ‘Oh, I’d love to get Lucius Malfoy for something …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You be careful, Arthur,’ said Mrs Weasley sharply, as they were ushered into the bank by a bowing goblin at the door. ‘That family’s trouble, don’t go biting off more than you can chew.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you don’t think I’m a match for Lucius Malfoy?’ said Mr Weasley indignantly, but he was distracted almost at once by the sight of Hermione’s parents, who were standing nervously at the counter that ran all along the great marble hall, waiting for Hermione to introduce them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you’re  <i class=\"calibre4\">Muggles! </i>’ said Mr Weasley delightedly. ‘We must have a drink! What’s that you’ve got there? Oh, you’re changing Muggle money. Molly, look!’ He pointed excitedly at the ten-pound notes in Mr Granger’s hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Meet you back here,’ Ron said to Hermione, as the Weasleys and Harry were led off to their underground vaults by another Gringotts goblin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The vaults were reached by means of small, goblin-driven carts that sped along miniature train-tracks through the bank’s underground tunnels. Harry enjoyed the breakneck journey down to the Weasleys’ vault, but felt dreadful, far worse than he had in Knockturn Alley, when it was opened. There was a very small pile of silver Sickles inside, and just one gold Galleon. Mrs Weasley felt right into the corners before sweeping the whole lot into her bag. Harry felt even worse when they reached his vault. He tried to block the contents from view as he hastily shoved handfuls of coins into a leather bag. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Back outside on the marble steps, they all separated. Percy muttered vaguely about needing a new quill. Fred and George had spotted their friend from Hogwarts, Lee Jordan. Mrs Weasley and Ginny were going to a second-hand robe shop. Mr Weasley was insisting on taking the Grangers off to the Leaky Cauldron for a drink. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll all meet at Flourish and Blotts in an hour to buy your </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>48 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">school books,’ said Mrs Weasley, setting off with Ginny. ‘And not one step down Knockturn Alley!’ she shouted at the twins’ retreating backs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione strolled off along the winding, cob-bled street. The bag of gold, silver and bronze jangling cheerfully in Harry’s pocket was clamouring to be spent, so he bought three large strawberry and peanut-butter ice-creams which they slurped happily as they wandered up the alley, examining the fascinating shop windows. Ron gazed longingly at a full set of Chudley Cannon robes in the windows of ‘Quality Quidditch Supplies’  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">until Hermione dragged them off to buy ink and parchment next door. In Gambol and Japes Wizarding Joke Shop, they met Fred, George and Lee Jordan, who were stocking up on ‘Dr Filibuster’s Fabulous Wet-Start, No-Heat Fireworks’, and in a tiny junk shop full of broken wands, wonky brass scales and old cloaks covered in potion stains they found Percy, deeply immersed in a small and deeply boring book called  <i class=\"calibre4\">Prefects Who Gained Power. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">A study of Hogwarts Prefects and their later careers</i>,’ Ron read aloud off the back cover. ‘That sounds  <i class=\"calibre4\">fascinating</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go away,’ Percy snapped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Course, he’s very ambitious, Percy, he’s got it all planned out … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he wants to be Minister of Magic …’ Ron told Harry and Hermione in an undertone, as they left Percy to it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">An hour later, they headed for Flourish and Blotts. They were by no means the only ones making their way to the bookshop. As they approached it, they saw to their surprise a large crowd jostling outside the doors, trying to get in. The reason for this was proclaimed by a large banner stretched across the upper windows: <i class=\"calibre4\">GILDEROY LOCKHART</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">will be signing copies of his autobiography</i> MAGICAL ME </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">today 12.30 – 4.30 pm</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can actually meet him!’ Hermione squealed. ‘I mean, he’s written almost the whole booklist!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The crowd seemed to be made up mostly of witches around Mrs Weasley’s age. A harassed-looking wizard stood at the door, saying, ‘Calmly, please ladies … don’t push, there … mind the books, now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At Flourish and Blotts 49 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione squeezed inside. A long queue wound right to the back of the shop, where Gilderoy Lockhart was signing his books. They each grabbed a copy of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Break with a</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Banshee, </i> and sneaked up the line to where the rest of the Weasleys were standing with Mr and Mrs Granger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, there you are, good,’ said Mrs Weasley. She sounded breathless and kept patting her hair. ‘We’ll be able to see him in a minute …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart came slowly into view, seated at a table surrounded by large pictures of his own face, all winking and flashing dazzlingly white teeth at the crowd. The real Lockhart was wearing robes of forget-me-not blue which exactly matched his eyes; his pointed wizard’s hat was set at a jaunty angle on his wavy hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A short, irritable-looking man was dancing around taking photographs with a large black camera that emitted puffs of purple smoke with every blinding flash. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Out of the way, there,’ he snarled at Ron, moving back to get a better shot. ‘This is for the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Big deal,’ said Ron, rubbing his foot where the photographer had stepped on it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart heard him. He looked up. He saw Ron – and then he saw Harry. He stared. Then he leapt to his feet and positively shouted, ‘It  <i class=\"calibre4\">can’t</i> be Harry Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The crowd parted, whispering excitedly. Lockhart dived forward, seized Harry’s arm and pulled him to the front. The crowd burst into applause. Harry’s face burned as Lockhart shook his hand for the photographer, who was clicking away madly, wafting thick smoke over the Weasleys. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nice big smile, Harry,’ said Lockhart, through his own gleaming teeth. ‘Together, you and I are worth the front page.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When he finally let go of Harry’s hand, Harry could hardly feel his fingers. He tried to sidle back over to the Weasleys, but Lockhart threw an arm around his shoulders and clamped him tightly to his side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ladies and gentlemen,’ he said loudly, waving for quiet. ‘What an extraordinary moment this is! The perfect moment for me to make a little announcement I’ve been sitting on for some time! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When young Harry here stepped into Flourish and Blotts today, he only wanted to buy my autobiography – which I shall be </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>50 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">happy to present him now, free of charge –’ the crowd applauded again, ‘– he had  <i class=\"calibre4\">no idea, </i>’ Lockhart continued, giving Harry a little shake that made his glasses slip to the end of his nose, ‘that he would shortly be getting much, much more than my book, <i class=\"calibre4\">Magical Me. </i> He and his school fellows will, in fact, be getting the real, magical me. Yes, ladies and gentlemen, I have great pleasure and pride in announcing that, this September, I will be taking up the post of Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The crowd cheered and clapped and Harry found himself being presented with the entire works of Gilderoy Lockhart. Staggering slightly under their weight, he managed to make his way out of the limelight to the edge of the room, where Ginny was standing next to her new cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You have these,’ Harry mumbled to her, tipping the books into the cauldron. ‘I’ll buy my own –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bet you loved that, didn’t you, Potter?’ said a voice Harry had no trouble recognising. He straightened up and found himself face to face with Draco Malfoy, who was wearing his usual sneer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Famous</i> Harry Potter,’ said Malfoy. ‘Can’t even go into a  <i class=\"calibre4\">bookshop</i> without making the front page.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Leave him alone, he didn’t want all that!’ said Ginny. It was the first time she had spoken in front of Harry. She was glaring at Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter, you’ve got yourself a  <i class=\"calibre4\">girlfriend! </i>’ drawled Malfoy. Ginny went scarlet as Ron and Hermione fought their way over, both clutching stacks of Lockhart’s books. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, it’s you,’ said Ron, looking at  Malfoy  as  if  he  were  something unpleasant on the sole of his shoe. ‘Bet you’re surprised to see Harry here, eh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not as surprised as I am to see you in a shop, Weasley,’ retorted Malfoy. ‘I suppose your parents will go hungry for a month to pay for that lot.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron went as red as Ginny. He dropped his books into the cauldron, too, and started towards Malfoy, but Harry and Hermione grabbed the back of his jacket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron!’ said Mr Weasley, struggling over with Fred and George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing? It’s mad in here, let’s go outside.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, well, well – Arthur Weasley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Mr Malfoy. He stood with his hand on Draco’s shoulder, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At Flourish and Blotts 51 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">sneering in just the same way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lucius,’ said Mr Weasley, nodding coldly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Busy time at the Ministry, I hear,’ said Mr Malfoy. ‘All those raids … I hope they’re paying you overtime?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He reached into Ginny’s cauldron and extracted, from amidst the glossy Lockhart books, a very old, very battered copy of  <i class=\"calibre4\">A</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Beginner’s Guide to Transfiguration. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Obviously not,’ he said. ‘Dear me, what’s the use of being a disgrace to the name of wizard if they don’t even pay you well for it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley flushed darker than either Ron or Ginny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We have a very different idea of what disgraces the name of wizard, Malfoy,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Clearly,’ said Mr Malfoy, his pale eyes straying to Mr and Mrs Granger, who were watching apprehensively. ‘The company you keep, Weasley … and I thought your family could sink no lower –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a thud of metal as Ginny’s cauldron went flying; Mr Weasley had thrown himself at Mr Malfoy, knocking him backwards into a bookshelf. Dozens of heavy spellbooks came thundering down on all their heads; there was a yell of ‘Get him, Dad!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">from Fred or George; Mrs Weasley was shrieking, ‘No, Arthur, no!’; the crowd stampeded backwards, knocking more shelves over; ‘Gentlemen, please – please!’ cried the assistant and then, louder than all, ‘Break it up, there, gents, break it up –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was wading towards them through the sea of books. In an instant he had pulled Mr Weasley and Mr Malfoy apart. Mr Weasley had a cut lip and Mr Malfoy had been hit in the eye by an <i class=\"calibre4\">Encyclopedia of Toadstools. </i> He was still holding Ginny’s old transfiguration book. He thrust it at her, his eyes glittering with malice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here, girl – take your book – it’s the best your father can give you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pulling himself out of Hagrid’s grip he beckoned to Draco and swept from the shop. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh should’ve ignored him, Arthur,’ said Hagrid, almost lifting Mr Weasley off his feet as he straightened his robes. ‘Rotten ter the core, the whole family, everyone knows that. No Malfoy’s worth listenin’ ter. Bad blood, that’s what it is. Come on now – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">let’s get outta here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The assistant looked as though he wanted to stop them leaving, but he barely came up to Hagrid’s waist and seemed to think better of it. They hurried up the street, the Grangers shaking with </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>52 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">fright and Mrs Weasley beside herself with fury. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A  <i class=\"calibre4\">fine</i> example to set to your children …  <i class=\"calibre4\">brawling</i> in public … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">what</i> Gilderoy Lockhart must’ve thought …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He was pleased,’ said Fred. ‘Didn’t you hear him as we were leaving? He was asking that bloke from the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i> if he’d be able to work the fight into his report – said it was all publicity.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But it was a subdued group who headed back to the fireside in the Leaky Cauldron, where Harry, the Weasleys and all their shopping would be travelling back to The Burrow using Floo powder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They said goodbye to the Grangers, who were leaving the pub for the Muggle street on the other side. Mr Weasley started to ask them how bus stops worked, but stopped quickly at the look on Mrs Weasley’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took off his glasses and put them safely in his pocket before helping himself to Floo powder. It definitely wasn’t his favourite way to travel. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER FIVE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Whomping Willow</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The end of the summer holidays came too quickly for Harry’s liking. He was looking forward to getting back to Hogwarts, but his month at The Burrow had been the happiest of his life. It was difficult not to feel jealous of Ron when he thought of the Dursleys and the sort of welcome he could expect next time he turned up in Privet Drive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On their last evening, Mrs Weasley conjured up a sumptuous dinner which included all of Harry’s favourite things, ending with a mouthwatering treacle pudding. Fred and George rounded off the evening with a display of Filibuster fireworks; they filled the kitchen with red and blue stars that bounced from ceiling to wall for at least half an hour. Then it was time for a last mug of hot chocolate and bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took a long while to get started next morning. They were up at cock-crow, but somehow they still seemed to have a great deal to do. Mrs Weasley dashed about in a bad mood looking for spare socks and quills, people kept colliding on the stairs, half-dressed with bits of toast in their hands, and Mr Weasley nearly broke his neck, tripping over a stray chicken as he crossed the yard carrying Ginny’s trunk to the car. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t see how eight people, six large trunks, two owls and a rat were going to fit into one small Ford Anglia. He had reckoned, of course, without the special features which Mr Weasley had added. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not a word to Molly,’ he whispered to Harry as he opened the boot and showed him how it had been magically expanded so that the trunks fitted easily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When at last they were all in the car, Mrs Weasley glanced into the back seat, where Harry, Ron, Fred, George and Percy were all sitting comfortably side by side, and said, ‘Muggles  <i class=\"calibre4\">do</i> know more </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>54 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">than we give them credit for, don’t they?’ She and Ginny got into the front seat, which had been stretched so that it resembled a park bench. ‘I mean, you’d never know it was this roomy from the outside, would you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley started up the engine and they trundled out of the yard, Harry turning back for a last look at the house. He barely had time to wonder when he’d see it again when they were back: George had forgotten his box of Filibuster fireworks. Five minutes after that, they skidded to a halt in the yard so that Fred could run in for his broomstick. They had almost reached the motorway when Ginny shrieked that she’d left her diary. By the time she had clambered back into the car, they were running very late, and tempers were running high. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley glanced at his watch and then at his wife. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Molly, dear –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">No, </i> Arthur.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one would see. This little button here is an Invisibility Booster I installed – that’d get us up in the air – then we fly above the clouds. We’d be there in ten minutes and no one would be any the wiser …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I said  <i class=\"calibre4\">no, </i> Arthur, not in broad daylight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They reached King’s Cross at a quarter to eleven. Mr Weasley dashed across the road to get trolleys for their trunks and they all hurried into the station. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had caught the Hogwarts Express the previous year. The tricky bit was getting onto platform nine and three-quarters, which wasn’t visible to the Muggle eye. What you had to do was walk through the solid barrier dividing platforms nine and ten. It didn’t hurt, but it had to be done carefully so that none of the Muggles noticed you vanishing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Percy first,’ said Mrs Weasley, looking nervously at the clock overhead, which showed they had only five minutes to disappear casually through the barrier. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy strode briskly forward and vanished. Mr Weasley went next, Fred and George followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll take Ginny and you two come right after us,’ Mrs Weasley told Harry and Ron, grabbing Ginny’s hand and setting off. In the blink of an eye they were gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s go together, we’ve only got a minute,’ Ron said to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry made sure that Hedwig’s cage was safely wedged on top </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Whomping Willow 55 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">of his trunk and wheeled his trolley about to face the barrier. He felt perfectly confident; this wasn’t nearly as uncomfortable as using Floo powder. Both of them bent low over the handles of their trolleys and walked purposefully towards the barrier, gathering speed. A few feet away from it, they broke into a run and – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">CRASH. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both trolleys hit the barrier and bounced backwards. Ron’s trunk fell off with a loud thump, Harry was knocked off his feet, and Hedwig’s cage bounced onto the shiny floor and she rolled away, shrieking indignantly. People all around them stared and a guard nearby yelled, ‘What in blazes d’you think you’re doing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lost control of the trolley,’ Harry gasped, clutching his ribs as he got up. Ron ran to pick up Hedwig, who was causing such a scene that there was a lot of muttering about cruelty to animals from the surrounding crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why can’t we get through?’ Harry hissed to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I dunno –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron looked wildly around. A dozen curious people were still watching them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re going to miss the train,’ Ron whispered. ‘I don’t understand why the gateway’s sealed itself …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up at the giant clock with a sickening feeling in the pit of his stomach. Ten seconds … nine seconds … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He wheeled his trolley forward cautiously until it was right against the barrier, and pushed with all his might. The metal remained solid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Three seconds … two seconds … one second … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s gone,’ said Ron, sounding stunned. ‘The train’s left. What if Mum and Dad can’t get back through to us? Have you got any Muggle money?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry gave a hollow laugh. ‘The Dursleys haven’t given me pocket money for about six years.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron pressed his ear to the cold barrier. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t hear a thing,’ he said tensely. ‘What’re we going to do? I don’t know how long it’ll take Mum and Dad to get back to us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They looked around. People were still watching them, mainly because of Hedwig’s continuing screeches. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think we’d better go and wait by the car,’ said Harry. ‘We’re attracting too much atten–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ said Ron, his eyes gleaming. ‘The car!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>56 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can fly the car to Hogwarts!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I thought –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re stuck, right? And we’ve got to get to school, haven’t we? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And even underage wizards are allowed to use magic if it’s a real emergency, section nineteen or something of the Restriction of Thingy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s feeling of panic turned suddenly to excitement. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you fly it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No problem,’ said Ron, wheeling his trolley around to face the exit. ‘C’mon, let’s go, if we hurry we’ll be able to follow the Hogwarts Express.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And they marched off through the crowd of curious Muggles, out of the station and back into the side road where the old Ford Anglia was parked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron unlocked the cavernous boot with a series of taps from his wand. They heaved their trunks back in, put Hedwig on the back seat and got into the front. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Check no one’s watching,’ said Ron, starting the ignition with another tap of his wand. Harry stuck his head out of the window: traffic was rumbling along the main road ahead, but their street was empty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron pressed a tiny silver button on the dashboard. The car around them vanished – and so did they. Harry could feel the seat vibrating beneath him, hear the engine, feel his hands on his knees and his glasses on his nose, but for all he could see, he had become a pair of eyeballs, floating a few feet above the ground in a dingy street full of parked cars. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s go,’ said Ron’s voice from his right. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The ground and the dirty buildings on either side fell away, dropping out of sight as the car rose; in seconds, the whole of London lay, smoky and glittering, below them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then there was a popping noise and the car, Harry and Ron reappeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Uh oh,’ said Ron, jabbing at the Invisibility Booster. ‘It’s faulty –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both of them pummelled it. The car vanished. Then it flickered back again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hold on!’ Ron yelled, and he slammed his foot on the accelerator; they shot straight into the low woolly clouds and everything </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Whomping Willow 57 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">turned dull and foggy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now what?’ said Harry, blinking at the solid mass of cloud pressing in on them from all sides. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We need to see the train to know what direction to go in,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dip back down again – quickly –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They dropped back beneath the clouds and twisted around in their seats, squinting at the ground – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can see it!’ Harry yelled. ‘Right ahead – there!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hogwarts Express was streaking along below them like a scarlet snake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Due north,’ said Ron, checking the compass on the dashboard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK, we’ll just have to check on it every half an hour or so. Hold on …’ And they shot up through the clouds. A minute later, they burst out into a blaze of sunlight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a different world. The wheels of the car skimmed the sea of fluffy cloud, the sky a bright, endless blue under the blinding white sun. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All we’ve got to worry about now are aeroplanes,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They looked at each other and started to laugh; for a long time, they couldn’t stop. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was as though they had been plunged into a fabulous dream. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This, thought Harry, was surely the only way to travel: past swirls and turrets of snowy cloud, in a car full of hot, bright sunlight, with a fat pack of toffees in the glove compartment, and the prospect of seeing Fred and George’s jealous faces when they landed smoothly and spectacularly on the sweeping lawn in front of Hogwarts castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They made regular checks on the train as they flew further and further north, each dip beneath the clouds showing them a different view. London was soon far behind them, replaced by neat green fields which gave way in turn to wide, purplish moors, villages with tiny toy churches and a great city alive with cars like multi-coloured ants. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Several uneventful hours later, however, Harry had to admit that some of the fun was wearing off. The toffees had made them extremely thirsty and they had nothing to drink. He and Ron had pulled off their jumpers, but Harry’s T-shirt was sticking to the back of his seat and his glasses kept sliding down to the end of his sweaty nose. He had stopped noticing the fantastic cloud shapes </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>58 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">now, and was thinking longingly of the train miles below, where you could buy ice-cold pumpkin juice from a trolley pushed by a plump witch.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Why</i> hadn’t they been able to get onto platform nine and three-quarters? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t be much further, can it?’ croaked Ron, hours later still, as the sun started to sink into their floor of cloud, staining it a deep pink. ‘Ready for another check on the train?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was still right below them, winding its way past a snow-capped mountain. It was much darker beneath the canopy of clouds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron put his foot on the accelerator and drove them upwards again, but as he did so, the engine began to whine. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron exchanged nervous glances. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s probably just tired,’ said Ron. ‘It’s never been this far before …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And they both pretended not to notice the whining growing louder and louder as the sky became steadily darker. Stars were blossoming in the blackness. Harry pulled his jumper back on, trying to ignore the way the windscreen wipers were now waving feebly, as though in protest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not far,’ said Ron, more to the car than to Harry, ‘not far now,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and he patted the dashboard nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they flew back beneath the clouds a little while later, they had to squint through the darkness for a landmark they knew. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">There! </i>’ Harry shouted, making Ron and Hedwig jump. ‘Straight ahead!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Silhouetted on the dark horizon, high on the cliff over the lake, stood the many turrets and towers of Hogwarts castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the car had begun to shudder and was losing speed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on,’ Ron said cajolingly, giving the steering wheel a little shake, ‘nearly there, come on –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The engine groaned. Narrow jets of steam were issuing from under the bonnet. Harry found himself gripping the edges of his seat very hard as they flew towards the lake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The car gave a nasty wobble. Glancing out of his window, Harry saw the smooth, black, glassy surface of the water, a mile below. Ron’s knuckles were white on the steering wheel. The car wobbled again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come  <i class=\"calibre4\">on, </i>’ Ron muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were over the lake … the castle was right ahead … Ron </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Whomping Willow 59 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">put his foot down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud clunk, a splutter, and the engine died completely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Uh oh,’ said Ron, into the silence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The nose of the car dropped. They were falling, gathering speed, heading straight for the solid castle wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Noooooo! </i>’ Ron yelled, swinging the steering wheel around; they missed the dark stone wall by inches as the car turned in a great arc, soaring over the dark greenhouses, then the vegetable patch and then out over the black lawns, losing height all the time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron let go of the steering wheel completely and pulled his wand out of his back pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘STOP! STOP!’ he yelled, whacking the dashboard and the windscreen, but they were still plummeting, the ground flying up towards them … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘MIND THAT TREE!’ Harry bellowed, lunging for the steering wheel, but too late – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">CRUNCH. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With an ear-splitting bang of metal on wood, they hit the thick tree trunk and dropped to the ground with a heavy jolt. Steam was billowing from under the crumpled bonnet; Hedwig was shrieking in terror, a golf-ball-sized lump was throbbing on Harry’s head where he had hit the windscreen, and to his right, Ron let out a low, despairing groan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you OK?’ Harry said urgently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My wand,’ said Ron, in a shaky voice. ‘Look at my wand.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It had snapped, almost in two; the tip was dangling limply, held on by a few splinters. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry  opened  his  mouth  to  say  he  was  sure  they’d  be  able  to mend it up at the school, but he never even got started. At that very moment, something hit his side of the car with the force of a charging bull, sending him lurching sideways into Ron, just as an equally heavy blow hit the roof. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s happen–?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gasped, staring through the windscreen, and Harry looked around just in time to see a branch as thick as a python smash into it. The tree they had hit was attacking them. Its trunk was bent almost double, and its gnarled boughs were pummelling every inch of the car it could reach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>60 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aaargh!’  said  Ron,  as  another twisted limb punched a large dent into his door; the windscreen was now trembling under a hail of blows from knuckle-like twigs and a branch as thick as a battering ram was pounding furiously on the roof, which seemed to be caving in – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Run for it!’ Ron shouted, throwing his full weight against his door, but next second he had been knocked backwards into Harry’s lap by a vicious upper cut from another branch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re done for!’ he moaned, as the ceiling sagged, but suddenly the floor of the car was vibrating – the engine had re-started. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Reverse! </i>’ Harry yelled, and the car shot backwards. The tree was still trying to hit them; they could hear its roots creaking as it almost ripped itself up, lashing out at them as they sped out of reach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That,’ panted Ron, ‘was close. Well done, car.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The car, however, had reached the end of its tether. With two smart clunks, the doors flew open and Harry felt his seat tip sideways: next thing he knew he was sprawled on the damp ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Loud thuds told him that the car was ejecting their luggage from the boot. Hedwig’s cage flew through the air and burst open; she rose out of it with a loud, angry screech and sped off towards the castle without a backwards look. Then, dented, scratched and steaming, the car rumbled off into the darkness, its rear lights blazing angrily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come back!’ Ron yelled after it, brandishing his broken wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dad’ll kill me!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the car disappeared from view with one last snort from its exhaust. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you  <i class=\"calibre4\">believe</i> our luck?’ said Ron miserably, bending down to pick up Scabbers the rat. ‘Of all the trees we could’ve hit, we had to get one that hits back.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He glanced over his shoulder at the ancient tree, which was still flailing its branches threateningly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on,’ said Harry wearily, ‘we’d better get up to the school …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It wasn’t at all the triumphant arrival they had pictured. Stiff, cold and bruised, they seized the ends of their trunks and began dragging them up the grassy slope, towards the great oak front doors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think the feast’s already started,’ said Ron, dropping his trunk at the foot of the front steps and crossing quietly to look through  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Whomping Willow 61 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">a brightly lit window. ‘Hey, Harry, come and look – it’s the Sorting!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hurried over and, together, he and Ron peered in at the Great Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Innumerable candles were hovering in mid-air over four long, crowded tables, making the golden plates and goblets sparkle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Overhead, the bewitched ceiling which always mirrored the sky outside, sparkled with stars. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the forest of pointed black Hogwarts hats, Harry saw a long line of scared-looking first-years filing into the Hall. Ginny was amongst them, easily visible because of her vivid Weasley hair. Meanwhile, Professor McGonagall, a bespectacled witch with her hair in a tight bun, was placing the famous Hogwarts Sorting Hat on a stool before the newcomers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Every year, this aged old hat, patched, frayed and dirty, sorted new students into the four Hogwarts houses (Gryffindor, Hufflepuff, Ravenclaw and Slytherin). Harry well remembered putting it on, exactly one year ago, and waiting, petrified, for its decision as it muttered aloud in his ear. For a few horrible seconds he had feared that the hat was going to put him in Slytherin, the house which had turned out more dark witches and wizards than any other – but he had ended up in Gryffindor, along with Ron, Hermione and the rest of the Weasleys. Last term, Harry and Ron had helped Gryffindor win the House Championship, beating Slytherin for the first time in seven years. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A very small, mousey-haired boy had been called forward to place the hat on his head. Harry’s eyes wandered past him to where Professor Dumbledore, the Headmaster, sat watching the Sorting from the staff table, his long silver beard and half-moon glasses shining brightly in the candlelight. Several seats along, Harry saw Gilderoy Lockhart, dressed in robes of aquamarine. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And there at the end was Hagrid, huge and hairy, drinking deeply from his goblet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on …’ Harry muttered to Ron. ‘There’s an empty chair at the staff table … Where’s Snape?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Severus Snape was Harry’s least favourite teacher. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry also happened to be Snape’s least favourite student. Cruel, sarcastic and disliked by everybody except the students from his own house (Slytherin), Snape taught Potions. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe he’s ill!’ said Ron hopefully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>62 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe he’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">left, </i>’ said Harry, ‘because he missed out on the Defence Against the Dark Arts job  <i class=\"calibre4\">again! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Or he might have been  <i class=\"calibre4\">sacked! </i>’ said Ron enthusiastically. ‘I mean, everyone hates him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Or maybe,’ said a very cold voice right behind them, ‘he’s waiting to hear why you two didn’t arrive on the school train.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry spun around. There, his black robes rippling in a cold breeze, stood Severus Snape. He was a thin man with sallow skin, a hooked nose and greasy, shoulder-length black hair, and at this moment, he was smiling in a way that told Harry he and Ron were in very deep trouble. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Follow me,’ said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Not daring even to look at each other, Harry and Ron followed Snape up the steps into the vast, echoing Entrance Hall, which was lit with flaming torches. A delicious smell of food was wafting from the Great Hall, but Snape led them away from the warmth and light, down a narrow stone staircase that led into the dungeons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In!’ he said, opening a door halfway down the cold passageway and pointing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They entered Snape’s office, shivering. The shadowy walls were lined with shelves of large glass jars, in which floated all manner of revolting things Harry didn’t really want to know the name of at the moment. The fireplace was dark and empty. Snape closed the door and turned to look at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So,’ he said softly, ‘the train isn’t good enough for the famous Harry Potter and his faithful sidekick Weasley. Wanted to arrive with a  <i class=\"calibre4\">bang, </i> did we, boys?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, sir, it was the barrier at King’s Cross, it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Silence!’ said Snape coldly. ‘What have you done with the car?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gulped. This wasn’t the first time Snape had given Harry the impression of being able to read minds. But a moment later, he understood, as Snape unrolled today’s issue of the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Evening</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Prophet. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You were seen,’ he hissed, showing them the headline: FLYING </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">FORD ANGLIA MYSTIFIES MUGGLES. He began to read aloud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ “Two Muggles in London, convinced they saw an old car flying over the Post Office tower … at noon in Norfolk, Mrs Hetty Bayliss, while hanging out her washing … Mr Angus Fleet, of Peebles, reported to police” … six or seven Muggles in all. I </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Whomping Willow 63 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">believe   <i class=\"calibre4\">your</i> father works in the Misuse of Muggle Artefacts Office?’ he said, looking up at Ron and smiling still more nastily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dear, dear … his own son …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt as though he’d just been walloped in the stomach by one of the mad tree’s larger branches. If anyone found out Mr Weasley had bewitched the car … he hadn’t thought of that … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I noticed, in my search of the park, that considerable damage seems to have been done to a very valuable Whomping Willow,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape went on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That tree did more damage to  <i class=\"calibre4\">us</i> than we –’ Ron blurted out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Silence! </i>’ snapped Snape again. ‘Most unfortunately, you are not in my house and the decision to expel you does not rest with me. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I shall go and fetch the people who  <i class=\"calibre4\">do</i> have that happy power. You will wait here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron stared at each other, white-faced. Harry didn’t feel hungry any more. He now felt extremely sick. He tried not to look at a large, slimy something suspended in green liquid on a shelf behind Snape’s desk. If Snape had gone to fetch Professor McGonagall, head of Gryffindor house, they were hardly any better off. She might be fairer than Snape, but she was still extremely strict. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ten minutes later, Snape returned, and sure enough it was Professor McGonagall who accompanied him. Harry had seen Professor McGonagall angry on several occasions, but either he had forgotten just how thin her mouth could go, or he had never seen her this angry before. She raised her wand the moment she entered. Harry and Ron both flinched, but she merely pointed it at the empty fireplace, where flames suddenly erupted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit,’ she said, and they both backed into chairs by the fire. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Explain,’ she said, her glasses glinting ominously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron launched into the story, starting with the barrier at the station refusing to let them through. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… so we had no choice, Professor, we couldn’t get on the train.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why didn’t you send us a letter by owl? I believe  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> have an owl?’ Professor McGonagall said coldly to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry gaped at her. Now she said it, that seemed the obvious thing to have done. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – I didn’t think –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That,’ said Professor McGonagall, ‘is obvious.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a knock on the office door and Snape, now looking </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>64 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">happier than ever, opened it. There stood the Headmaster, Professor Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s whole body went numb. Dumbledore was looking unusually grave. He stared down his very crooked nose at them and Harry suddenly found himself wishing he and Ron were still being beaten up by the Whomping Willow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a long silence. Then Dumbledore said, ‘Please explain why you did this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It would have been better if he had shouted. Harry hated the disappointment in his voice. For some reason, he was unable to look Dumbledore in the eyes, and spoke instead to his knees. He told Dumbledore everything except that Mr Weasley owned the bewitched car, making it sound as though he and Ron had happened to find a flying car parked outside the station. He knew Dumbledore would see through this at once, but Dumbledore asked no questions about the car. When Harry had finished, he merely continued to peer at them through his spectacles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll go and get our stuff,’ said Ron in a hopeless sort of voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you talking about, Weasley?’ barked Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, you’re expelling us, aren’t you?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked quickly at Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not today, Mr Weasley,’ said Dumbledore. ‘But I must impress upon both of you the seriousness of what you have done. I will be writing to both your families tonight. I must also warn you that if you do anything like this again, I will have no choice but to expel you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape looked as though Christmas had been cancelled. He cleared his throat and said, ‘Professor Dumbledore, these boys have flouted the Decree for the Restriction of Underage Wizardry, caused serious damage to an old and valuable tree … surely acts of this nature …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It will be for Professor McGonagall to decide on these boys’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">punishments, Severus,’ said Dumbledore calmly. ‘They are in her house and are therefore her responsibility.’ He turned to Professor McGonagall. ‘I must go back to the feast, Minerva, I’ve got to give out a few notices. Come, Severus, there’s a delicious-looking cus-tard tart I want to sample.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape shot a look of pure venom at Harry and Ron as he allowed himself to be swept out of his office, leaving them alone </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Whomping Willow 65 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">with Professor McGonagall, who was still eyeing them like a wrathful eagle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d better get along to the hospital wing, Weasley, you’re bleeding.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not much,’ said Ron, hastily wiping the cut over his eye with his sleeve. ‘Professor, I wanted to watch my sister being Sorted –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Sorting Ceremony is over,’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your sister is also in Gryffindor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, good,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And speaking of Gryffindor –’ Professor McGonagall said sharply, but Harry cut in: ‘Professor, when we took the car, term hadn’t started, so – so Gryffindor shouldn’t really have points taken from it, should it?’ he finished, watching her anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall gave him a piercing look, but he was sure she had almost smiled. Her mouth looked less thin, anyway. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I will not take any points from Gryffindor,’ she said, and Harry’s heart lightened considerably. ‘But you will both get a detention.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was better than Harry had expected. As for Dumbledore’s writing to the Dursleys, that was nothing. Harry knew perfectly well they’d just be disappointed that the Whomping Willow hadn’t squashed him flat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall raised her wand again and pointed it at Snape’s desk. A large plate of sandwiches, two silver goblets and a jug of iced pumpkin juice appeared with a  <i class=\"calibre4\">pop. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You will eat in here and then go straight up to your dormitory,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">she said. ‘I must also return to the feast.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When the door had closed behind her, Ron let out a long, low whistle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I thought we’d had it,’ he said, grabbing a sandwich. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So did I,’ said Harry, taking one too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you believe our luck, though?’ said Ron thickly through a mouthful of chicken and ham. ‘Fred and George must’ve flown that car five or six times and no Muggle ever saw  <i class=\"calibre4\">them. </i>’ He swallowed and took another huge bite. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Why</i> couldn’t we get through the barrier?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shrugged. ‘We’ll have to watch our step from now on, though,’ he said, taking a grateful swig of pumpkin juice. ‘Wish we could’ve gone up to the feast …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She didn’t want us showing off,’ said Ron sagely. ‘Doesn’t want </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>66 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">people to think it’s clever, arriving by flying car.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they had eaten as many sandwiches as they could (the plate kept re-filling itself) they rose and left the office, treading the familiar path to Gryffindor Tower. The castle was quiet; it seemed that the feast was over. They walked past muttering portraits and creaking suits of armour, and climbed narrow flights of stone stairs, until at last they reached the passage where the secret entrance to Gryffindor Tower was hidden, behind an oil painting of a very fat woman in a pink silk dress. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Password?’ she said, as they approached. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er –’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They didn’t know the new year’s password, not having met a Gryffindor Prefect yet, but help came almost immediately; they heard hurrying feet behind them and turned to see Hermione dashing towards them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">There</i> you are! Where have you  <i class=\"calibre4\">been? </i> The most  <i class=\"calibre4\">ridiculous</i> rumours – someone said you’d been expelled for crashing a flying <i class=\"calibre4\">car. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, we haven’t been expelled,’ Harry assured her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re not telling me you  <i class=\"calibre4\">did</i> fly here?’ said Hermione, sounding almost as severe as Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Skip the lecture,’ said Ron impatiently, ‘and tell us the new password.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s “wattlebird”,’ said Hermione impatiently, ‘but that’s not the point –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Her words were cut short, however, as the portrait of the fat lady swung open and there was a sudden storm of clapping. It looked as though the whole of Gryffindor house was still awake, packed into the circular common room, standing on the lop-sided tables and squashy armchairs, waiting for them to arrive. Arms reached through the portrait hole to pull Harry and Ron inside, leaving Hermione to scramble in after them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Brilliant!’ yelled Lee Jordan. ‘Inspired! What an entrance! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flying a car right into the Whomping Willow, people’ll be talking about that one for years!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good on you,’ said a fifth-year Harry had never spoken to; someone was patting him on the back as though he’d just won a marathon. Fred and George pushed their way to the front of the crowd and said together, ‘Why couldn’t you’ve called us back, eh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was scarlet in the face, grinning embarrassedly, but Harry </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Whomping Willow 67 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">could see one person who didn’t look happy at all. Percy was visible over the heads of some excited first-years, and he seemed to be trying to get near enough to start telling them off. Harry nudged Ron in the ribs and nodded in Percy’s direction. Ron got the point at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Got to get upstairs – bit tired,’ he said, and the two of them started pushing their way towards the door on the other side of the room, which led to a spiral staircase and the dormitories. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Night,’ Harry called back to Hermione, who was wearing a scowl just like Percy’s. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They managed to get to the other side of the common room, still having their backs slapped, and gained the peace of the staircase. They hurried up it, right to the top, and at last reached the door of their old dormitory, which now had a sign on it saying </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘second-years’. They entered the familiar, circular room, with its five four-posters hung with red velvet and its high, narrow windows. Their trunks had been brought up for them and placed at the ends of their beds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron grinned guiltily at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know I shouldn’t’ve enjoyed that or anything, but –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The dormitory door flew open and in came the other second-year Gryffindor boys, Seamus Finnigan, Dean Thomas and Neville Longbottom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Unbelievable! </i>’ beamed Seamus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Cool,’ said Dean. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Amazing,’ said Neville, awestruck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t help it. He grinned, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER SIX — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Gilderoy Lockhart</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The next day, however, Harry barely grinned once. Things started to go downhill from breakfast in the Great Hall. The four long house tables were laden with tureens of porridge, plates of kip-pers, mountains of toast and dishes of eggs and bacon, beneath the enchanted ceiling (today, a dull, cloudy grey). Harry and Ron sat down at the Gryffindor table next to Hermione, who had her copy of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Voyages with Vampires</i> propped open against a milk jug. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a slight stiffness in the way she said ‘Morning’ which told Harry that she was still disapproving of the way they had arrived. Neville Longbottom, on the other hand, greeted them cheerfully. Neville was a round-faced and accident-prone boy with the worst memory of anyone Harry had ever met. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Post’s due any minute – I think Gran’s sending on a few things I forgot.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had only just started his porridge when, sure enough, there was a rushing sound overhead and a hundred or so owls streamed in, circling the Hall and dropping letters and packages into the chattering crowd. A big, lumpy parcel bounced off Neville’s head, and a second later, something large and grey fell into Hermione’s jug, spraying them all with milk and feathers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Errol! </i>’ said Ron, pulling the bedraggled owl out by the feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Errol slumped, unconscious, onto the table, his legs in the air and a damp red envelope in his beak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh no –’ Ron gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s all right, he’s still alive,’ said Hermione, prodding Errol gently with the tip of her finger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not that – it’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">that. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was pointing at the red envelope. It looked quite ordinary to Harry, but Ron and Neville were both looking at it as though they expected it to explode. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart 69 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the matter?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She’s – she’s sent me a Howler,’ said Ron faintly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d better open it, Ron,’ said Neville, in a timid whisper. ‘It’ll be worse if you don’t. My Gran sent me one once, and I ignored it and –’ he gulped, ‘it was horrible.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked from their petrified faces to the red envelope. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s a Howler?’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Ron’s whole attention was fixed on the letter, which had begun to smoke at the corners. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Open it,’ Neville urged. ‘It’ll all be over in a few minutes …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron stretched out a shaking hand, eased the envelope from Errol’s beak and slit it open. Neville stuffed his fingers in his ears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A split second later, Harry knew why. He thought for a moment it <i class=\"calibre4\">had</i> exploded; a roar of sound filled the huge Hall, shaking dust from the ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘…   <i class=\"calibre4\">STEALING THE CAR, I WOULDN’T HAVE BEEN SURPRISED IF THEY’D EXPELLED YOU, YOU WAIT TILL I GET  </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">HOLD OF YOU, I DON’T SUPPOSE YOU STOPPED TO THINK </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">WHAT YOUR FATHER AND I WENT THROUGH WHEN WE SAW </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">IT HAD GONE</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley’s yells, a hundred times louder than usual, made the plates and spoons rattle on the table, and echoed deafeningly off the stone walls. People throughout the Hall were swivelling around to see who had received the Howler and Ron sank so low in his chair that only his crimson forehead could be seen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘…   <i class=\"calibre4\">LETTER FROM DUMBLEDORE LAST NIGHT, I THOUGHT </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">YOUR FATHER WOULD DIE OF SHAME, WE DIDN’T BRING YOU </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">UP TO BEHAVE LIKE THIS, YOU AND HARRY COULD BOTH </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">HAVE DIED</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had been wondering when his name was going to crop up.  He  tried  very  hard  to  look  as  though  he  couldn’t  hear  the voice that was making his eardrums throb. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘…   <i class=\"calibre4\">ABSOLUTELY DISGUSTED, YOUR FATHER’S FACING AN </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">INQUIRY AT WORK, IT’S ENTIRELY YOUR FAULT AND IF YOU </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">PUT ANOTHER TOE OUT OF LINE WE’LL BRING YOU </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\"> </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">STRAIGHT BACK HOME. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A ringing silence fell. The red envelope, which had dropped from Ron’s hand, burst into flames and curled into ashes. Harry and Ron sat stunned, as though a tidal wave had just passed over them. A few people laughed and gradually, a babble of talk broke </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>70 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">out again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione closed  <i class=\"calibre4\">Voyages with Vampires</i> and looked down at the top of Ron’s head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I don’t know what you expected, Ron, but you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t tell me I deserved it,’ snapped Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pushed his porridge away. His insides were burning with guilt. Mr Weasley was facing an inquiry at work. After all Mr and Mrs Weasley had done for him over the summer … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he had no time to dwell on this; Professor McGonagall was moving along the Gryffindor table, handing out timetables. Harry took his, and saw that they had double Herbology with the Hufflepuffs first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione left the castle together, crossed the vegetable patch and made for the greenhouses, where the magical plants were kept. At least the Howler had done one good thing: Hermione seemed to think they had now been punished enough and was being perfectly friendly again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As they neared the greenhouses they saw the rest of the class standing outside, waiting for Professor Sprout. Harry, Ron and Hermione had only just joined them when she came striding into view across the lawn, accompanied by Gilderoy Lockhart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Sprout’s arms were full of bandages, and with another twinge of guilt, Harry spotted the Whomping Willow in the distance, several of its branches now in slings. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Sprout was a squat little witch who wore a patched hat over her flyaway hair; there was usually a large amount of earth on her clothes, and her fingernails would have made Aunt Petunia faint. Gilderoy Lockhart, however, was immaculate in sweeping robes of turquoise, his golden hair shining under a perfectly positioned turquoise hat with gold trimming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, hello there!’ Lockhart called, beaming around at the assembled students. ‘Just been showing Professor Sprout the right way to doctor a Whomping Willow! But I don’t want you running away with the idea that I’m better at Herbology than she is! I just happen to have met several of these exotic plants on my travels …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Greenhouse Three today, chaps!’ said Professor Sprout, who was looking distinctly disgruntled, not at all her usual cheerful self. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a murmur of interest. They had only ever worked in Greenhouse One before – Greenhouse Three housed far more </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart 71 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">interesting and dangerous plants. Professor Sprout took a large key from her belt and unlocked the door. Harry caught a whiff of damp earth and fertiliser, mingling with the heavy perfume of some giant, umbrella-sized flowers dangling from the ceiling. He was about to follow Ron and Hermione inside when Lockhart’s hand shot out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! I’ve been wanting a word – you don’t mind if he’s a couple of minutes late, do you, Professor Sprout?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Judging by Professor Sprout’s scowl, she did mind, but Lockhart said, ‘That’s the ticket,’ and closed the greenhouse door in her face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ said Lockhart, his large white teeth gleaming in the sunlight as he shook his head. ‘Harry, Harry, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Completely nonplussed, Harry said nothing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When I heard – well, of course, it was all my fault. Could have kicked myself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had no idea what he was talking about. He was about to say so when Lockhart went on, ‘Don’t know when I’ve been more shocked. Flying a car to Hogwarts! Well, of course, I knew at once why you’d done it. Stood out a mile. Harry, Harry,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was remarkable how he could show every one of those brilliant teeth even when he wasn’t talking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gave you a taste for publicity, didn’t I?’ said Lockhart. ‘Gave you the  <i class=\"calibre4\">bug. </i> You got onto the front page of the paper with me and you couldn’t wait to do it again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – no, Professor, see –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, Harry, Harry,’ said Lockhart, reaching out and grasping his shoulder. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I understand. </i> Natural to want a bit more once you’ve had that first taste – and I blame myself for giving you that, because it was bound to go to your head – but see here, young man, you can’t start  <i class=\"calibre4\">flying cars</i> to try and get yourself noticed. Just calm down, all right? Plenty of time for all that when you’re older. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Yes, yes, I know what you’re thinking! “It’s all right for him, he’s an internationally famous wizard already!” But when I was twelve, I was just as much of a nobody as you are now. In fact, I’d say I was even more of a nobody! I mean, a few people have heard of you, haven’t they? All that business with He Who Must Not Be Named!’ He glanced at the lightning scar on Harry’s forehead. ‘I know, I know, it’s not quite as good as winning  <i class=\"calibre4\">Witch Weekly</i>’s Most-Charming-Smile Award five times in a row, as I have – but </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>72 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">it’s a  <i class=\"calibre4\">start, </i> Harry, it’s a  <i class=\"calibre4\">start. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gave Harry a hearty wink and strode off. Harry stood stunned for a few seconds, then, remembering he was supposed to be in the greenhouse, he opened the door and slid inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Sprout was standing behind a trestle bench in the centre of the greenhouse. About twenty pairs of different-coloured earmuffs were lying on the bench. When Harry had taken his place between Ron and Hermione, she said, ‘We’ll be re-potting Mandrakes today. Now, who can tell me the properties of the Mandrake?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To nobody’s surprise, Hermione’s hand was first into the air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mandrake, or Mandragora, is a powerful restorative,’ said Hermione, sounding as usual as though she had swallowed the textbook. ‘It is used to return people who have been transfigured or cursed, to their original state.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent. Ten points to Gryffindor,’ said Professor Sprout. ‘The Mandrake  forms  an  essential  part  of  most  antidotes.  It  is  also, however, dangerous. Who can tell me why?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s hand narrowly missed Harry’s glasses as it shot up again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The cry of the Mandrake is fatal to anyone who hears it,’ she said promptly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Precisely. Take another ten points,’ said Professor Sprout. ‘Now, the Mandrakes we have here are still very young.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She pointed to a row of deep trays as she spoke and everyone shuffled forward for a better look. A hundred or so tufty little plants, purplish green in colour, were growing there in rows. They looked quite unremarkable to Harry, who didn’t have the slightest idea what Hermione meant by the ‘cry’ of the Mandrake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone take a pair of earmuffs,’ said Professor Sprout. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a scramble as everyone tried to seize a pair that wasn’t pink and fluffy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When I tell you to put them on, make sure your ears are  <i class=\"calibre4\">completely</i> covered,’ said Professor Sprout. ‘When it is safe to remove them, I will give you the thumbs-up. Right – earmuffs  <i class=\"calibre4\">on. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry snapped the earmuffs over his ears. They shut out sound completely. Professor Sprout put a pink fluffy pair over her own ears, rolled up the sleeves of her robes, grasped one of the tufty plants firmly, and pulled hard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry let out a gasp of surprise that no one could hear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart 73 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Instead of roots, a small, muddy and extremely ugly baby popped out of the earth. The leaves were growing right out of his head. He had pale green, mottled skin, and was clearly bawling at the top of his lungs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Sprout took a large plant pot from under the table and plunged the Mandrake into it, burying him in dark, damp compost until only the tufted leaves were visible. Professor Sprout dusted off her hands, gave them all the thumbs-up and removed her own earmuffs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As our Mandrakes are only seedlings, their cries won’t kill yet,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">she said calmly, as though she’d just done nothing more exciting than water a begonia. ‘However, they  <i class=\"calibre4\">will</i> knock you out for several hours, and as I’m sure none of you want to miss your first day back, make sure your earmuffs are securely in place while you work. I will attract your attention when it is time to pack up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Four to a tray – there is a large supply of pots here – compost in the sacks over there – and be careful of the Venomous Tentacula, it’s teething.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She gave a sharp slap to a spiky, dark red plant as she spoke, making it draw in the long feelers that had been inching sneakily over her shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione were joined at their tray by a curly-haired Hufflepuff boy Harry knew by sight, but had never spoken to. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Justin Finch-Fletchley,’ he said brightly, shaking Harry by the hand. ‘Know who you are, of course, the famous Harry Potter … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and you’re Hermione Granger – always top in everything …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">(Hermione beamed as she had her hand shaken, too) ‘and Ron Weasley. Wasn’t that your flying car?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron didn’t smile. The Howler was obviously still on his mind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That Lockhart’s something, isn’t he?’ said Justin happily, as they began filling their plant pots with dragon-dung compost. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Awfully brave chap. Have you read his books? I’d have died of fear if I’d been cornered in a telephone box by a werewolf, but he stayed cool and – zap – just  <i class=\"calibre4\">fantastic. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My name was down for Eton, you know, I can’t tell you how glad I am I came here instead. Of course, mother was slightly disappointed, but since I made her read Lockhart’s books I think she’s begun to see how useful it’ll be to have a fully trained wizard in the family …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>74 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After that they didn’t have much chance to talk. Their earmuffs were back on and they needed to concentrate on the Mandrakes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Sprout had made it look extremely easy, but it wasn’t. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Mandrakes didn’t like coming out of the earth, but didn’t seem to want to go back into it either. They squirmed, kicked, flailed their sharp little fists and gnashed their teeth; Harry spent ten whole minutes trying to squash a particularly fat one into a pot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">By the end of the class, Harry, like everyone else, was sweaty, aching and covered in earth. They traipsed back to the castle for a quick wash and then the Gryffindors hurried off to Transfiguration. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall’s classes were always hard work, but today was especially difficult. Everything Harry had learned last year seemed to have leaked out of his head during the summer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was supposed to be turning a beetle into a button, but all he managed to do was give his beetle a lot of exercise as it scuttled over the desk top avoiding his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was having far worse problems. He had patched up his wand with some borrowed Spellotape, but it seemed to be damaged beyond repair. It kept crackling and sparking at odd moments, and every time Ron tried to transfigure his beetle it engulfed him in thick grey smoke which smelled of rotten eggs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Unable to see what he was doing, Ron accidentally squashed his beetle with his elbow and had to ask for a new one. Professor McGonagall wasn’t pleased. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was relieved to hear the lunch bell. His brain felt like a wrung sponge. Everyone filed out of the classroom except him and Ron, who was whacking his wand furiously on the desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stupid … useless … thing …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Write home for another one,’ Harry suggested, as the wand let off a volley of bangs like a firecracker. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh yeah, and get another Howler back,’ said Ron, stuffing the now hissing wand into his bag. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">It’s your own fault your wand got</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">snapped</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They went down to lunch, where Ron’s mood was not improved by Hermione showing them the handful of perfect coat buttons she had produced in Transfiguration. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’ve we got this afternoon?’ said Harry, hastily changing the subject. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Defence Against the Dark Arts,’ said Hermione at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart 75 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Why</i>,’ demanded Ron, seizing her timetable, ‘have you outlined all Lockhart’s lessons in little hearts?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione snatched the timetable back, flushing furiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They finished lunch and went outside into the overcast courtyard. Hermione sat down on a stone step and buried her nose in <i class=\"calibre4\">Voyages with Vampires</i> again. Harry and Ron stood talking about Quidditch for several minutes before Harry became aware that he was being closely watched. Looking up, he saw the very small, mousey-haired boy he’d seen trying on the Sorting Hat last night, staring at Harry as though transfixed. He was clutching what looked like an ordinary Muggle camera, and the moment Harry looked at him, he went bright red. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, Harry? I’m – I’m Colin Creevey,’ he said breathlessly, taking a tentative step forward. ‘I’m in Gryffindor, too. D’you think – would it be all right if – can I have a picture?’ he said, raising the camera hopefully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A picture?’ Harry repeated blankly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So I can prove I’ve met you,’ said Colin Creevey eagerly, edging further forwards. ‘I know all about you. Everyone’s told me. About how you survived when You Know Who tried to kill you and how he disappeared and everything and how you’ve still got a lightning scar on your forehead’ (his eyes raked Harry’s hairline), ‘and a boy in my dormitory said if I develop the film in the right potion, the pictures’ll  <i class=\"calibre4\">move. </i>’ Colin drew a great shuddering breath of excitement and said, ‘It’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">brilliant</i> here, isn’t it? I never knew all the odd stuff I could do was magic till I got the letter from Hogwarts. My dad’s a milkman, he couldn’t believe it either. So I’m taking loads of pictures to send home to him. And it’d be really good if I had one of you –’ he looked imploringly at Harry, ‘– </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">maybe your friend could take it and I could stand next to you? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then, could you sign it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Signed photos? </i> You’re giving out  <i class=\"calibre4\">signed photos, </i> Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Loud and scathing, Draco Malfoy’s voice echoed around the courtyard. He had stopped right behind Colin, flanked, as he always was at Hogwarts, by his large and thuggish cronies, Crabbe and Goyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone queue up!’ Malfoy roared to the crowd. ‘Harry Potter’s giving out signed photos!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I’m not,’ said Harry angrily, his fists clenching. ‘Shut up, Malfoy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>76 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re just jealous,’ piped up Colin, whose entire body was about as thick as Crabbe’s neck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Jealous? </i>’ said Malfoy, who didn’t need to shout any more; half the courtyard was listening in. ‘Of what? I don’t want a foul scar right across my head, thanks. I don’t think getting your head cut open makes you that special, myself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle were sniggering stupidly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eat slugs, Malfoy,’ said Ron angrily. Crabbe stopped laughing and started rubbing his conker-like knuckles in a menacing way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Be careful, Weasley,’ sneered Malfoy. ‘You don’t want to start any trouble or your mummy’ll have to come and take you away from school.’ He put on a shrill, piercing voice. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">If you put another</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">toe out of line </i>–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A knot of Slytherin fifth-years nearby laughed loudly at this. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Weasley would like a signed photo, Potter,’ smirked Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’d be worth more than his family’s whole house.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron whipped out his Spellotaped wand, but Hermione shut <i class=\"calibre4\">Voyages with Vampires</i> with a snap and whispered, ‘Look out!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s all this, what’s all this?’ Gilderoy Lockhart was striding towards them, his turquoise robes swirling behind him. ‘Who’s giving out signed photos?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry started to speak but he was cut short as Lockhart flung an arm around his shoulders and thundered jovially, ‘Shouldn’t have asked! We meet again, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pinned to Lockhart’s side and burning with humiliation, Harry saw Malfoy slide smirking back into the crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on then, Mr Creevey,’ said Lockhart, beaming at Colin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A double portrait, can’t say fairer than that, and we’ll  <i class=\"calibre4\">both</i> sign it for you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Colin fumbled for his camera and took the picture as the bell rang behind them, signalling the start of afternoon classes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Off you go, move along there,’ Lockhart called to the crowd, and he set off back to the castle with Harry, who was wishing he knew a good vanishing spell, still clasped to his side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A word to the wise, Harry,’ said Lockhart paternally as they entered the building through a side door. ‘I covered up for you back there with young Creevey – if he was photographing me, too, your schoolfellows won’t think you’re setting yourself up so much …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Deaf to Harry’s stammers, Lockhart swept him down a corridor </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart 77 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">lined with staring students and up a staircase. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me just say that handing out signed pictures at this stage of your career isn’t sensible – looks a tad bigheaded, Harry, to be frank. There may well come a time when, like me, you’ll need to keep a stack handy wherever you go, but –’ he gave a little chor-tle, ‘I don’t think you’re quite there yet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had reached Lockhart’s classroom and he let Harry go at last. Harry yanked his robes straight and headed for a seat at the very back of the class, where he busied himself with piling all seven of Lockhart’s books in front of him, so that he could avoid looking at the real thing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rest of the class came clattering in and Ron and Hermione sat down on either side of Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You could’ve fried an egg on your face,’ said Ron. ‘You’d better hope Creevey doesn’t meet Ginny, they’ll be starting a Harry Potter fan club.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up,’ snapped Harry. The last thing he needed was for Lockhart to hear the phrase ‘Harry Potter fan club’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When the whole class was seated, Lockhart cleared his throat loudly and silence fell. He reached forward, picked up Neville Longbottom’s copy of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Travels with Trolls</i> and held it up to show his own, winking portrait on the front. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Me,’ he said, pointing at it and winking as well, ‘Gilderoy Lockhart, Order of Merlin, Third Class, Honorary Member of the Dark Force Defence League and five times winner of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Witch</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Weekly</i>’s Most-Charming-Smile Award – but I don’t talk about that. I didn’t get rid of the Bandon Banshee by  <i class=\"calibre4\">smiling</i> at her!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He waited for them to laugh; a few people smiled weakly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see you’ve all bought a complete set of my books – well done. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I thought we’d start today with a little quiz. Nothing to worry about – just to check how well you’ve read them, how much you’ve taken in …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When he had handed out the test papers he returned to the front of the class and said, ‘You have thirty minutes. Start –  <i class=\"calibre4\">now! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked down at his paper and read: <i class=\"calibre4\">1.  What is Gilderoy Lockhart’s favourite colour? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">2.  What is Gilderoy Lockhart’s secret ambition? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">3.  What, in your opinion, is Gilderoy Lockhart’s greatest achieve-ment to date? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>78 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On and on it went, over three sides of paper, right down to: <i class=\"calibre4\">54. When is Gilderoy Lockhart’s birthday, and what would his</i> <i class=\"calibre4\"> ideal gift be? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Half an hour later, Lockhart collected in the papers and rifled through them in front of the class. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tut, tut – hardly any of you remembered that my favourite colour is lilac. I say so in  <i class=\"calibre4\">Year with a Yeti. </i> And a few of you need to read  <i class=\"calibre4\">Wanderings with Werewolves</i> more carefully – I clearly state in chapter twelve that my ideal birthday gift would be harmony between all magic and non-magic peoples – though I wouldn’t say no to a large bottle of Ogden’s Old Firewhisky!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gave them another roguish wink. Ron was now staring at Lockhart with an expression of disbelief on his face; Seamus Finnigan and Dean Thomas, who were sitting in front, were shaking with silent laughter. Hermione, on the other hand, was listening to Lockhart with rapt attention, and gave a start when he mentioned her name. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… but Miss Hermione Granger knew my secret ambition is to rid the world of evil and market my own range of hair-care potions – good girl! In fact –’ he flipped her paper over, ‘full marks! Where is Miss Hermione Granger?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione raised a trembling hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent!’ beamed Lockhart. ‘Quite excellent! Take ten points for Gryffindor! And so, to business …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He bent down behind his desk and lifted a large, covered cage onto it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now – be warned! It is my job to arm you against the foulest creatures known to wizardkind! You may find yourselves facing your worst fears in this room. Know only that no harm can befall you whilst I am here. All I ask is that you remain calm.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In spite of himself, Harry leaned around his pile of books for a better look at the cage. Lockhart placed a hand on the cover. Dean and Seamus had stopped laughing now. Neville was cowering in his front-row seat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I must ask you not to scream,’ said Lockhart in a low voice. ‘It might provoke them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the whole class held its breath, Lockhart whipped off the cover. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart 79 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ he said dramatically. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Freshly caught Cornish pixies</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Seamus Finnigan couldn’t control himself. He let out a snort of laughter which even Lockhart couldn’t mistake for a scream of terror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes?’ he smiled at Seamus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, they’re not – they’re not very –  <i class=\"calibre4\">dangerous, </i> are they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Seamus choked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be so sure!’ said Lockhart, waggling a finger annoyingly at Seamus. ‘Devilish tricky little blighters they can be!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The pixies were electric blue and about eight inches high, with pointed faces and voices so shrill it was like listening to a lot of budgies arguing. The moment the cover had been removed, they had started jabbering and rocketing around, rattling the bars and pulling bizarre faces at the people nearest them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right then,’ Lockhart said loudly. ‘Let’s see what you make of them!’ And he opened the cage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was pandemonium. The pixies shot in every direction like rockets. Two of them seized Neville by the ears and lifted him into the air. Several shot straight through the window, showering the back row with broken glass. The rest proceeded to wreck the classroom more effectively than a rampaging rhino. They grabbed ink bottles and sprayed the class with them, shredded books and papers, tore pictures from the walls, upended the waste bin, grabbed bags and books and threw them out of the smashed window; within minutes, half the class was sheltering under desks and Neville was swinging from the candelabra in the ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on now, round them up, round them up, they’re only pixies …’ Lockhart shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He rolled up his sleeves, brandished his wand and bellowed, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Peskipiksi Pesternomi! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It had absolutely no effect; one of the pixies seized Lockhart’s wand and threw it out of the window, too. Lockhart gulped and dived under his own desk, narrowly avoiding being squashed by Neville, who fell a second later as the candelabra gave way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The bell rang and there was a mad rush towards the exit. In the relative calm that followed, Lockhart straightened up, caught sight of Harry, Ron and Hermione, who were almost at the door, and said, ‘Well, I’ll ask you three to just nip the rest of them back into their cage.’ He swept past them and shut the door quickly behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>80 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you  <i class=\"calibre4\">believe</i> him?’ roared Ron, as one of the remaining pixies bit him painfully on the ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He just wants to give us some hands-on experience,’ said Hermione, immobilising two pixies at once with a clever Freezing Charm and stuffing them back into their cage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Hands on? </i>’ said Harry, who was trying to grab a pixie dancing out of reach with its tongue out. ‘Hermione, he didn’t have a clue what he was doing.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rubbish,’ said Hermione. ‘You’ve read his books – look at all those amazing things he’s done …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He  <i class=\"calibre4\">says</i> he’s done,’ Ron muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER SEVEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Mudbloods and Murmurs</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry spent a lot of time over the next few days dodging out of sight whenever he saw Gilderoy Lockhart coming down a corridor. Harder to avoid was Colin Creevey, who seemed to have memorised Harry’s timetable. Nothing seemed to give Colin a bigger thrill than to say, ‘All right, Harry?’ six or seven times a day and hear, ‘Hullo, Colin,’ back, however exasperated Harry sounded when he said it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hedwig was still angry with Harry about the disastrous car journey and Ron’s wand was still malfunctioning, surpassing itself on Friday morning by shooting out of Ron’s hand in Charms and hitting tiny old Professor Flitwick squarely between the eyes, creating a large, throbbing green boil where it had struck. So, with one thing and another, Harry was quite glad to reach the week-end. He, Ron and Hermione were planning to visit Hagrid on Saturday morning. Harry, however, was shaken awake several hours earlier than he would have liked by Oliver Wood, captain of the Gryffindor Quidditch team. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Whassamatter?’ said Harry groggily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quidditch practice!’ said Wood. ‘Come on!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry squinted at the window. There was a thin mist hanging across the pink and gold sky. Now he was awake, he couldn’t understand how he could have slept through the racket the birds were making. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oliver,’ Harry croaked, ‘it’s the crack of dawn.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Exactly,’ said Wood. He was a tall and burly sixth-year and, at the moment, his eyes were gleaming with a mad enthusiasm. ‘It’s part of our new training programme. Come on, grab your broom and let’s go,’ said Wood heartily. ‘None of the other teams have started training yet, we’re going to be first off the mark this year …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Yawning and shivering slightly, Harry climbed out of bed and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>82 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">tried to find his Quidditch robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good man,’ said Wood. ‘Meet you on the pitch in fifteen minutes.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When he’d found his scarlet team robes and pulled on his cloak for warmth, Harry scribbled a note to Ron explaining where he’d gone and went down the spiral staircase to the common room, his Nimbus Two Thousand on his shoulder. He had just reached the portrait hole when there was a clatter behind him and Colin Creevey came dashing down the spiral staircase, his camera swinging madly around his neck and something clutched in his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I heard someone saying your name on the stairs, Harry! Look what I’ve got here! I’ve had it developed, I wanted to show you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked bemusedly at the photograph Colin was brandishing under his nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A moving, black and white Lockhart was tugging hard on an arm Harry recognised as his own. He was pleased to see that his photographic self was putting up a good fight and refusing to be dragged into view. As Harry watched, Lockhart gave up and slumped, panting, against the white edge of the picture. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Will you sign it?’ said Colin eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry flatly, glancing around to check that the room was really deserted. ‘Sorry, Colin, I’m in a hurry – Quidditch practice.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He climbed through the portrait hole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh wow! Wait for me! I’ve never watched a Quidditch game before!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Colin scrambled through the hole after him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’ll be really boring,’ Harry said quickly, but Colin ignored him, his face shining with excitement. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You were the youngest house player in a hundred years, weren’t you, Harry? Weren’t you?’ said Colin, trotting alongside him. ‘You must be brilliant. I’ve never flown. Is it easy? Is that your own broom? Is that the best one there is?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t know how to get rid of him. It was like having an extremely talkative shadow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t really understand Quidditch,’ said Colin breathlessly. ‘Is it true there are four balls? And two of them fly round trying to knock people off their brooms?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry heavily, resigned to explaining the complicated </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mudbloods and Murmurs 83 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">rules of Quidditch. ‘They’re called Bludgers. There are two Beaters on each team, who carry clubs to beat the Bludgers away from their side. Fred and George Weasley are the Gryffindor Beaters.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what are the other balls for?’ Colin asked, tripping down a couple of steps because he was gazing open-mouthed at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, the Quaffle – that’s the biggish red one – is the one that scores goals. Three Chasers on each team throw the Quaffle to each other and try and get it through the goalposts at the end of the pitch – they’re three long poles with hoops on the end.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And the fourth ball –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– is the Golden Snitch,’ said Harry, ‘and it’s very small, very fast and difficult to catch. But that’s what the Seeker’s got to do, because a game of Quidditch doesn’t end until the Snitch has been caught. And whichever team’s Seeker gets the Snitch earns his team an extra hundred and fifty points.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you’re Gryffindor Seeker, aren’t you?’ said Colin in awe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry, as they left the castle and started across the dew-drenched grass. ‘And there’s the Keeper, too. He guards the goalposts. That’s it, really.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Colin didn’t stop questioning Harry all the way down the sloping lawns to the Quidditch pitch, and Harry only shook him off when he reached the changing rooms. Colin called after him in a piping voice, ‘I’ll go and get a good seat, Harry!’ and hurried off to the stands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rest of the Gryffindor team were already in the changing room. Wood was the only person who looked truly awake. Fred and George Weasley were sitting, puffy-eyed and tousle-haired, next to fourth-year Alicia Spinnet, who seemed to be nodding off against the wall behind her. Her fellow Chasers, Katie Bell and Angelina Johnson, were yawning, side by side, opposite them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There you are, Harry, what kept you?’ said Wood briskly. ‘Now, I wanted a quick talk with you all before we actually get onto the pitch, because I spent the summer devising a whole new training programme, which I really think will make all the difference …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood was holding up a large diagram of a Quidditch pitch, on which were drawn many lines, arrows and crosses in different-coloured inks. He took out his wand, tapped the board and the arrows began to wiggle over the diagram like caterpillars. As Wood launched into a speech about his new tactics, Fred Weasley’s head drooped right onto Alicia Spinnet’s shoulder and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>84 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he began to snore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The first board took nearly twenty minutes to explain, but there was another board under that, and a third under that one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sank into a stupor as Wood droned on and on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So,’ said Wood, at long last, jerking Harry from a wistful fan-tasy about what he could be eating for breakfast at this very moment up at the castle, ‘is that clear? Any questions?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve got a question, Oliver,’ said George, who had woken with a start. ‘Why couldn’t you have told us all this yesterday when we were awake?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood wasn’t pleased. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, listen here, you lot,’ he said, glowering at them all, ‘we should have won the Quidditch Cup last year. We’re easily the best team. But unfortunately, owing to circumstances beyond our control …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shifted guiltily in his seat. He had been unconscious in the hospital wing for the final match of the previous year, meaning that Gryffindor had been a player short and had suffered their worst defeat in three hundred years. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood took a moment to regain control of himself. Their last defeat was clearly still torturing him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So, this year, we train harder than ever before … OK, let’s go and put our new theories into practice!’ Wood shouted, seizing his broomstick and leading the way out of the changing rooms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stiff-legged and still yawning, his team followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had been in the changing room so long that the sun was up properly now, although remnants of mist hung over the grass in the stadium. As Harry walked onto the pitch, he saw Ron and Hermione sitting in the stands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aren’t you finished yet?’ called Ron incredulously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Haven’t even started,’ said Harry, looking jealously at the toast and marmalade Ron and Hermione had brought out of the Great Hall. ‘Wood’s been teaching us new moves.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He mounted his broomstick and kicked at the ground, soaring up into the air. The cool morning air whipped his face, waking him far more effectively than Wood’s long talk. It felt wonderful to be back on the Quidditch pitch. He soared right around the stadium at full speed, racing Fred and George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that funny clicking noise?’ called Fred, as they hurtled around the corner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mudbloods and Murmurs 85 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked into the stands. Colin was sitting in one of the highest seats, his camera raised, taking picture after picture, the sound strangely magnified in the deserted stadium. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look this way, Harry! This way!’ he cried shrilly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s that?’ said Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No idea,’ Harry lied, putting on a spurt of speed that took him as far away as possible from Colin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on?’ said Wood, frowning, as he skimmed through the air towards them. ‘Why’s that first-year taking pictures? I don’t like it. He could be a Slytherin spy, trying to find out about our new training programme.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s in Gryffindor,’ said Harry quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And the Slytherins don’t need a spy, Oliver,’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What makes you say that?’ said Wood testily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because they’re here in person,’ said George, pointing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Several people in green robes were walking onto the pitch, broomsticks in their hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t believe it!’ Wood hissed in outrage. ‘I booked the pitch for today! We’ll see about this!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood shot towards the ground, landing rather harder than he meant to in his anger, staggering slightly as he dismounted. Harry, Fred and George followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Flint!’ Wood bellowed at the Slytherin captain. ‘This is our practice time! We got up specially! You can clear off now!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Marcus Flint was even larger than Wood. He had a look of troll-ish cunning on his face as he replied, ‘Plenty of room for all of us, Wood.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Angelina, Alicia and Katie had come over, too. There were no girls on the Slytherin team – who stood, shoulder to shoulder, facing the Gryffindors, leering to a man. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I booked the pitch!’ said Wood, positively spitting with rage. ‘I booked it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,’ said Flint, ‘but I’ve got a specially signed note here from Professor Snape.  <i class=\"calibre4\">I, Professor S. Snape, give the Slytherin team permission to practise today on the Quidditch pitch, owing to the need to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">train their new Seeker</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve got a new Seeker?’ said Wood, distracted. ‘Where?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And from behind the six large figures before them came a sev-enth, smaller boy, smirking all over his pale, pointed face. It was Draco Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>86 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aren’t you Lucius Malfoy’s son?’ said Fred, looking at Malfoy with dislike. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Funny you should mention Draco’s father,’ said Flint, as the whole Slytherin team smiled still more broadly. ‘Let me show you the generous gift he’s made to the Slytherin team.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All seven of them held out their broomsticks. Seven highly polished, brand-new handles and seven sets of fine gold lettering spelling the words ‘Nimbus Two Thousand and One’ gleamed under the Gryffindors’ noses in the early-morning sun. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very latest model. Only came out last month,’ said Flint carelessly, flicking a speck of dust from the end of his own. ‘I believe it outstrips the old Two Thousand series by a considerable amount. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As for the old Cleansweeps,’ he smiled nastily at Fred and George, who were both clutching Cleansweep Fives, ‘sweeps the board with them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">None of the Gryffindor team could think of anything to say for a moment. Malfoy was smirking so broadly his cold eyes were reduced to slits. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh look,’ said Flint. ‘A pitch invasion.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione were crossing the grass to see what was going on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s happening?’ Ron asked Harry. ‘Why aren’t you playing? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And what’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">he</i> doing here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was looking at Malfoy, taking in his Slytherin Quidditch robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m the new Slytherin Seeker, Weasley,’ said Malfoy, smugly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone’s just been admiring the brooms my father’s bought our team.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gaped, open-mouthed, at the seven superb broomsticks in front of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good, aren’t they?’ said Malfoy smoothly. ‘But perhaps the Gryffindor team will be able to raise some gold and get new brooms, too. You could raffle off those Cleansweep Fives, I expect a museum would bid for them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Slytherin team howled with laughter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘At least no one on the Gryffindor team had to  <i class=\"calibre4\">buy</i> their way in,’ said Hermione sharply. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">They</i> got in on pure talent.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The smug look on Malfoy’s face flickered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one asked your opinion, you filthy little Mudblood,’ he spat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mudbloods and Murmurs 87 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knew at once that Malfoy had said something really bad because there was an instant uproar at his words. Flint had to dive in front of Malfoy to stop Fred and George jumping on him, Alicia shrieked, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">How dare you! </i>’ and Ron plunged his hand into his robes, pulled out his wand, yelling, ‘You’ll pay for that one, Malfoy!’ and pointed it furiously under Flint’s arm at Malfoy’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A loud bang echoed around the stadium and a jet of green light shot out of the wrong end of Ron’s wand, hitting him in the stomach and sending him reeling backwards onto the grass. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron! Ron! Are you all right?’ squealed Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron opened his mouth to speak, but no words came out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Instead he gave an almighty belch and several slugs dribbled out of his mouth onto his lap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Slytherin team were paralysed with laughter. Flint was doubled up, hanging on to his new broomstick for support. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy was on all fours, banging the ground with his fist. The Gryffindors were gathered around Ron, who kept belching large, glistening slugs. Nobody seemed to want to touch him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d better get him to Hagrid’s, it’s nearest,’ said Harry to Hermione, who nodded bravely, and the pair of them pulled Ron up by the arms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What happened, Harry? What happened? Is he ill? But you can cure him, can’t you?’ Colin had run down from his seat and was now dancing alongside them as they left the pitch. Ron gave a huge heave and more slugs dribbled down his front. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oooh,’ said Colin, fascinated and raising his camera. ‘Can you hold him still, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of the way, Colin!’ said Harry angrily. He and Hermione supported Ron out of the stadium and across the grounds towards the edge of the Forest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nearly there, Ron,’ said Hermione, as the gamekeeper’s cabin came into view. ‘You’ll be all right in a minute … almost there …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were within twenty feet of Hagrid’s house when the front door opened, but it wasn’t Hagrid who emerged. Gilderoy Lockhart, wearing robes of palest mauve today, came striding out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quick, behind here,’ Harry hissed, dragging Ron behind a nearby bush. Hermione followed, somewhat reluctantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s a simple matter if you know what you’re doing!’ Lockhart was saying loudly to Hagrid. ‘If you need help, you know where I </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>88 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">am! I’ll let you have a copy of my book – I’m surprised you haven’t already got one. I’ll sign one tonight and send it over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Well, goodbye!’ And he strode away towards the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry waited until Lockhart was out of sight, then pulled Ron out of the bush and up to Hagrid’s front door. They knocked urgently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid appeared at once, looking very grumpy, but his expression brightened when he saw who it was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bin wonderin’ when you’d come ter see me – come in, come in </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– thought you mighta bin Professor Lockhart back again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione supported Ron over the threshold, into the one-roomed cabin, which had an enormous bed in one corner, a fire crackling merrily in another. Hagrid didn’t seem perturbed by Ron’s slug problem, which Harry hastily explained as he lowered Ron into a chair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Better out than in,’ he said cheerfully, plonking a large copper basin in front of him. ‘Get ’em all up, Ron.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t think there’s anything to do except wait for it to stop,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Hermione anxiously, watching Ron bend over the basin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s a difficult curse to work at the best of times, but with a broken wand …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was bustling around, making them tea. His boarhound, Fang, was slobbering over Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What did Lockhart want with you, Hagrid?’ Harry asked, scratching Fang’s ears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Givin’ me advice on gettin’ kelpies out of a well,’ growled Hagrid, moving a half-plucked rooster off his scrubbed table and setting down the teapot. ‘Like I don’ know. An’ bangin’ on about some Banshee he banished. If one word of it was true, I’ll eat my kettle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was most unlike Hagrid to criticise a Hogwarts teacher and Harry looked at him in surprise. Hermione, however, said in a voice somewhat higher than usual, ‘I think you’re being a bit unfair. Professor Dumbledore obviously thought he was the best man for the job –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He was the  <i class=\"calibre4\">on’y</i> man for the job,’ said Hagrid, offering them a plate of treacle toffee, while Ron coughed squelchily into his basin. ‘An’ I mean the  <i class=\"calibre4\">on’y</i> one. Gettin’ very difficult ter find anyone fer the Dark Arts job. People aren’t too keen ter take it on, see. They’re startin’ ter think it’s jinxed. No one’s lasted long fer a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mudbloods and Murmurs 89 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">while now. So tell me,’ said Hagrid, jerking his head at Ron, ‘who was he tryin’ ter curse?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy called Hermione something. It must’ve been really bad, because everyone went mad.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It   <i class=\"calibre4\">was</i> bad,’ said Ron hoarsely, emerging over the table top, looking pale and sweaty. ‘Malfoy called her “Mudblood”, Hagrid –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron dived out of sight again as a fresh wave of slugs made their appearance. Hagrid looked outraged. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He didn’!’ he growled at Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He did,’ she said. ‘But I don’t know what it means. I could tell it was really rude, of course …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s about the most insulting thing he could think of,’ gasped Ron, coming back up. ‘Mudblood’s a really foul name for someone who was Muggle-born – you know, non-magic parents. There are some wizards – like Malfoy’s family – who think they’re better than everyone else because they’re what people call pure-blood.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gave a small burp, and a single slug fell into his outstretched hand. He threw it into the basin and continued, ‘I mean, the rest of us know it doesn’t make any difference at all. Look at Neville Longbottom – he’s pure-blood and he can hardly stand a cauldron the right way up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An’ they haven’t invented a spell our Hermione can’t do,’ said Hagrid proudly, making Hermione go a brilliant shade of magenta. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s a disgusting thing to call someone,’ said Ron, wiping his sweaty brow with a shaking hand. ‘Dirty blood, see. Common blood. It’s mad. Most wizards these days are half-blood anyway. If we hadn’t married Muggles we’d’ve died out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He retched and ducked out of sight again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I don’ blame yeh fer tryin’ ter curse him, Ron,’ said Hagrid loudly over the thuds of more slugs hitting the basin. ‘Bu’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">maybe it was a good thing yer wand backfired. ’Spect Lucius Malfoy would’ve come marchin’ up ter school if yeh’d cursed his son. Least yer not in trouble.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry would have pointed out that trouble didn’t come much worse than having slugs pouring out of your mouth, but he couldn’t; Hagrid’s treacle toffee had cemented his jaws together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ said Hagrid suddenly, as though struck by a sudden thought, ‘gotta bone ter pick with yeh. I’ve heard you’ve bin givin’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">out signed photos. How come I haven’t got one?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Furious, Harry wrenched his teeth apart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>90 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have  <i class=\"calibre4\">not</i> been giving out signed photos,’ he said hotly. ‘If Lockhart’s still putting that about –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But then he saw that Hagrid was laughing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m on’y jokin’,’ he said, patting Harry genially on the back and sending him, face first, into the table. ‘I knew yeh hadn’t really. I told Lockhart yeh didn’ need teh. Yer more famous than him without tryin’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bet he didn’t like that,’ said Harry, sitting up and rubbing his chin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’ think he did,’ said Hagrid, his eyes twinkling. ‘An’ then I told him I’d never read one o’ his books an’ he decided ter go. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Treacle toffee, Ron?’ he added, as Ron re-appeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No thanks,’ said Ron weakly. ‘Better not risk it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come an’ see what I’ve bin growin’,’ said Hagrid, as Harry and Hermione finished the last of their tea. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In the small vegetable patch behind Hagrid’s house were a dozen of the largest pumpkins Harry had ever seen. Each was the size of a large boulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gettin’ on well, aren’t they?’ said Hagrid happily. ‘Fer the Hallowe’en feast … should be big enough by then.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’ve you been feeding them?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid looked over his shoulder to check that they were alone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I’ve bin givin’ them – you know – a bit o’ help.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry noticed Hagrid’s flowery pink umbrella leaning against the back wall of the cabin. Harry had had reason to believe before now that this umbrella was not all it looked; in fact, he had the strong impression that Hagrid’s old school wand was concealed inside it. Hagrid wasn’t supposed to use magic. He had been expelled from Hogwarts in his third year, but Harry had never found out why – any mention of the matter and Hagrid would clear his throat loudly and become mysteriously deaf until the subject was changed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An Engorgement Charm, I suppose?’ said Hermione, halfway between disapproval and amusement. ‘Well, you’ve done a good job on them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s what yer little sister said,’ said Hagrid, nodding at Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Met her jus’ yesterday.’ Hagrid looked sideways at Harry, his beard twitching. ‘Said she was jus’ lookin’ round the grounds, but I reckon she was hopin’ she might run inter someone else at my house.’ He winked at Harry. ‘If yeh ask me,  <i class=\"calibre4\">she</i> wouldn’ say no ter a signed –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mudbloods and Murmurs 91 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, shut up,’ said Harry. Ron snorted with laughter and the ground was sprayed with slugs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Watch it!’ Hagrid roared, pulling Ron away from his precious pumpkins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was nearly lunchtime and as Harry had only had one bit of treacle toffee since dawn, he was keen to go back to school to eat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They said goodbye to Hagrid and walked back up to the castle, Ron hiccoughing occasionally, but only bringing up two, very small slugs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had barely set foot in the cool Entrance Hall when a voice rang out. ‘There you are, Potter, Weasley.’ Professor McGonagall was walking towards them, looking stern. ‘You will both do your detentions this evening.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are we doing, Professor?’ said Ron, nervously suppress-ing a burp. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You</i> will be polishing the silver in the trophy room with Mr Filch,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘And no magic, Weasley –  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">elbow grease.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gulped. Argus Filch, the caretaker, was loathed by every student in the school. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you, Potter, will be helping Professor Lockhart answer his fan mail,’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh no – can’t I go and do the trophy room, too?’ said Harry desperately. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly not,’ said Professor McGonagall, raising her eyebrows. ‘Professor Lockhart requested you particularly. Eight o’clock sharp, both of you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron slouched into the Great Hall in states of deepest gloom, Hermione behind them, wearing a  <i class=\"calibre4\">well-you-did-break-school-rules</i> sort of expression. Harry didn’t fancy his shepherd’s pie as much as he’d thought. Both he and Ron felt they’d got the worse deal. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Filch’ll have me there all night,’ said Ron heavily. ‘No magic! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There must be about a hundred cups in that room. I’m no good at Muggle cleaning.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d swap any time,’ said Harry hollowly. ‘I’ve had loads of practice with the Dursleys. Answering Lockhart’s fan mail … he’ll be a nightmare …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Saturday afternoon seemed to melt away, and in what seemed like no time, it was five minutes to eight, and Harry was dragging </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>92 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">his feet along the second-floor corridor to Lockhart’s office. He gritted his teeth and knocked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door flew open at once. Lockhart beamed down at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, here’s the scallywag!’ he said. ‘Come in, Harry, come in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Shining brightly on the walls by the light of many candles were countless framed photographs of Lockhart. He had even signed a few of them. Another large pile lay on his desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can address the envelopes!’ Lockhart told Harry, as though this was a huge treat. ‘This first one’s to Gladys Gudgeon, bless her – huge fan of mine.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The minutes snailed by. Harry let Lockhart’s voice wash over him, occasionally saying, ‘Mmm’ and ‘Right’ and ‘Yeah’. Now and then he caught a phrase like ‘Fame’s a fickle friend, Harry’ or </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Celebrity is as celebrity does, remember that’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The candles burned lower and lower, making the light dance over the many moving faces of Lockhart watching him. Harry moved his aching hand over what felt like the thousandth envelope, writing out Veronica Smethley’s address. It must be nearly time to leave, Harry thought miserably, please let it be nearly time … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then he heard something – something quite apart from the spitting of the dying candles and Lockhart’s prattle about his fans. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a voice, a voice to chill the bone-marrow, a voice of breath-taking, ice-cold venom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Come … come to me … let me rip you … let me tear you … let me</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">kill you </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry gave a huge jump and a large lilac blot appeared on Veronica Smethley’s street. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What? </i>’ he said loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know!’ said Lockhart. ‘Six solid months at the top of the best-seller list! Broke all records!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry frantically. ‘That voice!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry?’ said Lockhart, looking puzzled. ‘What voice?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That – that voice that said – didn’t you hear it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart was looking at Harry in high astonishment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What   <i class=\"calibre4\">are</i> you talking about, Harry? Perhaps you’re getting a little drowsy? Great Scott – look at the time! We’ve been here nearly four hours! I’d never have believed it – the time’s flown, hasn’t it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t answer. He was straining his ears to hear the voice again, but there was no sound now except for Lockhart telling  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mudbloods and Murmurs 93 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">him he mustn’t expect a treat like this every time he got detention. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Feeling dazed, Harry left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It  was  so  late  that  the  Gryffindor  common  room  was  almost empty. Harry went straight up to the dormitory. Ron wasn’t back yet. Harry pulled on his pyjamas, got into bed and waited. Half an hour later, Ron arrived, nursing his right arm and bringing a strong smell of polish into the darkened room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My muscles have all seized up,’ he groaned, sinking on his bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fourteen times he made me buff up that Quidditch Cup before he was satisfied. And then I had another slug attack all over a Special Award for Services to the School. Took ages to shift the slime … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">How was it with Lockhart?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Keeping his voice low so as not to wake Neville, Dean and Seamus, Harry told Ron exactly what he had heard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And Lockhart said he couldn’t hear it?’ said Ron. Harry could see him frowning in the moonlight. ‘D’you think he was lying? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But I don’t get it – even someone invisible would’ve had to open the door.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know,’ said Harry, lying back in his four-poster and staring at the canopy above him. ‘I don’t get it, either.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER EIGHT — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Deathday Party</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">October arrived, spreading a damp chill over the grounds and into the castle. Madam Pomfrey, the matron, was kept busy by a sudden spate of colds among the staff and students. Her Pepperup Potion worked instantly, though it left the drinker smoking at the ears for several hours afterwards. Ginny Weasley, who had been looking peaky, was bullied into taking some by Percy. The steam pouring from under her vivid hair gave the impression that her whole head was on fire. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Raindrops the size of bullets thundered on the castle windows for days on end; the lake rose, the flowerbeds turned into muddy streams and Hagrid’s pumpkins swelled to the size of garden sheds. Oliver Wood’s enthusiasm for regular training sessions, however, was not dampened, which was why Harry was to be found, late one stormy Saturday afternoon a few days before Hallowe’en, returning to Gryffindor Tower, drenched to the skin and splattered with mud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Even aside from the rain and wind it hadn’t been a happy practice session. Fred and George, who had been spying on the Slytherin team, had seen for themselves the speed of those new Nimbus Two Thousand and Ones. They reported that the Slytherin team were no more than seven greenish blurs, shooting through the air like jump-jets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry squelched along the deserted corridor he came across somebody who looked just as preoccupied as he was. Nearly Headless Nick, the ghost of Gryffindor Tower, was staring morosely out of a window, muttering under his breath, ‘… don’t fulfil their requirements … half an inch, if that …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello, Nick,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello, hello,’ said Nearly Headless Nick, starting and looking round. He wore a dashing, plumed hat on his long curly hair, and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Deathday Party 95 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">a tunic with a ruff, which concealed the fact that his neck was almost completely severed. He was pale as smoke, and Harry could see right through him to the dark sky and torrential rain outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You look troubled, young Potter,’ said Nick, folding a transparent letter as he spoke and tucking it inside his doublet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So do you,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,’ Nearly Headless Nick waved an elegant hand, ‘a matter of no importance … it’s not as though I really wanted to join … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">thought I’d apply, but apparently I “don’t fulfil requirements”.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In spite of his airy tone, there was a look of great bitterness on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you would think, wouldn’t you,’ he erupted suddenly, pulling the letter back out of his pocket, ‘that getting hit forty-five times in the neck with a blunt axe would qualify you to join the Headless Hunt?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – yes,’ said Harry, who was obviously supposed to agree. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I mean, nobody wishes more than I do that it had all been quick and clean, and my head had come off properly, I mean, it would have saved me a great deal of pain and ridicule. However …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly Headless Nick shook his letter open and read furiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">‘We can only accept huntsmen whose heads have parted company</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">with their bodies. You will appreciate that it would be impossible</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">otherwise for members to participate in hunt activities such as</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Horseback Head-Juggling and Head Polo. It is with the greatest</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">regret, therefore, that I must inform you that you do not fulfil our</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">requirements. With very best wishes, Sir Patrick Delaney-Podmore.’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fuming, Nearly Headless Nick stuffed the letter away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Half an inch of skin and sinew holding my neck on, Harry! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Most people would think that’s good and beheaded, but oh no, it’s not enough for Sir Properly Decapitated-Podmore.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly Headless Nick took several deep breaths and then said, in a far calmer tone, ‘So – what’s bothering you? Anything I can do?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry. ‘Not unless you know where we can get seven free Nimbus Two Thousand and Ones for our match against Sly–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rest of Harry’s sentence was drowned by a high-pitched mewing from somewhere near his ankles. He looked down and found himself gazing into a pair of lamp-like yellow eyes. It was Mrs Norris, the skeletal grey cat who was used by the caretaker, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>96 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Argus Filch, as a sort of deputy in his endless battle against students. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d better get out of here, Harry,’  said  Nick  quickly.  ‘Filch isn’t in a good mood. He’s got flu and some third-years accidentally plastered frog brains all over the ceiling in dungeon five; he’s been cleaning all morning, and if he sees you dripping mud all over the place …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Harry, backing away from the accusing stare of Mrs Norris, but not quickly enough. Drawn to the spot by the mystery-ous power that seemed to connect him with his foul cat, Argus Filch burst suddenly through a tapestry to Harry’s right, wheezing and looking wildly about for the rule-breaker. There was a thick tartan scarf bound around his head, and his nose was unusually purple. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Filth!’ he shouted, his jowls aquiver, his eyes popping alarm-ingly as he pointed at the muddy puddle that had dripped from Harry’s Quidditch robes. ‘Mess and muck everywhere! I’ve had enough of it, I tell you! Follow me, Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So Harry waved a gloomy goodbye to Nearly Headless Nick, and followed Filch back downstairs, doubling the number of muddy footprints on the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never been inside Filch’s office before; it was a place most students avoided. The room was dingy and windowless, lit by a single oil lamp dangling from the low ceiling. A faint smell of fried fish lingered about the place. Wooden filing cabinets stood around the walls; from their labels, Harry could see that they contained details of every pupil Filch had ever punished. Fred and George Weasley had an entire drawer to themselves. A highly polished collection of chains and manacles hung on the wall behind Filch’s desk. It was common knowledge that he was always begging Dumbledore to let him suspend students by their ankles from the ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch grabbed a quill from a pot on his desk and began shuffling around looking for parchment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dung,’ he muttered furiously, ‘great sizzling dragon bogies … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">frog brains … rat intestines … I’ve had enough of it … make an <i class=\"calibre4\">example</i> … where’s the form … yes …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He retrieved a large roll of parchment from his desk drawer and stretched it out in front of him, dipping his long black quill into the ink pot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Deathday Party 97 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Name</i> … Harry Potter.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Crime</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was only a bit of mud!’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s only a bit of mud to you, boy, but to me it’s an extra hour scrubbing!’ shouted Filch, a drip shivering unpleasantly at the end of his bulbous nose. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Crime</i> … befouling the castle …  <i class=\"calibre4\">suggested</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">sentence</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dabbing at his streaming nose, Filch squinted unpleasantly at Harry, who waited with bated breath for his sentence to fall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But as Filch lowered his quill, there was a great BANG! on the ceiling of the office, which made the oil lamp rattle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘PEEVES!’ Filch roared, flinging down his quill in a transport of rage. ‘I’ll have you this time, I’ll have you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And without a backwards glance at Harry, Filch ran flat-footed from the office, Mrs Norris streaking alongside him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves was the school poltergeist, a grinning, airborne menace who lived to cause havoc and distress. Harry didn’t much like Peeves, but couldn’t help feeling grateful for his timing. Hopefully, whatever Peeves had done (and it sounded as though he’d wrecked something very big this time) would distract Filch from Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Thinking that he should probably wait for Filch to come back, Harry sank into a moth-eaten chair next to the desk. There was only one thing on it apart from his half-completed form: a large, glossy, purple envelope with silver lettering on the front. With a quick glance at the door to check that Filch wasn’t on his way back, Harry picked up the envelope and read: <i class=\"calibre4\">KWIKSPELL</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">A Correspondence Course in</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Beginners’ Magic</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Intrigued, Harry flicked the envelope open and pulled out the sheaf of parchment inside. More curly silver writing on the front page said: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Feel out of step in the world of modern magic? Find yourself</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">making excuses not to perform simple spells? Ever been taunted</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">for your woeful wandwork? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There is an answer! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>98 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Kwikspell is an all-new, fail-safe, quick-result, easy-learn</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">course. Hundreds of witches and wizards have benefited from</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the Kwikspell method! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Madam Z. Nettles of Topsham writes:</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">‘I had no memory for incantations and my potions were a family</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">joke! Now, after a Kwikspell course, I am the centre of attention</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">at parties and friends beg for the recipe of my Scintillation</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Solution!’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Warlock D.J. Prod of Didsbury says:</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">‘My wife used to sneer at my feeble charms but one month into</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">your fabulous Kwikspell course I succeeded in turning her into a</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">yak! Thank you, Kwikspell!’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fascinated, Harry thumbed through the rest of the envelope’s contents. Why on earth did Filch want a Kwikspell course? Did this mean he wasn’t a proper wizard? Harry was just reading ‘Lesson One: Holding Your Wand (Some Useful Tips)’ when shuffling footsteps outside told him Filch was coming back. Stuffing the parchment back into the envelope, Harry threw it back onto the desk just as the door opened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch was looking triumphant. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That vanishing cabinet was extremely valuable!’ he was saying gleefully to Mrs Norris. ‘We’ll have Peeves out this time, my sweet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His eyes fell on Harry and then darted to the Kwikspell envelope which, Harry realised too late, was lying two feet away from where it had started. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch’s pasty face went brick red. Harry braced himself for a tidal wave of fury. Filch hobbled across to his desk, snatched up the envelope and threw it into a drawer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you – did you read –?’ he spluttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ Harry lied quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch’s knobbly hands were twisting together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I thought you’d read my private … not that it’s mine … for a friend … be that as it may … however …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was staring at him, alarmed; Filch had never looked madder. His eyes were popping, a tic was going in one of his pouchy cheeks and the tartan scarf didn’t help. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very well … go … and don’t breathe a word … not that … how-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Deathday Party 99 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ever, if you didn’t read … go now, I have to write up Peeves’ report </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Amazed at his luck, Harry sped out of the office, up the corridor and back upstairs. To escape from Filch’s office without punishment was probably some kind of school record. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! Harry! Did it work?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly Headless Nick came gliding out of a classroom. Behind him, Harry could see the wreckage of a large black and gold cabinet which appeared to have been dropped from a great height. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I persuaded Peeves to crash it right over Filch’s office,’ said Nick eagerly. ‘Thought it might distract him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Was that you?’ said Harry gratefully. ‘Yeah, it worked, I didn’t even get detention. Thanks, Nick!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They set off up the corridor together. Nearly Headless Nick, Harry noticed, was still holding Sir Patrick’s rejection letter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wish there was something I could do for you about the Headless Hunt,’ Harry said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly Headless Nick stopped in his tracks and Harry walked right through him. He wished he hadn’t; it was like stepping through an icy shower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But there  <i class=\"calibre4\">is</i> something you could do for me,’ said Nick excitedly. ‘Harry – would I be asking too much – but no, you wouldn’t want –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What is it?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, this Hallowe’en will be my five hundredth deathday,’ said Nearly Headless Nick, drawing himself up and looking dignified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said Harry, not sure whether he should look sorry or happy about this. ‘Right.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m holding a party down in one of the roomier dungeons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Friends will be coming from all over the country. It would be such an   <i class=\"calibre4\">honour</i> if you would attend. Mr Weasley and Miss Granger would be most welcome too, of course – but I dare say you’d rather go to the school feast?’ He watched Harry on tenterhooks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry quickly, ‘I’ll come –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear boy! Harry Potter, at my Deathday Party! And,’ he hesitated, looking excited, ‘do you think you could  <i class=\"calibre4\">possibly</i> mention to Sir Patrick how  <i class=\"calibre4\">very</i> frightening and impressive you find me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of – of course,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly Headless Nick beamed at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>100 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A Deathday Party?’ said Hermione keenly, when Harry had changed at last and joined her and Ron in the common room. ‘I bet there aren’t many living people who can say they’ve been to one of those – it’ll be fascinating!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why would anyone want to celebrate the day they died?’ said Ron, who was halfway through his Potions homework and grumpy. ‘Sounds dead depressing to me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Rain was still lashing the windows, which were now inky black, but inside, all looked bright and cheerful. The firelight glowed over the countless squashy armchairs where people sat reading, talking, doing homework or, in the case of Fred and George Weasley, trying to find out what would happen if you fed a Filibuster Firework to a Salamander. Fred had ‘rescued’ the brilliant orange, fire-dwelling lizard from a Care of Magical Creatures class and it was now smouldering gently on a table surrounded by a knot of curious people. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was on the point of telling Ron and Hermione about Filch and the Kwikspell course when the Salamander suddenly whizzed into the air, emitting loud sparks and bangs as it whirled wildly round the room. The sight of Percy bellowing himself hoarse at Fred and George, the spectacular display of tangerine stars showering from the Salamander’s mouth, and its escape into the fire, with accompanying explosions, drove both Filch and the Kwikspell envelope from Harry’s mind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">By the time Hallowe’en arrived, Harry was regretting his rash promise to go to the Deathday Party. The rest of the school were happily anticipating their Hallowe’en feast; the Great Hall had been decorated with the usual live bats, Hagrid’s vast pumpkins had been carved into lanterns large enough for three men to sit in and there were rumours that Dumbledore had booked a troupe of dancing skeletons for the entertainment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A promise is a promise,’ Hermione reminded Harry bossily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You  <i class=\"calibre4\">said</i> you’d go to the Deathday Party.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So, at seven o’clock, Harry, Ron and Hermione walked straight past the doorway to the packed Great Hall, which was glittering invitingly with gold plates and candles, and directed their steps instead towards the dungeons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The passageway leading to Nearly Headless Nick’s party had been lined with candles too, though the effect was far from cheer-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Deathday Party 101 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ful: these were long, thin, jet-black tapers, all burning bright blue, casting a dim, ghostly light even over their own living faces. The temperature dropped with every step they took. As Harry shivered and drew his robes tightly around him, he heard what sounded like a thousand fingernails scraping an enormous blackboard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is that supposed to be  <i class=\"calibre4\">music? </i>’ Ron whispered. They turned a corner and saw Nearly Headless Nick standing at a doorway hung with black velvet drapes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear friends,’ he said mournfully, ‘welcome, welcome … so pleased you could come …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He swept off his plumed hat and bowed them inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was an incredible sight. The dungeon was full of hundreds of pearly-white, translucent people, mostly drifting around a crowded dance floor, waltzing to the dreadful, quavering sound of thirty musical saws, played by an orchestra on a black-draped platform. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A chandelier overhead blazed midnight blue with a thousand more black candles. Their breath rose in a mist before them; it was like stepping into a freezer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shall we have a look around?’ Harry suggested, wanting to warm up his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Careful not to walk through anyone,’ said Ron nervously, and they set off around the edge of the dance floor. They passed a group of gloomy nuns, a ragged man wearing chains, and the Fat Friar, a cheerful Hufflepuff ghost, who was talking to a knight with an arrow sticking out of his forehead. Harry wasn’t surprised to see that the Bloody Baron, a gaunt, staring Slytherin ghost covered in silver bloodstains, was being given a wide berth by the other ghosts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh no,’ said Hermione, stopping abruptly. ‘Turn back, turn back, I don’t want to talk to Moaning Myrtle –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who?’ said Harry, as they backtracked quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She haunts the girls’ toilet on the first floor,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She haunts a  <i class=\"calibre4\">toilet? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes. It’s been out of order all year because she keeps having tantrums and flooding the place. I never went in there anyway if I could avoid it, it’s awful trying to go to the loo with her wailing at you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look, food!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On the other side of the dungeon was a long table, also covered in black velvet. They approached it eagerly, but next moment had </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>102 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">stopped in their tracks, horrified. The smell was quite disgusting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Large, rotten fish were laid on handsome silver platters; cakes, burned charcoal black, were heaped on salvers; there was a great maggoty haggis, a slab of cheese covered in furry green mould and, in pride of place, an enormous grey cake in the shape of a tombstone, with tar-like icing forming the words, <i class=\"calibre4\">Sir Nicholas de Mimsy-Porpington  </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">died 31st October, 1492</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry watched, amazed, as a portly ghost approached the table, crouched low and walked through it, his mouth held wide so that it passed through one of the stinking salmon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you taste it if you walk through it?’ Harry asked him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Almost,’ said the ghost sadly, and he drifted away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I expect they’ve let it rot to give it a stronger flavour,’ said Hermione knowledgeably, pinching her nose and leaning closer to look at the putrid haggis. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can we move? I feel sick,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had barely turned around, however, when a little man swooped suddenly from under the table and came to a halt in mid-air before them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello, Peeves,’ said Harry cautiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Unlike the ghosts around them, Peeves the poltergeist was the very reverse of pale and transparent. He was wearing a bright orange party hat, a revolving bow-tie and a broad grin on his wide, wicked face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nibbles?’ he said sweetly, offering them a bowl of peanuts covered in fungus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No thanks,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Heard you talking about poor Myrtle,’ said Peeves, his eyes dancing. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Rude</i> you was about poor Myrtle.’ He took a deep breath and bellowed, ‘OY! MYRTLE!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, no, Peeves, don’t tell her what I said, she’ll be really upset,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione whispered frantically. ‘I didn’t mean it, I don’t mind her </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– er, hello, Myrtle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The squat ghost of a girl had glided over. She had the glummest face Harry had ever seen, half-hidden behind lank hair and thick, pearly spectacles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ she said sulkily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Deathday Party 103 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How are you, Myrtle?’ said Hermione, in a falsely bright voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s nice to see you out of the toilet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Myrtle sniffed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss Granger was just talking about you –’ said Peeves slyly in Myrtle’s ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just saying – saying – how nice you look tonight,’ said Hermione, glaring at Peeves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Myrtle eyed Hermione suspiciously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re making fun of me,’ she said, silver tears welling rapidly in her small, see-through eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – honestly – didn’t I just say how nice Myrtle’s looking?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Hermione, nudging Harry and Ron painfully in the ribs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yeah …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She did …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t lie to me,’ Myrtle gasped, tears now flooding down her face, while Peeves chuckled happily over her shoulder. ‘D’you think I don’t know what people call me behind my back? Fat Myrtle! Ugly Myrtle! Miserable, moaning, moping Myrtle!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve missed out “spotty”,’ Peeves hissed in her ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Moaning Myrtle burst into anguished sobs and fled from the dungeon. Peeves shot after her, pelting her with mouldy peanuts, yelling, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Spotty! Spotty! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, dear,’ said Hermione sadly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly Headless Nick now drifted towards them through the crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Enjoying yourselves?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yes,’ they lied. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not a bad turnout,’ said Nearly Headless Nick proudly. ‘The Wailing Widow came all the way up from Kent … It’s nearly time for my speech, I’d better go and warn the orchestra …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The orchestra, however, stopped playing at that very moment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They, and everyone else in the dungeon, fell silent, looking around in excitement, as a hunting horn sounded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, here we go,’ said Nearly Headless Nick bitterly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the dungeon wall burst a dozen ghost horses, each ridden by a headless horseman. The assembly clapped wildly; Harry started to clap too, but stopped quickly at the sight of Nick’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The horses galloped into the middle of the dance floor and halted, rearing and plunging; a large ghost at the front, whose </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>104 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bearded head was under his arm, blowing the horn, leapt down, lifted his head high in the air so he could see over the crowd (everyone laughed) and strode over to Nearly Headless Nick, squashing his head back onto his neck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nick!’ he roared. ‘How are you? Head still hanging in there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gave a hearty guffaw and clapped Nearly Headless Nick on the shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome, Patrick,’ said Nick stiffly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Live ’uns!’ said Sir Patrick, spotting Harry, Ron and Hermione and giving a huge, fake jump of astonishment, so that his head fell off again (the crowd howled with laughter). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very amusing,’ said Nearly Headless Nick darkly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t mind Nick!’ shouted Sir Patrick’s head from the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Still upset we won’t let him join the Hunt! But I mean to say – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">look at the fellow –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think,’ said Harry hurriedly, at a meaningful look from Nick, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nick’s very – frightening and – er –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ha!’ yelled Sir Patrick’s head. ‘Bet he asked you to say that!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I could have everyone’s attention, it’s time for my speech!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Nearly Headless Nick loudly, striding towards the podium and climbing into an icy-blue spotlight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My late lamented lords, ladies and gentlemen, it is my great sorrow …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But nobody heard much more. Sir Patrick and the rest of the Headless Hunt had just started a game of Head Hockey and the crowd were turning to watch. Nearly Headless Nick tried vainly to recapture his audience, but gave up as Sir Patrick’s head went sail-ing past him to loud cheers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was very cold by now, not to mention hungry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t stand much more of this,’ Ron muttered, his teeth chattering, as the orchestra ground back into action and the ghosts swept back onto the dance floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s go,’ Harry agreed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They backed towards the door, nodding and beaming at anyone who looked at them, and a minute later were hurrying back up the passageway full of black candles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pudding might not be finished yet,’ said Ron hopefully, leading the way towards the steps to the Entrance Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then Harry heard it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… <i class=\"calibre4\"> rip … tear … kill </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Deathday Party 105 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was the same voice, the same cold, murderous voice he had heard in Lockhart’s office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stumbled to a halt, clutching at the stone wall, listening with all his might, looking around, squinting up and down the dimly lit passageway. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, what’re you –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s that voice again – shut up a minute –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… <i class=\"calibre4\"> soo hungry … for so long </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Listen!’ said Harry urgently, and Ron and Hermione froze, watching him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… <i class=\"calibre4\"> kill … time to kill </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The voice was growing fainter. Harry was sure it was moving away – moving upwards. A mixture of fear and excitement gripped him as he stared at the dark ceiling; how could it be moving upwards? Was it a phantom, to whom stone ceilings didn’t matter? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This way,’ he shouted, and he began to run, up the stairs, into the Entrance Hall. It was no good hoping to hear anything here, the babble of talk from the Hallowe’en feast was echoing out of the Great Hall. Harry sprinted up the marble staircase to the first floor, Ron and Hermione clattering behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, what are we –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SHH!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry strained his ears. Distantly, from the floor above, and growing fainter still, he heard the voice: ‘… <i class=\"calibre4\"> I smell blood … I</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">SMELL BLOOD! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His stomach lurched. ‘It’s going to kill someone!’ he shouted, and ignoring Ron and Hermione’s bewildered faces, he ran up the next flight of steps three at a time, trying to listen over his own pounding footsteps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hurtled around the whole of the second floor, Ron and Hermione panting behind him, not stopping until they turned a corner into the last, deserted passage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,  <i class=\"calibre4\">what</i> was that all about?’ said Ron, wiping sweat off his face. ‘I couldn’t hear anything …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione gave a sudden gasp, pointing down the corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Look! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something was shining on the wall ahead. They approached, slowly, squinting through the darkness. Foot-high words had been daubed on the wall between two windows, shimmering in the  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>106 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">light cast by the flaming torches. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">THE CHAMBER OF SECRETS HAS BEEN OPENED. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">ENEMIES OF THE HEIR, BEWARE. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that thing – hanging underneath?’ said Ron, a slight quiver in his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As they edged nearer, Harry almost slipped over: there was a large puddle of water on the floor. Ron and Hermione grabbed him, and they inched towards the message, eyes fixed on a dark shadow beneath it. All three of them realised what it was at once, and leapt backwards with a splash. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Norris, the caretaker’s cat, was hanging by her tail from the torch bracket. She was stiff as a board, her eyes wide and staring. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a few seconds, they didn’t move. Then Ron said, ‘Let’s get out of here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shouldn’t we try and help –’ Harry began awkwardly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Trust me,’ said Ron. ‘We don’t want to be found here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But it was too late. A rumble, as though of distant thunder, told them that the feast had just ended. From either end of the corridor where they stood came the sound of hundreds of feet climbing the stairs, and the loud, happy talk of well-fed people; next moment, students were crashing into the passage from both ends. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The chatter, the bustle, the noise died suddenly as the people in front spotted the hanging cat. Harry, Ron and Hermione stood alone, in the middle of the corridor, as silence fell among the mass of students, pressing forward to see the grisly sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then someone shouted through the quiet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Enemies of the heir, beware! You’ll be next, Mudbloods!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Draco Malfoy. He had pushed to the front of the crowd, his cold eyes alive, his usually bloodless face flushed, as he grinned at the sight of the hanging, immobile cat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER NINE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Writing on the Wall</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on here? What’s going on?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Attracted no doubt by Malfoy’s shout, Argus Filch came shouldering his way through the crowd. Then he saw Mrs Norris and fell back, clutching his face in horror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My cat! My cat! What’s happened to Mrs Norris?’ he shrieked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And his popping eyes fell on Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You! </i>’ he screeched, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You! </i> You’ve murdered my cat! You’ve killed her! I’ll kill you! I’ll –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Argus! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore had arrived on the scene, followed by a number of other teachers. In seconds, he had swept past Harry, Ron and Hermione and detached Mrs Norris from the torch bracket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come with me, Argus,’ he said to Filch. ‘You too, Mr Potter, Mr Weasley, Miss Granger.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart stepped forward eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My office is nearest, Headmaster – just upstairs – please feel free –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, Gilderoy,’ said Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The silent crowd parted to let them pass. Lockhart, looking excited and important, hurried after Dumbledore; so did Professors McGonagall and Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As they entered Lockhart’s darkened office there was a flurry of movement across the walls; Harry saw several of the Lockharts in the pictures dodging out of sight, their hair in rollers. The real Lockhart lit the candles on his desk and stood back. Dumbledore laid Mrs Norris on the polished surface and began to examine her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione exchanged tense looks and sank into chairs outside the pool of candlelight, watching. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The tip of Dumbledore’s long, crooked nose was barely an inch from Mrs Norris’s fur. He was looking at her closely through his </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>108 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">half-moon spectacles, his long fingers gently prodding and poking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall was bent almost as close, her eyes narrowed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape loomed behind them, half in shadow, wearing a most peculiar expression: it was as though he was trying hard not to smile. And Lockhart was hovering around all of them, making suggestions. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was definitely a curse that killed her – probably the Transmogrifian Torture. I’ve seen it used many times, so unlucky I wasn’t there, I know the very counter-curse that would have saved her …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart’s comments were punctuated by Filch’s dry, racking sobs. He was slumped in a chair by the desk, unable to look at Mrs Norris, his face in his hands. Much as he detested Filch, Harry couldn’t help feeling a bit sorry for him, though not nearly as sorry as he felt for himself. If Dumbledore believed Filch, he would be expelled for sure. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore was now muttering strange words under his breath and tapping Mrs Norris with his wand, but nothing happened: she continued to look as though she had been recently stuffed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… I remember something very similar happening in Ouagadougou,’ said Lockhart, ‘a series of attacks, the full story’s in my autobiography. I was able to provide the townsfolk with various amulets which cleared the matter up at once …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The photographs of Lockhart on the walls were all nodding in agreement as he talked. One of them had forgotten to remove his hairnet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last Dumbledore straightened up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She’s not dead, Argus,’ he said softly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart stopped abruptly in the middle of counting the number of murders he had prevented. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not dead?’ choked Filch, looking through his fingers at Mrs Norris. ‘But why’s she all – all stiff and frozen?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She has been Petrified,’ said Dumbledore (‘Ah! I thought so!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Lockhart). ‘But how, I cannot say …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ask  <i class=\"calibre4\">him! </i>’ shrieked Filch, turning his blotched and tear-stained face to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No second-year could have done this,’ said Dumbledore firmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It would take Dark Magic of the most advanced –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He did it, he did it!’ Filch spat, his pouchy face purpling. ‘You </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The  Writing on the Wall 109 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">saw what he wrote on the wall! He found – in my office – he knows I’m a – I’m a –’ Filch’s face worked horribly. ‘He knows I’m a Squib!’ he finished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I never  <i class=\"calibre4\">touched</i> Mrs Norris!’ Harry said loudly, uncomfortably aware of everyone looking at him, including all the Lockharts on the walls. ‘And I don’t even know what a Squib  <i class=\"calibre4\">is. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rubbish!’ snarled Filch. ‘He saw my Kwikspell letter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I might speak, Headmaster,’ said Snape from the shadows, and Harry’s sense of foreboding increased; he was sure nothing Snape had to say was going to do him any good. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter and his friends may have simply been in the wrong place at the wrong time,’ he said, a slight sneer curling his mouth as though he doubted it, ‘but we do have a set of suspicious circumstances here. Why were they in the upstairs corridor at all? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Why weren’t they at the Hallowe’en feast?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione all launched into an explanation about the Deathday Party, ‘… there were hundreds of ghosts, they’ll tell you we were there –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But why not join the feast afterwards?’ said Snape, his black eyes glittering in the candlelight. ‘Why go up to that corridor?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione looked at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because – because –’ Harry said, his heart thumping very fast; something told him it would sound very far-fetched if he told them he had been led there by a bodiless voice no one but he could hear, ‘because we were tired and wanted to go to bed,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Without any supper?’ said Snape, a triumphant smile flickering across his gaunt face. ‘I didn’t think ghosts provided food fit for living people at their parties.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We weren’t hungry,’ said Ron loudly, as his stomach gave a huge rumble. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s nasty smile widened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I suggest, Headmaster, that Potter is not being entirely truth-ful,’ he said. ‘It might be a good idea if he were deprived of certain privileges until he is ready to tell us the whole story. I personally feel he should be taken off the Gryffindor Quidditch team until he is ready to be honest.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Really, Severus,’ said Professor McGonagall sharply, ‘I see no reason to stop the boy playing Quidditch. This cat wasn’t hit over the head with a broomstick. There is no evidence at all that Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>110 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">has done anything wrong.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore was giving Harry a searching look. His twinkling light-blue gaze made Harry feel as though he was being X-rayed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Innocent until proven guilty, Severus,’ he said firmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape looked furious. So did Filch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My cat has been Petrified!’ he shrieked, his eyes popping. ‘I want to see some  <i class=\"calibre4\">punishment! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We will be able to cure her, Argus,’ said Dumbledore patiently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Sprout recently managed to procure some Mandrakes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As soon as they have reached their full size, I will have a potion made which will revive Mrs Norris.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll make it,’ Lockhart butted in. ‘I must have done it a hundred times, I could whip up a Mandrake Restorative Draught in my sleep –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excuse me,’ said Snape icily, ‘but I believe I am the Potions master at this school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a very awkward pause. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You may go,’ Dumbledore said to Harry, Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They went, as quickly as they could without actually running. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they were a floor up from Lockhart’s office, they turned into an empty classroom and closed the door quietly behind them. Harry squinted at his friends’ darkened faces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think I should have told them about that voice I heard?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Ron, without hesitation. ‘Hearing voices no one else can hear isn’t a good sign, even in the wizarding world.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something in Ron’s voice made Harry ask, ‘You do believe me, don’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Course I do,’ said Ron quickly. ‘But – you must admit it’s weird …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know it’s weird,’ said Harry. ‘The whole thing’s weird. What was that writing on the wall about?  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Chamber has been opened</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… what’s that supposed to mean?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know, it rings a sort of bell,’ said Ron slowly. ‘I think someone told me a story about a secret chamber at Hogwarts once … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">might’ve been Bill …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what on earth’s a Squib?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To his surprise, Ron stifled a snigger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – it’s not funny really – but as it’s Filch …’ he said. ‘A Squib is someone who was born into a wizarding family but hasn’t got any magic powers. Kind of the opposite of Muggle-born wizards, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The  Writing on the Wall 111 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">but Squibs are quite unusual. If Filch’s trying to learn magic from a Kwikspell course, I reckon he must be a Squib. It would explain a lot. Like why he hates students so much.’ Ron gave a satisfied smile. ‘He’s bitter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A clock chimed somewhere. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Midnight,’ said Harry. ‘We’d better get to bed before Snape comes along and tries to frame us for something else.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a few days, the school could talk of little but the attack on Mrs Norris. Filch kept it fresh in everyone’s minds by pacing the spot where she had been attacked, as though he thought the attacker might come back. Harry had seen him scrubbing the message on the wall with ‘Mrs Skower’s All-Purpose Magical Mess Remover’, but to no effect; the words still gleamed as brightly as ever on the stone. When Filch wasn’t guarding the scene of the crime, he was skulking red-eyed through the corridors, lunging out at unsuspecting students and trying to put them in detention for things like ‘breathing loudly’ and ‘looking happy’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny Weasley seemed very disturbed by Mrs Norris’s fate. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">According to Ron, she was a great cat-lover. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you hadn’t really got to know Mrs Norris,’ Ron told her bracingly. ‘Honestly, we’re much better off without her.’ Ginny’s lip trembled. ‘Stuff like this doesn’t often happen at Hogwarts,’ Ron assured her. ‘They’ll catch the nutter who did it and have him out of here in no time. I just hope he’s got time to Petrify Filch before he’s expelled. I’m only joking –’ Ron added hastily, as Ginny blanched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The attack had also had an effect on Hermione. It was quite usual for Hermione to spend a lot of time reading, but she was now doing almost nothing else. Nor could Harry and Ron get much response from her when they asked what she was up to, and not until the following Wednesday did they find out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had been held back in Potions, where Snape had made him stay behind to scrape tubeworms off the desks. After a hurried lunch, he went upstairs to meet Ron in the library, and saw Justin Finch-Fletchley, the Hufflepuff boy from Herbology, coming towards him. Harry had just opened his mouth to say hello when Justin caught sight of him, turned abruptly and sped off in the opposite direction. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry found Ron at the back of the library, measuring his </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>112 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">History of Magic homework. Professor Binns had asked for a three-foot long composition on ‘The Medieval Assembly of European Wizards’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t believe it, I’m still eight inches short …’ said Ron furiously, letting go of his parchment, which sprang back into a roll, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘and Hermione’s done four feet seven inches and her writing’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">tiny. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is she?’ asked Harry, grabbing the tape measure and unrolling his own homework. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Somewhere over there,’ said Ron, pointing along the shelves, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘looking for another book. I think she’s trying to read the whole library before Christmas.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry told Ron about Justin Finch-Fletchley running away from him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno why you care, I thought he was a bit of an idiot,’ said Ron, scribbling away, making his writing as large as possible. ‘All that rubbish about Lockhart being so great –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione emerged from between the bookshelves. She looked irritable and at last seemed ready to talk to them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">All</i> the copies of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Hogwarts: A History</i> have been taken out,’ she said, sitting down next to Harry and Ron. ‘And there’s a two-week waiting list. I  <i class=\"calibre4\">wish</i> I hadn’t left my copy at home, but I couldn’t fit it in my trunk with all the Lockhart books.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why do you want it?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The same reason everyone else wants it,’ said Hermione, ‘to read up on the legend of the Chamber of Secrets.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ said Harry quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s just it. I can’t remember,’ said Hermione, biting her lip. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And I can’t find the story anywhere else –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, let me read your composition,’ said Ron desperately, checking his watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I won’t,’ said Hermione, suddenly severe. ‘You’ve had ten days to finish it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I only need another two inches, go on …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The bell rang. Ron and Hermione led the way to History of Magic, bickering. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">History of Magic was the dullest subject on their timetable. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Binns, who taught it, was their only ghost teacher, and the most exciting thing that ever happened in his classes was his entering the room through the blackboard. Ancient and shriv-elled, many people said he hadn’t noticed he was dead. He had </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The  Writing on the Wall 113 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">simply got up to teach one day and left his body behind him in an armchair in front of the staff-room fire; his routine had not varied in the slightest since. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Today was as boring as ever. Professor Binns opened his notes and began to read in a flat drone like an old vacuum cleaner until nearly everyone in the class was in a deep stupor, occasionally coming round long enough to copy down a name or date, then falling asleep again. He had been speaking for half an hour when something happened that had never happened before. Hermione put up her hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Binns, glancing up in the middle of a deadly dull lecture on the International Warlock Convention of 1289, looked amazed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss – er –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Granger, Professor. I was wondering if you could tell us anything about the Chamber of Secrets,’ said Hermione in a clear voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dean Thomas, who had been sitting with his mouth hanging open, gazing out of the window, jerked out of his trance; Lavender Brown’s head came up off her arms and Neville’s elbow slipped off his desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Binns blinked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My subject is History of Magic,’ he said in his dry, wheezy voice. ‘I deal with  <i class=\"calibre4\">facts, </i> Miss Granger, not myths and legends.’ He cleared his throat with a small noise like chalk snapping and continued, ‘In September of that year, a sub-committee of Sardinian sorcerers –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stuttered to a halt. Hermione’s hand was waving in the air again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss Grant?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, sir, don’t legends always have a basis in fact?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Binns was looking at her in such amazement, Harry was sure no student had ever interrupted him before, alive or dead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Professor Binns slowly, ‘yes, one could argue that, I suppose.’ He peered at Hermione as though he had never seen a student properly before. ‘However, the legend of which you speak is such a very  <i class=\"calibre4\">sensational, </i> even  <i class=\"calibre4\">ludicrous</i> tale …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the whole class was now hanging on Professor Binns’s every word. He looked dimly at them all, every face turned to his. Harry </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>114 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">could tell he was completely thrown by such an unusual show of interest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, very well,’ he said slowly. ‘Let me see … the Chamber of Secrets … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You all know, of course, that Hogwarts was founded over a thousand years ago – the precise date is uncertain – by the four greatest witches and wizards of the age. The four school houses are named after them: Godric Gryffindor, Helga Hufflepuff, Rowena Ravenclaw and Salazar Slytherin. They built this castle together, far from prying Muggle eyes, for it was an age when magic was feared by common people, and witches and wizards suffered much persecution.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He paused, gazed blearily around the room, and continued, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘For a few years, the founders worked in harmony together, seek-ing out youngsters who showed signs of magic and bringing them to the castle to be educated. But then disagreements sprang up between them. A rift began to grow between Slytherin and the others. Slytherin wished to be more  <i class=\"calibre4\">selective</i> about the students admitted to Hogwarts. He believed that magical learning should be kept within all-magic families. He disliked taking students of Muggle parentage, believing them to be untrustworthy. After a while, there was a serious argument on the subject between Slytherin and Gryffindor, and Slytherin left the school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Binns paused again, pursing his lips, looking like a wrinkled old tortoise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Reliable historical sources tell us this much,’ he said, ‘but these honest facts have been obscured by the fanciful legend of the Chamber of Secrets. The story goes that Slytherin had built a hidden chamber in the castle, of which the other founders knew nothing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Slytherin, according to the legend, sealed the Chamber of Secrets so that none would be able to open it until his own true heir arrived at the school. The heir alone would be able to unseal the Chamber of Secrets, unleash the horror within, and use it to purge the school of all who were unworthy to study magic.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was silence as he finished telling the story, but it wasn’t the usual, sleepy silence that filled Professor Binns’s classes. There was unease in the air as everyone continued to watch him, hoping for more. Professor Binns looked faintly annoyed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The whole thing is arrant nonsense, of course,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Naturally, the school has been searched for evidence of such a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The  Writing on the Wall 115 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">chamber, many times, by the most learned witches and wizards. It does not exist. A tale told to frighten the gullible.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s hand was back in the air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sir – what exactly do you mean by the ‘horror within’ the Chamber?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That is believed to be some sort of monster, which the heir of Slytherin alone can control,’ said Professor Binns in his dry, reedy voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The class exchanged nervous looks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I tell you, the thing does not exist,’ said Professor Binns, shuffling his notes. ‘There is no Chamber and no monster.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But, sir,’ said Seamus Finnigan, ‘if the Chamber can only be opened by Slytherin’s true heir, no one else  <i class=\"calibre4\">would</i> be able to find it, would they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nonsense, O’Flaherty,’ said Professor Binns in an aggravated tone. ‘If a long succession of Hogwarts headmasters and head-mistresses haven’t found the thing –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But, Professor,’ piped up Parvati Patil, ‘you’d probably have to use Dark Magic to open it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just because a wizard  <i class=\"calibre4\">doesn’t</i> use Dark Magic, doesn’t mean he <i class=\"calibre4\">can’t, </i> Miss Pennyfeather,’ snapped Professor Binns. ‘I repeat, if the likes of Dumbledore –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But maybe you’ve got to be related to Slytherin, so Dumbledore couldn’t –’ began Dean Thomas, but Professor Binns had had enough. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That will do,’ he said sharply. ‘It is a myth! It does not exist! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There is not a shred of evidence that Slytherin ever built so much as a secret broom cupboard! I regret telling you such a foolish story! We will return, if you please, to  <i class=\"calibre4\">history</i>, to solid, believable, verifiable  <i class=\"calibre4\">fact! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And within five minutes, the class had sunk back into its usual torpor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I always knew Salazar Slytherin was a twisted old loony,’ Ron told Harry and Hermione, as they fought their way through the teem-ing corridors at the end of the lesson to drop off their bags before dinner. ‘But I never knew he started all this pure-blood stuff. I wouldn’t be in his house if you paid me. Honestly, if the Sorting Hat had tried to put me in Slytherin, I’d’ve got the train straight back home …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>116 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione nodded fervently, but Harry didn’t say anything. His stomach had just dropped unpleasantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never told Ron and Hermione that the Sorting Hat had seriously considered putting  <i class=\"calibre4\">him</i>  in  Slytherin.  He  could remember, as though it was yesterday, the small voice that had spoken in his ear when he’d placed the Hat on his head a year before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You could be great, you know, it’s all here in your head, and</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Slytherin would help you on the way to greatness, no doubt about</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">that </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry, who had already heard of Slytherin house’s repute-tion for turning out dark wizards, had thought desperately, ‘Not Slytherin!’ and the Hat had said, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Oh, well, if you’re sure … better be</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Gryffindor </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As they were shunted along in the throng, Colin Creevey went past. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hiya, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hullo, Colin,’ said Harry automatically. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry – Harry – a boy in my class has been saying you’re –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Colin was so small he couldn’t fight against the tide of people bearing him towards the Great Hall; they heard him squeak, ‘See you, Harry!’ and he was gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s a boy in his class saying about you?’ Hermione wondered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That I’m Slytherin’s heir, I expect,’ said Harry, his stomach dropping another inch or so, as he suddenly remembered the way Justin Finch-Fletchley had run away from him at lunchtime. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘People here’ll believe anything,’ said Ron in disgust. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The crowd thinned and they were able to climb the next staircase without difficulty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you   <i class=\"calibre4\">really</i> think there’s a Chamber of Secrets?’ Ron asked Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know,’ she said, frowning. ‘Dumbledore couldn’t cure Mrs Norris, and that makes me think that whatever attacked her might not be – well – human.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As she spoke, they turned a corner and found themselves at the end of the very corridor where the attack had happened. They stopped and looked. The scene was just as it had been that night, except that there was no stiff cat hanging from the torch bracket, and an empty chair stood against the wall bearing the message </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The  Writing on the Wall 117 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Chamber has been opened.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s where Filch has been keeping guard,’ Ron muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They looked at each other. The corridor was deserted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t hurt to have a poke around,’ said Harry, dropping his bag and getting to his hands and knees so that he could crawl along, searching for clues. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scorch marks!’ he said. ‘Here – and here –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come and look at this!’ said Hermione. ‘This is funny …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry got up and crossed to the window next to the message on the wall. Hermione was pointing at the topmost pane, where around twenty spiders were scuttling, apparently fighting to get through a small crack in the glass. A long, silvery thread was dangling like a rope, as though they had all climbed it in their hurry to get outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you ever seen spiders act like that?’ said Hermione wonderingly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry, ‘have you, Ron? Ron?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked over his shoulder. Ron was standing well back, and seemed to be fighting the impulse to run. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – don’t – like – spiders,’ said Ron tensely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I never knew that,’ said Hermione, looking at Ron in surprise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve used spiders in potions loads of times …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t mind them dead,’ said Ron, who was carefully looking anywhere but at the window, ‘I just don’t like the way they move …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione giggled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not funny,’ said Ron, fiercely. ‘If you must know, when I was three, Fred turned my – my teddy bear into a dirty great spider because I broke his toy broomstick. You wouldn’t like them either if you’d been holding your bear and suddenly it had too many legs and …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He broke off, shuddering. Hermione was obviously still trying not to laugh. Feeling they had better get off the subject, Harry said, ‘Remember all that water on the floor? Where did that come from? Someone’s mopped it up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was about here,’ said Ron, recovering himself to walk a few paces past Filch’s chair and pointing. ‘Level with this door.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He reached for the brass doorknob but suddenly withdrew his hand as though he’d been burned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the matter?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>118 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t go in there,’ said Ron gruffly, ‘that’s a girls’ toilet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Ron, there won’t be anyone in there,’ said Hermione, standing up and coming over. ‘That’s Moaning Myrtle’s place. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Come on, let’s have a look.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And ignoring the large ‘Out of Order’ sign, she opened the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was the gloomiest, most depressing bathroom Harry had ever set foot in. Under a large, cracked and spotted mirror were a row of chipped, stone sinks. The floor was damp and reflected the dull light given off by the stubs of a few candles, burning low in their holders; the wooden doors to the cubicles were flaking and scratched and one of them was dangling off its hinges. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione put her fingers to her lips and set off towards the end cubicle. When she reached it she said, ‘Hello, Myrtle, how are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron went to look. Moaning Myrtle was floating on the cistern of the toilet, picking a spot on her chin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is a  <i class=\"calibre4\">girls’</i> bathroom,’ she said, eyeing Ron and Harry suspiciously. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">They’re</i> not girls.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ Hermione agreed. ‘I just wanted to show them how – er – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">nice it is in here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She waved vaguely at the dirty old mirror and the damp floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ask her if she saw anything,’ Harry mouthed at Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you whispering?’ said Myrtle, staring at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ said Harry quickly. ‘We wanted to ask –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wish people would stop talking behind my back!’ said Myrtle, in a voice choked with tears. ‘I  <i class=\"calibre4\">do</i> have feelings, you know, even if I  <i class=\"calibre4\">am</i> dead.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Myrtle, no one wants to upset you,’ said Hermione. ‘Harry only –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one wants to upset me! That’s a good one!’ howled Myrtle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My life was nothing but misery at this place and now people come along ruining my death!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We wanted to ask you if you’d seen anything funny lately,’ said Hermione quickly, ‘because a cat was attacked right outside your front door on Hallowe’en.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you see anyone near here that night?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wasn’t paying attention,’ said Myrtle dramatically. ‘Peeves upset me so much I came in here and tried to  <i class=\"calibre4\">kill</i> myself. Then, of course, I remembered that I’m – that I’m –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Already dead,’ said Ron helpfully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The  Writing on the Wall 119 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Myrtle gave a tragic sob, rose up in the air, turned over and dived head first into the toilet, splashing water all over them and vanishing from sight; from the direction of her muffled sobs, she had come to rest somewhere in the U-bend. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron stood with their mouths open, but Hermione shrugged wearily and said, ‘Honestly, that was almost cheerful for Myrtle … come on, let’s go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had barely closed the door on Myrtle’s gurgling sobs when a loud voice made all three of them jump. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘RON!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy Weasley had stopped dead at the head of the stairs, prefect badge agleam, an expression of complete shock on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s a  <i class=\"calibre4\">girls’</i> bathroom!’ he gasped. ‘What were  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just having a look around,’ Ron shrugged. ‘Clues, you know …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy swelled in a manner that reminded Harry forcefully of Mrs Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get – away – from – there –’ he said, striding towards them and starting to chivvy them along, flapping his arms. ‘Don’t you <i class=\"calibre4\">care</i> what this looks like? Coming back here while everyone’s at dinner …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why shouldn’t we be here?’ said Ron hotly, stopping short and glaring at Percy. ‘Listen, we never laid a finger on that cat!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s what I told Ginny,’ said Percy fiercely, ‘but she still seems to think you’re going to be expelled; I’ve never seen her so upset, crying her eyes out. You might think of  <i class=\"calibre4\">her</i>, all the first-years are thoroughly over-excited by this business –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000001999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You</i> don’t care about Ginny,’ said Ron, whose ears were reddening now. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You’re</i> just worried I’m going to mess up your chances of being Head Boy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Five points from Gryffindor!’ Percy said tersely, fingering his prefect badge. ‘And I hope it teaches you a lesson! No more  <i class=\"calibre4\">detective work, </i> or I’ll write to Mum!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he strode off, the back of his neck as red as Ron’s ears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione chose seats as far as possible from Percy in the common room that night. Ron was still in a very bad temper and kept blotting his Charms homework. When he reached absently for his wand to remove the smudges, it ignited the parchment. Fuming almost as much as his homework, Ron slammed <i class=\"calibre4\">The Standard Book of Spells, Grade 2</i> shut. To Harry’s surprise, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>120 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione followed suit. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who can it be, though?’ she said in a quiet voice, as though continuing a conversation they had just been having. ‘Who’d  <i class=\"calibre4\">want</i> all the Squibs and Muggle-borns out of Hogwarts?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s think,’ said Ron in mock puzzlement. ‘Who do we know who thinks Muggle-borns are scum?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked at Hermione. Hermione looked back, unconvinced. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you’re talking about Malfoy –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course I am!’ said Ron. ‘You heard him: “<i class=\"calibre4\">You’ll be next,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Mudbloods! </i>” Come on, you’ve only got to look at his foul rat face to know it’s him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy, the heir of Slytherin?’ said Hermione sceptically. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at his family,’ said Harry, closing his books, too. ‘The whole lot of them have been in Slytherin, he’s always boasting about it. They could easily be Slytherin’s descendants. His father’s definitely evil enough.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They could’ve had the key to the Chamber of Secrets for cen-turies!’ said Ron. ‘Handing it down, father to son …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Hermione cautiously, ‘I suppose it’s possible …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But how do we prove it?’ said Harry darkly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There might be a way,’ said Hermione slowly, dropping her voice still further with a quick glance across the room at Percy. ‘Of course, it would be difficult. And dangerous, very dangerous. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We’d be breaking about fifty school rules, I expect.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If, in a month or so, you feel like explaining, you will let us know, won’t you?’ said Ron irritably. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right,’ said Hermione coldly. ‘What we’d need to do is to get inside the Slytherin common room and ask Malfoy a few questions without him realising it’s us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But that’s impossible,’ Harry said, as Ron laughed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, it’s not,’ said Hermione. ‘All we’d need would be some Polyjuice Potion.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ said Ron and Harry together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape mentioned it in class a few weeks ago –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think we’ve got nothing better to do in Potions than listen to Snape?’ muttered Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It transforms you into somebody else. Think about it! We could change into three of the Slytherins. No one would know it was us. Malfoy would probably tell us anything. He’s probably boasting about it in the Slytherin common room right now, if only </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The  Writing on the Wall 121 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">we could hear him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This Polyjuice stuff sounds a bit dodgy to me,’ said Ron, frowning. ‘What if we were stuck looking like three of the Slytherins for ever?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It wears off after a while,’ said Hermione, waving her hand impatiently, ‘but getting hold of the recipe will be very difficult. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape said it was in a book called  <i class=\"calibre4\">Moste Potente Potions</i> and it’s bound to be in the Restricted Section of the library.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was only one way to get out a book from the Restricted Section: you needed a signed note of permission from a teacher. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hard to see why we’d want the book, really,’ said Ron, ‘if we weren’t going to try and make one of the potions.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think,’ said Hermione, ‘that if we made it sound as though we were just interested in the theory, we might stand a chance …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, come on, no teacher’s going to fall for that,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’d have to be really thick …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Rogue Bludger</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Since the disastrous episode of the pixies, Professor Lockhart had not brought live creatures to class. Instead, he read passages from his books to them, and sometimes re-enacted some of the more dramatic bits. He usually picked Harry to help him with these reconstructions; so far, Harry had been forced to play a simple Transylvanian villager whom Lockhart had cured of a Babbling Curse, a yeti with a head-cold, and a vampire who had been unable to eat anything except lettuce since Lockhart had dealt with him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was hauled to the front of the class during their very next Defence Against the Dark Arts lesson, this time acting a werewolf. If he hadn’t had a very good reason for keeping Lockhart in a good mood, he would have refused to do it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nice loud howl, Harry – exactly – and then, if you’ll believe it, I pounced – like this –  <i class=\"calibre4\">slammed</i> him to the floor – thus – with one hand, I managed to hold him down – with my other, I put my wand to his throat – I then screwed up my remaining strength and performed the immensely complex Homorphus Charm – he let out a piteous moan – go on, Harry – higher than that – good – the fur vanished – the fangs shrank – and he turned back into a man. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Simple, yet effective – and another village will remember me forever as the hero who delivered them from the monthly terror of werewolf attacks.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The bell rang and Lockhart got to his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Homework: compose a poem about my defeat of the Wagga Wagga werewolf! Signed copies of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Magical Me</i> to the author of the best one!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The class began to leave. Harry returned to the back of the room, where Ron and Hermione were waiting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready?’ Harry muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Rogue Bludger 123 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wait till everyone’s gone,’ said Hermione nervously. ‘All right …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She approached Lockhart’s desk, a piece of paper clutched tightly in her hand, Harry and Ron right behind her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – Professor Lockhart?’ Hermione stammered. ‘I wanted to – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">to get this book out of the library. Just for background reading.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She held out the piece of paper, her hand shaking slightly. ‘But the thing is, it’s in the Restricted Section of the library, so I need a teacher to sign for it – I’m sure it would help me understand what you say in  <i class=\"calibre4\">Gadding with Ghouls</i> about slow-acting venoms …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Gadding with Ghouls! </i>’ said Lockhart, taking the note from Hermione and smiling widely at her. ‘Possibly my very favourite book. You enjoyed it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yes,’ said Hermione eagerly. ‘So clever, the way you trapped that last one with the tea-strainer …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I’m sure no one will mind me giving the best student in the year a little extra help,’ said Lockhart warmly, and he pulled out an enormous peacock quill. ‘Yes, nice, isn’t it?’ he said, mis-reading the revolted look on Ron’s face. ‘I usually save it for book-signings.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He scrawled an enormous loopy signature on the note and handed it back to Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So, Harry,’ said Lockhart, while Hermione folded the note with fumbling fingers and slipped it into her bag, ‘tomorrow’s the first Quidditch match of the season, I believe? Gryffindor against Slytherin, is it not? I hear you’re a useful player. I was a Seeker, too. I was asked to try for the National Squad, but preferred to dedicate my life to the eradication of the Dark Forces. Still, if ever you feel the need for a little private training, don’t hesitate to ask. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Always happy to pass on my expertise to less able players …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry made an indistinct noise in his throat and then hurried off after Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t believe it,’ he said, as the three of them examined the signature on the note, ‘He didn’t even  <i class=\"calibre4\">look</i> at the book we wanted.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s because he’s a brainless git,’ said Ron. ‘But who cares, we’ve got what we needed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He is  <i class=\"calibre4\">not</i> a brainless git,’ said Hermione shrilly, as they half-ran towards the library. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just because he said you were the best student in the year …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They dropped their voices as they entered the muffled stillness of the library. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>124 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pince, the librarian, was a thin, irritable woman who looked like an underfed vulture. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Moste Potente Potions? </i>’ she repeated suspiciously, trying to take the note from Hermione; but Hermione wouldn’t let go. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I was wondering if I could keep it,’ she said breathlessly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, come on,’ said Ron, wrenching it from her grasp and thrusting it at Madam Pince. ‘We’ll get you another autograph. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart’ll sign anything if it stands still long enough.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pince held the note up to the light, as though determined to detect a forgery, but it passed the test. She stalked away between the lofty shelves and returned several minutes later carrying a large and mouldy-looking book. Hermione put it carefully into her bag and they left, trying not to walk too quickly or look too guilty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Five minutes later, they were barricaded in Moaning Myrtle’s out-of-order bathroom once again. Hermione had overridden Ron’s objections by pointing out that it was the last place anyone in their right minds would go, so they were guaranteed some pri-vacy. Moaning Myrtle was crying noisily in her cubicle, but they were ignoring her, and she them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione opened  <i class=\"calibre4\">Moste Potente Potions</i> carefully, and the three of them bent over the damp-spotted pages. It was clear from a glance why it belonged in the Restricted Section. Some of the potions had effects almost too gruesome to think about, and there were some very unpleasant illustrations, which included a man who seemed to have been turned inside out and a witch sprouting several extra pairs of arms out of her head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here it is,’ said Hermione excitedly, as she found the page headed   <i class=\"calibre4\">The Polyjuice Potion. </i> It was decorated with drawings of people halfway through transforming into other people. Harry sincerely hoped the artist had imagined the looks of intense pain on their faces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is the most complicated potion I’ve ever seen,’ said Hermione, as they scanned the recipe. ‘Lacewing flies, leeches, fluxweed and knotgrass,’ she murmured, running her finger down the list of ingredients. ‘Well, they’re easy enough, they’re in the student store-cupboard, we can help ourselves. Oooh, look, powdered horn of a Bicorn – don’t know where we’re going to get that … Shredded skin of a Boomslang – that’ll be tricky, too – and of course a bit of whoever we want to change into.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Rogue Bludger 125 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excuse me?’ said Ron sharply. ‘What d’you mean, a bit of whoever we’re changing into? I’m drinking  <i class=\"calibre4\">nothing</i> with Crabbe’s toenails in it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione continued as though she hadn’t heard him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We don’t have to worry about that yet, though, because we add those bits last …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron turned, speechless, to Harry, who had another worry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you realise how much we’re going to have to steal, Hermione? Shredded skin of Boomslang, that’s definitely not in the students’ cupboard. What’re we going to do, break into Snape’s private stores? I don’t know if this is a good idea …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione shut the book with a snap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, if you two are going to chicken out, fine,’ she said. There were bright pink patches on her cheeks and her eyes were brighter than usual. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> don’t want to break rules, you know.  <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> think threatening Muggle-borns is far worse than brewing up a difficult potion. But if you don’t want to find out if it’s Malfoy, I’ll go straight to Madam Pince now and hand the book back in …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I never thought I’d see the day when you’d be persuading us to break rules,’ said Ron. ‘All right, we’ll do it. But not toenails, OK?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How long will it take to make, anyway?’ said Harry, as Hermione, looking happier, opened the book again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, as the fluxweed has got to be picked at the full moon and the lacewings have got to be stewed for twenty-one days  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… I’d say it’d be ready in about a month, if we can get all the ingredients.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A month?’ said Ron. ‘Malfoy could have attacked half the Muggle-borns in the school by then!’ But Hermione’s eyes narrowed dangerously again, and he added swiftly, ‘But it’s the best plan we’ve got, so full steam ahead, I say.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">However, while Hermione was checking that the coast was clear for them to leave the bathroom, Ron muttered to Harry, ‘It’ll be a lot less hassle if you can just knock Malfoy off his broom tomorrow.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry woke early on Saturday morning and lay for a while thinking about the coming Quidditch match. He was nervous, mainly at the thought of what Wood would say if Gryffindor lost, but also at the idea of facing a team mounted on the fastest racing brooms gold could buy. He had never wanted to beat Slytherin so badly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After half an hour of lying there with his insides churning, he got </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>126 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">up, dressed, and went down to breakfast early, where he found the rest of the Gryffindor team huddled at the long, empty table, all looking uptight and not speaking much. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As eleven o’clock approached, the whole school started to make its way down to the Quidditch stadium. It was a muggy sort of day with a hint of thunder in the air. Ron and Hermione came hurrying over to wish Harry good luck as he entered the changing rooms. The team pulled on their scarlet Gryffindor robes, then sat down to listen to Wood’s usual pre-match pep talk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Slytherin have better brooms than us,’ he began, ‘no point denying it. But we’ve got better  <i class=\"calibre4\">people</i> on our brooms. We’ve trained harder than they have, we’ve been flying in all weathers –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">(‘Too true,’ muttered George Weasley. ‘I haven’t been properly dry since August’) ‘– and we’re going to make them rue the day they let that little bit of slime, Malfoy, buy his way onto their team.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Chest heaving with emotion, Wood turned to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’ll be down to you, Harry, to show them that a Seeker has to have something more than a rich father. Get to that Snitch before Malfoy or die trying, Harry, because we’ve got to win today, we’ve got to.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So no pressure, Harry,’ said Fred, winking at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As they walked out onto the pitch, a roar of noise greeted them; mainly cheers, because Ravenclaw and Hufflepuff were anxious to see Slytherin beaten, but the Slytherins in the crowd made their boos and hisses heard too. Madam Hooch, the Quidditch teacher, asked Flint and Wood to shake hands, which they did, giving each other threatening stares and gripping rather harder than was necessary. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘On my whistle,’ said Madam Hooch, ‘three … two … one …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a roar from the crowd to speed them upwards, the fourteen players rose towards the leaden sky. Harry flew higher than any of them, squinting around for the Snitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right there, Scarhead?’ yelled Malfoy, shooting underneath him as though to show off the speed of his broom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had no time to reply. At that very moment, a heavy black Bludger came pelting towards him; he avoided it so narrowly that he felt it ruffle his hair as it passed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Close one, Harry!’ said George, streaking past him with his club in his hand, ready to knock the Bludger back towards a Slytherin. Harry saw George give the Bludger a powerful whack in </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Rogue Bludger 127 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the direction of Adrian Pucey, but the Bludger changed direction in mid-air and shot straight for Harry again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dropped quickly to avoid it, and George managed to hit it hard towards Malfoy. Once again, the Bludger swerved like a boomerang and shot at Harry’s head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry put on a burst of speed and zoomed towards the other end of the pitch. He could hear the Bludger whistling along behind him. What was going on? Bludgers never concentrated on one player like this, it was their job to try and unseat as many people as possible … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred Weasley was waiting for the Bludger at the other end. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ducked as Fred swung at the Bludger with all his might; the Bludger was knocked off course. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s done it!’ Fred yelled happily, but he was wrong; as though it was magnetically attracted towards Harry, the Bludger pelted after him once more and Harry was forced to fly off at full speed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It had started to rain; Harry felt heavy drops fall onto his face, splattering onto his glasses. He didn’t have a clue what was going on in the rest of the game until he heard Lee Jordan, who was commentating, say, ‘Slytherin lead, sixty points to zero.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Slytherins’ superior brooms were clearly doing their jobs, and meanwhile the mad Bludger was doing all it could to knock Harry out of the air. Fred and George were now flying so close to him on either side that Harry could see nothing at all except their flailing arms and had no chance to look for the Snitch, let alone catch it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Someone’s – tampered – with – this – Bludger –’ Fred grunted, swinging his bat with all his might at it as it launched a new attack on Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We need time out,’ said George, trying to signal to Wood and stop the Bludger breaking Harry’s nose at the same time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood had obviously got the message. Madam Hooch’s whistle rang out and Harry, Fred and George dived for the ground, still trying to avoid the mad Bludger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on?’ said Wood, as the Gryffindor team huddled together, while Slytherins in the crowd jeered. ‘We’re being flat-tened. Fred, George, where were you when that Bludger stopped Angelina scoring?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We were twenty feet above her, stopping the other Bludger </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>128 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">murdering Harry, Oliver,’ said George angrily. ‘Someone’s fixed it – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">it won’t leave Harry alone, it hasn’t gone for anyone else all game. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Slytherins must have done something to it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But the Bludgers have been locked in Madam Hooch’s office since our last practice, and there was nothing wrong with them then …’ said Wood, anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch was walking towards them. Over her shoulder, Harry could see the Slytherin team jeering and pointing in his direction. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Listen,’ said Harry, as she came nearer and nearer, ‘with you two flying round me all the time the only way I’m going to catch the Snitch is if it flies up my sleeve. Go back to the rest of the team and let me deal with the rogue one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be thick,’ said Fred. ‘It’ll take your head off.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood was looking from Harry to the Weasleys. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oliver, this is mad,’ said Alicia Spinnet angrily. ‘You can’t let Harry deal with that thing on his own. Let’s ask for an inquiry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If we stop now, we’ll have to forfeit the match!’ said Harry. ‘And we’re not losing to Slytherin just because of a mad Bludger! Come on, Oliver, tell them to leave me alone!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is all your fault,’ George said angrily to Wood. ‘ “Get the Snitch or die trying” – what a stupid thing to tell him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch had joined them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready to resume play?’ she asked Wood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood looked at the determined look on Harry’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right,’ he said. ‘Fred, George, you heard Harry – leave him alone and let him deal with the Bludger on his own.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rain was falling more heavily now. On Madam Hooch’s whistle, Harry kicked hard into the air and heard the tell-tale whoosh of the Bludger behind him. Higher and higher Harry climbed. He looped and swooped, spiralled, zig-zagged and rolled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slightly dizzy, he nevertheless kept his eyes wide open. Rain was speckling his glasses and ran up his nostrils as he hung upside down, avoiding another fierce dive from the Bludger. He could hear laughter from the crowd; he knew he must look very stupid, but the rogue Bludger was heavy and couldn’t change direction as quickly as he could. He began a kind of roller-coaster ride around the edges of the stadium, squinting through the silver sheets of rain to the Gryffindor goalposts, where Adrian Pucey was trying to get past Wood … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Rogue Bludger 129 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A whistling in Harry’s ear told him the Bludger had just missed him again; he turned right over and sped in the opposite direction. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Training for the ballet, Potter?’ yelled Malfoy, as Harry was forced to do a stupid kind of twirl in mid-air to dodge the Bludger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Off Harry fled, the Bludger trailing a few feet behind him: and then, glaring back at Malfoy in hatred, he saw it,  <i class=\"calibre4\">the Golden</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Snitch. </i> It was hovering inches above Malfoy’s left ear – and Malfoy, busy laughing at Harry, hadn’t seen it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For an agonising moment, Harry hung in mid-air, not daring to speed towards Malfoy in case he looked up and saw the Snitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">WHAM! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had stayed still a second too long. The Bludger had hit him at last, smashed into his elbow, and Harry felt his arm break. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dimly, dazed by the searing pain in his arm, he slid sideways on his rain-drenched broom, one knee still crooked over it, his right arm dangling useless at his side. The Bludger came pelting back for a second attack, this time aiming at his face. Harry swerved out of the way, one idea firmly lodged in his numb brain:  <i class=\"calibre4\">get to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Malfoy. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through a haze of rain and pain he dived for the shimmering, sneering face below him and saw its eyes widen with fear: Malfoy thought Harry was attacking him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What the –’ he gasped, careering out of Harry’s way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took his remaining hand off his broom and made a wild snatch; he felt his fingers close on the cold Snitch but was now only gripping the broom with his legs and there was a yell from the crowd below as he headed straight for the ground, trying hard not to pass out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a splattering thud he hit the mud and rolled off his broom. His arm was hanging at a very strange angle. Riddled with pain, he heard, as though from a distance, a good deal of whistling and shouting. He focused on the Snitch clutched in his good hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aha,’ he said vaguely, ‘we’ve won.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he fainted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He came round, rain falling on his face, still lying on the pitch, with someone leaning over him. He saw a glitter of teeth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh no, not you,’ he moaned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Doesn’t know what he’s saying,’ said Lockhart loudly, to the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>130 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">anxious crowd of Gryffindors pressing around them. ‘Not to worry, Harry. I’m about to fix your arm.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">No! </i>’ said Harry. ‘I’ll keep it like this, thanks …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He tried to sit up, but the pain was terrible. He heard a familiar clicking noise nearby. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t want a photo of this, Colin,’ he said loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lie back, Harry,’ said Lockhart soothingly. ‘It’s a simple charm I’ve used countless times.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why can’t I just go to the hospital wing?’ said Harry through clenched teeth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He should really, Professor,’ said a muddy Wood, who couldn’t help grinning even though his Seeker was injured. ‘Great capture, Harry, really spectacular, your best yet, I’d say.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the thicket of legs around him, Harry spotted Fred and George Weasley, wrestling the rogue Bludger into a box. It was still putting up a terrific fight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stand back,’ said Lockhart, who was rolling up his jade-green sleeves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – don’t –’ said Harry weakly, but Lockhart was twirling his wand and a second later had directed it straight at Harry’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A strange and unpleasant sensation started at Harry’s shoulder and spread all the way down to his fingertips. It felt as though his arm was being deflated. He didn’t dare look at what was happening. He had shut his eyes, his face turned away from his arm, but his worst fears were realised as the people above him gasped and Colin Creevey began clicking away madly. His arm didn’t hurt any more – but nor did it feel remotely like an arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,’ said Lockhart. ‘Yes. Well, that can sometimes happen. But the point is, the bones are no longer broken. That’s the thing to bear in mind. So, Harry, just toddle up to the Hospital Wing – ah, Mr Weasley, Miss Granger, would you escort him? – and Madam Pomfrey will be able to – er – tidy you up a bit.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry got to his feet, he felt strangely lopsided. Taking a deep breath he looked down at his right side. What he saw nearly made him pass out again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Poking out of the end of his robes was what looked like a thick, flesh-coloured rubber glove. He tried to move his fingers. Nothing happened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart hadn’t mended Harry’s bones. He had removed them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Rogue Bludger 131 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey wasn’t at all pleased. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You should have come straight to me!’ she raged, holding up the sad, limp remainder of what, half an hour before, had been a working arm. ‘I can mend bones in a second – but growing them back –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You will be able to, won’t you?’ said Harry desperately. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll be able to, certainly, but it will be painful,’ said Madam Pomfrey grimly, throwing Harry a pair of pyjamas. ‘You’ll have to stay the night …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione waited outside the curtain drawn around Harry’s bed while Ron helped him into his pyjamas. It took a while to stuff the rubbery, boneless arm into a sleeve. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How can you stick up for Lockhart now, Hermione, eh?’ Ron called through the curtain as he pulled Harry’s limp fingers through the cuff. ‘If Harry had wanted de-boning he would have asked.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyone can make a mistake,’ said Hermione, ‘And it doesn’t hurt any more, does it, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry, ‘but it doesn’t do anything else, either.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As he swung himself onto the bed, his arm flapped pointlessly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione and Madam Pomfrey came around the curtain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey was holding a large bottle of something labelled </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Skele-Gro’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re in for a rough night,’ she said, pouring out a steaming beakerful and handing it to him. ‘Regrowing bones is a nasty business.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So was taking the Skele-Gro. It burned Harry’s mouth and throat as it went down, making him cough and splutter. Still tut-tutting about dangerous sports and inept teachers, Madam Pomfrey retreated, leaving Ron and Hermione to help Harry gulp down some water. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We won, though,’ said Ron, a grin breaking across his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was some catch you made. Malfoy’s face … he looked ready to kill!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I want to know how he fixed that Bludger,’ said Hermione darkly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can add that to the list of questions we’ll ask him when we’ve taken the Polyjuice Potion,’ said Harry, sinking back onto his pillows. ‘I hope it tastes better than this stuff …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If it’s got bits of Slytherins in it? You’ve got to be joking,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>132 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door of the hospital wing burst open at that moment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filthy and soaking wet, the rest of the Gryffindor team had arrived to see Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Unbelievable flying, Harry,’ said George. ‘I’ve just seen Marcus Flint yelling at Malfoy. Something about having the Snitch on top of his head and not noticing. Malfoy didn’t seem too happy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had brought cakes, sweets and bottles of pumpkin juice; they gathered around Harry’s bed and were just getting started on what promised to be a good party when Madam Pomfrey came storming over, shouting, ‘This boy needs rest, he’s got thirty-three bones to regrow! Out! OUT!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Harry was left alone, with nothing to distract him from the stabbing pains in his limp arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hours and hours later, Harry woke quite suddenly in the pitch blackness and gave a small yelp of pain: his arm now felt full of large splinters. For a second, he thought it was that which had woken him. Then, with a thrill of horror, he realised that someone was sponging his forehead in the dark. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get off!’ he said loudly, and then, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Dobby! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The house-elf’s goggling tennis-ball eyes were peering at Harry through the darkness. A single tear was running down his long, pointed nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter came back to school,’ he whispered miserably. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby warned and warned Harry Potter. Ah sir, why didn’t you heed Dobby? Why didn’t Harry Potter go back home when he missed the train?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry heaved himself up on his pillows and pushed Dobby’s sponge away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’re you doing here?’ he said. ‘And how did you know I missed the train?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s lip trembled and Harry was seized by a sudden suspicion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was  <i class=\"calibre4\">you! </i>’ he said slowly. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You</i> stopped the barrier letting us through!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Indeed yes, sir,’ said Dobby, nodding his head vigorously, ears flapping. ‘Dobby hid and watched for Harry Potter and sealed the gateway and Dobby had to iron his hands afterwards –’ he showed Harry ten, long, bandaged fingers, ‘– but Dobby didn’t care, sir, for he thought Harry Potter was safe, and  <i class=\"calibre4\">never</i> did Dobby dream that </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Rogue Bludger 133 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter would get to school another way!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was rocking backwards and forwards, shaking his ugly head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby was so shocked when he heard Harry Potter was back at Hogwarts, he let his master’s dinner burn! Such a flogging Dobby never had, sir …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry slumped back onto his pillows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You nearly got Ron and me expelled,’ he said fiercely. ‘You’d better clear off before my bones come back, Dobby, or I might strangle you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby smiled weakly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby is used to death threats, sir. Dobby gets them five times a day at home.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He blew his nose on a corner of the filthy pillowcase he wore, looking so pathetic that Harry felt his anger ebb away in spite of himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why d’you wear that thing, Dobby?’ he asked curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This, sir?’ said Dobby, plucking at the pillowcase. ‘ ’Tis a mark of the house-elf’s enslavement, sir. Dobby can only be freed if his masters present him with clothes, sir. The family is careful not to pass Dobby even a sock, sir, for then he would be free to leave their house for ever.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby mopped his bulging eyes and said suddenly, ‘Harry Potter   <i class=\"calibre4\">must</i> go home! Dobby thought his Bludger would be enough to make –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Your</i> Bludger?’ said Harry, anger rising once more. ‘What d’you mean,  <i class=\"calibre4\">your</i> Bludger?  <i class=\"calibre4\">You</i> made that Bludger try and kill me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not kill you, sir, never kill you!’ said Dobby, shocked. ‘Dobby wants to save Harry Potter’s life! Better sent home, grievously injured, than remain here, sir! Dobby only wanted Harry Potter hurt enough to be sent home!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, is that all?’ said Harry angrily. ‘I don’t suppose you’re going to tell me  <i class=\"calibre4\">why</i> you wanted me sent home in pieces?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, if Harry Potter only knew!’ Dobby groaned, more tears dripping onto his ragged pillowcase. ‘If he knew what he means to us, to the lowly, the enslaved, us dregs of the magical world! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby remembers how it was when He Who Must Not Be Named was at the height of his powers, sir! We house-elves were treated like vermin, sir! Of course, Dobby is still treated like that, sir,’ he admitted, drying his face on the pillowcase. ‘But mostly, sir, life </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>134 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">has improved for my kind since you triumphed over He Who Must Not Be Named. Harry Potter survived, and the Dark Lord’s power was broken, and it was a new dawn, sir, and Harry Potter shone like a beacon of hope for those of us who thought the dark days would never end, sir … And now, at Hogwarts, terrible things are to happen, are perhaps happening already, and Dobby cannot let Harry Potter stay here now that history is to repeat itself, now that the Chamber of Secrets is open once more –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby froze, horror-struck, then grabbed Harry’s water jug from his bedside table and cracked it over his own head, toppling out of sight. A second later, he crawled back onto the bed, cross-eyed, muttering, ‘Bad Dobby, very bad Dobby …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So there  <i class=\"calibre4\">is</i> a Chamber of Secrets?’ Harry whispered. ‘And – did you say it’s been opened  <i class=\"calibre4\">before? Tell</i> me, Dobby!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He seized the elf’s bony wrist as Dobby’s hand inched towards the water jug. ‘But I’m not Muggle-born – how can I be in danger from the Chamber?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, sir, ask no more, ask no more of poor Dobby,’ stammered the elf, his eyes huge in the dark. ‘Dark deeds are planned in this place, but Harry Potter must not be here when they happen. Go home, Harry Potter. Go home. Harry Potter must not meddle in this, sir, ’tis too dangerous –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who is it, Dobby?’ Harry said, keeping a firm hold on Dobby’s wrist to stop him hitting himself with the water jug again. ‘Who’s opened it? Who opened it last time?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby can’t, sir, Dobby can’t, Dobby mustn’t tell!’ squealed the elf. ‘Go home, Harry Potter, go home!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not going anywhere!’ said Harry fiercely. ‘One of my best friends is Muggle-born, she’ll be first in line if the Chamber really has been opened –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter risks his own life for his friends!’ moaned Dobby, in a kind of miserable ecstasy. ‘So noble! So valiant! But he must save himself, he must, Harry Potter must not –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby suddenly froze, his bat ears quivering. Harry heard it, too. There were footsteps coming down the passageway outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby must go!’ breathed the elf, terrified; there was a loud crack, and Harry’s fist was suddenly clenched on thin air. He slumped back into bed, his eyes on the dark doorway to the hospital wing as the footsteps drew nearer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Next moment, Dumbledore was backing into the dormitory, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Rogue Bludger 135 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">wearing a long woolly dressing gown and a nightcap. He was carrying one end of what looked like a statue. Professor McGonagall appeared a second later, carrying its feet. Together, they heaved it onto a bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get Madam Pomfrey,’ whispered Dumbledore, and Professor McGonagall hurried past the end of Harry’s bed out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry lay quite still, pretending to be asleep. He heard urgent voices, and then Professor McGonagall swept back into view, closely followed by Madam Pomfrey, who was pulling a cardigan on over her nightdress. He heard a sharp intake of breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What happened?’ Madam Pomfrey whispered to Dumbledore, bending over the statue on the bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Another attack,’ said Dumbledore. ‘Minerva found him on the stairs.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There was a bunch of grapes next to him,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘We think he was trying to sneak up here to visit Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s stomach gave a horrible lurch. Slowly and carefully, he raised himself a few inches so he could look at the statue on the bed. A ray of moonlight lay across its staring face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Colin Creevey. His eyes were wide and his hands were stuck up in front of him, holding his camera. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Petrified?’ whispered Madam Pomfrey. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘But I shudder to think … If Albus hadn’t been on the way downstairs for hot chocolate, who knows what might have …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The three of them stared down at Colin. Then Dumbledore leaned forward and prised the camera out of Colin’s rigid grip. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t think he managed to get a picture of his attacker?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Professor McGonagall eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore didn’t answer. He prised open the back of the camera. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good gracious!’ said Madam Pomfrey. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A jet of steam had hissed out of the camera. Harry, three beds away, caught the acrid smell of burnt plastic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Melted,’ said Madam Pomfrey wonderingly, ‘all melted …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What does this  <i class=\"calibre4\">mean, </i> Albus?’ Professor McGonagall asked urgently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It means,’ said Dumbledore, ‘that the Chamber of Secrets is indeed open again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>136 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey clapped a hand to her mouth. Professor McGonagall stared at Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Albus … surely …  <i class=\"calibre4\">who? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The question is not  <i class=\"calibre4\">who, </i>’ said Dumbledore, his eyes on Colin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The question is,  <i class=\"calibre4\">how</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And from what Harry could see of Professor McGonagall’s shadowy face, she didn’t understand this any better than he did. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER ELEVEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Duelling Club</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry woke up on Sunday morning to find the dormitory blazing with winter sunlight and his arm re-boned but very stiff. He sat up quickly and looked over at Colin’s bed, but it had been blocked from view by the high curtains Harry had changed behind yesterday. Seeing that he was awake, Madam Pomfrey came bustling over with a breakfast tray and then began bending and stretching his arm and fingers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All in order,’ she said, as he clumsily fed himself porridge left-handed. ‘When you’ve finished eating, you may leave.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dressed as quickly as he could and hurried off to Gryffindor Tower, desperate to tell Ron and Hermione about Colin and Dobby, but they weren’t there. Harry left to look for them, wondering where they could have got to and feeling slightly hurt that they weren’t interested in whether he had his bones back or not. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry passed the library, Percy Weasley strolled out of it, looking in far better spirits than last time they’d met. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, hello, Harry,’ he said. ‘Excellent flying yesterday, really excellent. Gryffindor have just taken the lead for the House Cup – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you earned fifty points!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You haven’t seen Ron or Hermione, have you?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I haven’t,’ said Percy, his smile fading. ‘I hope Ron’s not in another  <i class=\"calibre4\">girls’ toilet</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry forced a laugh, watched Percy out of sight and then headed straight for Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. He couldn’t see why Ron and Hermione would be in there again, but after making sure that neither Filch nor any Prefects were around, he opened the door and heard their voices coming from a locked cubicle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s me,’ he said, closing the door behind him. There was a clunk, a splash and a gasp from within the cubicle and he saw </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>138 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s eye peering through the keyhole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry! </i>’ she said. ‘You gave us such a fright. Come in – how’s your arm?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fine,’ said Harry, squeezing into the cubicle. An old cauldron was perched on the toilet, and a crackling from under the rim told Harry they had lit a fire beneath it. Conjuring up portable, water-proof fires was a speciality of Hermione’s. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d’ve come to meet you, but we decided to get started on the Polyjuice Potion,’ Ron explained, as Harry, with difficulty, locked the cubicle again. ‘We’ve decided this is the safest place to hide it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry started to tell them about Colin, but Hermione interrupted. ‘We already know, we heard Professor McGonagall telling Professor Flitwick this morning. That’s why we decided we’d better get going –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The sooner we get a confession out of Malfoy, the better,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">snarled Ron. ‘D’you know what I think? He was in such a foul temper after the Quidditch match, he took it out on Colin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s something else,’ said Harry, watching Hermione tearing bundles of knotgrass and throwing them into the potion. ‘Dobby came to visit me in the middle of the night.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione looked up, amazed. Harry told them everything Dobby had told him – or hadn’t told him. Ron and Hermione listened with their mouths open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Chamber of Secrets has been opened  <i class=\"calibre4\">before? </i>’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This settles it,’ said Ron in a triumphant voice. ‘Lucius Malfoy must’ve opened the Chamber when he was at school here and now he’s told dear old Draco how to do it. It’s obvious. Wish Dobby’d told you what kind of monster’s in there, though. I want to know how come nobody’s noticed it sneaking round the school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe it can make itself invisible,’ said Hermione, prodding leeches to the bottom of the cauldron. ‘Or maybe it can disguise itself – pretend to be a suit of armour or something. I’ve read about Chameleon Ghouls …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You read too much, Hermione,’ said Ron, pouring dead lacewings on top of the leeches. He crumpled up the empty lacewing bag and looked round at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So Dobby stopped us getting on the train and broke your arm …’ He shook his head. ‘You know what, Harry? If he doesn’t stop trying to save your life he’s going to kill you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Duelling Club 139 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The news that Colin Creevey had been attacked and was now lying as though dead in the hospital wing had spread through the entire school by Monday morning. The air was suddenly thick with rumour and suspicion. The first-years were now moving around the castle in tight-knit groups, as though scared they would be attacked if they ventured forth alone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny Weasley, who sat next to Colin Creevey in Charms, was distraught, but Harry felt that Fred and George were going the wrong way about cheering her up. They were taking it in turns to cover themselves with fur or boils and jump out at her from behind statues. They only stopped when Percy, apoplectic with rage, told them he was going to write to Mrs Weasley and tell her Ginny was having nightmares. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Meanwhile, hidden from the teachers, a roaring trade in talis-mans, amulets and other protective devices was sweeping the school. Neville Longbottom bought a large, evil-smelling green onion, a pointed purple crystal and a rotting newt-tail before the other Gryffindor boys pointed out that he was in no danger: he was a pure-blood, and therefore unlikely to be attacked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They went for Filch first,’ Neville said, his round face fearful, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘and everyone knows I’m almost a Squib.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In the second week of December Professor McGonagall came around as usual, collecting names of those who would be staying at school for Christmas. Harry, Ron and Hermione signed her list; they had heard that Malfoy was staying, which struck them as very suspicious. The holidays would be the perfect time to use the Polyjuice Potion and try to worm a confession out of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Unfortunately, the potion was only half-finished. They still needed the Bicorn horn and the Boomslang skin, and the only place they were going to get them was from Snape’s private stores. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry privately felt he’d rather face Slytherin’s legendary monster than have Snape catch him robbing his office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What we need,’ said Hermione briskly, as Thursday afternoon’s double Potions lesson loomed nearer, ‘is a diversion. Then one of us can sneak into Snape’s office and take what we need.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron looked at her nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think I’d better do the actual stealing,’ Hermione continued, in a matter-of-fact tone. ‘You two will be expelled if you get in any more trouble, and I’ve got a clean record. So all you need to do is </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>140 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">cause enough mayhem to keep Snape busy for five minutes or so.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry smiled feebly. Deliberately causing mayhem in Snape’s Potions class was about as safe as poking a sleeping dragon in the eye. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Potions lessons took place in one of the large dungeons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Thursday afternoon’s lesson proceeded in the usual way. Twenty cauldrons stood steaming between the wooden desks, on which stood brass scales and jars of ingredients. Snape prowled through the fumes, making waspish remarks about the Gryffindors’ work while the Slytherins sniggered appreciatively. Draco Malfoy, who was Snape’s favourite student, kept flicking puffer-fish eyes at Ron and Harry, who knew that if they retaliated they would get detention faster than you could say ‘unfair’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s Swelling Solution was far too runny, but he had his mind on more important things. He was waiting for Hermione’s signal, and he hardly listened as Snape paused to sneer at his watery potion. When Snape turned and walked off to bully Neville, Hermione caught Harry’s eye and nodded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ducked swiftly down behind his cauldron, pulled one of Fred’s Filibuster fireworks out of his pocket and gave it a quick prod with his wand. The firework began to fizz and sputter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Knowing he had only seconds, Harry straightened up, took aim, and lobbed it into the air; it landed right on target in Goyle’s cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Goyle’s potion exploded, showering the whole class. People shrieked as splashes of the Swelling Solution hit them. Malfoy got a faceful and his nose began to swell like a balloon; Goyle blundered around, his hands over his eyes, which had expanded to the size of dinner plates, while Snape was trying to restore calm and find out what had happened. Through the confusion, Harry saw Hermione slip quietly out of the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Silence! SILENCE!’ Snape roared. ‘Anyone who has been splashed, come here for a Deflating Draught. When I find out who did this …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried not to laugh as he watched Malfoy hurry forward, his head drooping with the weight of a nose like a small melon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As half the class lumbered up to Snape’s desk, some weighed down with arms like clubs, others unable to talk through gigantic puffed-up lips, Harry saw Hermione slide back into the dungeon, the front of her robes bulging. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Duelling Club 141 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When everyone had taken a swig of antidote and the various swellings had subsided, Snape swept over to Goyle’s cauldron and scooped out the twisted black remains of the firework. There was a sudden hush. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I ever find out who threw this,’ Snape whispered, ‘I shall <i class=\"calibre4\">make sure</i> that person is expelled.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry arranged his face into what he hoped was a puzzled expression. Snape was looking right at him, and the bell which rang ten minutes later could not have been more welcome. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He knew it was me,’ Harry told Ron and Hermione, as they hurried back to Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. ‘I could tell.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione threw the new ingredients into the cauldron and began to stir feverishly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’ll be ready in a fortnight,’ she said happily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape can’t prove it was you,’ said Ron reassuringly to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What can he do?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Knowing Snape, something foul,’ said Harry, as the potion frothed and bubbled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A week later, Harry, Ron and Hermione were walking across the Entrance Hall when they saw a small knot of people gathered around the noticeboard, reading a piece of parchment that had just been pinned up. Seamus Finnigan and Dean Thomas beckoned them over, looking excited. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re starting a Duelling Club!’ said Seamus. ‘First meeting tonight! I wouldn’t mind duelling lessons, they might come in handy one of these days …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What, you reckon Slytherin’s monster can duel?’ said Ron, but he too read the sign with interest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Could be useful,’ he said to Harry and Hermione as they went into dinner. ‘Shall we go?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione were all for it, so at eight o’clock that evening they hurried back to the Great Hall. The long dining tables had vanished and a golden stage had appeared along one wall, lit by thousands of candles floating overhead. The ceiling was velvety black once more and most of the school seemed to be packed beneath it, all carrying their wands and looking excited. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wonder who’ll be teaching us?’ said Hermione, as they edged into the chattering crowd. ‘Someone told me Flitwick was a duelling champion when he was young, maybe it’ll be him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>142 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As long as it’s not –’ Harry began, but he ended on a groan: Gilderoy Lockhart was walking onto the stage, resplendent in robes of deep plum and accompanied by none other than Snape, wearing his usual black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart waved an arm for silence and called, ‘Gather round, gather round! Can everyone see me? Can you all hear me? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Excellent! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, Professor Dumbledore has granted me permission to start this little Duelling Club, to train you all up in case you ever need to defend yourselves as I myself have done on countless occasions </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– for full details, see my published works. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me introduce my assistant Professor Snape,’ said Lockhart, flashing a wide smile. ‘He tells me he knows a tiny little bit about duelling himself and has sportingly agreed to help me with a short demonstration before we begin. Now, I don’t want any of you youngsters to worry – you’ll still have your Potions master when I’m through with him, never fear!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wouldn’t it be good if they finished each other off?’ Ron muttered in Harry’s ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s upper lip was curling. Harry wondered why Lockhart was still smiling; if Snape had been looking at  <i class=\"calibre4\">him</i> like that he’d have been running as fast as he could in the opposite direction. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart and Snape turned to face each other and bowed; at least, Lockhart did, with much twirling of his hands, whereas Snape jerked his head irritably. Then they raised their wands like swords in front of them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As you see, we are holding our wands in the accepted combat-ive position,’ Lockhart told the silent crowd. ‘On the count of three, we will cast our first spells. Neither of us will be aiming to kill, of course.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wouldn’t bet on that,’ Harry murmured, watching Snape baring his teeth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One – two – three –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both of them swung their wands up and over their shoulders. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape cried: ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expelliarmus! </i>’ There was a dazzling flash of scarlet light and Lockhart was blasted off his feet: he flew backwards off the stage, smashed into the wall and slid down it to sprawl on the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy and some of the other Slytherins cheered. Hermione was dancing on tiptoes. ‘Do you think he’s all right?’ she squealed through her fingers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Duelling Club 143 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who cares?’ said Harry and Ron together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart was getting unsteadily to his feet. His hat had fallen off and his wavy hair was standing on end. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, there you have it!’ he said, tottering back onto the platform. ‘That was a Disarming Charm – as you see, I’ve lost my wand – ah, thank you, Miss Brown. Yes, an excellent idea to show them that, Professor Snape, but if you don’t mind my saying so, it was very obvious what you were about to do. If I had wanted to stop you it would have been only too easy. However, I felt it would be instructive to let them see …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape was looking murderous. Possibly Lockhart had noticed, because he said, ‘Enough demonstrating! I’m going to come amongst you now and put you all into pairs. Professor Snape, if you’d like to help me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They moved through the crowd, matching up partners. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart teamed Neville with Justin Finch-Fletchley, but Snape reached Harry and Ron first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Time to split up the dream team, I think,’ he sneered. ‘Weasley, you can partner Finnigan. Potter –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry moved automatically towards Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t think so,’ said Snape, smiling coldly. ‘Mr Malfoy, come over here. Let’s see what you make of the famous Potter. And you, Miss Granger – you can partner Miss Bulstrode.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy strutted over, smirking. Behind him walked a Slytherin girl who reminded Harry of a picture he’d seen in  <i class=\"calibre4\">Holidays with</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hags. </i> She was large and square and her heavy jaw jutted aggres-sively. Hermione gave her a weak smile which she did not return. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Face your partners!’ called Lockhart, back on the platform, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘and bow!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Malfoy barely inclined their heads, not taking their eyes off each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wands at the ready!’ shouted Lockhart. ‘When I count to three, cast your charms to disarm your opponent –  <i class=\"calibre4\">only</i> to disarm them  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– we don’t want any accidents. One … two … three …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry swung his wand over his shoulder, but Malfoy had already started on ‘two’: his spell hit Harry so hard he felt as though he’d been hit over the head with a saucepan. He stumbled, but everything still seemed to be working, and wasting no more time, Harry pointed his wand straight at Malfoy and shouted, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Rictusempra! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>144 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A jet of silver light hit Malfoy in the stomach and he doubled up, wheezing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I said disarm only! </i>’ Lockhart shouted in alarm over the heads of the battling crowd, as Malfoy sank to his knees; Harry had hit him with a Tickling Charm, and he could barely move for laughing. Harry hung back, with a vague feeling it would be unsporting to bewitch Malfoy while he was on the floor, but this was a mistake. Gasping for breath, Malfoy pointed his wand at Harry’s knees, choked, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Tarantallegra! </i>’ and next second Harry’s legs had begun to jerk around out of his control in a kind of quickstep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop! Stop!’ screamed Lockhart, but Snape took charge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Finite Incantatem! </i>’ he shouted; Harry’s feet stopped dancing, Malfoy stopped laughing and they were able to look up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A haze of greenish smoke was hovering over the scene. Both Neville and Justin were lying on the floor, panting; Ron was holding up an ashen-faced Seamus, apologising for whatever his broken wand had done; but Hermione and Millicent Bulstrode were still moving; Millicent had Hermione in a headlock and Hermione was whimpering in pain. Both their wands lay forgotten on the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry leapt forward and pulled Millicent off. It was difficult; she was a lot bigger than he was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dear, dear,’ said Lockhart, skittering through the crowd, looking at the aftermath of the duels. ‘Up you get, Macmillan … careful there, Miss Fawcett … pinch it hard, it’ll stop bleeding in a second, Boot … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think I’d better teach you how to  <i class=\"calibre4\">block</i> unfriendly spells,’ said Lockhart, standing flustered in the midst of the hall. He glanced at Snape, whose black eyes glinted, and looked quickly away. ‘Let’s have a volunteer pair – Longbottom and Finch-Fletchley, how about you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A bad idea, Professor Lockhart,’ said Snape, gliding over like a large and malevolent bat. ‘Longbottom causes devastation with the simplest spells. We’ll be sending what’s left of Finch-Fletchley up to the hospital wing in a matchbox.’ Neville’s round pink face went pinker. ‘How about Malfoy and Potter?’ said Snape with a twisted smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent idea!’ said Lockhart, gesturing Harry and Malfoy into the middle of the Hall as the crowd backed away to give them room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, Harry,’ said Lockhart, ‘when Draco points his wand at </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Duelling Club 145 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you, you do  <i class=\"calibre4\">this. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He raised his own wand, attempted a complicated sort of wiggling action and dropped it. Snape smirked as Lockhart quickly picked it up, saying, ‘Whoops – my wand is a little over-excited.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape moved closer to Malfoy, bent down and whispered something in his ear. Malfoy smirked, too. Harry looked nervously up at Lockhart and said, ‘Professor, could you show me that blocking thing again?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scared?’ muttered Malfoy, so that Lockhart couldn’t hear him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You wish,’ said Harry out of the corner of his mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart cuffed Harry merrily on the shoulder. ‘Just do what I did, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What, drop my wand?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Lockhart wasn’t listening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Three – two – one – go!’ he shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy raised his wand quickly and bellowed, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Serpensortia! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The end of his wand exploded. Harry watched, aghast, as a long black snake shot out of it, fell heavily onto the floor between them and raised itself, ready to strike. There were screams as the crowd backed swiftly away, clearing the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t move, Potter,’ said Snape lazily, clearly enjoying the sight of Harry standing motionless, eye to eye with the angry snake. ‘I’ll get rid of it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Allow me!’ shouted Lockhart. He brandished his wand at the snake and there was a loud bang; the snake, instead of vanishing, flew ten feet into the air and fell back to the floor with a loud smack. Enraged, hissing furiously, it slithered straight towards Justin Finch-Fletchley and raised itself again, fangs exposed, poised to strike. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wasn’t sure what made him do it. He wasn’t even aware of  deciding  to  do  it.  All  he  knew  was  that  his  legs  were  carrying him forward as though he was on castors and that he had shouted stupidly at the snake, ‘Leave him!’ And miraculously – inexplica-bly – the snake slumped to the floor, docile as a thick black garden hose, its eyes now on Harry. Harry felt the fear drain out of him. He knew the snake wouldn’t attack anyone now, though how he knew it, he couldn’t have explained. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked up at Justin, grinning, expecting to see Justin looking relieved, or puzzled, or even grateful – but certainly not angry and scared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>146 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do you think you’re playing at?’ he shouted, and before Harry could say anything, Justin had turned and stormed out of the Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape stepped forward, waved his wand and the snake vanished in a small puff of black smoke. Snape, too, was looking at Harry in an unexpected way: it was a shrewd and calculating look, and Harry didn’t like it. He was also dimly aware of an ominous muttering all around the walls. Then he felt a tugging on the back of his robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on,’ said Ron’s voice in his ear. ‘Move – come  <i class=\"calibre4\">on</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron steered him out of the Hall, Hermione hurrying alongside them. As they went through the doors, the people on either side drew away as though they were frightened of catching something. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t have a clue what was going on, and neither Ron nor Hermione explained anything until they had dragged him all the way up to the empty Gryffindor common room. Then Ron pushed Harry into an armchair and said, ‘You’re a Parselmouth. Why didn’t you tell us?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m a what?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">A Parselmouth! </i>’ said Ron. ‘You can talk to snakes!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know,’ said Harry. ‘I mean, that’s only the second time I’ve ever done it. I accidentally set a boa constrictor on my cousin Dudley at the zoo once – long story – but it was telling me it had never seen Brazil and I sort of set it free without meaning to. That was before I knew I was a wizard …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A boa constrictor told you it had never seen Brazil?’ Ron repeated faintly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So?’ said Harry. ‘I bet loads of people here can do it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh no they can’t,’ said Ron. ‘It’s not a very common gift. Harry, this is bad.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s bad?’ said Harry, starting to feel quite angry. ‘What’s wrong with everyone? Listen, if I hadn’t told that snake not to attack Justin –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, that’s what you said to it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you mean? You were there … you heard me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I heard you speaking Parseltongue,’ said Ron, ‘snake language. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You could have been saying anything. No wonder Justin panicked, you sounded like you were egging the snake on or something. It was creepy, you know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry gaped at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Duelling Club 147 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I spoke a different language? But – I didn’t realise – how can I speak a language without knowing I can speak it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron shook his head. Both he and Hermione were looking as though someone had died. Harry couldn’t see what was so terrible. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you want to tell me what’s wrong with stopping a dirty great snake biting Justin’s head off?’ he said. ‘What does it matter  <i class=\"calibre4\">how</i> I did it as long as Justin doesn’t have to join the Headless Hunt?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It matters,’ said Hermione, speaking at last in a hushed voice, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘because being able to talk to snakes was what Salazar Slytherin was famous for. That’s why the symbol of Slytherin house is a serpent.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s mouth fell open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Exactly,’ said Ron. ‘And now the whole school’s going to think you’re his great-great-great-great-grandson or something …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I’m not,’ said Harry, with a panic he couldn’t quite explain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll find that hard to prove,’ said Hermione. ‘He lived about a thousand years ago; for all we know, you could be.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry lay awake for hours that night. Through a gap in the hang-ings round his four-poster he watched snow starting to drift past the tower window, and wondered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Could</i> he be a descendant of Salazar Slytherin? He didn’t know anything about his father’s family, after all. The Dursleys had always forbidden questions about his wizarding relatives. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quietly, Harry tried to say something in Parseltongue. The words  wouldn’t  come.  It  seemed  he  had  to  be  face  to  face  with  a snake to do it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I’m in  <i class=\"calibre4\">Gryffindor, </i>’ Harry thought. ‘The Sorting Hat wouldn’t have put me in here if I had Slytherin blood …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ah</i>,’ said a nasty little voice in his brain, ‘But the Sorting Hat <i class=\"calibre4\">wanted</i> to put you in Slytherin, don’t you remember?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned over. He’d see Justin next day in Herbology and he’d explain that he’d been calling the snake off, not egging it on, which (he thought angrily, pummelling his pillow) any fool should have realised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">By next morning, however, the snow that had begun in the night had turned into a blizzard so thick that the last Herbology lesson of term was cancelled: Professor Sprout wanted to fit socks and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>148 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">scarves on the Mandrakes, a tricky operation she would entrust to no one else, now that it was so important for the Mandrakes to grow quickly and revive Mrs Norris and Colin Creevey. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry fretted about this next to the fire in the Gryffindor common room, while Ron and Hermione used their lesson off to play a game of wizard chess. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘For heaven’s sake, Harry,’ said Hermione, exasperated, as one of Ron’s bishops wrestled her knight off his horse and dragged him off the board. ‘Go and  <i class=\"calibre4\">find</i> Justin if it’s so important to you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So Harry got up and left through the portrait hole, wondering where Justin might be. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The castle was darker than it usually was in daytime, because of the thick, swirling grey snow at every window. Shivering, Harry walked past classrooms where lessons were taking place, catching snatches of what was happening within. Professor McGonagall was shouting at someone who, by the sound of it, had turned his friend into a badger. Resisting the urge to take a look, Harry  walked  on  by,  thinking  that  Justin  might  be  using  his  free lesson to catch up on some work, and deciding to check the library first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A group of the Hufflepuffs who should have been in Herbology were indeed sitting at the back of the library, but they didn’t seem to be working. Between the long lines of high bookshelves, Harry could see that their heads were close together and they were having what looked like an absorbing conversation. He couldn’t see whether Justin was among them. He was walking towards them when something of what they were saying met his ears, and he paused to listen, hidden in the Invisibility section. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So anyway,’ a stout boy was saying, ‘I told Justin to hide up in our dormitory. I mean to say, if Potter’s marked him down as his next victim, it’s best if he keeps a low profile for a while. Of course, Justin’s been waiting for something like this to happen ever since he let slip to Potter he was Muggle-born. Justin actually <i class=\"calibre4\">told</i> him he’d been down for Eton. That’s not the kind of thing you bandy about with Slytherin’s heir on the loose, is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You definitely think it  <i class=\"calibre4\">is</i> Potter, then, Ernie?’ said a girl with blonde pigtails anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hannah,’ said the stout boy solemnly, ‘he’s a Parselmouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone knows that’s the mark of a dark wizard. Have you ever heard of a decent one who could talk to snakes? They called </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Duelling Club 149 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slytherin himself Serpent-tongue.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was some heavy murmuring at this, and Ernie went on, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Remember what was written on the wall?  <i class=\"calibre4\">Enemies of the Heir</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Beware. </i> Potter had some sort of run-in with Filch. Next thing we know, Filch’s cat’s attacked. That first-year, Creevey, was annoying Potter at the Quidditch match, taking pictures of him while he was lying in the mud. Next thing we know, Creevey’s been attacked.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He always seems so nice, though,’ said Hannah uncertainly, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘and, well, he’s the one who made You Know Who disappear. He can’t be all bad, can he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ernie lowered his voice mysteriously, the Hufflepuffs bent closer, and Harry edged nearer so that he could catch Ernie’s words. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one knows how he survived that attack by You Know Who. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I mean to say, he was only a baby when it happened. He should have been blasted into smithereens. Only a really powerful Dark Wizard could have survived a curse like that.’ He dropped his voice until it was barely more than a whisper, and said, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">That’s</i> probably why You Know Who wanted to kill him in the first place. Didn’t want another Dark Lord  <i class=\"calibre4\">competing</i> with him. I wonder what other powers Potter’s been hiding?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t take any more. Clearing his throat loudly, he stepped out from behind the bookshelves. If he hadn’t been feeling so angry, he would have found the sight that greeted him funny: every one of the Hufflepuffs looked as though they had been Petrified by the sight of him, and the colour was draining out of Ernie’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello,’ said Harry. ‘I’m looking for Justin Finch-Fletchley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hufflepuffs’ worst fears had clearly been confirmed. They all looked fearfully at Ernie. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do you want with him?’ said Ernie, in a quavering voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wanted to tell him what really happened with that snake at the Duelling Club,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ernie bit his white lips and then, taking a deep breath, said, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We were all there. We saw what happened.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then you noticed that, after I spoke to it, the snake backed off?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All I saw,’ said Ernie stubbornly, though he was trembling as he spoke, ‘was you speaking Parseltongue and chasing the snake towards Justin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>150 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I didn’t chase it at him!’ Harry said, his voice shaking with anger. ‘It didn’t even  <i class=\"calibre4\">touch</i> him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was a very near miss,’ said Ernie. ‘And in case you’re getting ideas,’ he added hastily, ‘I might tell you that you can trace my family back through nine generations of witches and warlocks and my blood’s as pure as anyone’s, so –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t care what sort of blood you’ve got!’ said Harry fiercely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why would I want to attack Muggle-borns?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve heard you hate those Muggles you live with,’ said Ernie swiftly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not possible to live with the Dursleys and not hate them,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Harry. ‘I’d like to see you try it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned on his heel and stormed out of the library, earning himself a reproving glare from Madam Pince, who was polishing the gilded cover of a large spellbook. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry blundered up the corridor, barely noticing where he was going, he was in such a fury. The result was that he walked into something very large and solid, which knocked him backwards onto the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, hullo, Hagrid,’ Harry said, looking up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s face was entirely hidden by a woolly, snow-covered balaclava, but it couldn’t possibly be anyone else, as he filled most of the corridor in his moleskin overcoat. A dead rooster was hanging from one of his massive, gloved hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All righ’, Harry?’ he said, pulling up the balaclava so he could speak. ‘Why aren’t yeh in class?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Cancelled,’ said Harry, getting up. ‘What’re you doing in here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid held up the limp rooster. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Second one killed this term,’ he explained. ‘It’s either foxes or a Blood-Suckin’ Bugbear, an’ I need the Headmaster’s permission ter put a charm round the hen-coop.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He peered more closely at Harry from under his thick, snow-flecked eyebrows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh sure yeh’re all righ’? Yeh look all hot an’ bothered.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t bring himself to repeat what Ernie and the rest of the Hufflepuffs had been saying about him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s nothing,’ he said. ‘I’d better get going, Hagrid, it’s Transfiguration next and I’ve got to pick up my books.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He walked off, his mind still full of what Ernie had said about him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Duelling Club 151 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Justin’s been waiting for something like this to happen ever since</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">he let slip to Potter he was Muggle-born </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stamped up the stairs and turned along another corridor, which was particularly dark; the torches had been extinguished by a strong, icy draught which was blowing through a loose window pane. He was halfway down the passage when he tripped head-long over something lying on the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned to squint at what he’d fallen over, and felt as though his stomach had dissolved. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Justin Finch-Fletchley was lying on the floor, rigid and cold, a look of shock frozen on his face, his eyes staring blankly at the ceiling. And that wasn’t all. Next to him was another figure, the strangest sight Harry had ever seen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Nearly Headless Nick, no longer pearly-white and transparent, but black and smoky, floating immobile and horizontal, six inches off the floor. His head was half off and his face wore an expression of shock identical to Justin’s. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry got to his feet, his breathing fast and shallow, his heart doing a kind of drum-roll against his ribs. He looked wildly up and down the deserted corridor and saw a line of spiders scuttling as fast as they could away from the bodies. The only sounds were the muffled voices of teachers from the classes on either side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He could run, and no one would ever know he had been there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he couldn’t just leave them lying here … he had to get help. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Would anyone believe he hadn’t had anything to do with this? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As he stood there, panicking, a door right next to him opened with a bang. Peeves the poltergeist came shooting out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why, it’s potty wee Potter!’ cackled Peeves, knocking Harry’s glasses askew as he bounced past him. ‘What’s Potter up to? Why’s Potter lurking –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves stopped, halfway through a mid-air somersault. Upside-down, he spotted Justin and Nearly Headless Nick. He flipped the right way up, filled his lungs and, before Harry could stop him, screamed, ‘ATTACK! ATTACK! ANOTHER ATTACK! NO </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">MORTAL OR GHOST IS SAFE! RUN FOR YOUR LIVES! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ATTAAAACK!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crash – crash – crash: door after door flew open along the corridor and people flooded out. For several long minutes, there was a scene of such confusion that Justin was in danger of being squashed and people kept standing in Nearly Headless Nick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>152 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry found himself pinned against the wall as the teachers shouted for quiet. Professor McGonagall came running, followed by her own class, one of whom still had black and white striped hair. She used her wand to set off a loud bang, which restored silence, and ordered everyone back into their classes. No sooner had the scene cleared somewhat than Ernie the Hufflepuff arrived, panting, on the scene. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Caught in the act! </i>’ Ernie yelled, his face stark white, pointing his finger dramatically at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That will do, Macmillan!’ said Professor McGonagall sharply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves was bobbing overhead, now grinning wickedly, survey-ing the scene; Peeves always loved chaos. As the teachers bent over Justin and Nearly Headless Nick, examining them, Peeves broke into song: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Oh Potter, you rotter, oh what have you done? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">You’re killing off students, you think it’s good fun </i>–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s enough Peeves!’ barked Professor McGonagall, and Peeves zoomed away backwards, with his tongue out at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Justin was carried up to the hospital wing by Professor Flitwick and Professor Sinistra of the Astronomy department, but nobody seemed to know what to do for Nearly Headless Nick. In the end, Professor McGonagall conjured a large fan out of thin air, which she gave to Ernie with instructions to waft Nearly Headless Nick up the stairs. This Ernie did, fanning Nick along like a silent black hovercraft. This left Harry and Professor McGonagall alone together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This way, Potter,’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor,’ said Harry at once, ‘I swear I didn’t –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is out of my hands, Potter,’ said Professor McGonagall curtly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They marched in silence around a corner and she stopped before a large and extremely ugly stone gargoyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sherbet lemon!’ she said. This was evidently a password, because the gargoyle sprang suddenly to life, and hopped aside as the wall behind him split in two. Even full of dread for what was coming, Harry couldn’t fail to be amazed. Behind the wall was a spiral staircase which was moving smoothly upwards, like an escalator. As he and Professor McGonagall stepped onto it, Harry heard the wall thud closed behind them. They rose upwards in circles, higher and higher, until at last, slightly dizzy, Harry could </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Duelling Club 153 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">see a gleaming oak door ahead, with a brass knocker in the shape of a griffon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He knew where he was being taken. This must be where Dumbledore lived. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TWELVE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Polyjuice Potion</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They stepped off the stone staircase at the top and Professor McGonagall rapped on the door. It opened silently and they entered. Professor McGonagall told Harry to wait, and left him there, alone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked around. One thing was certain: of all the teachers’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">offices Harry had visited so far this year, Dumbledore’s was by far the  most  interesting.  If  he  hadn’t  been  scared  out  of  his  wits  that he was about to be thrown out of school, he would have been very pleased to have a chance to look around it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a large and beautiful circular room, full of funny little noises. A number of curious silver instruments stood on spindle-legged tables, whirring and emitting little puffs of smoke. The walls were covered with portraits of old headmasters and head-mistresses, all of whom were snoozing gently in their frames. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was also an enormous, claw-footed desk, and, sitting on a shelf behind it, a shabby, tattered wizard’s hat – the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Sorting Hat. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hesitated. He cast a wary eye around the sleeping witches and wizards on the walls. Surely it couldn’t hurt if he took the Hat down and tried it on again? Just to see … just to make sure it  <i class=\"calibre4\">had</i> put him in the right house. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He walked quietly around the desk, lifted the Hat from its shelf, and lowered it slowly onto his head. It was much too large and slipped down over his eyes, just as it had done the last time he’d put it on. Harry stared at the black inside of the Hat, waiting. Then a small voice said in his ear, ‘Bee in your bonnet, Harry Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er, yes,’ Harry muttered. ‘Er – sorry to bother you – I wanted to ask –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve been wondering whether I put you in the right house,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said the Hat smartly. ‘Yes … you were particularly difficult to place. But I stand by what I said before –’ Harry’s heart leapt ‘–  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Polyjuice Potion 155 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you  <i class=\"calibre4\">would</i> have done well in Slytherin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s stomach plummeted. He grabbed the point of the Hat and pulled it off. It hung limply in his hand, grubby and faded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pushed it back onto its shelf, feeling sick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re wrong,’ he said aloud to the still and silent Hat. It didn’t move. Harry backed away, watching it. Then a strange, gagging noise behind him made him wheel around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He wasn’t alone after all. Standing on a golden perch behind the door was a decrepit-looking bird which resembled a half-plucked turkey. Harry stared at it and the bird looked balefully back, making its gagging noise again. Harry thought it looked very ill. Its eyes were dull and, even as Harry watched, a couple more feathers fell out of its tail. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was just thinking that all he needed was for Dumbledore’s pet bird to die while he was alone in the office with it, when the bird burst into flames. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry yelled in shock and backed away into the desk. He looked feverishly around in case there was a glass of water somewhere, but couldn’t see one. The bird, meanwhile, had become a fireball; it gave one loud shriek and next second there was nothing but a smouldering pile of ash on the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The office door opened. Dumbledore came in, looking very sombre. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor,’ Harry gasped, ‘your bird – I couldn’t do anything – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he just caught fire –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To Harry’s astonishment, Dumbledore smiled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘About time, too,’ he said. ‘He’s been looking dreadful for days, I’ve been telling him to get a move on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He chuckled at the stunned look on Harry’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fawkes is a phoenix, Harry. Phoenixes burst into flame when it is time for them to die and are reborn from the ashes. Watch him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked down in time to see a tiny, wrinkled, new-born bird poke its head out of the ashes. It was quite as ugly as the old one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s a shame you had to see him on a Burning Day,’ said Dumbledore, seating himself behind his desk. ‘He’s really very handsome most of the time: wonderful red and gold plumage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fascinating creatures, phoenixes. They can carry immensely heavy loads, their tears have healing powers and they make highly <i class=\"calibre4\">faithful</i> pets.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>156 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In the shock of Fawkes catching fire, Harry had forgotten what he was there for, but it all came back to him as Dumbledore settled himself in the high-backed chair behind the desk and fixed Harry with his penetrating, light-blue stare. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before Dumbledore could speak another word, however, the door of the office flew open with an almighty bang and Hagrid burst in, a wild look in his eyes, his balaclava perched on top of his shaggy black head and the dead rooster still swinging from his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It wasn’ Harry, Professor Dumbledore!’ said Hagrid urgently. ‘I was talkin’ ter him  <i class=\"calibre4\">seconds</i> before that kid was found, he never had time, sir …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore tried to say something, but Hagrid went ranting on, waving the rooster around in his agitation, sending feathers everywhere. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… It can’t’ve bin him, I’ll swear it in front o’ the Ministry o’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Magic if I have to …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid, I –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… Yeh’ve got the wrong boy, sir, I  <i class=\"calibre4\">know</i> Harry never –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Hagrid! </i>’ said Dumbledore loudly. ‘I do  <i class=\"calibre4\">not</i> think that Harry attacked those people.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said Hagrid, the rooster falling limply at his side. ‘Right. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I’ll wait outside then, Headmaster.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he stomped out looking embarrassed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t think it was me, Professor?’ Harry repeated hopefully, as Dumbledore brushed rooster feathers off his desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, Harry, I don’t,’ said Dumbledore, though his face was sombre again. ‘But I still want to talk to you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry waited nervously while Dumbledore considered him, the tips of his long fingers together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I must ask you, Harry, whether there is anything you’d like to tell me,’ he said gently. ‘Anything at all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t know what to say. He thought of Malfoy shouting, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll be next, Mudbloods!’ and of the Polyjuice Potion, simmer-ing away in Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. Then he thought of the disembodied voice he had heard twice and remembered what Ron had said: ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Hearing voices no one else can hear isn’t a good sign, even</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">in the wizarding world. </i>’ He thought, too, about what everyone was saying about him, and his growing dread that he was somehow connected with Salazar Slytherin … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Polyjuice Potion 157 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry, ‘there isn’t anything, Professor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The double attack on Justin and Nearly Headless Nick turned what had hitherto been nervousness into real panic. Curiously, it was Nearly Headless Nick’s fate that seemed to worry people most. What could possibly do that to a ghost, people asked each other; what terrible power could harm someone who was already dead? There was almost a stampede to book seats on the Hogwarts Express so that students could go home for Christmas. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘At this rate, we’ll be the only ones left,’ Ron told Harry and Hermione. ‘Us, Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle. What a jolly holiday it’s going to be.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle, who always did whatever Malfoy did, had signed up to stay over the holidays too. But Harry was glad that most people were leaving. He was tired of people skirting around him in the corridors, as though he was about to sprout fangs or spit poison; tired of all the muttering, pointing and hissing as he passed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred and George, however, found all this very funny. They went out of their way to march ahead of Harry down the corridors, shouting, ‘Make way for the heir of Slytherin, seriously evil wizard coming through …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy was deeply disapproving of this behaviour. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It is  <i class=\"calibre4\">not</i> a laughing matter,’ he said coldly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, get out of the way, Percy,’ said Fred. ‘Harry’s in a hurry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, he’s nipping off to the Chamber of Secrets for a cup of tea with his fanged servant,’ said George, chortling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny didn’t find it amusing either. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,  <i class=\"calibre4\">don’t, </i>’ she wailed every time Fred asked Harry loudly who he was planning to attack next, or George pretended to ward Harry off with a large clove of garlic when they met. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t mind; it made him feel better that Fred and George, at least, thought the idea of his being Slytherin’s heir was quite ludicrous. But their antics seemed to be aggravating Draco Malfoy, who looked increasingly sour each time he saw them at it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s because he’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">bursting</i> to say it’s really him,’ said Ron knowingly. ‘You know how he hates anyone beating him at anything, and you’re getting all the credit for his dirty work.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not for long,’ said Hermione in a satisfied tone. ‘The Polyjuice </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>158 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Potion’s nearly ready. We’ll be getting the truth out of him any day now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last the term ended, and a silence deep as the snow on the grounds descended on the castle. Harry found it peaceful, rather than gloomy, and enjoyed the fact that he, Hermione and the Weasleys had the run of Gryffindor Tower, which meant they could play Exploding Snap loudly without bothering anyone, and practise duelling in private. Fred, George and Ginny had chosen to stay at school rather than visit Bill in Egypt with Mr and Mrs Weasley. Percy, who disapproved of what he termed their childish behaviour, didn’t spend much time in the Gryffindor common room. He had already told them pompously that  <i class=\"calibre4\">he</i> was only staying over Christmas because it was his duty as a Prefect to support the teachers during this troubled time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Christmas morning dawned, cold and white. Harry and Ron, the only ones left in their dormitory, were woken very early by Hermione, who burst in, fully dressed and carrying presents for them both. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wake up,’ she said loudly, pulling back the curtains at the window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione – you’re not supposed to be in here,’ said Ron, shielding his eyes against the light. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Merry Christmas to you, too,’ said Hermione, throwing him his present. ‘I’ve been up for nearly an hour, adding more lacewings to the Potion. It’s ready.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat up, suddenly wide awake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you sure?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Positive,’ said Hermione, shifting Scabbers the rat so that she could sit down on the end of his four-poster. ‘If we’re going to do it, I say it should be tonight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment, Hedwig swooped into the room, carrying a very small package in her beak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello,’ said Harry happily, as she landed on his bed, ‘are you speaking to me again?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She nibbled his ear in an affectionate sort of way, which was a far better present than the one which she had brought him, which turned out to be from the Dursleys. They had sent Harry a tooth-pick and a note telling him to find out whether he’d be able to stay at Hogwarts for the summer holidays, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Polyjuice Potion 159 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rest of Harry’s Christmas presents were far more satisfac-tory. Hagrid had sent him a large tin of treacle fudge, which Harry decided to soften by the fire before eating; Ron had given him a book called  <i class=\"calibre4\">Flying with the Cannons, </i> a book of interesting facts about his favourite Quidditch team; and Hermione had bought him a luxury eagle-feather quill. Harry opened the last present to find a new, hand-knitted jumper from Mrs Weasley, and a large plum cake. He put up her card with a fresh surge of guilt, thinking about Mr Weasley’s car, which hadn’t been seen since its crash with the Whomping Willow, and the bout of rule-breaking he and Ron were planning next. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No one, not even someone dreading taking Polyjuice Potion later, could fail to enjoy Christmas dinner at Hogwarts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Great Hall looked magnificent. Not only were there a dozen frost-covered Christmas trees and thick streamers of holly and mistletoe criss-crossing the ceiling, but enchanted snow was falling, warm and dry, from the ceiling. Dumbledore led them in a few of his favourite carols, Hagrid booming more and more loudly with every goblet of eggnog he consumed. Percy, who hadn’t noticed that Fred had bewitched his prefect badge so that it now read ‘Pinhead’, kept asking them all what they were sniggering at. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t even care that Draco Malfoy was making loud, snide remarks about his new jumper from the Slytherin table. With a bit of luck, Malfoy would be getting his come-uppance in a few hours’ time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron had barely finished their third helpings of Christmas pudding when Hermione ushered them out of the Hall to finalise their plans for the evening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We still need a bit of the people you’re changing into,’ said Hermione matter-of-factly, as though she was sending them to the supermarket for washing-powder. ‘And obviously, it’ll be best if you can get something of Crabbe and Goyle’s; they’re Malfoy’s best friends, he’ll tell them anything. And we also need to make sure the real Crabbe and Goyle can’t burst in on us while we’re interro-gating him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve got it all worked out,’ she went on smoothly, ignoring Harry and Ron’s stupefied faces. She held up two plump chocolate cakes. ‘I’ve filled these with a simple Sleeping Draught. All you have to do is make sure Crabbe and Goyle find them. You know </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>160 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">how greedy they are, they’re bound to eat them. Once they’re asleep, pull out a few of their hairs and hide them in a broom cupboard.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron looked incredulously at each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, I don’t think –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That could go seriously wrong –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione had a steely glint in her eye not unlike the one Professor McGonagall sometimes had. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Potion will be useless without Crabbe and Goyle’s hair,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">she said sternly. ‘You do  <i class=\"calibre4\">want</i> to investigate Malfoy, don’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, all right, all right,’ said Harry. ‘But what about you? Whose hair are you ripping out?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve already got mine!’ said Hermione brightly, pulling a tiny bottle out of her pocket and showing them the single hair inside it. ‘Remember Millicent Bulstrode wrestling with me at the Duelling Club? She left this on my robes when she was trying to strangle me! And she’s gone home for Christmas – so I’ll just have to tell the Slytherins I’ve decided to come back.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Hermione had bustled off to check on the Polyjuice Potion again, Ron turned to Harry with a doom-laden expression. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you ever heard of a plan where so many things could go wrong?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But to Harry and Ron’s utter amazement, stage one of the operation went just as smoothly as Hermione had said. They lurked in the deserted Entrance Hall after Christmas tea, waiting for Crabbe and Goyle, who had remained alone at the Slytherin table, shovel-ling down fourth helpings of trifle. Harry had perched the chocolate cakes on the end of the banisters. When they spotted Crabbe and Goyle coming out of the Great Hall, Harry and Ron hid quickly behind a suit of armour next to the front door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How thick can you get?’ Ron whispered ecstatically, as Crabbe gleefully pointed out the cakes to Goyle and grabbed them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grinning stupidly, they stuffed the cakes whole into their large mouths. For a moment, both of them chewed greedily, looks of triumph on their faces. Then, without the smallest change of expression, they both keeled over backwards onto the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Much the most difficult bit was hiding them in the cupboard across the hall. Once they were safely stowed amongst the buckets and mops, Harry yanked out a couple of the bristles that covered </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Polyjuice Potion 161 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Goyle’s forehead and Ron pulled out several of Crabbe’s hairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They also stole their shoes, because their own were far too small for Crabbe- and Goyle-sized feet. Then, still stunned at what they had just done, they sprinted up to Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They could hardly see for the thick black smoke issuing from the cubicle in which Hermione was stirring the cauldron. Pulling their robes up over their faces, Harry and Ron knocked softly on the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They heard the scrape of the lock and Hermione emerged, shiny-faced and looking anxious. Behind her they heard the  <i class=\"calibre4\">gloop</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">gloop</i> of the bubbling, treacle-thick Potion. Three glass tumblers stood ready on the toilet seat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you get them?’ Hermione asked breathlessly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry showed her Goyle’s hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good. And I sneaked these spare robes out of the laundry,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione said, holding up a small sack. ‘You’ll need bigger sizes once you’re Crabbe and Goyle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The three of them stared into the cauldron. Close up, the Potion looked like thick, dark mud, bubbling sluggishly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sure I’ve done everything right,’ said Hermione, nervously re-reading the splotched page of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Moste Potente Potions. </i> ‘It looks like the book says it should … Once we’ve drunk it, we’ll have exactly an hour before we change back into ourselves.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now what?’ Ron whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We separate it into three glasses and add the hairs.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione ladled large dollops of the Potion into each of the glasses. Then, her hand trembling, she shook Millicent Bulstrode’s hair out of its bottle into the first glass. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Potion hissed loudly like a boiling kettle and frothed madly. A second later, it had turned a sick sort of yellow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Urgh – essence of Millicent Bulstrode,’ said Ron, eyeing it with loathing. ‘Bet it tastes disgusting.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Add yours, then,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dropped Goyle’s hair into the middle glass and Ron put Crabbe’s into the last one. Both glasses hissed and frothed: Goyle’s turned the khaki colour of a bogey, Crabbe’s a dark, murky brown. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on,’ said Harry, as Ron and Hermione reached for their glasses. ‘We’d better not all drink them in here: once we turn into </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>162 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle we won’t fit. And Millicent Bulstrode’s no pixie.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good thinking,’ said Ron, unlocking the door. ‘We’ll take separate cubicles.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Careful not to spill a drop of his Polyjuice Potion, Harry slipped into the middle cubicle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready?’ he called. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready,’ came Ron and Hermione’s voices. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One … two … three …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pinching his nose, Harry drank the Potion down in two large gulps. It tasted like overcooked cabbage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Immediately, his insides started writhing as though he’d just swallowed live snakes – doubled up, he wondered whether he was going to be sick – then a burning sensation spread rapidly from his stomach to the very ends of his fingers and toes. Next, bringing him gasping to all fours, came a horrible melting feeling, as the skin all over his body bubbled like hot wax, and before his eyes, his hands began to grow, the fingers thickened, the nails broadened and the knuckles were bulging like bolts. His shoulders stretched painfully and a prickling on his forehead told him that hair was creeping down towards his eyebrows; his robes ripped as his chest expanded like a barrel bursting its hoops; his feet were agony in shoes four sizes too small … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As suddenly as it had started, everything stopped. Harry lay face down on the cold stone floor, listening to Myrtle gurgling morosely in the end toilet. With difficulty, he kicked off his shoes and stood up. So this was what it felt like, being Goyle. His large hands trembling, he pulled off his old robes, which were hanging a foot above his ankles, pulled on the spare ones and laced up Goyle’s boat-like shoes. He reached up to brush his hair out of his eyes and met only the short growth of wiry bristles, low on his forehead. Then he realised that his glasses were clouding his eyes, because Goyle obviously didn’t need them. He took them off and called, ‘Are you two OK?’ Goyle’s low rasp of a voice issued from his mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ came the deep grunt of Crabbe from his right. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry unlocked his door and stepped in front of the cracked mirror. Goyle stared back at him out of dull, deep-set eyes. Harry scratched his ear. So did Goyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s door opened. They stared at each other. Except that he looked pale and shocked, Ron was indistinguishable from Crabbe, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Polyjuice Potion 163 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">from the pudding-basin haircut to the long, gorilla arms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is unbelievable,’ said Ron, approaching the mirror and prodding Crabbe’s flat nose. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Unbelievable</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d better get going,’ said Harry, loosening the watch that was cutting into Goyle’s thick wrist. ‘We’ve still got to find out where the Slytherin common room is, I only hope we can find someone to follow …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron, who had been gazing at Harry, said, ‘You don’t know how bizarre it is to see Goyle  <i class=\"calibre4\">thinking</i>.’ He banged on Hermione’s door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon, we need to go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A high-pitched voice answered him. ‘I – I don’t think I’m going to come after all. You go on without me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, we know Millicent Bulstrode’s ugly, no one’s going to know it’s you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – really – I don’t think I’ll come. You two hurry up, you’re wasting time.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked at Ron, bewildered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">That</i> looks more like Goyle,’ said Ron. ‘That’s how he looks every time a teacher asks him a question.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, are you OK?’ said Harry through the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fine – I’m fine … Go on –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked at his watch. Five of their precious sixty minutes had already passed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll meet you back here, all right?’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron opened the door of the bathroom carefully, checked that the coast was clear and set off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t swing your arms like that,’ Harry muttered to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Crabbe holds them sort of stiff …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How’s this?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, that’s better.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They went down the marble staircase. All they needed now was a Slytherin whom they could follow to the Slytherin common room, but there was nobody around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Any ideas?’ muttered Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Slytherins always come up to breakfast from over there,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Ron, nodding at the entrance to the dungeons. The words had barely left his mouth when a girl with long curly hair emerged from the entrance. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excuse me,’ said Ron, hurrying up to her, ‘we’ve forgotten the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>164 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">way to our common room.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I beg your pardon?’ said the girl stiffly. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Our</i> common room?  <i class=\"calibre4\">I’m</i> a Ravenclaw.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She walked away, looking suspiciously back at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron hurried down the stone steps into the darkness, their footsteps echoing particularly loudly as Crabbe and Goyle’s huge feet hit the floor, feeling that this wasn’t going to be as easy as they had hoped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The labyrinthine passages were deserted. They walked deeper and deeper under the school, constantly checking their watches to see how much time they had left. After a quarter of an hour, just when they were getting desperate, they heard a sudden movement ahead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ha!’ said Ron excitedly. ‘There’s one of them now!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The figure was emerging from a side room. As they hurried nearer, however, their hearts sank. It wasn’t a Slytherin, it was Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’re you doing down here?’ said Ron in surprise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy looked affronted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That,’ he said stiffly, ‘is none of your business. It’s Crabbe, isn’t it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wh– oh, yeah,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, get off to your dormitories,’ said Percy sternly. ‘It’s not safe to go wandering around dark corridors these days.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You</i> are,’ Ron pointed out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I,’ said Percy, drawing himself up, ‘am a Prefect. Nothing’s about to attack  <i class=\"calibre4\">me. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A voice suddenly echoed behind Harry and Ron. Draco Malfoy was strolling towards them, and for the first time in his life, Harry was pleased to see him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There you are,’ he drawled, looking at them. ‘Have you two been pigging out in the Great Hall all this time? I’ve been looking for you, I want to show you something really funny.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy glanced witheringly at Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what’re you doing down here, Weasley?’ he sneered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy looked outraged. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You want to show a bit more respect to a school Prefect!’ he said. ‘I don’t like your attitude!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy sneered and motioned Harry and Ron to follow him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry almost said something apologetic to Percy but caught him-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Polyjuice Potion 165 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">self just in time. He and Ron hurried after Malfoy, who said as they turned into the next passage, ‘That Peter Weasley –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Percy,’ Ron corrected him automatically. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Whatever,’ said Malfoy. ‘I’ve noticed him sneaking around a lot lately. And I bet I know what he’s up to. He thinks he’s going to catch Slytherin’s heir single-handed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gave a short, derisive laugh. Harry and Ron exchanged excited looks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy paused by a stretch of bare, damp stone wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the new password again?’ he said to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er –’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh yeah –  <i class=\"calibre4\">pure-blood! </i>’ said Malfoy, not listening, and a stone door concealed in the wall slid open. Malfoy marched through it and Harry and Ron followed him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Slytherin common room was a long, low underground room with rough stone walls and ceiling, from which round, greenish lamps were hanging on chains. A fire was crackling under an elaborately carved mantelpiece ahead of them, and several Slytherins were silhouetted around it in carved chairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wait here,’ said Malfoy to Harry and Ron, motioning them to a pair of empty chairs set back from the fire. ‘I’ll go and get it – my father’s just sent it to me –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wondering what Malfoy was going to show them, Harry and Ron sat down, doing their best to look at home. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy came back a minute later, holding what looked like a newspaper cutting. He thrust it under Ron’s nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’ll give you a laugh,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry saw Ron’s eyes widen in shock. He read the cutting quickly, gave a very forced laugh and handed it to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It had been clipped out of the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet, </i> and it said: <i class=\"calibre4\">ENQUIRY AT THE MINISTRY OF MAGIC</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Arthur Weasley, Head of the Misuse of Muggle Artefacts Office,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">was today fined fifty Galleons for bewitching a Muggle car. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Mr Lucius Malfoy, a governor of Hogwarts School of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Witchcraft and Wizardry, where the enchanted car crashed earlier</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">this year, called today for Mr Weasley’s resignation. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">‘Weasley has brought the Ministry into disrepute,’ Mr</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Malfoy told our reporter. ‘He is clearly unfit to draw up our</i>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>166 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">laws and his ridiculous Muggle Protection Act should be scrapped</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">immediately.’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Mr Weasley was unavailable for comment, although his</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">wife told reporters to clear off or she’d set the family ghoul</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">on them. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well?’ said Malfoy impatiently, as Harry handed the cutting back to him. ‘Don’t you think it’s funny?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ha, ha,’ said Harry bleakly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Arthur Weasley loves Muggles so much he should snap his wand in half and go and join them,’ said Malfoy scornfully. ‘You’d never know the Weasleys were pure-bloods, the way they behave.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s – or rather, Crabbe’s – face was contorted with fury. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up with you, Crabbe?’ snapped Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stomach ache,’ Ron grunted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, go up to the hospital wing and give all those Mudbloods a kick from me,’ said Malfoy, snickering. ‘You know, I’m surprised the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i> hasn’t reported all these attacks yet,’ he went on thoughtfully. ‘I suppose Dumbledore’s trying to hush it all up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He’ll be sacked if it doesn’t stop soon. Father’s always said Dumbledore’s the worst thing that’s ever happened to this place. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He loves Muggle-borns. A decent Headmaster would never’ve let slime like that Creevey in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy started taking pictures with an imaginary camera and did a cruel but accurate impression of Colin: ‘Potter, can I have your picture, Potter? Can I have your autograph? Can I lick your shoes, please, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He dropped his hands and looked at Harry and Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the  <i class=\"calibre4\">matter</i> with you two?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Far too late, Harry and Ron forced themselves to laugh, but Malfoy seemed satisfied; perhaps Crabbe and Goyle were always slow on the uptake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Saint Potter, the Mudbloods’ friend,’ said Malfoy slowly. ‘He’s another one with no proper wizard feeling, or he wouldn’t go around with that jumped-up Granger Mudblood. And people think  <i class=\"calibre4\">he’s</i> Slytherin’s heir!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron waited with bated breath: Malfoy was surely seconds away from telling them it was him. But then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I   <i class=\"calibre4\">wish</i> I knew who it  <i class=\"calibre4\">is, </i>’ said Malfoy petulantly. ‘I could help them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Polyjuice Potion 167 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s jaw dropped so that Crabbe’s face looked even more gormless than usual. Fortunately, Malfoy didn’t notice, and Harry, thinking fast, said, ‘You must have some idea who’s behind it all …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know I haven’t, Goyle, how many times do I have to tell you?’ snapped Malfoy. ‘And father won’t tell me  <i class=\"calibre4\">anything</i> about the last time the Chamber was opened, either. Of course, it was fifty years ago, so it was before his time, but he knows all about it, and he says that it was all kept quiet and it’ll look suspicious if I know too much about it. But I know one thing: last time the Chamber of Secrets was opened, a Mudblood  <i class=\"calibre4\">died. </i> So I bet it’s only a matter of time before one of them’s killed this time … I hope it’s Granger,’ he said with relish. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was clenching Crabbe’s gigantic fists. Feeling that it would be a bit of a give-away if Ron punched Malfoy, Harry shot him a warning look and said, ‘D’you know if the person who opened the Chamber last time was caught?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yeah … whoever it was was expelled,’ said Malfoy. ‘They’re probably still in Azkaban.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Azkaban?’ said Harry, puzzled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Azkaban –  <i class=\"calibre4\">the wizard prison, </i> Goyle,’ said Malfoy, looking at him in disbelief. ‘Honestly, if you were any slower, you’d be going backwards.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He shifted restlessly in his chair and said, ‘Father says to keep my head down and let the heir of Slytherin get on with it. He says the school needs ridding of all the Mudblood filth, but not to get mixed up in it. Of course, he’s got a lot on his plate at the moment. You know the Ministry of Magic raided our Manor last week?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to force Goyle’s dull face into a look of concern. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah …’ said Malfoy. ‘Luckily, they didn’t find much. Father’s got some  <i class=\"calibre4\">very</i> valuable Dark Arts stuff. But luckily, we’ve got our own secret chamber under the drawing-room floor –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ho!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy looked at him. So did Harry. Ron blushed. Even his hair was turning red. His nose was also slowly lengthening – their hour was up. Ron was turning back into himself, and from the look of horror he was suddenly giving Harry, he must be, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They both jumped to their feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Medicine for my stomach,’ Ron grunted, and without further </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>168 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ado they sprinted the length of the Slytherin common room, hurled themselves at the stone wall and dashed up the passage, hoping against hope that Malfoy hadn’t noticed anything. Harry could feel his feet slipping around in Goyle’s huge shoes and had to hoist up his robes as he shrank; they crashed up the steps into the dark Entrance Hall, which was full of a muffled pounding coming from the cupboard where they’d locked Crabbe and Goyle. Leaving their shoes outside the cupboard door, they sprinted in their socks up the marble staircase towards Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, it wasn’t a complete waste of time,’ Ron panted, closing the bathroom door behind them. ‘I know we still haven’t found out who’s doing the attacks, but I’m going to write to Dad tomorrow and tell him to check under the Malfoys’ drawing room.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry checked his face in the cracked mirror. He was back to normal. He put his glasses on as Ron hammered on the door of Hermione’s cubicle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, come out, we’ve got loads to tell you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go away!’ Hermione squeaked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron looked at each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the matter?’ said Ron. ‘You must be back to normal by now, we are …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Moaning Myrtle glided suddenly through the cubicle door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never seen her looking so happy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ooooooh, wait till you see,’ she said. ‘It’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">awful! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They heard the lock slide back and Hermione emerged, sobbing, her robes pulled up over her head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up?’ said Ron uncertainly. ‘Have you still got Millicent’s nose or something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione let her robes fall and Ron backed into the sink. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Her face was covered in black fur. Her eyes had gone yellow and there were long pointed ears poking through her hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was a c-cat hair!’ she howled. ‘M-Millicent Bulstrode m-must have a cat! And the P-Potion isn’t supposed to be used for animal transformations!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Uh oh,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll be teased something  <i class=\"calibre4\">dreadful, </i>’ said Myrtle happily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s OK, Hermione,’ said Harry quickly. ‘We’ll take you up to the hospital wing. Madam Pomfrey never asks too many questions …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Polyjuice Potion 169 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took a long time to persuade Hermione to leave the bathroom. Moaning Myrtle sped them on their way with a hearty guffaw. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wait till everyone finds out you’ve got a  <i class=\"calibre4\">tail! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER THIRTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Very Secret Diary</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione remained in the hospital wing for several weeks. There was a flurry of rumour about her disappearance when the rest of the school arrived back from their Christmas holidays, because of course everyone thought that she had been attacked. So many students filed past the hospital wing trying to catch a glimpse of her that Madam Pomfrey took out her curtains again and placed them around Hermione’s bed, to spare her the shame of being seen with a furry face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron went to visit her every evening. When the new term started, they brought her each day’s homework. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I’d sprouted whiskers, I’d take a break from work,’ said Ron, tipping a stack of books onto Hermione’s bedside table one evening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be silly, Ron, I’ve got to keep up,’ said Hermione briskly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Her spirits were greatly improved by the fact that all the hair had gone from her face and her eyes were turning slowly back to brown. ‘I don’t suppose you’ve got any new leads?’ she added in a whisper, so that Madam Pomfrey couldn’t hear her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ said Harry gloomily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I was so  <i class=\"calibre4\">sure</i> it was Malfoy,’ said Ron, for about the hundredth time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ asked Harry, pointing to something gold sticking out from under Hermione’s pillow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just a Get Well card,’ said Hermione hastily, trying to poke it out of sight, but Ron was too quick for her. He pulled it out, flicked it open and read aloud: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">To Miss Granger, wishing you a speedy recovery, from your concerned teacher, Professor Gilderoy Lockhart, Order of Merlin, Third</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Class, Honorary Member of the Dark Force Defence League and five</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">times winner of </i> Witch Weekly’ <i class=\"calibre4\">s Most-Charming-Smile Award</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Very Secret Diary 171 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron looked up at Hermione, disgusted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You sleep with this under your  <i class=\"calibre4\">pillow? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione was spared answering by Madam Pomfrey sweeping over with her evening dose of medicine. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is Lockhart the smarmiest bloke you’ve ever met, or what?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron said to Harry as they left the dormitory and started up the stairs towards Gryffindor Tower. Snape had given them so much homework, Harry thought he was likely to be in the sixth year before he finished it. Ron was just saying he wished he had asked Hermione how many rat tails you were supposed to add to a Hair-Raising Potion, when an angry outburst from the floor above reached their ears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s Filch,’ Harry muttered, as they hurried up the stairs and paused, out of sight, listening hard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t think someone else’s been attacked?’ said Ron tensely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They stood still, their heads inclined towards Filch’s voice, which sounded quite hysterical. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… <i class=\"calibre4\"> even more work for me! Mopping all night, like I haven’t got</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">enough to do! No, this is the final straw, I’m going to Dumbledore </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His footsteps receded and they heard a distant door slam. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They poked their heads around the corner. Filch had clearly been manning his usual lookout post: they were once again on the spot where Mrs Norris had been attacked. They saw at a glance what Filch had been shouting about. A great flood of water stretched over half the corridor, and it looked as though it was still seeping from under the door of Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Now Filch had stopped shouting, they could hear Myrtle’s wails echoing off the bathroom walls. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Now</i> what’s up with her?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s go and see,’ said Harry, and holding their robes over their ankles they stepped through the great wash of water to the door bearing its ‘Out of Order’ sign, ignored it as always, and entered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Moaning Myrtle was crying, if possible, louder and harder than ever before. She seemed to be hiding down her usual toilet. It was dark in the bathroom, because the candles had been extinguished in the great rush of water that had left both walls and floor soaking wet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up, Myrtle?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s that?’ glugged Myrtle miserably. ‘Come to throw some-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>172 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">thing else at me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry waded across to her cubicle and said, ‘Why would I throw something at you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t ask me,’ Myrtle shouted, emerging with a wave of yet more water, which splashed onto the already sopping floor. ‘Here I am, minding my own business, and someone thinks it’s funny to throw a book at me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But it can’t hurt you if someone throws something at you,’ said Harry, reasonably. ‘I mean, it’d just go right through you, wouldn’t it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had said the wrong thing. Myrtle puffed herself up and shrieked, ‘Let’s all throw books at Myrtle, because  <i class=\"calibre4\">she</i> can’t feel it! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ten points if you can get it through her stomach! Fifty points if it goes through her head! Well, ha ha ha! What a lovely game, I <i class=\"calibre4\">don’t</i> think!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who threw it at you, anyway?’ asked Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> don’t know … I was just sitting in the U-bend, thinking about death, and it fell right through the top of my head,’ said Myrtle, glaring at them. ‘It’s over there, it got washed out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron looked under the sink, where Myrtle was pointing. A small, thin book lay there. It had a shabby black cover and was as wet as everything else in the bathroom. Harry stepped forward to pick it up, but Ron suddenly flung out an arm to hold him back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you mad?’ said Ron. ‘It could be dangerous.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Dangerous? </i>’ said Harry, laughing. ‘Come off it, how could it be dangerous?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d be surprised,’ said Ron, who was looking apprehensively at the book. ‘Some of the books the Ministry’s confiscated – Dad’s told me – there was one that burned your eyes out. And everyone who read  <i class=\"calibre4\">Sonnets of a Sorcerer</i> spoke in limericks for the rest of their lives. And some old witch in Bath had a book that you could <i class=\"calibre4\">never stop reading! </i> You just had to wander around with your nose in it, trying to do everything one-handed. And –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, I’ve got the point,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The little book lay on the floor, nondescript and soggy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, we won’t find out unless we look at it,’ he said, and he ducked round Ron and picked it off the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry saw at once that it was a diary, and the faded year on the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Very Secret Diary 173 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">cover told him it was fifty years old. He opened it eagerly. On the first page he could just make out the name ‘T. M. Riddle’ in smudged ink. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on,’ said Ron, who had approached cautiously and was looking over Harry’s shoulder. ‘I know that name … T. M. Riddle got an award for special services to the school fifty years ago.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How on earth d’you know that?’ said Harry in amazement. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because Filch made me polish his shield about fifty times in detention,’ said Ron resentfully. ‘That was the one I burped slugs all over. If you’d wiped slime off a name for an hour, you’d remember it, too.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry peeled the wet pages apart. They were completely blank. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There wasn’t the faintest trace of writing on any of them, not even </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Auntie Mabel’s birthday’, or ‘dentist, half past three’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He never wrote in it,’ said Harry, disappointed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wonder why someone wanted to flush it away?’ said Ron curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned to the back cover of the book and saw the printed name of a newsagent’s in Vauxhall Road, London. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He must’ve been Muggle-born,’ said Harry thoughtfully, ‘to have bought a diary from Vauxhall Road …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, it’s not much use to you,’ said Ron. He dropped his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fifty points if you can get it through Myrtle’s nose.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, however, pocketed it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione left the hospital wing, de-whiskered, tail-less and fur-free, at the beginning of February. On her first evening back in Gryffindor Tower, Harry showed her T. M. Riddle’s diary and told her the story of how they had found it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oooh, it might have hidden powers,’ said Hermione enthusiastically, taking the diary and looking at it closely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If it has, it’s hiding them very well,’ said Ron. ‘Maybe it’s shy. I don’t know why you don’t chuck it, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wish I knew why someone  <i class=\"calibre4\">did</i> try to chuck it,’ said Harry. ‘I wouldn’t mind knowing how Riddle got an award for special services to Hogwarts, either.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Could’ve been anything,’ said Ron. ‘Maybe he got thirty O.W.Ls or saved a teacher from the giant squid. Maybe he murdered Myrtle, that would’ve done everyone a favour …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry could tell from the arrested look on Hermione’s face </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>174 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">that she was thinking what he was thinking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Ron, looking from one to the other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, the Chamber of Secrets was opened fifty years ago, wasn’t it?’ he said. ‘That’s what Malfoy said.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah …’ said Ron slowly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And   <i class=\"calibre4\">this diary</i> is fifty years old,’ said Hermione, tapping it excitedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Ron, wake up,’ snapped Hermione. ‘We know the person who opened the Chamber last time was expelled  <i class=\"calibre4\">fifty years ago. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We know T. M. Riddle got an award for special services to the school   <i class=\"calibre4\">fifty years ago. </i> Well, what if Riddle got his special award for  <i class=\"calibre4\">catching the heir of Slytherin? </i> His diary would probably tell us everything: where the Chamber is, and how to open it, and what sort of creature lives in it. The person who’s behind the attacks this time wouldn’t want that lying around, would they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s a  <i class=\"calibre4\">brilliant</i> theory, Hermione,’ said Ron, ‘with just one tiny little flaw.  <i class=\"calibre4\">There’s nothing written in his diary. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione was pulling her wand out of her bag. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It might be invisible ink!’ she whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She tapped the diary three times and said, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Aparecium! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nothing happened. Undaunted, Hermione shoved her hand back into her bag and pulled out what appeared to be a bright red eraser. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s a Revealer, I got it in Diagon Alley,’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She rubbed hard on ‘January the first’. Nothing happened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m telling you, there’s nothing to find in there,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddle just got a diary for Christmas and couldn’t be bothered filling it in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t explain, even to himself, why he didn’t just throw Riddle’s diary away. The fact was that even though he  <i class=\"calibre4\">knew</i> the diary was blank, he kept absent-mindedly picking it up and turning the pages, as though it was a story he wanted to finish. And while Harry was sure he had never heard the name T. M. Riddle before, it still seemed to mean something to him, almost as though Riddle was a friend he’d had when he was very small, and half-forgotten. But this was absurd. He’d never had friends before Hogwarts, Dudley had made sure of that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nevertheless, Harry was determined to find out more about </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Very Secret Diary 175 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle, so, next day at break, he headed for the trophy room to examine Riddle’s special award, accompanied by an interested Hermione and a thoroughly unconvinced Ron, who told them he’d seen enough of the trophy room to last him a lifetime. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle’s burnished gold shield was tucked away in a corner cabinet. It didn’t carry details of why it had been given to him (‘Good thing, too, or it’d be even bigger and I’d still be polishing it,’ said Ron). However, they did find Riddle’s name on an old Medal for Magical Merit, and on a list of old Head Boys. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He sounds like Percy,’ said Ron, wrinkling his nose in disgust. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Prefect, Head Boy – probably top of every class.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You say that like it’s a bad thing,’ said Hermione, in a slightly hurt voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The sun had now begun to shine weakly on Hogwarts again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Inside the castle, the mood had grown more hopeful. There had been no more attacks since those on Justin and Nearly Headless Nick, and Madam Pomfrey was pleased to report that the Mandrakes were becoming moody and secretive, meaning that they were fast leaving childhood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The moment their acne clears up, they’ll be ready for re-potting again,’ Harry heard her telling Filch kindly one afternoon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And after that, it won’t be long until we’re cutting them up and stewing them. You’ll have Mrs Norris back in no time.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps the heir of Slytherin had lost his or her nerve, thought Harry. It must be getting riskier and riskier to open the Chamber of Secrets, with the school so alert and suspicious. Perhaps the monster, whatever it was, was even now settling itself down to hibernate for another fifty years … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ernie Macmillan of Hufflepuff didn’t take this cheerful view. He was still convinced that Harry was the guilty one, that he had </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘given himself away’ at the Duelling Club. Peeves wasn’t helping matters: he kept popping up in the crowded corridors singing ‘Oh Potter, you rotter …’, now with a dance-routine to match. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gilderoy Lockhart seemed to think he himself had made the attacks stop. Harry overheard him telling Professor McGonagall so while the Gryffindors were lining up for Transfiguration. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t think there’ll be any more trouble, Minerva,’ he said, tapping his nose knowingly and winking. ‘I think the Chamber has been locked for good this time. The culprit must have known </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>176 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">it was only a matter of time before I caught them. Rather sensible to stop now, before I came down hard on them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know, what the school needs now is a morale-booster. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wash away the memories of last term! I won’t say any more just now, but I think I know just the thing …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He tapped his nose again and strode off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart’s idea of a morale-booster became clear at breakfast time on February the fourteenth. Harry hadn’t had much sleep because of a late-running Quidditch practice the night before, and he hurried down to the Great Hall slightly late. He thought, for a moment, that he’d walked through the wrong doors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The walls were all covered with large, lurid pink flowers. Worse still, heart-shaped confetti was falling from the pale blue ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went over to the Gryffindor table, where Ron was sitting looking sickened, and Hermione seemed to have come over rather giggly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on?’ Harry asked them, sitting down, and wiping confetti off his bacon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron pointed to the teachers’ table, apparently too disgusted to speak. Lockhart, wearing lurid pink robes to match the decora-tions, was waving for silence. The teachers on either side of him were looking stony-faced. From where he sat, Harry could see a muscle going in Professor McGonagall’s cheek. Snape looked as though someone had just fed him a large beaker of Skele-Gro. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Happy Valentine’s Day!’ Lockhart shouted. ‘And may I thank the forty-six people who have so far sent me cards! Yes, I have taken the liberty of arranging this little surprise for you all – and it doesn’t end here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart clapped his hands and through the doors to the Entrance Hall marched a dozen surly-looking dwarfs. Not just any dwarfs, however. Lockhart had them all wearing golden wings and carrying harps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My friendly, card-carrying cupids!’ beamed Lockhart. ‘They will be roving around the school today delivering your Valentines! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And the fun doesn’t stop here! I’m sure my colleagues will want to enter into the spirit of the occasion! Why not ask Professor Snape to show you how to whip up a Love Potion! And while you’re at it, Professor Flitwick knows more about Entrancing Enchantments than any wizard I’ve ever met, the sly old dog!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Flitwick buried his face in his hands. Snape was look-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Very Secret Diary 177 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ing as though the first person to ask him for a Love Potion would be force-fed poison. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, Hermione, tell me you weren’t one of the forty-six,’ said Ron, as they left the Great Hall for their first lesson. Hermione suddenly became very interested in searching her bag for her timetable and didn’t answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All day long, the dwarfs kept barging into their classes to deliver Valentines, to the annoyance of the teachers, and late that afternoon, as the Gryffindors were walking upstairs for Charms, one of them caught up with Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oy, you! ’Arry Potter!’ shouted a particularly grim-looking dwarf, elbowing people out of the way to get to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hot all over at the thought of being given a Valentine in front of a queue of first-years, which happened to include Ginny Weasley, Harry tried to escape. The dwarf, however, cut his way through the crowd by kicking people’s shins, and reached him before he’d gone two paces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve got a musical message to deliver to ’Arry Potter in person,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he said, twanging his harp in a threatening sort of way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Not here, </i>’ Harry hissed, trying to escape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stay  <i class=\"calibre4\">still! </i>’ grunted the dwarf, grabbing hold of Harry’s bag and pulling him back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me go!’ Harry snarled, tugging. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a loud ripping noise, his bag split in two. His books, wand, parchment and quill spilled onto the floor and his ink bottle smashed over the lot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry scrambled around, trying to pick it all up before the dwarf started singing, causing something of a hold-up in the corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on here?’ came the cold, drawling voice of Draco Malfoy. Harry started stuffing everything feverishly into his ripped bag, desperate to get away before Malfoy could hear his musical Valentine. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s all this commotion?’ said another familiar voice, as Percy Weasley arrived. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Losing his head, Harry tried to make a run for it, but the dwarf seized him around the knees and brought him crashing to the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ he said, sitting on Harry’s ankles, ‘here is your singing Valentine: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>178 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">‘His eyes are as green as a fresh pickled toad,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">His hair is as dark as a blackboard. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I wish he was mine, he’s really divine,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">The hero who conquered the Dark Lord.’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry would have given all the gold in Gringotts to evaporate on the spot. Trying valiantly to laugh along with everyone else, he got up, his feet numb from the weight of the dwarf, as Percy Weasley did his best to disperse the crowd, some of whom were crying with mirth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Off you go, off you go, the bell rang five minutes ago, off to class, now,’ he said, shooing some of the younger students away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">And</i> you, Malfoy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, glancing over, saw Malfoy stoop and snatch up something. Leering, he showed it to Crabbe and Goyle, and Harry realised that he’d got Riddle’s diary. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Give that back,’ said Harry quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wonder what Potter’s written in this?’ said Malfoy, who obviously hadn’t noticed the year on the cover, and thought he had Harry’s own diary. A hush fell over the onlookers. Ginny was staring from the diary to Harry, looking terrified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hand it over, Malfoy,’ said Percy sternly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When I’ve had a look,’ said Malfoy, waving the diary tauntingly at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy said, ‘As a school Prefect –’, but Harry had lost his temper. He pulled out his wand and shouted, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expelliarmus! </i>’ and just as Snape had disarmed Lockhart, so Malfoy found the diary shooting out of his hand into the air. Ron, grinning broadly, caught it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ said Percy loudly. ‘No magic in the corridors. I’ll have to report this, you know!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry didn’t care, he’d got one over on Malfoy, and that was worth five points from Gryffindor any day. Malfoy was looking furious, and as Ginny passed him to enter her classroom, he yelled spitefully after her, ‘I don’t think Potter liked your Valentine much!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny covered her face with her hands and ran into class. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snarling, Ron pulled out his wand, too, but Harry pulled him away. Ron didn’t need to spend the whole of Charms belching slugs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It wasn’t until they had reached Professor Flitwick’s class that Harry noticed something rather odd about Riddle’s diary. All his </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Very Secret Diary 179 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">other books were drenched in scarlet ink. The diary, however, was as clean as it had been before the ink bottle had smashed all over it. He tried to point this out to Ron, but Ron was having trouble with his wand again; large purple bubbles were blossoming out of the end, and he wasn’t much interested in anything else. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went to bed before anyone else in his dormitory that night. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This was partly because he didn’t think he could stand Fred and George singing, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">His eyes are as green as a fresh pickled toad</i>’, one more time, and partly because he wanted to examine Riddle’s diary again, and knew that Ron thought he was wasting his time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000002999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat on his four-poster and flicked through the blank pages, not one of which had a trace of scarlet ink on it. Then he pulled a new bottle out of his bedside cabinet, dipped his quill into it, and dropped a blot onto the first page of the diary. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The ink shone brightly on the paper for a second and then, as though it was being sucked into the page, vanished. Excited, Harry loaded up his quill a second time and wrote, ‘My name is Harry Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The words shone momentarily on the page and they too sank without trace. Then, at last, something happened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Oozing back out of the page, in his very own ink, came words Harry had never written. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Hello, Harry Potter. My name is Tom Riddle. How did you come</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">by my diary? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">These words, too, faded away, but not before Harry had started to scribble back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Someone tried to flush it down a toilet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He waited eagerly for Riddle’s reply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lucky that I recorded my memories in some more lasting way than</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">ink. But I always knew that there would be those who would not want</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">this diary read</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do you mean?’ Harry scrawled, blotting the page in his excitement. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I mean that this diary holds memories of terrible things. Things</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">which were covered up. Things which happened at Hogwarts School</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">of Witchcraft and Wizardry</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s where I am now,’ Harry wrote quickly. ‘I’m at Hogwarts, and horrible stuff’s been happening. Do you know anything about the Chamber of Secrets?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>180 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His heart was hammering. Riddle’s reply came quickly, his writing becoming untidier, as though he was hurrying to tell all he knew. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Of course I know about the Chamber of Secrets. In my day, they</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">told us it was a legend, that it did not exist. But this was a lie. In my</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">fifth year, the Chamber was opened and the monster attacked several</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">students, finally killing one. I caught the person who’d opened the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Chamber and he was expelled. But the Headmaster, Professor Dippet,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">ashamed that such a thing had happened at Hogwarts, forbade me to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">tell the truth. A story was given out that the girl had died in a freak</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">accident. They gave me a nice, shiny, engraved trophy for my trouble</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">and warned me to keep my mouth shut. But I knew it could happen</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">again. The monster lived on, and the one who had the power to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">release it was not imprisoned</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry nearly upset his ink bottle in his hurry to write back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s happening again now. There have been three attacks and no one seems to know who’s behind them. Who was it last time?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I can show you, if you like,’</i> came Riddle’s reply.  <i class=\"calibre4\">‘You don’t have to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">take my word for it. I can take you inside my memory of the night</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">when I caught him</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hesitated, his quill suspended over the diary. What did Riddle mean? How could he be taken inside somebody else’s memory? He glanced nervously at the door to the dormitory, which was growing dark. When he looked back at the diary, he saw fresh words forming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Let me show you</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry paused for a fraction of a second and then wrote two letters. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The pages of the diary began to blow as though caught in a high wind, stopping halfway through the month of June. Mouth hanging open, Harry saw that the little square for June the thir-teenth seemed to have turned into a minuscule television screen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His hands trembling slightly, he raised the book to press his eye against the little window, and before he knew what was happening, he was tilting forwards; the window was widening, he felt his body leave his bed and he was pitched headfirst through the opening in the page, into a whirl of colour and shadow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He felt his feet hit solid ground, and stood, shaking, as the blurred shapes around him came suddenly into focus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Very Secret Diary 181 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He knew immediately where he was. This circular room with the sleeping portraits was Dumbledore’s office – but it wasn’t Dumbledore who was sitting behind the desk. A wizened, frail-looking wizard, bald except for a few wisps of white hair, was reading a letter by candlelight. Harry had never seen this man before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sorry,’ he said shakily, ‘I didn’t mean to butt in …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the wizard didn’t look up. He continued to read, frowning slightly. Harry drew nearer to his desk and stammered, ‘Er – I’ll just go, shall I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Still the wizard ignored him. He didn’t seem even to have heard him. Thinking that the wizard might be deaf, Harry raised his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry I disturbed you, I’ll go now,’ he half-shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The wizard folded up the letter with a sigh, stood up, walked past Harry without glancing at him and went to draw the curtains at his window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The sky outside the window was ruby red; it seemed to be sunset. The wizard went back to the desk, sat down and twiddled his thumbs, watching the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked around the office. No Fawkes the phoenix; no whirring silver contraptions. This was Hogwarts as Riddle had known it, meaning that this unknown wizard was Headmaster, not Dumbledore, and he, Harry, was little more than a phantom, completely invisible to the people of fifty years ago. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a knock on the office door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Enter,’ said the old wizard in a feeble voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A boy of about sixteen entered, taking off his pointed hat. A silver Prefect’s badge was glinting on his chest. He was much taller than Harry, but he, too, had jet-black hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, Riddle,’ said the Headmaster. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You wanted to see me, Professor Dippet?’ said Riddle. He looked nervous. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit down,’ said Dippet. ‘I’ve just been reading the letter you sent me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said Riddle. He sat down, gripping his hands together very tightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear boy,’ said Dippet kindly, ‘I cannot possibly let you stay at school over the summer. Surely you want to go home for the holidays?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>182 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Riddle at once, ‘I’d much rather stay at Hogwarts than go back to that – to that –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You live in a Muggle orphanage during the holidays, I believe?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Dippet curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, sir,’ said Riddle, reddening slightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You are Muggle-born?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Half-blood, sir,’ said Riddle. ‘Muggle father, witch mother.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And are both your parents –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My mother died just after I was born, sir. They told me at the orphanage she lived just long enough to name me: Tom after my father, Marvolo after my grandfather.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dippet clucked his tongue sympathetically. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The thing is, Tom,’ he sighed, ‘special arrangements might have been made for you, but in the current circumstances …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You mean all these attacks, sir?’ said Riddle, and Harry’s heart leapt, and he moved closer, scared of missing anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Precisely,’ said the Headmaster. ‘My dear boy, you must see how foolish it would be of me to allow you to remain at the castle when term ends. Particularly in the light of the recent tragedy … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the death of that poor little girl … You will be safer by far at your orphanage. As a matter of fact, the Ministry of Magic is even now talking about closing the school. We are no nearer locating the – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">er – source of all this unpleasantness …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle’s eyes had widened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sir – if the person was caught … If it all stopped …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do you mean?’ said Dippet, with a squeak in his voice, sitting up in his chair. ‘Riddle, do you mean you know something about these attacks?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, sir,’ said Riddle quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry was sure it was the same sort of ‘no’ that he himself had given Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dippet sank back, looking faintly disappointed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You may go, Tom …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle slid off his chair and stumped out of the room. Harry followed him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Down the moving spiral staircase they went, emerging next to the gargoyle in the darkening corridor. Riddle stopped, and so did Harry, watching him. Harry could tell that Riddle was doing some serious thinking. He was biting his lip, his forehead furrowed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, as though he had suddenly reached a decision, he hur-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Very Secret Diary 183 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ried off, Harry gliding noiselessly behind him. They didn’t see another person until they reached the Entrance Hall, when a tall wizard with long, sweeping auburn hair and beard called to Riddle from the marble staircase. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing, wandering around this late, Tom?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry gaped at the wizard. He was none other than a fifty-year-younger Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I had to see the Headmaster, sir,’ said Riddle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, hurry off to bed,’ said Dumbledore, giving Riddle exactly the kind of penetrating stare Harry knew so well. ‘Best not to roam the corridors these days. Not since …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He sighed heavily, bade Riddle goodnight and strode off. Riddle watched him out of sight and then, moving quickly, headed straight down the stone steps to the dungeons, with Harry in hot pursuit. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But to Harry’s disappointment, Riddle led him not into a hidden passageway or a secret tunnel but the very dungeon in which Harry had Potions with Snape. The torches hadn’t been lit, and when Riddle pushed the door almost closed, Harry could only just see Riddle, standing stock-still by the door, watching the passage outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It felt to Harry that they were there for at least an hour. All he could see was the figure of Riddle at the door, staring through the crack, waiting like a statue. And just when Harry had stopped feeling expectant and tense, and started wishing he could return to the present, he heard something move beyond the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Someone was creeping along the passage. He heard whoever it was pass the dungeon where he and Riddle were hidden. Riddle, quiet as a shadow, edged through the door and followed, Harry tiptoeing behind him, forgetting that he couldn’t be heard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For perhaps five minutes they followed the footsteps, until Riddle stopped suddenly, his head inclined in the direction of new noises. Harry heard a door creak open, and then someone speaking in a hoarse whisper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon … gotta get yeh outta here … c’mon now … in the box …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was something familiar about that voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle suddenly jumped around the corner. Harry stepped out behind him. He could see the dark outline of a huge boy who was crouching in front of an open door, a very large box next to it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Evening, Rubeus,’ said Riddle sharply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>184 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The boy slammed the door shut and stood up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What yer doin’ down here, Tom?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle stepped closer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s all over,’ he said. ‘I’m going to have to turn you in, Rubeus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They’re talking about closing Hogwarts if the attacks don’t stop.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’yeh –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t think you meant to kill anyone. But monsters don’t make good pets. I suppose you just let it out for exercise and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It never killed no one!’ said the large boy, backing against the closed door. From behind him, Harry could hear a funny rustling and clicking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Rubeus,’ said Riddle, moving yet closer. ‘The dead girl’s parents will be here tomorrow. The least Hogwarts can do is make sure that the thing that killed their daughter is slaughtered …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It wasn’ him!’ roared the boy, his voice echoing in the dark passage. ‘He wouldn’! He never!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stand aside,’ said Riddle, drawing out his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His spell lit the corridor with a sudden flaming light. The door behind the large boy flew open with such force it knocked him into the wall opposite. And out of it came something that made Harry let out a long, piercing scream no one but he seemed to hear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A vast, low-slung, hairy body and a tangle of black legs; a gleam of many eyes and a pair of razor-sharp pincers – Riddle raised his wand again, but he was too late. The thing bowled him over as it scuttled away, tearing up the corridor and out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle scrambled to his feet, looking after it; he raised his wand, but the huge boy leapt on him, seized his wand and threw him back down, yelling, ‘NOOOOOOO!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The scene whirled, the darkness became complete, Harry felt himself falling and, with a crash, he landed spread-eagled on his four-poster in the Gryffindor dormitory, Riddle’s diary lying open on his stomach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before he had had time to regain his breath, the dormitory door opened and Ron came in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There you are,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat up. He was sweating and shaking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up?’ said Ron, looking at him with concern. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was Hagrid, Ron. Hagrid opened the Chamber of Secrets fifty years ago.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER FOURTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Cornelius Fudge</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione had always known that Hagrid had an unfortunate liking for large and monstrous creatures. During their first year at Hogwarts he had tried to raise a dragon in his little wooden house, and it would be a long time before they forgot the giant, three-headed dog he’d christened ‘Fluffy’. And if, as a boy, Hagrid had heard that a monster was hidden somewhere in the castle, Harry was sure he’d have gone to any lengths for a glimpse of it. He’d probably thought it was a shame that the monster had been cooped up so long, and thought it deserved the chance to stretch its many legs; Harry could just imagine the thirteen-year-old Hagrid trying to fit a lead and collar on it. But he was equally certain that Hagrid would never have meant to kill anybody. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry half-wished he hadn’t found out how to work Riddle’s diary. Again and again Ron and Hermione made him recount what he’d seen, until he was heartily sick of telling them and sick of the long, circular conversations that followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddle   <i class=\"calibre4\">might</i> have got the wrong person,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe it was some other monster that was attacking people …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How many monsters d’you think this place can hold?’ Ron asked dully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We always knew Hagrid had been expelled,’ said Harry miserably. ‘And the attacks must’ve stopped after Hagrid was kicked out. Otherwise, Riddle wouldn’t have got his award.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron tried a different tack. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddle   <i class=\"calibre4\">does</i> sound like Percy – who asked him to grass on Hagrid, anyway?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But the monster had  <i class=\"calibre4\">killed</i> someone, Ron,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And Riddle was going to go back to some Muggle orphanage if they closed Hogwarts,’ said Harry. ‘I don’t blame him for wanting to stay here …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>186 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron bit his lip, then said tentatively, ‘You met Hagrid down Knockturn Alley, didn’t you, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He was buying a Flesh-Eating Slug Repellent,’ said Harry quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The three of them fell silent. After a long pause, Hermione voiced the knottiest question of all in a hesitant voice: ‘Do you think we should go and  <i class=\"calibre4\">ask</i> Hagrid about it all?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’d be a cheerful visit,’ said Ron. ‘Hello, Hagrid, tell us, have you been setting anything mad and hairy loose in the castle lately?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In the end, they decided that they wouldn’t say anything to Hagrid unless there was another attack, and as more and more days went by with no whisper from the disembodied voice, they became hopeful that they would never need to talk to him about why he had been expelled. It was now nearly four months since Justin and Nearly Headless Nick had been Petrified, and nearly everybody seemed to think that the attacker, whoever it was, had retired for good. Peeves had finally got bored of his ‘Oh Potter, you rotter’ song, Ernie Macmillan asked Harry quite politely to pass a bucket of leaping toadstools in Herbology one day, and in March several of the Mandrakes threw a loud and raucous party in Greenhouse Three. This made Professor Sprout very happy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The moment they start trying to move into each other’s pots, we’ll know they’re fully mature,’ she told Harry. ‘Then we’ll be able to revive those poor people in the hospital wing.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The second-years were given something new to think about during their Easter holidays. The time had come to choose their subjects for the third year, a matter that Hermione, at least, took very seriously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It could affect our whole future,’ she told Harry and Ron, as they pored over lists of new subjects, marking them with ticks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I just want to give up Potions,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can’t,’ said Ron gloomily. ‘We keep all our old subjects, or I’d’ve ditched Defence Against the Dark Arts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But that’s very important!’ said Hermione, shocked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not the way Lockhart teaches it,’ said Ron. ‘I haven’t learned anything from him except not to set pixies loose.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville Longbottom had been sent letters from all the witches and wizards in his family, all giving him different advice on what to choose. Confused and worried, he sat reading the subject lists </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cornelius Fudge 187 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">with his tongue poking out, asking people whether they thought Arithmancy sounded more difficult than Study of Ancient Runes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dean Thomas, who, like Harry, had grown up with Muggles, ended up closing his eyes and jabbing his wand at the list, then picking the subjects it landed on. Hermione took nobody’s advice but signed up for everything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry smiled grimly to himself at the thought of what Uncle Vernon and Aunt Petunia would say if he tried to discuss his career in wizardry with them. Not that he didn’t get any guidance: Percy Weasley was eager to share his experience. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Depends where you want to  <i class=\"calibre4\">go, </i> Harry,’ he said. ‘It’s never too early to think about the future, so I’d recommend Divination. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">People say Muggle Studies is a soft option, but I personally think wizards should have a thorough understanding of the non-magical community, particularly if they’re thinking of working in close contact with them – look at my father, he has to deal with Muggle business all the time. My brother Charlie was always more of an outdoor type, so he went for Care of Magical Creatures. Play to your strengths, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the only thing Harry felt he was really good at was Quidditch. In the end, he chose the same new subjects as Ron, feeling that if he was rubbish at them, at least he’d have someone friendly to help him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor’s next Quidditch match would be against Hufflepuff. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood was insisting on team practices every night after dinner, so that Harry barely had time for anything but Quidditch and homework. However, the training sessions were getting better, or at least drier, and the evening before Saturday’s match, he went up to his dormitory to drop off his broomstick, feeling Gryffindor’s chances for the Quidditch Cup had never been better. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But his cheerful mood didn’t last long. At the top of the stairs to the dormitory, he met Neville Longbottom, who was looking frantic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry – I don’t know who did it. I just found –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Watching Harry fearfully, Neville pushed open the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The contents of Harry’s trunk had been thrown everywhere. His cloak lay ripped on the floor. The bedclothes had been pulled off his four-poster and the drawer had been pulled out of his bedside cabinet, the contents strewn over the mattress. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>188 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry walked over to the bed, open-mouthed, treading on a few loose pages of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Travels with Trolls. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As he and Neville pulled the blankets back onto his bed, Ron, Dean and Seamus came in. Dean swore loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What happened, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No idea,’ said Harry. But Ron was examining Harry’s robes. All the pockets were hanging out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Someone’s been looking for something,’ said Ron. ‘Is there anything missing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry started to pick up all his things and throw them into his trunk. It was only as he threw the last of the Lockhart books back into it that he realised what wasn’t there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddle’s diary’s gone,’ he said in an undertone to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jerked his head towards the dormitory door and Ron followed him out. They hurried back down to the Gryffindor common room, which was half-empty, and joined Hermione, who was sitting alone, reading a book called  <i class=\"calibre4\">Ancient Runes Made Easy. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione looked aghast at the news. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But – only a Gryffindor could have stolen – nobody else knows our password …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Exactly,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They woke next day to brilliant sunshine and a light, refreshing breeze. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Perfect Quidditch conditions!’ said Wood enthusiastically at the Gryffindor table, loading the team’s plates with scrambled eggs. ‘Harry, buck up there, you need a decent breakfast.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had been staring down the packed Gryffindor table, wondering if the new owner of Riddle’s diary was right in front of his eyes. Hermione had been urging him to report the robbery, but Harry didn’t like the idea. He’d have to tell a teacher all about the diary and how many people knew why Hagrid had been expelled fifty years ago? He didn’t want to be the one who brought it all up again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As he left the Great Hall with Ron and Hermione to go and collect his Quidditch things, another, very serious worry was added to Harry’s growing list. He had just set foot on the marble staircase when he heard it yet again: ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Kill this time … let me rip … tear </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He shouted aloud and Ron and Hermione both jumped away </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cornelius Fudge 189 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">from him in alarm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The voice!’ said Harry, looking over his shoulder. ‘I just heard it again – didn’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron shook his head, wide-eyed. Hermione, however, clapped a hand to her forehead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry – I think I’ve just understood something! I’ve got to go to the library!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And she sprinted away, up the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What</i> does she understand?’ said Harry distractedly, still looking around, trying to tell where the voice had come from. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Loads more than I do,’ said Ron, shaking his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But why’s she got to go to the library?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because that’s what Hermione does,’ said Ron, shrugging. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When in doubt, go to the library.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood, irresolute, trying to catch the voice again, but people were now emerging from the Great Hall behind him, talking loudly, exiting through the front doors on their way to the Quidditch pitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d better get moving,’ said Ron. ‘It’s nearly eleven – the match.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry raced up to Gryffindor Tower, collected his Nimbus Two Thousand and joined the large crowd swarming across the grounds, but his mind was still in the castle, along with the bodiless voice, and as he pulled on his scarlet robes in the changing room, his only comfort was that everyone was now outside to watch the game. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The teams walked onto the pitch to tumultuous applause. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Oliver Wood took off for a warm-up flight around the goalposts, Madam Hooch released the balls. The Hufflepuffs, who played in canary yellow, were standing in a huddle, having a last-minute discussion of tactics. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was just mounting his broom when Professor McGonagall came half-marching, half-running across the pitch, carrying an enormous purple megaphone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s heart dropped like a stone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This match has been cancelled,’ Professor McGonagall called through the megaphone, addressing the packed stadium. There were boos and shouts. Oliver Wood, looking devastated, landed and ran towards Professor McGonagall without getting off his broomstick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>190 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Professor!’ he shouted. ‘We’ve got to play … the Cup … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Gryffindor</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall ignored him and continued to shout through her megaphone: ‘All students are to make their way back to the house common rooms, where their Heads of Houses will give them further information. As quickly as you can, please!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then she lowered the megaphone and beckoned Harry over to her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter, I think you’d better come with me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wondering how she could possibly suspect him this time, Harry saw Ron detach himself from the complaining crowd; he came running up to them as they set off towards the castle. To Harry’s surprise, Professor McGonagall didn’t object. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, perhaps you’d better come too, Weasley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Some of the students swarming around them were grumbling about the match being cancelled, others looked worried. Harry and Ron followed Professor McGonagall back into the school and up the marble staircase. But they weren’t taken to anybody’s office this time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This will be a bit of a shock,’ said Professor McGonagall in a surprisingly gentle voice as they approached the hospital wing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There has been another attack … another  <i class=\"calibre4\">double</i> attack.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s insides did a horrible somersault. Professor McGonagall pushed the door open and he and Ron entered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey was bending over a sixth-year girl with long curly hair. Harry recognised her as the Ravenclaw they’d accident-tally asked for directions to the Slytherin common room. And on the bed next to her was – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Hermione! </i>’ Ron groaned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione lay utterly still, her eyes open and glassy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They were found near the library,’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t suppose either of you can explain this? It was on the floor next to them …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She was holding up a small, circular mirror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron shook their heads, both staring at Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I will escort you back to Gryffindor Tower,’ said Professor McGonagall heavily. ‘I need to address the students in any case.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All students will return to their house common rooms by six o’clock in the evening. No student is to leave the dormitories after </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cornelius Fudge 191 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">that time. You will be escorted to each lesson by a teacher. No student is to use the bathroom unaccompanied by a teacher. All further Quidditch training and matches are to be postponed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There will be no more evening activities.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindors packed inside the common room listened to Professor McGonagall in silence. She rolled up the parchment from which she had been reading and said in a somewhat choked voice, ‘I need hardly add that I have rarely been so distressed. It is likely that the school will be closed unless the culprit behind these attacks is caught. I would urge anyone who thinks they might know anything about them to come forward.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She climbed somewhat awkwardly out of the portrait hole, and the Gryffindors began talking immediately. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s two Gryffindors down, not counting a Gryffindor ghost, one Ravenclaw and one Hufflepuff,’ said the Weasley twins’ friend Lee Jordan, counting on his fingers. ‘Haven’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">any</i> of the teachers noticed that the Slytherins are all safe? Isn’t it  <i class=\"calibre4\">obvious</i> all this stuff’s coming from Slytherin? The  <i class=\"calibre4\">heir</i> of Slytherin, the  <i class=\"calibre4\">monster</i> of Slytherin – why don’t they just chuck all the Slytherins out?’ he roared, to nods and scattered applause. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy Weasley was sitting in a chair behind Lee, but for once he didn’t seem keen to make his views heard. He was looking pale and stunned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Percy’s in shock,’ George told Harry quietly. ‘That Ravenclaw girl – Penelope Clearwater – she’s a Prefect. I don’t think he thought the monster would dare attack a  <i class=\"calibre4\">Prefect. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry was only half-listening. He didn’t seem to be able to get rid of the picture of Hermione, lying on the hospital bed as though carved out of stone. And if the culprit wasn’t caught soon, he was looking at a lifetime back with the Dursleys. Tom Riddle had turned Hagrid in because he was faced with the prospect of a Muggle orphanage if the school closed. Harry now knew exactly how he had felt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’re we going to do?’ said Ron quietly in Harry’s ear. ‘D’you think they suspect Hagrid?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got to go and talk to him,’ said Harry, making up his mind. ‘I can’t believe it’s him this time, but if he set the monster loose last time he’ll know how to get inside the Chamber of Secrets, and that’s a start.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>192 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But McGonagall said we’ve got to stay in our tower unless we’re in class –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think,’ said Harry, more quietly still, ‘it’s time to get my dad’s old Cloak out again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had inherited just one thing from his father: a long and silvery Invisibility Cloak. It was their only chance of sneaking out of the school to visit Hagrid without anyone knowing about it. They went to bed at the usual time, waited until Neville, Dean and Seamus had stopped discussing the Chamber of Secrets and finally fallen asleep, then got up, dressed again, and threw the Cloak over themselves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The journey through the dark and deserted castle corridors wasn’t enjoyable. Harry, who had wandered the castle at night several times before, had never seen it so crowded after sunset. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Teachers, Prefects and ghosts were marching the corridors in pairs, staring around for any unusual activity. Their Invisibility Cloak didn’t stop them making any noise, and there was a particularly tense moment when Ron stubbed his toe only yards from the spot where Snape was standing guard. Thankfully, Snape sneezed at almost exactly the moment Ron swore. It was with relief that they reached the oak front doors and eased them open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a clear, starry night. They hurried towards the lighted windows of Hagrid’s house, and pulled off the Cloak only when they were right outside his front door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Seconds after they had knocked, Hagrid flung it open. They found themselves face to face, with him aiming a crossbow at them, Fang the boarhound barking loudly behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ he said, lowering the weapon and staring at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’re you two doin’ here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that for?’ said Harry, pointing at the crossbow as they stepped inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothin’ … nothin’,’ Hagrid muttered. ‘I’ve bin expectin’ … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">doesn’ matter … Sit down … I’ll make tea …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He hardly seemed to know what he was doing. He nearly extinguished the fire, spilling water from the kettle on it, and then smashed the teapot with a nervous jerk of his massive hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you OK, Hagrid?’ said Harry. ‘Did you hear about Hermione?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, I heard, all righ’,’ said Hagrid, a slight break in his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cornelius Fudge 193 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He kept glancing nervously at the windows. He poured them both large mugs of boiling water (he had forgotten to add tea bags) and was just putting a slab of fruitcake on a plate, when there was a loud knock on the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid dropped the fruitcake. Harry and Ron exchanged panic-stricken looks, then threw the Invisibility Cloak back over themselves and retreated into a corner. Hagrid checked that they were hidden, seized his crossbow and flung open his door once more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good evening, Hagrid.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Dumbledore. He entered, looking deadly serious, and was followed by a second, very odd-looking man. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The stranger was a short, portly man with rumpled grey hair and an anxious expression. He was wearing a strange mixture of clothes: a pin-striped suit, a scarlet tie, a long black cloak and pointed purple boots. Under his arm he carried a lime-green bowler. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s Dad’s boss!’ Ron breathed. ‘Cornelius Fudge, the Minister of Magic!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry elbowed Ron hard to make him shut up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid had gone pale and sweaty. He dropped into one of his chairs and looked from Dumbledore to Cornelius Fudge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bad business, Hagrid,’ said Fudge, in rather clipped tones. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very bad business. Had to come. Four attacks on Muggle-borns. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Things’ve gone far enough. Ministry’s got to act.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I never,’ said Hagrid, looking imploringly at Dumbledore, ‘you know I never, Professor Dumbledore, sir …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I want it understood, Cornelius, that Hagrid has my full confidence,’ said Dumbledore, frowning at Fudge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look, Albus,’ said Fudge, uncomfortably. ‘Hagrid’s record’s against him. Ministry’s got to do something – the school governors have been in touch.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yet again, Cornelius, I tell you that taking Hagrid away will not help in the slightest,’ said Dumbledore. His blue eyes were full of a fire Harry had never seen before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at it from my point of view,’ said Fudge, fidgeting with his bowler. ‘I’m under a lot of pressure. Got to be seen to be doing something. If it turns out it wasn’t Hagrid, he’ll be back and no more said. But I’ve got to take him. Got to. Wouldn’t be doing my duty –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Take me?’ said Hagrid, who was trembling. ‘Take me where?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>194 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘For a short stretch only,’ said Fudge, not meeting Hagrid’s eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not a punishment, Hagrid, more a precaution. If someone else is caught, you’ll be let out with a full apology …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not Azkaban?’ croaked Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before Fudge could answer, there was another loud rap on the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore answered it. It was Harry’s turn for an elbow in the ribs: he’d let out an audible gasp. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Lucius Malfoy strode into Hagrid’s hut, swathed in a long black travelling cloak, smiling a cold and satisfied smile. Fang started to growl. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Already here, Fudge,’ he said approvingly. ‘Good, good …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’re  you  doin’  here?’  said  Hagrid  furiously.  ‘Get  outta  my house!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear man, please believe me, I have no pleasure at all in being inside your – er – d’you call this a house?’ said Lucius Malfoy, sneering as he looked around the small cabin. ‘I simply called at the school and was told that the Headmaster was here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what exactly did you want with me, Lucius?’ said Dumbledore. He spoke politely, but the fire was still blazing in his blue eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Dreadful</i> thing, Dumbledore,’ said Mr Malfoy lazily, taking out a long roll of parchment, ‘but the governors feel it’s time for you to step aside. This is an Order of Suspension – you’ll find all twelve signatures on it. I’m afraid we feel you’re losing your touch. How many attacks have there been now? Two more this afternoon, wasn’t it? At this rate, there’ll be no Muggle-borns left at Hogwarts, and we all know what an  <i class=\"calibre4\">awful</i> loss that would be to the school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, now, see here, Lucius,’ said Fudge, looking alarmed, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore suspended … no, no … last thing we want just now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The appointment – or suspension – of the Headmaster is a matter for the governors, Fudge,’ said Mr Malfoy smoothly. ‘And as Dumbledore has failed to stop these attacks …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now look, Lucius, if  <i class=\"calibre4\">Dumbledore</i> can’t stop them –’ said Fudge, whose upper lip was sweating now, ‘I mean to say, who  <i class=\"calibre4\">can? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That remains to be seen,’ said Mr Malfoy, with a nasty smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But as all twelve of us have voted …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid leapt to his feet, his shaggy black head grazing the ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cornelius Fudge 195 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An’ how many did yeh have ter threaten an’ blackmail before they agreed, Malfoy, eh?’ he roared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dear, dear, you know, that temper of yours will lead you into trouble one of these days, Hagrid,’ said Mr Malfoy. ‘I would advise you not to shout at the Azkaban guards like that. They won’t like it at all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh can’ take Dumbledore!’ yelled Hagrid, making Fang the boarhound cower and whimper in his basket. ‘Take him away, an’ the Muggle-borns won’ stand a chance! There’ll be killin’s next!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Calm yourself, Hagrid,’ said Dumbledore sharply. He looked at Lucius Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If the governors want my removal, Lucius, I shall of course step aside.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ stuttered Fudge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">No! </i>’ growled Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore had not taken his bright blue eyes off Lucius Malfoy’s cold grey ones. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘However,’ said Dumbledore, speaking very slowly and clearly, so that none of them could miss a word, ‘you will find that I will only   <i class=\"calibre4\">truly</i> have left this school when none here are loyal to me. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You will also find that help will always be given at Hogwarts to those who ask for it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a second, Harry was almost sure Dumbledore’s eyes flickered towards the corner where he and Ron stood hidden. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Admirable sentiments,’ said Malfoy, bowing. ‘We shall all miss your – er – highly individual way of running things, Albus, and only hope that your successor will manage to prevent any – ah – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">“<i class=\"calibre4\">killin’s</i>”.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He strode to the cabin door, opened it and bowed Dumbledore out. Fudge, fiddling with his bowler, waited for Hagrid to go ahead of him, but Hagrid stood his ground, took a deep breath and said carefully, ‘If anyone wanted ter find out some  <i class=\"calibre4\">stuff, </i> all they’d have ter do would be ter follow the  <i class=\"calibre4\">spiders. </i> That’d lead ’em right! That’s all I’m sayin’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge stared at him in amazement. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, I’m comin’,’ said Hagrid, pulling on his moleskin overcoat. But as he was about to follow Fudge through the door, he stopped again and said loudly, ‘An’ someone’ll need ter feed Fang while I’m away.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>196 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door banged shut and Ron pulled the Invisibility Cloak off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re in trouble now,’ he said hoarsely. ‘No Dumbledore. They might as well close the school tonight. There’ll be an attack a day with him gone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fang started howling, scratching at the closed door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER FIFTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Aragog</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Summer was creeping over the grounds around the castle; sky and lake alike turned periwinkle blue and flowers large as cabbages burst into bloom in the greenhouses. But with no Hagrid visible from the castle windows, striding the grounds with Fang at his heels, the scene didn’t look right to Harry; no better, in fact, than the inside of the castle, where things were so horribly wrong. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron had tried to visit Hermione, but visitors were now barred from the hospital wing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re taking no more chances,’ Madam Pomfrey told them severely through a crack in the hospital door. ‘No, I’m sorry, there’s every chance the attacker might come back to finish these people off …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With Dumbledore gone, fear had spread as never before, so that the sun warming the castle walls outside seemed to stop at the mullioned windows. There was barely a face to be seen in the school that didn’t look worried and tense, and any laughter that rang through the corridors sounded shrill and unnatural and was quickly stifled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry constantly repeated Dumbledore’s final words to himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I will only truly have left this school when none here are loyal to me </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">… Help will always be given at Hogwarts to those who ask for it</i>.’ But what good were these words? Who exactly were they supposed to ask for help, when everyone was just as confused and scared as they were? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s hint about the spiders was far easier to understand – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the trouble was, there didn’t seem to be a single spider left in the castle to follow. Harry looked everywhere he went, helped (rather reluctantly) by Ron. They were hampered, of course, by the fact that they weren’t allowed to wander off on their own, but had to move around the castle in a pack with the other Gryffindors. Most </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>198 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">of their fellow students seemed glad that they were being shepherded from class to class by teachers, but Harry found it very irk-some. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One person, however, seemed to be thoroughly enjoying the atmosphere of terror and suspicion. Draco Malfoy was strutting around the school as though he had just been appointed Head Boy. Harry didn’t realise what he was so pleased about until the Potions lesson about a fortnight after Dumbledore and Hagrid had left, when, sitting right behind Malfoy, Harry overheard him gloat-ing to Crabbe and Goyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I always thought Father might be the one who got rid of Dumbledore,’ he said, not troubling to keep his voice down. ‘I told you he thinks Dumbledore’s the worst Headmaster the school’s ever had. Maybe we’ll get a decent Headmaster now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Someone who won’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">want</i> the Chamber of Secrets closed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">McGonagall won’t last long, she’s only filling in …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape swept past Harry, making no comment about Hermione’s empty seat and cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sir,’ said Malfoy loudly. ‘Sir, why don’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> apply for the Headmaster’s job?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, now, Malfoy,’ said Snape, though he couldn’t suppress a thin-lipped smile. ‘Professor Dumbledore has only been suspended by the governors. I dare say he’ll be back with us soon enough.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, right,’ said Malfoy, smirking. ‘I expect you’d have Father’s vote, sir, if you wanted to apply for the job.  <i class=\"calibre4\">I’ll</i> tell Father you’re the best teacher here, sir …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape smirked as he swept off around the dungeon, fortunately not spotting Seamus Finnigan, who was pretending to vomit into his cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m quite surprised the Mudbloods haven’t all packed their bags by now,’ Malfoy went on. ‘Bet you five Galleons the next one dies. Pity it wasn’t Granger …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The bell rang at that moment, which was lucky; at Malfoy’s last words, Ron had leapt off his stool, and in the scramble to collect bags and books, his attempts to reach Malfoy went unnoticed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me at him,’ Ron growled, as Harry and Dean hung onto his arms. ‘I don’t care, I don’t need my wand, I’m going to kill him with my bare hands –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hurry up, I’ve got to take you all to Herbology,’ barked Snape over the class’s heads, and off they went, crocodile fashion, with </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aragog 199 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Dean bringing up the rear, Ron still trying to get loose. It was only safe to let go of him when Snape had seen them out of the castle, and they were making their way across the vegetable patch towards the greenhouses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Herbology class was very subdued; there were now two missing from their number, Justin and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Sprout set them all to work pruning the Abyssinian Shrivelfigs. Harry went to tip an armful of withered stalks onto the compost heap and found himself face to face with Ernie Macmillan. Ernie took a deep breath and said, very formally, ‘I just want to say, Harry, that I’m sorry I ever suspected you. I know you’d never attack Hermione Granger, and I apologise for all the stuff I said. We’re all in the same boat now, and, well –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He held out a pudgy hand, and Harry shook it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ernie and his friend Hannah came to work at the same Shrivelfig as Harry and Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That Draco Malfoy character,’ said Ernie, breaking off dead twigs, ‘he seems very pleased about all this, doesn’t he? D’you know, I think  <i class=\"calibre4\">he</i> might be Slytherin’s heir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s clever of you,’ said Ron, who didn’t seem to have for-given Ernie as readily as Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> think it’s Malfoy, Harry?’ Ernie asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry, so firmly that Ernie and Hannah stared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A second later, Harry spotted something that made him hit Ron over the hand with his pruning shears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ouch! </i> What’re you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was pointing at the ground a few feet away. Several large spiders were scurrying across the earth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yeah,’ said Ron, trying, and failing, to look pleased. ‘But we can’t follow them now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ernie and Hannah were listening curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry watched the spiders running away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Looks like they’re heading for the Forbidden Forest …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Ron looked even unhappier about that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At the end of the lesson Professor Sprout escorted the class to their Defence Against the Dark Arts lesson. Harry and Ron lagged behind the others so they could talk out of earshot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll have to use the Invisibility Cloak again,’ Harry told Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can take Fang with us. He’s used to going into the Forest with Hagrid, he might be some help.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>200 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Ron, who was twirling his wand nervously in his fingers. ‘Er – aren’t there – aren’t there supposed to be werewolves in the Forest?’ he added, as they took their usual places at the back of Lockhart’s classroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Preferring not to answer that question, Harry said, ‘There are good things in there, too. The centaurs are all right, and the unicorns.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had never been into the Forbidden Forest before. Harry had entered it only once, and had hoped never to do so again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart bounded into the room and the class stared at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Every other teacher in the place was looking grimmer than usual, but Lockhart appeared nothing short of buoyant. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come now,’ he cried, beaming around him, ‘why all these long faces?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">People swapped exasperated looks, but nobody answered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you people realise,’ said Lockhart, speaking slowly, as though they were all a bit dim, ‘the danger has passed! The culprit has been taken away.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Says who?’ said Dean Thomas loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear young man, the Minister of Magic wouldn’t have taken Hagrid if he hadn’t been one hundred per cent sure that he was guilty,’ said Lockhart, in the tone of someone explaining that one and one made two. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yes he would,’ said Ron, even more loudly than Dean. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I flatter myself I know a  <i class=\"calibre4\">touch</i> more about Hagrid’s arrest than you do, Mr Weasley,’ said Lockhart in a self-satisfied tone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron started to say that he didn’t think so, somehow, but stopped in mid-sentence when Harry kicked him hard under the desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We weren’t there, remember?’ Harry muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Lockhart’s disgusting cheeriness, his hints that he had always thought Hagrid was no good, his confidence that the whole business was now at an end, irritated Harry so much that he yearned to throw  <i class=\"calibre4\">Gadding with Ghouls</i> right in Lockhart’s stupid face. Instead he contented himself with scrawling a note to Ron: ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Let’s do it tonight</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron read the message, swallowed hard and looked sideways at the empty seat usually filled by Hermione. The sight seemed to stiffen his resolve, and he nodded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aragog 201 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindor common room was always very crowded these days, because from six o’clock onwards, the Gryffindors had nowhere else to go. They also had plenty to talk about, with the result that the common room often didn’t empty until past midnight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went to get the Invisibility Cloak out of his trunk right after dinner, and spent the evening sitting on it, waiting for the room to clear. Fred and George challenged Harry and Ron to a few games of Exploding Snap and Ginny sat watching them, very subdued in Hermione’s usual chair. Harry and Ron kept losing on purpose, trying to finish the games quickly, but even so, it was well past midnight when Fred, George and Ginny finally went to bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron waited for the distant sounds of two dormitory doors closing before seizing the Cloak, throwing it over themselves, and climbing through the portrait hole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was another difficult journey through the castle, dodging all the teachers. At last they reached the Entrance Hall, slid back the lock on the oak front doors, squeezed between them, trying to stop any creaking, and stepped out into the moonlit grounds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Course,’ said Ron abruptly, as they strode across the black grass, ‘we might get to the Forest and find there’s nothing to follow. Those spiders might not’ve been going there at all. I know it  looked  like  they  were  moving  in  that  sort  of  general  direction, but …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His voice tailed away hopefully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They reached Hagrid’s house, sad and sorry-looking with its blank windows. When Harry pushed the door open, Fang went mad with joy at the sight of them. Worried he might wake everyone at the castle with his deep, booming barks, they hastily fed him treacle fudge from a tin on the mantelpiece, which glued his teeth together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry left the Invisibility Cloak on Hagrid’s table. There would be no need for it in the pitch-dark Forest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon, Fang, we’re going for a walk,’ said Harry, patting his leg, and Fang bounded happily out of the house behind them, dashed to the edge of the Forest and lifted his leg against a large sycamore tree. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took out his wand, murmured, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lumos! </i>’ and a tiny light appeared at the end of it, just enough to let them watch the path </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>202 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">for signs of spiders. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good thinking,’ said Ron. ‘I’d light mine too, but you know – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">it’d probably blow up or something …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tapped Ron on the shoulder, pointing at the grass. Two solitary spiders were hurrying away from the wandlight into the shade of the trees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ Ron sighed, as though resigned to the worst, ‘I’m ready. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Let’s go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So, with Fang scampering around them, sniffing tree roots and leaves, they entered the Forest. By the glow of Harry’s wand, they followed the steady trickle of spiders moving along the path. They walked for about twenty minutes, not speaking, listening hard for noises other than breaking twigs and rustling leaves. Then, when the trees had become thicker than ever, so that the stars overhead were no longer visible, and Harry’s wand shone alone in the sea of dark, they saw their spider guides leaving the path. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry paused, trying to see where the spiders were going, but everything outside his little sphere of light was pitch black. He had never been this deep into the Forest before. He could vividly remember Hagrid advising him not to leave the Forest path last time he’d been in here. But Hagrid was miles away now, probably sitting in a cell in Azkaban, and he had also said to follow the spiders. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something wet touched Harry’s hand and he jumped backwards, crushing Ron’s foot, but it was only Fang’s nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you reckon?’ Harry said to Ron, whose eyes he could just make out, reflecting the light from his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve come this far,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So they followed the darting shadows of the spiders into the trees. They couldn’t move very quickly now; there were tree roots and stumps in their way, barely visible in the near blackness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could feel Fang’s hot breath on his hand. More than once, they had to stop, so that Harry could crouch down and find the spiders in the wandlight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked for what seemed like at least half an hour, their robes snagging on low-slung branches and brambles. After a while, they noticed that the ground seemed to be sloping downwards, though the trees were as thick as ever. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then Fang suddenly let loose a great, echoing bark, making both Harry and Ron jump out of their skins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aragog 203 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Ron loudly, looking around into the pitch dark, and gripping Harry’s elbow very hard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s something moving over there,’ Harry breathed. ‘Listen … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sounds like something big.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They listened. Some distance to their right, the something big was snapping branches as it carved a path through the trees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh no,’ said Ron. ‘Oh no, oh no, oh –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up,’ said Harry frantically. ‘It’ll hear you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hear   <i class=\"calibre4\">me? </i>’ said Ron in an unnaturally high voice. ‘It’s already heard Fang!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The darkness seemed to be pressing on their eyeballs as they stood, terrified, waiting. There was a strange rumbling noise and then silence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you think it’s doing?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Probably getting ready to pounce,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They waited, shivering, hardly daring to move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think it’s gone?’ Harry whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, to their right, came a sudden blaze of light, so bright in the darkness that both of them flung up their hands to shield their eyes. Fang yelped and tried to run, but got lodged in a tangle of thorns and yelped even louder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ Ron shouted, his voice breaking with relief. ‘Harry, it’s our car!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry blundered after Ron towards the light, stumbling and tripping, and a moment later they had emerged into a clearing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley’s car was standing, empty, in the middle of a circle of thick trees under a roof of dense branches, its headlamps ablaze. As Ron walked, open-mouthed, towards it, it moved slowly towards him, exactly like a large, turquoise dog greeting its owner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s been here all the time!’ said Ron delightedly, walking around the car. ‘Look at it. The Forest’s turned it wild …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The wings of the car were scratched and smeared with mud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Apparently it had taken to trundling around the Forest on its own. Fang didn’t seem at all keen on it; he kept close to Harry, who could feel him quivering. His breathing slowing down again, Harry stuffed his wand back into his robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>204 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And we thought it was going to attack us!’ said Ron, leaning against the car and patting it. ‘I wondered where it had gone!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry squinted around on the floodlit ground for signs of more spiders, but they had all scuttled away from the glare of the head-lights. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve lost the trail,’ he said. ‘C’mon, let’s go and find them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron didn’t speak. He didn’t move. His eyes were fixed on a point some ten feet above the Forest floor, right behind Harry. His face was livid with terror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t even have time to turn around. There was a loud clicking noise and suddenly he felt something long and hairy seize him around the middle and lift him off the ground, so that he was hanging, face down. Struggling, terrified, he heard more clicking, and saw Ron’s legs leave the ground too, heard Fang whimpering and howling – next moment, he was being swept away into the dark trees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Head hanging, Harry saw that what had hold of him was marching on six immensely long, hairy legs, the front two clutching him tightly below a pair of shining black pincers. Behind him, he could hear another of the creatures, no doubt carrying Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were moving into the very heart of the Forest. Harry could hear Fang fighting to free himself from a third monster, whining loudly, but Harry couldn’t have yelled even if he had wanted to; he seemed to have left his voice back with the car in the clearing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He never knew how long he was in the creature’s clutches; he only knew that the darkness suddenly lifted enough for him to see that the leaf-strewn ground was now swarming with spiders. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Craning his neck sideways, he realised that they had reached the rim of a vast hollow, a hollow which had been cleared of trees, so that the stars shone brightly onto the worst scene he had ever clapped eyes upon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Spiders. Not tiny spiders like those surging over the leaves below. Spiders the size of carthorses, eight-eyed, eight-legged, black, hairy, gigantic. The massive specimen that was carrying Harry made its way down the steep slope, towards a misty domed web in the very centre of the hollow, while its fellows closed in all around it, clicking their pincers excitedly at the sight of its load. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry fell to the ground on all fours as the spider released him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Fang thudded down next to him. Fang wasn’t howling any more, but cowering silently on the spot. Ron looked exactly </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aragog 205 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">like Harry felt. His mouth was stretched wide in a kind of silent scream and his eyes were popping. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry suddenly realised that the spider which had dropped him was saying something. It had been hard to tell, because he clicked his pincers with every word he spoke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aragog!’ it called. ‘Aragog!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And from the middle of the misty domed web, a spider the size of a small elephant emerged, very slowly. There was grey in the black of his body and legs, and each of the eyes on his ugly, pincered head was milky white. He was blind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What is it?’ he said, clicking his pincers rapidly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Men,’ clicked the spider who had caught Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is it Hagrid?’ said Aragog, moving closer, his eight milky eyes wandering vaguely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Strangers,’ clicked the spider who had brought Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Kill them,’ clicked Aragog fretfully. ‘I was sleeping …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re friends of Hagrid’s,’ Harry shouted. His heart seemed to have left his chest to pound in his throat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Click, click, click went the pincers of the spiders all around the hollow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aragog paused. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid has never sent men into our hollow before,’ he said slowly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid’s in trouble,’ said Harry, breathing very fast. ‘That’s why we’ve come.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In trouble?’ said the aged spider, and Harry thought he heard concern beneath the clicking pincers. ‘But why has he sent you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry thought of getting to his feet, but decided against it; he didn’t think his legs would support him. So he spoke from the ground, as calmly as he could. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They think, up at the school, that Hagrid’s been setting a – a – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">something on students. They’ve taken him to Azkaban.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aragog clicked his pincers furiously, and all around the hollow the sound was echoed by the crowd of spiders; it was like applause, except applause didn’t usually make Harry feel sick with fear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But that was years ago,’ said Aragog fretfully. ‘Years and years ago. I remember it well. That’s why they made him leave the school. They believed that  <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> was the monster that dwells in what they call the Chamber of Secrets. They thought that Hagrid had </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>206 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">opened the Chamber and set me free.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you … you didn’t come from the Chamber of Secrets?’ said Harry, who could feel cold sweat on his forehead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I!’ said Aragog, clicking angrily. ‘I was not born in the castle. I come from a distant land. A traveller gave me to Hagrid when I was an egg. Hagrid was only a boy, but he cared for me, hidden in a cupboard in the castle, feeding me on scraps from the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid  is  my  good  friend,  and  a  good  man.  When  I  was  discovered, and blamed for the death of a girl, he protected me. I have lived here in the Forest ever since, where Hagrid still visits me. He even found me a wife, Mosag, and you see how our family has grown, all through Hagrid’s goodness …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry summoned what remained of his courage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you never – never attacked anyone?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never,’ croaked the old spider. ‘It would have been my instinct, but from respect of Hagrid, I never harmed a human. The body of the girl who was killed was discovered in a bathroom. I never saw any part of the castle but the cupboard in which I grew up. Our kind like the dark and the quiet …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But then … Do you know what  <i class=\"calibre4\">did</i> kill that girl?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because whatever it is, it’s back and attacking people again –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His words were drowned by a loud outbreak of clicking and the rustling of many long legs shifting angrily; large black shapes shifted all around him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The thing that lives in the castle,’ said Aragog, ‘is an ancient creature we spiders fear above all others. Well do I remember how I pleaded with Hagrid to let me go, when I sensed the beast moving about the school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What is it?’ said Harry urgently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">More loud clicking, more rustling; the spiders seemed to be closing in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We do not speak of it!’ said Aragog fiercely. ‘We do not name it! I never even told Hagrid the name of that dread creature, though he asked me, many times.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t want to press the subject, not with the spiders pressing closer on all sides. Aragog seemed to be tired of talking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was backing slowly into his domed web, but his fellow spiders continued to inch slowly towards Harry and Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll just go, then,’ Harry called desperately to Aragog, hearing leaves rustling behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aragog 207 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go?’ said Aragog slowly. ‘I think not …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But – but –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My sons and daughters do not harm Hagrid, on my command. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But I cannot deny them fresh meat, when it wanders so willingly into our midst. Goodbye, friend of Hagrid.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry spun around. Feet away, towering above him, was a solid wall of spiders, clicking, their many eyes gleaming in their ugly black heads … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Even as he reached for his wand, Harry knew it was no good, there were too many of them, but as he tried to stand, ready to die fighting, a loud, long note sounded, and a blaze of light flamed through the hollow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley’s car was thundering down the slope, headlamps glaring, its horn screeching, knocking spiders aside; several were thrown onto their backs, their endless legs waving in the air. The car screeched to a halt in front of Harry and Ron and the doors flew open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get Fang!’ Harry yelled, diving into the front seat; Ron seized the boarhound round the middle and threw him, yelping, into the back of the car. The doors slammed shut. Ron didn’t touch the accelerator but the car didn’t need him; the engine roared and they were off, hitting more spiders. They sped up the slope, out of the hollow, and they were soon crashing through the Forest, branches whipping the windows as the car wound its way cleverly through the widest gaps, following a path it obviously knew. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked sideways at Ron. His mouth was still open in the silent scream, but his eyes weren’t popping any more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you OK?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron stared straight ahead, unable to speak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They smashed their way through the undergrowth, Fang howling loudly in the back seat, and Harry saw the wing mirror snap off as they squeezed past a large oak. After ten noisy, rocky minutes, the trees thinned, and Harry could again see patches of sky. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The car stopped so suddenly that they were nearly thrown into the windscreen. They had reached the edge of the Forest. Fang flung himself at the window in his anxiety to get out and when Harry opened the door, he shot off through the trees to Hagrid’s house, tail between his legs. Harry got out too, and after a minute or so, Ron seemed to regain the feeling in his limbs and followed, still stiff-necked and staring. Harry gave the car a grateful pat as it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>208 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">reversed back into the Forest and disappeared from view. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went back into Hagrid’s cabin to get the Invisibility Cloak. Fang was trembling under a blanket in his basket. When Harry got outside again, he found Ron being violently sick in the pumpkin patch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Follow the spiders,’ said Ron weakly, wiping his mouth on his sleeve. ‘I’ll never forgive Hagrid. We’re lucky to be alive.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I bet he thought Aragog wouldn’t hurt friends of his,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s exactly Hagrid’s problem!’ said Ron, thumping the wall of the cabin. ‘He always thinks monsters aren’t as bad as they’re made out, and look where it’s got him! A cell in Azkaban!’ He was shivering uncontrollably now. ‘What was the point of sending us in there? What have we found out, I’d like to know?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That Hagrid never opened the Chamber of Secrets,’ said Harry, throwing the cloak over Ron and prodding him in the arm to make him walk. ‘He was innocent.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gave a loud snort. Evidently, hatching Aragog out in a cupboard wasn’t his idea of being innocent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the castle loomed nearer Harry twitched the Cloak to make sure their feet were hidden, then pushed the creaking front doors ajar. They walked carefully back across the Entrance Hall and up the marble staircase, holding their breath as they passed corridors where watchful sentries were walking. At last they reached the safety of the Gryffindor common room, where the fire had burned itself into glowing ash. They took off the Cloak and climbed the winding staircase to their dormitory. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron fell onto his bed without bothering to get undressed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, however, didn’t feel very sleepy. He sat on the edge of his four-poster, thinking hard about everything Aragog had said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The creature that was lurking somewhere in the castle, he thought, sounded like a sort of monster Voldemort – even other monsters didn’t want to name it. But he and Ron were no closer to finding out what it was, or how it Petrified its victims. Even Hagrid had never known what was in the Chamber of Secrets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry swung his legs up onto his bed and leaned back against his pillows, watching the moon glinting at him through the tower window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He couldn’t see what else they could do. They had hit dead ends everywhere. Riddle had caught the wrong person, the heir of </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aragog 209 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slytherin had got off, and no one could tell whether it was the same person, or a different one, who had opened the Chamber this time. There was nobody else to ask. Harry lay down, still thinking about what Aragog said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was becoming drowsy when what seemed like their very last hope occurred to him and he suddenly sat bolt upright. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron,’ he hissed through the dark. ‘Ron!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron woke with a yelp like Fang’s, stared wildly around and saw Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron – that girl who died. Aragog said she was found in a bathroom,’ said Harry, ignoring Neville’s snuffling snores from the corner. ‘What if she never left the bathroom? What if she’s still there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron rubbed his eyes, frowning through the moonlight. And then he understood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You  <i class=\"calibre4\">don’t</i> think – not  <i class=\"calibre4\">Moaning Myrtle? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER SIXTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Chamber of Secrets</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All those times we were in that bathroom, and she was just three toilets away,’ said Ron bitterly at breakfast next day, ‘and we could’ve asked her, and now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It had been hard enough trying to look for spiders. Escaping their teachers long enough to sneak into a girls’ bathroom, the girls’ bathroom, moreover, right next to the scene of the first attack, was going to be almost impossible. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But something happened in their first lesson, Transfiguration, which drove the Chamber of Secrets out of their minds for the first time in weeks. Ten minutes into the class, Professor McGonagall told them that their exams would start on the first of June, one week from today. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Exams? </i>’ howled Seamus Finnigan. ‘We’re still getting  <i class=\"calibre4\">exams? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud bang behind Harry as Neville Longbottom’s wand slipped, vanishing one of the legs on his desk. Professor McGonagall restored it with a wave of her own wand, and turned, frowning, to Seamus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The whole point of keeping the school open at this time is for you to receive your education,’ she said sternly. ‘The exams will therefore take place as usual, and I trust you are all revising hard.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Revising hard! It had never occurred to Harry that there would be exams with the castle in this state. There was a great deal of mutinous muttering around the room, which made Professor McGonagall scowl even more darkly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore’s instructions were to keep the school running as normally as possible,’ she said. ‘And that, I need hardly point out, means finding out how much you have learned this year.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked down at the pair of white rabbits he was supposed to be turning into slippers. What had he learned so far this </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber of Secrets 211 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">year? He couldn’t seem to think of anything that would be useful in an exam. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron looked as though he’d just been told he had to go and live in the Forbidden Forest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you imagine me taking exams with this?’ he asked Harry, holding up his wand, which had just started whistling loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Three days before their first exam, Professor McGonagall made another announcement at breakfast. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have good news,’ she said, and the Great Hall, instead of falling silent, erupted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore’s coming back!’ several people yelled joyfully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve caught the heir of Slytherin!’ squealed a girl on the Ravenclaw table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quidditch matches are back on!’ roared Wood excitedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When the hubbub had subsided, Professor McGonagall said, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Sprout has informed me that the Mandrakes are ready for cutting at last. Tonight, we will be able to revive those people who have been Petrified. I need hardly remind you all that one of them may well be able to tell us who, or what, attacked them. I am hopeful that this dreadful year will end with our catching the culprit.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was an explosion of cheering. Harry looked over at the Slytherin table and wasn’t at all surprised to see that Draco Malfoy hadn’t joined in. Ron, however, was looking happier than he’d looked in days. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It won’t matter that we never asked Myrtle, then!’ he said to Harry. ‘Hermione’ll probably have all the answers when they wake her up! Mind you, she’ll go mad when she finds out we’ve got exams in three days’ time. She hasn’t revised. It might be kinder to leave her where she is till they’re over.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Just then, Ginny Weasley came over and sat down next to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She looked tense and nervous, and Harry noticed that her hands were twisting in her lap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up?’ said Ron, helping himself to more porridge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny didn’t say anything, but glanced up and down the Gryffindor table with a scared look on her face that reminded Harry of someone, though he couldn’t think who. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Spit it out,’ said Ron, watching her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry suddenly realised who Ginny looked like. She was </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>212 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">rocking backwards and forwards slightly in her chair, exactly like Dobby did when he was teetering on the edge of revealing forbidden information. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve got to tell you something,’ Ginny mumbled, carefully not looking at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What is it?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny looked as though she couldn’t find the right words. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What? </i>’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny opened her mouth, but no sound came out. Harry leaned forward and spoke quietly, so that only Ginny and Ron could hear him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is it something about the Chamber of Secrets? Have you seen something? Someone acting oddly?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny drew a deep breath and, at that precise moment, Percy Weasley appeared, looking tired and wan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you’ve finished eating, I’ll take that seat, Ginny. I’m starving, I’ve only just come off patrol duty.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny jumped up as though her chair had just been electrified, gave Percy a fleeting, frightened look, and scarpered away. Percy sat down and grabbed a mug from the centre of the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Percy!’ said Ron angrily. ‘She was just about to tell us something important!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Halfway through a gulp of tea, Percy choked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What sort of thing?’ he said, coughing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I just asked her if she’d seen anything odd, and she started to say –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – that – that’s nothing to do with the Chamber of Secrets,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Percy at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How do you know?’ said Ron, his eyebrows raised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, er, if you must know, Ginny, er, walked in on me the other day when I was – well, never mind – the point is, she spotted me doing something and I, um, I asked her not to mention it to anybody. I must say, I did think she’d keep her word. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It’s nothing, really, I’d just rather –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never seen Percy look so uncomfortable. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What were you doing, Percy?’ said Ron, grinning. ‘Go on, tell us, we won’t laugh.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy didn’t smile back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pass me those rolls, Harry, I’m starving.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber of Secrets 213 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knew the whole mystery might be solved tomorrow without their help, but he wasn’t about to pass up a chance to speak to Myrtle if it turned up – and to his delight it did, mid-morning, when they were being led to History of Magic by Gilderoy Lockhart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart, who had so often assured them that all danger had passed, only to be proved wrong straight away, was now whole-heartedly convinced that it was hardly worth the trouble to see them safely down the corridors. His hair wasn’t as sleek as usual; it seemed he had been up most of the night, patrolling the fourth floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mark my words,’ he said, ushering them around a corner, ‘the first words out of those poor Petrified people’s mouths will be, “<i class=\"calibre4\">It</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">was Hagrid</i>.” Frankly, I’m astounded Professor McGonagall thinks all these security measures are necessary.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I agree, sir,’ said Harry, making Ron drop his books in surprise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, Harry,’ said Lockhart graciously, while they waited for a long line of Hufflepuffs to pass. ‘I mean, we teachers have quite enough to be getting on with, without walking students to classes and standing guard all night …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s right,’ said Ron, catching on. ‘Why don’t you leave us here, sir, we’ve only got one more corridor to go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know, Weasley, I think I will,’ said Lockhart. ‘I really should go and prepare my next class.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he hurried off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Prepare his class,’ Ron sneered after him. ‘Gone to curl his hair, more like.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They let the rest of the Gryffindors draw ahead of them, then darted down a side passage and hurried off towards Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. But just as they were congratulating each other on their brilliant scheme … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter! Weasley! What are you doing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Professor McGonagall, and her mouth was the thinnest of thin lines. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We were – we were –’ Ron stammered, ‘we were going to – to go and see –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione,’ said Harry. Ron and Professor McGonagall both looked at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We haven’t seen her for ages, Professor,’ Harry went on hurriedly, treading on Ron’s foot, ‘and we thought we’d sneak into the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>214 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">hospital wing, you know, and tell her the Mandrakes are nearly ready and, er, not to worry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall was still staring at him, and for a moment, Harry thought she was going to explode, but when she spoke, it was in a strangely croaky voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course,’ she said, and Harry, amazed, saw a tear glistening in her beady eye. ‘Of course, I realise this has all been hardest on the friends of those who have been … I quite understand. Yes, Potter, of course you may visit Miss Granger. I will inform Professor Binns where you’ve gone. Tell Madam Pomfrey I have given my permission.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron walked away, hardly daring to believe that they’d avoided detention. As they turned the corner, they distinctly heard Professor McGonagall blow her nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That,’ said Ron fervently, ‘was the best story you’ve ever come up with.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had no choice now but to go to the hospital wing and tell Madam Pomfrey that they had Professor McGonagall’s permission to visit Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey let them in, but reluctantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s just no  <i class=\"calibre4\">point</i> talking to a Petrified person,’ she said, and they had to admit she was right when they’d taken their seats next to Hermione. It was plain that Hermione didn’t have the faintest inkling that she had visitors, and that they might just as well tell her bedside cabinet not to worry for all the good it would do. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wonder if she did see the attacker, though?’ said Ron, looking sadly at Hermione’s rigid face. ‘Because if he sneaked up on them all, no one’ll ever know …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry wasn’t looking at Hermione’s face. He was more interested in her right hand. It lay clenched on top of her blankets, and bending closer, he saw that a piece of paper was scrunched inside her fist. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Making sure that Madam Pomfrey was nowhere near, he pointed this out to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Try and get it out,’ Ron whispered, shifting his chair so that he blocked Harry from Madam Pomfrey’s view. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was no easy task. Hermione’s hand was clamped so tightly around the paper that Harry was sure he was going to tear it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">While Ron kept watch he tugged and twisted, and at last, after several tense minutes, the paper came free. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber of Secrets 215 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a page torn from a very old library book. Harry smoothed it out eagerly and Ron leaned close to read it too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Of the many fearsome beasts and monsters that roam our land,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">there is none more curious or more deadly than the Basilisk,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">known also as the King of Serpents. This snake, which may</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">reach gigantic size, and live many hundreds of years, is born</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">from a chicken’s egg, hatched beneath a toad. Its methods of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">killing are most wondrous, for aside from its deadly and venomous fangs, the Basilisk has a murderous stare, and all who are</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">fixed with the beam of its eye shall suffer instant death. Spiders</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">flee before the Basilisk, for it is their mortal enemy, and the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Basilisk flees only from the crowing of the rooster, which is fatal</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">to it. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And beneath this, a single word had been written, in a hand Harry recognised as Hermione’s.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Pipes. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was as though somebody had just flicked a light on in his brain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron,’ he breathed, ‘this is it. This is the answer. The monster in the Chamber’s a  <i class=\"calibre4\">Basilisk</i> – a giant serpent!  <i class=\"calibre4\">That’s</i> why I’ve been hearing that voice all over the place, and nobody else has heard it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It’s because I understand Parseltongue …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up at the beds around him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Basilisk kills people by looking at them. But no one’s died </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– because no one looked it straight in the eye. Colin saw it through his camera. The Basilisk burned up all the film inside it, but Colin just got Petrified. Justin … Justin must’ve seen the Basilisk through Nearly Headless Nick! Nick got the full blast of it, but he couldn’t die  <i class=\"calibre4\">again</i> … and Hermione and that Ravenclaw Prefect were found with a mirror next to them. Hermione had just realised the monster was a Basilisk. I bet you anything she warned the first person she met to look round corners with a mirror first! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And that girl pulled out her mirror – and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s jaw had dropped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And Mrs Norris?’ he whispered eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry thought hard, picturing the scene on the night of Hallowe’en. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The water …’ he said slowly, ‘the flood from Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. I bet you Mrs Norris only saw the reflection …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>216 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He scanned the page in his hand eagerly. The more he looked at it, the more it made sense. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">The Basilisk flees only from the crowing of the rooster, which is</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">fatal to it! </i>’ he read aloud. ‘Hagrid’s roosters were killed! The heir of Slytherin didn’t want one anywhere near the castle once the Chamber was opened!  <i class=\"calibre4\">Spiders flee before the Basilisk! </i> It all fits!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But how’s the Basilisk been getting around the place?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A dirty great snake … Someone would’ve seen …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, however, pointed at the word Hermione had scribbled at the foot of the page. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pipes,’ he said. ‘Pipes … Ron, it’s been using the plumbing. I’ve been hearing that voice inside the walls …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron suddenly grabbed Harry’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The entrance to the Chamber of Secrets!’ he said hoarsely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What if it’s a bathroom? What if it’s in –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– <i class=\"calibre4\"> Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom</i>,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They sat there, excitement coursing through them, hardly able to believe it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This means,’ said Harry, ‘I can’t be the only Parselmouth in the school. The heir of Slytherin’s one, too. That’s how they’ve been controlling the Basilisk.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’re we going to do?’ said Ron, whose eyes were flashing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shall we go straight to McGonagall?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s go to the staff room,’ said Harry, jumping up. ‘She’ll be there in ten minutes, it’s nearly break.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They ran downstairs. Not wanting to be discovered hanging around in another corridor, they went straight into the deserted staff room. It was a large, panelled room full of dark wooden chairs. Harry and Ron paced around it, too excited to sit down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the bell to signal break never came. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Instead, echoing through the corridors came Professor McGonagall’s voice, magically magnified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">All students to return to their house dormitories at once. All</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">teachers return to the staff room. Immediately, please</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wheeled around to stare at Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not another attack? Not now?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’ll we do?’ said Ron, aghast. ‘Go back to the dormitory?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry, glancing around. There was an ugly sort of wardrobe to his left, full of the teachers’ cloaks. ‘In here. Let’s hear what it’s all about. Then we can tell them what we’ve found out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber of Secrets 217 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They hid themselves inside it, listening to the rumbling of hundreds of people moving overhead, and the staff-room door banging open. From between the musty folds of the cloaks, they watched the teachers filtering into the room. Some of them were looking puzzled, others downright scared. Then Professor McGonagall arrived. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It has happened,’ she told the silent staff room. ‘A student has been taken by the monster. Right into the Chamber itself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Flitwick let out a squeal. Professor Sprout clapped her hands over her mouth. Snape gripped the back of a chair very hard and said, ‘How can you be sure?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The heir of Slytherin,’ said Professor McGonagall, who was very white, ‘left another message. Right underneath the first one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Her skeleton will lie in the Chamber for ever</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Flitwick burst into tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who is it?’ said Madam Hooch, who had sunk, weak-kneed into a chair. ‘Which student?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ginny Weasley,’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt Ron slide silently down onto the wardrobe floor beside him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We shall have to send all the students home tomorrow,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘This is the end of Hogwarts. Dumbledore always said …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The staff-room door banged open again. For one wild moment, Harry was sure it would be Dumbledore. But it was Lockhart, and he was beaming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So sorry – dozed off – what have I missed?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He didn’t seem to notice that the other teachers were looking at him with something remarkably like hatred. Snape stepped forward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just the man,’ he said. ‘The very man. A girl has been snatched by the monster, Lockhart. Taken into the Chamber of Secrets itself. Your moment has come at last.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart blanched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s right, Gilderoy,’ chipped in Professor Sprout. ‘Weren’t you saying just last night that you’ve known all along where the entrance to the Chamber of Secrets is?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – well, I –’ spluttered Lockhart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, didn’t you tell me you were sure you knew what was inside it?’ piped up Professor Flitwick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>218 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D-did I? I don’t recall …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I certainly remember you saying you were sorry you hadn’t had a crack at the monster before Hagrid was arrested,’ said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Didn’t you say that the whole affair had been bungled, and that you should have been given a free rein from the first?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart stared around at his stony-faced colleagues. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I … I really never … You may have misunderstood …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll leave it to you, then, Gilderoy,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘Tonight will be an excellent time to do it. We’ll make sure everyone’s out of your way. You’ll be able to tackle the monster all by yourself. A free rein at last.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart gazed desperately around him, but nobody came to the rescue. He didn’t look remotely handsome any more. His lip was trembling, and in the absence of his usually toothy grin he looked weak-chinned and weedy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘V-very well,’ he said. ‘I’ll – I’ll be in my office, getting – getting ready.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he left the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Professor McGonagall, whose nostrils were flared, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘that’s got  <i class=\"calibre4\">him</i> out from under our feet. The Heads of Houses should go and inform their students what has happened. Tell them the Hogwarts Express will take them home first thing tomorrow. Will the rest of you please make sure no students have been left outside their dormitories.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The teachers rose, and left one by one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was probably the worst day of Harry’s entire life. He, Ron, Fred and George sat together in a corner of the Gryffindor common room, unable to say anything to each other. Percy wasn’t there. He had gone to send an owl to Mr and Mrs Weasley, then shut himself up in his dormitory. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No afternoon ever lasted as long as that one, nor had Gryffindor Tower ever been so crowded, yet so quiet. Near sunset, Fred and George went up to bed, unable to sit there any longer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She knew something, Harry,’ said Ron, speaking for the first time since they had entered the wardrobe in the staff room. ‘That’s why she was taken. It wasn’t some stupid thing about Percy at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She’d found out something about the Chamber of Secrets. That must be why she was –’ Ron rubbed his eyes frantically. ‘I mean, she was a pure-blood. There can’t be any other reason.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber of Secrets 219 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could see the sun sinking, blood red, below the skyline. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This was the worst he had ever felt. If only there was something they could do. Anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ said Ron, ‘d’you think there’s any chance at all she’s not </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– you know –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t know what to say. He couldn’t see how Ginny could still be alive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you  know  what?’  said  Ron,  ‘I  think  we  should  go  and  see Lockhart. Tell him what we know. He’s going to try and get into the Chamber. We can tell him where we think it is, and tell him it’s a Basilisk in there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Because Harry couldn’t think of anything else to do, and because he wanted to be doing something, he agreed. The Gryffindors around them were so miserable, and felt so sorry for the Weasleys, that nobody tried to stop them as they got up, crossed the room, and left through the portrait hole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Darkness was falling as they walked down to Lockhart’s office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There seemed to be a lot of activity going on inside it. They could hear scraping, thumps and hurried footsteps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knocked and there was a sudden silence from inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then the door opened the tiniest crack and they saw one of Lockhart’s eyes peering through it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh … Mr Potter … Mr Weasley …’ he said, opening the door a mite wider. ‘I’m rather busy at the moment. If you would be quick …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor, we’ve got some information for you,’ said Harry. ‘We think it’ll help you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – well – it’s not terribly –’ The side of Lockhart’s face that they could see looked very uncomfortable. ‘I mean – well – all right.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He opened the door and they entered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His office had been almost completely stripped. Two large trunks stood open on the floor. Robes, jade green, lilac, midnight blue, had been hastily folded into one of them; books were jumbled untidily into the other. The photographs that had covered the walls were now crammed into boxes on the desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you going somewhere?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er, well, yes,’ said Lockhart, ripping a life-size poster of himself from the back of the door as he spoke, and starting to roll it up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Urgent call … unavoidable … got to go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>220 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about my sister?’ said Ron jerkily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, as to that – most unfortunate,’ said Lockhart, avoiding their eyes as he wrenched open a drawer and started emptying the contents into a bag. ‘No one regrets more than I –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re the Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher!’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can’t go now! Not with all the dark stuff going on here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I must say … when I took the job …’ Lockhart muttered, now piling socks on top of his robes, ‘nothing in the job descrip-tion … didn’t expect …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You mean you’re  <i class=\"calibre4\">running away? </i>’ said Harry disbelievingly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘After all that stuff you did in your books?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Books can be misleading,’ said Lockhart delicately. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You wrote them!’ Harry shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear boy,’ said Lockhart, straightening up and frowning at Harry. ‘Do use your common sense. My books wouldn’t have sold half as well if people didn’t think  <i class=\"calibre4\">I’d</i> done all those things. No one wants to read about some ugly old Armenian warlock, even if he did save a village from werewolves. He’d look dreadful on the front cover. No dress sense at all. And the witch who banished the Bandon Banshee had a hairy chin. I mean, come on …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you’ve just been taking credit for what a load of other people have done?’ said Harry incredulously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, Harry,’ said Lockhart, shaking his head impatiently, ‘it’s not nearly as simple as that. There was work involved. I had to track these people down. Ask them exactly how they managed to do what they did. Then I had to put a Memory Charm on them so they wouldn’t remember doing it. If there’s one thing I pride myself on, it’s my Memory Charms. No, it’s been a lot of work, Harry. It’s not all book-signings and publicity photos, you know. You want fame, you have to be prepared for a long hard slog.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He banged the lids of his trunks shut and locked them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s see,’ he said. ‘I think that’s everything. Yes. Only one thing left.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled out his wand and turned to them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Awfully sorry, boys, but I’ll have to put a Memory Charm on you now. Can’t have you blabbing my secrets all over the place. I’d never sell another book …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry reached his wand just in time. Lockhart had barely raised his, when Harry bellowed, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expelliarmus! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber of Secrets 221 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart was blasted backwards, falling over his trunk. His wand flew high into the air; Ron caught it, and flung it out of the open window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shouldn’t have let Professor Snape teach us that one,’ said Harry furiously, kicking Lockhart’s trunk aside. Lockhart was looking up at him, weedy once more. Harry was still pointing his wand at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you want me to do?’ said Lockhart weakly. ‘I don’t know where the Chamber of Secrets is. There’s nothing I can do.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re in luck,’ said Harry, forcing Lockhart to his feet at wandpoint. ‘We think  <i class=\"calibre4\">we</i> know where it is.  <i class=\"calibre4\">And</i> what’s inside it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Let’s go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They marched Lockhart out of his office and down the nearest stairs, along the dark corridor where the messages shone on the wall, to the door of Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They sent Lockhart in first. Harry was pleased to see that he was shaking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Moaning Myrtle was sitting on the cistern of the end toilet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, it’s you,’ she said, when she saw Harry. ‘What do you want this time?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘To ask you how you died,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Myrtle’s whole aspect changed at once. She looked as though she had never been asked such a flattering question. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ooooh, it was dreadful,’ she said with relish. ‘It happened right in here. I died in this very cubicle. I remember it so well. I’d hidden because Olive Hornby was teasing me about my glasses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door was locked, and I was crying, and then I heard somebody come in. They said something funny. A different language, I think it must have been. Anyway, what really got me was that it was a  <i class=\"calibre4\">boy</i> speaking. So I unlocked the door, to tell him to go and use his own toilet, and then –’ Myrtle swelled importantly, her face shining, ‘I  <i class=\"calibre4\">died. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No idea,’ said Myrtle in hushed tones. ‘I just remember seeing a pair of great big yellow eyes. My whole body sort of seized up, and then I was floating away …’ She looked dreamily at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And then I came back again. I was determined to haunt Olive Hornby, you see. Oh, she was sorry she’d ever laughed at my glasses.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>222 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where exactly did you see the eyes?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Somewhere there,’ said Myrtle, pointing vaguely towards the sink in front of her toilet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron hurried over to it. Lockhart was standing well back, a look of utter terror on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It looked like an ordinary sink. They examined every inch of it, inside and out, including the pipes below. And then Harry saw it: scratched on the side of one of the copper taps was a tiny snake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That tap’s never worked,’ said Myrtle brightly, as he tried to turn it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ said Ron, ‘say something. Something in Parseltongue.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ Harry thought hard. The only times he’d ever managed to speak Parseltongue were when he’d been faced with a real snake. He stared hard at the tiny engraving, trying to imagine it was real. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Open up,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked at Ron, who shook his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘English,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked back at the snake, willing himself to believe it was alive. If he moved his head, the candlelight made it look as though it was moving. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Open up,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Except that the words weren’t what he heard; a strange hissing had escaped him, and at once the tap glowed with a brilliant white light and began to spin. Next second, the sink began to move. The sink, in fact, sank, right out of sight, leaving a large pipe exposed, a pipe wide enough for a man to slide into. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry heard Ron gasp and looked up again. He had made up his mind what he was going to do. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going down there,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He couldn’t not go, not now they had found the entrance to the Chamber, not if there was even the faintest, slimmest, wildest chance that Ginny might be alive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Me too,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a pause. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, you hardly seem to need me,’ said Lockhart, with a shadow of his old smile. ‘I’ll just –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He put his hand on the door knob, but Ron and Harry both pointed their wands at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can go first,’ Ron snarled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber of Secrets 223 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">White-faced and wandless, Lockhart approached the opening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Boys,’ he said, his voice feeble, ‘boys, what good will it do?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jabbed him in the back with his wand. Lockhart slid his legs into the pipe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I really don’t think –’ he started to say, but Ron gave him a push, and he slid out of sight. Harry followed quickly. He lowered himself slowly into the pipe, then let go. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was like rushing down an endless, slimy, dark slide. He could see more pipes branching off in all directions, but none as large as theirs, which twisted and turned, sloping steeply downwards, and he knew that he was falling deeper below the school than even the dungeons. Behind him he could hear Ron, thudding slightly at the curves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then, just as he had begun to worry about what would happen when he hit the ground, the pipe levelled out, and he shot out of the end with a wet thud, landing on the damp floor of a dark stone tunnel, large enough to stand in. Lockhart was getting to his feet a little way away, covered in slime and white as a ghost. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood aside as Ron came whizzing out of the pipe, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We must be miles under the school,’ said Harry, his voice echoing in the black tunnel. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Under the lake, probably,’ said Ron, squinting around at the dark, slimy walls. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All three of them turned to stare into the darkness ahead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lumos! </i>’ Harry muttered to his wand and it lit again. ‘C’mon,’  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he said to Ron and Lockhart, and off they went, their footsteps slapping loudly on the wet floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The tunnel was so dark that they could only see a little distance ahead. Their shadows on the wet walls looked monstrous in the wandlight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Remember,’ Harry said quietly, as they walked cautiously forward, ‘any sign of movement, close your eyes straight away …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the tunnel was quiet as the grave, and the first unexpected sound they heard was a loud  <i class=\"calibre4\">crunch</i> as Ron stepped on what turned out to be a rat’s skull. Harry lowered his wand to look at the floor and saw that it was littered with small animal bones. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Trying very hard not to imagine what Ginny might look like if they found her, Harry led the way forward, round a dark bend in the tunnel. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, there’s something up there …’ said Ron hoarsely, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>224 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">grabbing Harry’s shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They froze, watching. Harry could just see the outline of something huge and curved, lying right across the tunnel. It wasn’t moving. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe it’s asleep,’ he breathed, glancing back at the other two. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart’s hands were pressed over his eyes. Harry turned back to look at the thing, his heart beating so fast it hurt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Very slowly, his eyes as narrow as he could make them and still see, Harry edged forward, his wand held high. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The light slid over a gigantic snake skin, of a vivid, poisonous green, lying curled and empty across the tunnel floor. The creature that had shed it must have been twenty feet long at least. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Blimey,’ said Ron weakly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a sudden movement behind them. Gilderoy Lockhart’s knees had given way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get up,’ said Ron sharply, pointing his wand at Lockhart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart got to his feet – then he dived at Ron, knocking him to the ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jumped forward, but too late. Lockhart was straightening up, panting, Ron’s wand in his hand and a gleaming smile back on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The adventure ends here, boys!’ he said. ‘I shall take a bit of this skin back up to the school, tell them I was too late to save the girl, and that you two  <i class=\"calibre4\">tragically</i> lost your minds at the sight of her mangled body. Say goodbye to your memories!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He raised Ron’s Spellotaped wand high over his head and yelled, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Obliviate! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The wand exploded with the force of a small bomb. Harry flung his arms over his head and ran, slipping over the coils of snake skin, out of the way of great chunks of tunnel ceiling which were thundering to the floor. Next moment, he was standing alone, gazing at a solid wall of broken rock. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron!’ he shouted. ‘Are you OK? Ron!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m here!’ came Ron’s muffled voice from behind the rockfall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m OK. This git’s not, though – he got blasted by the wand.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a dull thud and a loud ‘ow!’. It sounded as though Ron had just kicked Lockhart in the shins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What now?’ Ron’s voice said, sounding desperate. ‘We can’t get through. It’ll take ages …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up at the tunnel ceiling. Huge cracks had </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber of Secrets 225 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">appeared in it. He had never tried to break apart anything as large as these rocks by magic, and now didn’t seem a good moment to try – what if the whole tunnel caved in? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was another thud and another ‘ow!’ from behind the rocks. They were wasting time. Ginny had already been in the Chamber of Secrets for hours. Harry knew there was only one thing to do. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wait there,’ he called to Ron. ‘Wait with Lockhart. I’ll go on. If I’m not back in an hour …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a very pregnant pause. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll try and shift some of this rock,’ said Ron, who seemed to be trying to keep his voice steady. ‘So you can – can get back through. And, Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you in a bit,’ said Harry, trying to inject some confidence into his shaking voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he set off alone past the giant snake skin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Soon the distant noise of Ron straining to shift the rocks was gone. The tunnel turned and turned again. Every nerve in Harry’s body was tingling unpleasantly. He wanted the tunnel to end, yet dreaded what he’d find when it did. And then, at last, as he crept around yet another bend, he saw a solid wall ahead on which two entwined serpents were carved, their eyes set with great, glinting emeralds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry approached, his throat very dry. There was no need to pretend these stone snakes were real, their eyes looked strangely alive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He could guess what he had to do. He cleared his throat, and the emerald eyes seemed to flicker. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Open</i>,’ said Harry, in a low, faint hiss. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The serpents parted as the wall cracked open, the halves slid smoothly out of sight, and Harry, shaking from head to foot, walked inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER SEVENTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Heir of Slytherin</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was standing at the end of a very long, dimly lit chamber. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Towering stone pillars entwined with more carved serpents rose to support a ceiling lost in darkness, casting long black shadows through the odd, greenish gloom that filled the place. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His heart beating very fast, Harry stood listening to the chill silence. Could the Basilisk be lurking in a shadowy corner, behind a pillar? And where was Ginny? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled out his wand and moved forward between the ser-pentine columns. Every careful footstep echoed loudly off the shadowy walls. He kept his eyes narrowed, ready to clamp them shut at the smallest sign of movement. The hollow eye sockets of the stone snakes seemed to be following him. More than once, with a jolt of the stomach, he thought he saw one stir. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, as he drew level with the last pair of pillars, a statue high as the Chamber itself loomed into view, standing against the back wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had to crane his neck to look up into the giant face above: it was ancient and monkey-like, with a long thin beard that fell almost to the bottom of the wizard’s sweeping stone robes, where two enormous grey feet stood on the smooth chamber floor. And between the feet, face down, lay a small, black-robed figure with flaming red hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ginny! </i>’ Harry muttered, sprinting to her and dropping to his knees. ‘Ginny! Don’t be dead! Please don’t be dead!’ He flung his wand aside, grabbed Ginny’s shoulders and turned her over. Her face was white as marble, and as cold, yet her eyes were closed, so she wasn’t Petrified. But then she must be … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ginny, please wake up,’ Harry muttered desperately, shaking her. Ginny’s head lolled hopelessly from side to side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She won’t wake,’ said a soft voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Heir of Slytherin 227 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jumped and spun around on his knees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A tall, black-haired boy was leaning against the nearest pillar, watching. He was strangely blurred around the edges, as though Harry was looking at him through a misted window. But there was no mistaking him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tom –  <i class=\"calibre4\">Tom Riddle? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle nodded, not taking his eyes off Harry’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you mean, she won’t wake?’ Harry said desperately. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She’s not – she’s not –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She’s still alive,’ said Riddle. ‘But only just.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at him. Tom Riddle had been at Hogwarts fifty years ago, yet here he stood, a weird, misty light shining about him, not a day older than sixteen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you a ghost?’ Harry said uncertainly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A memory,’ said Riddle quietly. ‘Preserved in a diary for fifty years.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pointed towards the floor near the statue’s giant toes. Lying open there was the little black diary Harry had found in Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom. For a second, Harry wondered how it had got there – but there were more pressing matters to deal with. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve got to help me, Tom,’ Harry said, raising Ginny’s head again. ‘We’ve got to get her out of here. There’s a Basilisk … I don’t know where it is, but it could be along any moment. Please, help me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle didn’t move. Harry, sweating, managed to hoist Ginny half off the floor, and bent to pick up his wand again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But his wand had gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you see –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked up. Riddle was still watching him – twirling Harry’s wand between his long fingers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thanks,’ said Harry, stretching out his hand for it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A smile curled the corners of Riddle’s mouth. He continued to stare at Harry, twirling the wand idly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Listen,’ said Harry urgently, his knees sagging with Ginny’s dead weight, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">we’ve got to go! </i> If the Basilisk comes …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It won’t come until it is called,’ said Riddle calmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry lowered Ginny back onto the floor, unable to hold her up any longer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you mean?’ he said. ‘Look, give me my wand, I might need it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>228 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle’s smile broadened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You won’t be needing it,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you mean, I won’t be –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve waited a long time for this, Harry Potter,’ said Riddle. ‘For the chance to see you. To speak to you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look,’ said Harry, losing patience, ‘I don’t think you get it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We’re in the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Chamber of Secrets. </i> We can talk later.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re going to talk now,’ said Riddle, still smiling broadly, and he pocketed Harry’s wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at him. There was something very funny going on here. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did Ginny get like this?’ he asked slowly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, that’s an interesting question,’ said Riddle pleasantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And quite a long story. I suppose the real reason Ginny Weasley’s like this is because she opened her heart and spilled all her secrets to an invisible stranger.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you talking about?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The diary,’ said Riddle. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">My</i> diary. Little Ginny’s been writing in it for months and months, telling me all her pitiful worries and woes: how her brothers  <i class=\"calibre4\">tease</i> her, how she had to come to school with second-hand robes and books, how –’ Riddle’s eyes glinted  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– how she didn’t think famous, good, great Harry Potter would <i class=\"calibre4\">ever</i> like her …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All the time he spoke, Riddle’s eyes never left Harry’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was an almost hungry look in them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s very  <i class=\"calibre4\">boring, </i> having to listen to the silly little troubles of an eleven-year-old girl,’ he went on. ‘But I was patient. I wrote back, I was sympathetic, I was kind. Ginny simply  <i class=\"calibre4\">loved</i> me.  <i class=\"calibre4\">No one’s ever</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">understood me like you, Tom … I’m so glad I’ve got this diary to confide in … It’s like having a friend I can carry round in my pocket</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle laughed, a high, cold laugh that didn’t suit him. It made the hairs stand up on the back of Harry’s neck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I say it myself, Harry, I’ve always been able to charm the people I needed. So Ginny poured out her soul to me, and her soul happened to be exactly what I wanted. I grew stronger and stronger on a diet of her deepest fears, her darkest secrets. I grew powerful, far more powerful than little Miss Weasley. Powerful enough to start feeding Miss Weasley a few of  <i class=\"calibre4\">my</i> secrets, to start pouring a little of  <i class=\"calibre4\">my</i> soul back into  <i class=\"calibre4\">her</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Heir of Slytherin 229 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you mean?’ said Harry, whose mouth had gone very dry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Haven’t you guessed yet, Harry Potter?’ said Riddle softly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ginny Weasley opened the Chamber of Secrets. She strangled the school roosters and daubed threatening messages on the walls. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She set the serpent of Slytherin on four Mudbloods, and the Squib’s cat.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ Harry whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Riddle, calmly. ‘Of course, she didn’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">know</i> what she was doing at first. It was very amusing. I wish you could have seen her new diary entries … Far more interesting, they became … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Tom</i>,’ he recited, watching Harry’s horrified face, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I think I’m</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">losing my memory. There are rooster feathers all over my robes and I</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">don’t know how they got there. Dear Tom, I can’t remember what I did</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">on the night of Hallowe’en, but a cat was attacked and I’ve got paint</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">all down my front. Dear Tom, Percy keeps telling me I’m pale and I’m</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">not myself. I think he suspects me … There was another attack today</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">and I don’t know where I was. Tom, what am I going to do? I think I’m</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">going mad … I think I’m the one attacking everyone, Tom! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s fists were clenched, the nails digging deep into his palms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It took a very long time for stupid little Ginny to stop trusting her diary,’ said Riddle. ‘But she finally became suspicious and tried to dispose of it. And that’s where  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> came in, Harry. You found it, and I couldn’t have been more delighted. Of all the people who could have picked it up, it was  <i class=\"calibre4\">you, </i> the very person I was most anxious to meet …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And why did you want to meet me?’ said Harry. Anger was coursing through him and it was an effort to keep his voice steady. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, you see, Ginny told me all about you, Harry,’ said Riddle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your whole  <i class=\"calibre4\">fascinating</i> history.’ His eyes roved over the lightning scar on Harry’s forehead, and his expression grew hungrier. ‘I knew  I  must  find  out  more  about  you,  talk  to  you,  meet  you  if  I could. So I decided to show you my famous capture of that great oaf, Hagrid, to gain your trust.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid’s my friend,’ said Harry, his voice now shaking. ‘And you framed him, didn’t you? I thought you made a mistake, but –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle laughed his high laugh again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was my word against Hagrid’s, Harry. Well, you can imagine how it looked to old Armando Dippet. On the one hand, Tom </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>230 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle, poor but brilliant, parentless but so  <i class=\"calibre4\">brave, </i> school Prefect, model student; on the other hand, big, blundering Hagrid, in trouble every other week, trying to raise werewolf cubs under his bed, sneaking off to the Forbidden Forest to wrestle trolls. But I admit, even  <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> was surprised how well the plan worked. I thought <i class=\"calibre4\">someone</i> must realise that Hagrid couldn’t possibly be the heir of Slytherin. It had taken  <i class=\"calibre4\">me</i> five whole years to find out everything I could about the Chamber of Secrets and discover the secret entrance … as though Hagrid had the brains, or the power! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Only the Transfiguration teacher, Dumbledore, seemed to think Hagrid was innocent. He persuaded Dippet to keep Hagrid and train him as gamekeeper. Yes, I think Dumbledore might have guessed. Dumbledore never seemed to like me as much as the other teachers did …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I bet Dumbledore saw right through you,’ said Harry, his teeth gritted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, he certainly kept an annoyingly close watch on me after Hagrid was expelled,’ said Riddle carelessly. ‘I knew it wouldn’t be safe to open the Chamber again while I was still at school. But I wasn’t going to waste those long years I’d spent searching for it. I decided to leave behind a diary, preserving my sixteen-year-old self in its pages, so that one day, with luck, I would be able to lead another in my footsteps, and finish Salazar Slytherin’s noble work.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, you haven’t finished it,’ said Harry triumphantly. ‘No one’s died this time, not even the cat. In a few hours the Mandrake Draught will be ready and everyone who was Petrified will be all right again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Haven’t I already told you,’ said Riddle quietly, ‘that killing Mudbloods doesn’t matter to me any more? For many months now, my new target has been –  <i class=\"calibre4\">you. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Imagine how angry I was when the next time my diary was opened, it was Ginny who was writing to me, not you. She saw you with the diary, you see, and panicked. What if you found out how to work it, and I repeated all her secrets to you? What if, even worse, I told you who’d been strangling roosters? So the foolish little brat waited until your dormitory was deserted and stole it back. But I knew what I must do. It was clear to me that you were on the trail of Slytherin’s heir. From everything Ginny </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Heir of Slytherin 231 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">had told me about you, I knew you would go to any lengths to solve the mystery – particularly if one of your best friends was attacked. And Ginny had told me the whole school was buzzing because you could speak Parseltongue … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So I made Ginny write her own farewell on the wall and come down here to wait. She struggled and cried and became  <i class=\"calibre4\">very</i> boring. But there isn’t much life left in her: she put too much into the diary, into me. Enough to let me leave its pages at last. I have been waiting for you to appear since we arrived here. I knew you’d come. I have many questions for you, Harry Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Like what?’ Harry spat, fists still clenched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Riddle, smiling pleasantly, ‘how is it that a baby with no extraordinary magical talent managed to defeat the greatest wizard of all time? How did  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> escape with nothing but a scar, while Lord Voldemort’s powers were destroyed?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was an odd red gleam in his hungry eyes now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why do you care how I escaped?’ said Harry slowly. ‘Voldemort was after your time.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Voldemort,’ said Riddle softly, ‘is my past, present and future, Harry Potter …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled Harry’s wand from his pocket and began to trace it through the air, writing three shimmering words: TOM MARVOLO RIDDLE </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he waved the wand once, and the letters of his name re-arranged themselves: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I AM LORD VOLDEMORT </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You see?’ he whispered. ‘It was a name I was already using at Hogwarts, to my most intimate friends only, of course. You think I was going to use my filthy Muggle father’s name for ever? I, in whose veins runs the blood of Salazar Slytherin himself, through my mother’s side? I, keep the name of a foul, common Muggle, who abandoned me even before I was born, just because he found out his wife was a witch? No, Harry. I fashioned myself a new name, a name I knew wizards everywhere would one day fear to speak, when I had become the greatest sorcerer in the world!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s brain seemed to have jammed. He stared numbly at Riddle, at the orphaned boy who had grown up to murder Harry’s own parents, and so many others … At last he forced himself to speak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re not,’ he said, his quiet voice full of hatred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>232 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not what?’ snapped Riddle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not the greatest sorcerer in the world,’ said Harry, breathing fast. ‘Sorry to disappoint you, and all that, but the greatest wizard in the world is Albus Dumbledore. Everyone says so. Even when you were strong, you didn’t dare try and take over at Hogwarts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore saw through you when you were at school and he still frightens you now, wherever you’re hiding these days.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The smile had gone from Riddle’s face, to be replaced by a very ugly look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore’s been driven out of this castle by the mere <i class=\"calibre4\">memory</i> of me!’ he hissed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s not as gone as you might think!’ Harry retorted. He was speaking at random, wanting to scare Riddle, wishing rather than believing it to be true. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle opened his mouth, but froze. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Music was coming from somewhere. Riddle whirled around to stare down the empty chamber. The music was growing louder. It was eerie, spine-tingling, unearthly; it lifted the hair on Harry’s scalp and made his heart feel as though it was swelling to twice its normal size. Then, as the music reached such a pitch that Harry felt it vibrating inside his own ribs, flames erupted at the top of the nearest pillar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A crimson bird the size of a swan had appeared, piping its weird music to the vaulted ceiling. It had a glittering golden tail as long as a peacock’s and gleaming golden talons, which were gripping a ragged bundle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A second later, the bird was flying straight at Harry. It dropped the ragged thing it was carrying at his feet, then landed heavily on his shoulder. As it folded its great wings, Harry looked up and saw it had a long, sharp golden beak and beady black eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The bird stopped singing. It sat still and warm next to Harry’s cheek, gazing steadily at Riddle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s a phoenix …’ said Riddle, staring shrewdly back at it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Fawkes? </i>’ Harry breathed, and he felt the bird’s golden claws squeeze his shoulder gently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And   <i class=\"calibre4\">that</i> –’ said Riddle, now eyeing the ragged thing that Fawkes had dropped, ‘that’s the old school Sorting Hat.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So it was. Patched, frayed and dirty, the Hat lay motionless at Harry’s feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle began to laugh again. He laughed so hard that the dark </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Heir of Slytherin 233 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">chamber rang with it, as though ten Riddles were laughing at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is what Dumbledore sends his defender! A songbird and an old hat! Do you feel brave, Harry Potter? Do you feel safe now?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t answer. He might not see what use Fawkes or the Sorting Hat were, but he was no longer alone, and he waited with mounting courage for Riddle to stop laughing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘To business, Harry,’ said Riddle, still smiling broadly. ‘Twice – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">in  <i class=\"calibre4\">your</i> past, in  <i class=\"calibre4\">my</i> future – we have met. And twice I failed to kill you.  <i class=\"calibre4\">How did you survive? </i> Tell me everything. The longer you talk,’ he added softly, ‘the longer you stay alive.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was thinking fast, weighing his chances. Riddle had the wand. He, Harry, had Fawkes and the Sorting Hat, neither of which would be much good in a duel. It looked bad, all right. But the longer Riddle stood there, the more life was dwindling out of Ginny … and in the meantime, Harry noticed suddenly, Riddle’s outline was becoming clearer, more solid. If it had to be a fight between him and Riddle, better sooner than later. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one knows why you lost your powers when you attacked me,’ said Harry abruptly. ‘I don’t know myself. But I know why you couldn’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">kill</i> me. Because my mother died to save me. My common  <i class=\"calibre4\">Muggle-born</i> mother,’ he added, shaking with suppressed rage. ‘She stopped you killing me. And I’ve seen the real you, I saw you last year. You’re a wreck. You’re barely alive. That’s where all your power got you. You’re in hiding. You’re ugly, you’re foul!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Riddle’s face contorted. Then he forced it into an awful smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So.  Your  mother  died  to  save  you.  Yes,  that’s  a  powerful counter-charm. I can see now – there is nothing special about you, after all. I wondered, you see. Because there are strange like-nesses between us, Harry Potter. Even you must have noticed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both half-bloods, orphans, raised by Muggles. Probably the only two Parselmouths to come to Hogwarts since the great Slytherin himself. We even  <i class=\"calibre4\">look</i> something alike … But after all, it was merely a lucky chance that saved you from me. That’s all I wanted to know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood, tense, waiting for Riddle to raise his wand. But Riddle’s twisted smile was widening again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, Harry, I’m going to teach you a little lesson. Let’s match the powers of Lord Voldemort, heir of Salazar Slytherin, against famous Harry Potter, and the best weapons Dumbledore can give him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>234 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He cast an amused eye over Fawkes and the Sorting Hat, then walked away. Harry, fear spreading up his numb legs, watched Riddle stop between the high pillars and look up into the stone face of Slytherin, high above him in the half-darkness. Riddle opened his mouth wide and hissed – but Harry understood what he was saying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Speak to me, Slytherin, greatest of the Hogwarts Four</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wheeled around to look up at the statue, Fawkes swaying on his shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slytherin’s gigantic stone face was moving. Horror-struck, Harry saw his mouth opening, wider and wider, to make a huge black hole. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And something was stirring inside the statue’s mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something was slithering up from its depths. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry backed away until he hit the dark Chamber wall, and as he shut his eyes tight he felt Fawkes’s wing sweep his cheek as he took flight. Harry wanted to shout, ‘Don’t leave me!’ but what chance did a phoenix have against the king of serpents? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something huge hit the stone floor of the chamber, Harry felt it shudder. He knew what was happening, he could sense it, could almost see the giant serpent uncoiling itself from Slytherin’s mouth. Then he heard Riddle’s hissing voice: ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Kill him</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Basilisk was moving towards Harry, he could hear its heavy body slithering ponderously across the dusty floor. Eyes still tightly shut, Harry began to run blindly sideways, his hands outstretched, feeling his way. Riddle was laughing … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tripped. He fell hard onto the stone and tasted blood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The serpent was barely feet from him, he could hear it coming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud, explosive spitting sound right above him and then something heavy hit Harry so hard that he was smashed against the wall. Waiting for fangs to sink through his body he heard more mad hissing, something thrashing wildly off the pillars. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He couldn’t help it. He opened his eyes wide enough to squint at what was going on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The enormous serpent, bright, poisonous green, thick as an oak trunk, had raised itself high in the air and its great blunt head was weaving drunkenly between the pillars. As Harry trembled, ready to close his eyes if it turned, he saw what had distracted the snake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fawkes was soaring around its head, and the Basilisk was </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Heir of Slytherin 235 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">snapping furiously at him with fangs long and thin as sabres. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fawkes dived. His long golden beak sank out of sight and a sudden shower of dark blood spattered the floor. The snake’s tail thrashed, narrowly missing Harry, and before Harry could shut his eyes, it turned. Harry looked straight into its face, and saw that its eyes, both its great bulbous yellow eyes, had been punctured by the phoenix; blood was streaming to the floor and the snake was spitting in agony. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">No! </i>’ Harry heard Riddle screaming. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Leave the bird! Leave the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">bird! The boy is behind you! You can still smell him! Kill him! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The blinded serpent swayed, confused, still deadly. Fawkes was circling its head, piping his eerie song, jabbing here and there at the Basilisk’s scaly nose as the blood poured from its ruined eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Help me, help me,’ Harry muttered wildly, ‘someone, anyone!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The snake’s tail whipped across the floor again. Harry ducked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something soft hit his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Basilisk had swept the Sorting Hat into Harry’s arms. Harry seized it. It was all he had left, his only chance. He rammed it onto his head and threw himself flat onto the floor as the Basilisk’s tail swung over him again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Help me … help me </i>…’ Harry thought, his eyes screwed tight under the Hat. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Please help me! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was no answering voice. Instead, the Hat contracted, as though an invisible hand was squeezing it very tightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something very hard and heavy thudded onto the top of Harry’s head, almost knocking him out. Stars winking in front of his eyes, he grabbed the top of the Hat to pull it off and felt something long and hard beneath it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A gleaming silver sword had appeared inside the Hat, its handle glittering with rubies the size of eggs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Kill the boy! Leave the bird! The boy is behind you! Sniff – smell</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">him! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was on his feet, ready. The Basilisk’s head was falling, its body coiling around, hitting pillars as it twisted to face him. He could see the vast, bloody eye sockets, see the mouth stretching wide, wide enough to swallow him whole, lined with fangs long as his sword, thin, glittering, venomous … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It lunged blindly. Harry dodged and it hit the Chamber wall. It lunged again, and its forked tongue lashed Harry’s side. He raised the sword in both his hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>236 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Basilisk lunged again, and this time its aim was true. Harry threw his whole weight behind the sword and drove it to the hilt into the roof of the serpent’s mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000003999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But as warm blood drenched Harry’s arms, he felt a searing pain just above his elbow. One long, poisonous fang was sinking deeper and deeper into his arm and it splintered as the Basilisk keeled over sideways and fell, twitching, to the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry slid down the wall. He gripped the fang that was spreading poison through his body and wrenched it out of his arm. But he knew it was too late. White-hot pain was spreading slowly and steadily from the wound. Even as he dropped the fang and watched his own blood soaking his robes, his vision went foggy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Chamber was dissolving in a whirl of dull colour. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A patch of scarlet swam past and Harry heard a soft clatter of claws beside him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fawkes,’ said Harry thickly. ‘You were brilliant, Fawkes …’ He felt the bird lay its beautiful head on the spot where the serpent’s fang had pierced him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He could hear echoing footsteps and then a dark shadow moved in front of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re dead, Harry Potter,’ said Riddle’s voice above him. ‘Dead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Even Dumbledore’s bird knows it. Do you see what he’s doing, Potter? He’s crying.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry blinked. Fawkes’s head slid in and out of focus. Thick, pearly tears were trickling down the glossy feathers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going to sit here and watch you die, Harry Potter. Take your time. I’m in no hurry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt drowsy. Everything around him seemed to be spinning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So ends the famous Harry Potter,’ said Riddle’s distant voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Alone in the Chamber of Secrets, forsaken by his friends, defeated at last by the Dark Lord he so unwisely challenged. You’ll be back with your dear Mudblood mother soon, Harry … She bought you twelve years of borrowed time … but Lord Voldemort got you in the end, as you knew he must.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">If this is dying, thought Harry, it’s not so bad. Even the pain was leaving him … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But was this dying? Instead of going black, the Chamber seemed to be coming back into focus. Harry gave his head a little shake and there was Fawkes, still resting his head on Harry’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Heir of Slytherin 237 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A pearly patch of tears was shining all around the wound – except that there  <i class=\"calibre4\">was</i> no wound. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get away, bird,’ said Riddle’s voice suddenly. ‘Get away from him. I said,  <i class=\"calibre4\">get away! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry raised his head. Riddle was pointing Harry’s wand at Fawkes; there was a bang like a gun and Fawkes took flight again in a whirl of gold and scarlet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Phoenix tears …’ said Riddle quietly, staring at Harry’s arm. ‘Of course … healing powers … I forgot …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked into Harry’s face. ‘But it makes no difference. In fact, I prefer it this way. Just you and me, Harry Potter … you and me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He raised the wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, in a rush of wings, Fawkes soared back overhead and something fell into Harry’s lap –  <i class=\"calibre4\">the diary. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a split second, both Harry and Riddle, wand still raised, stared at it. Then, without thinking, without considering, as though he had meant to do it all along, Harry seized the Basilisk fang on the floor next to him and plunged it straight into the heart of the book. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a long, dreadful, piercing scream. Ink spurted out of the diary in torrents, streaming over Harry’s hands, flooding the floor. Riddle was writhing and twisting, screaming and flailing and then … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had gone. Harry’s wand fell to the floor with a clatter and there was silence. Silence except for the steady  <i class=\"calibre4\">drip drip</i> of ink still oozing from the diary. The Basilisk venom had burned a sizzling hole right through it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Shaking all over, Harry pulled himself up. His head was spinning as though he’d just travelled miles by Floo powder. Slowly, he gathered together his wand and the Sorting Hat, and, with a huge tug, retrieved the glittering sword from the roof of the Basilisk’s mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then came a faint moan from the end of the Chamber. Ginny was stirring. As Harry hurried towards her, she sat up. Her bemused eyes travelled from the huge form of the dead Basilisk, over Harry, in his blood-soaked robes, then to the diary in his hand. She drew a great, shuddering gasp and tears began to pour down her face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry – oh, Harry – I tried to tell you at b-breakfast, but I c- <i class=\"calibre4\">couldn’t</i>  say  it  in  front  of  Percy.  It  was   <i class=\"calibre4\">me, </i> Harry – but I – I  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>238 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">s-swear I d-didn’t mean to – R-Riddle made me, he t-took me over </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– and –  <i class=\"calibre4\">how</i> did you kill that – that thing? W-where’s Riddle? The last thing I r-remember is him coming out of the diary –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s all right,’ said Harry, holding up the diary, and showing Ginny the fang hole, ‘Riddle’s finished. Look! Him  <i class=\"calibre4\">and</i> the Basilisk. C’mon, Ginny, let’s get out of here –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m  going  to  be  expelled!’  Ginny  wept,  as  Harry  helped  her awkwardly to her feet. ‘I’ve looked forward to coming to Hogwarts ever since B-Bill came and n-now I’ll have to leave and –  <i class=\"calibre4\">w-what’ll</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Mum and Dad say? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fawkes was waiting for them, hovering in the Chamber entrance. Harry urged Ginny forward; they stepped over the motionless coils of the dead Basilisk, through the echoing gloom and back into the tunnel. Harry heard the stone doors close behind them with a soft hiss. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After a few minutes’ progress up the dark tunnel, a distant sound of slowly shifting rock reached Harry’s ears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron!’ Harry yelled, speeding up. ‘Ginny’s OK! I’ve got her!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He heard Ron give a strangled cheer and they turned the next bend to see his eager face staring through the sizeable gap he had managed to make in the rock fall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ginny! </i>’ Ron thrust an arm through the gap in the rock to pull her through first. ‘You’re alive! I don’t believe it! What happened?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He tried to hug her but Ginny held him off, sobbing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you’re okay, Ginny,’ said Ron, beaming at her. ‘It’s over now, it’s – where did that bird come from?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fawkes had swooped through the gap after Ginny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s Dumbledore’s,’ said Harry, squeezing through himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And how come you’ve got a  <i class=\"calibre4\">sword? </i>’ said Ron, gaping at the glittering weapon in Harry’s hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll explain when we get out of here,’ said Harry, with a sideways glance at Ginny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Later,’ Harry said quickly. He didn’t think it was a good idea to tell Ron yet who’d been opening the Chamber, not in front of Ginny, anyway. ‘Where’s Lockhart?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Back there,’ said Ron, grinning and jerking his head up the tunnel towards the pipe. ‘He’s in a bad way. Come and see.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Led by Fawkes, whose wide scarlet wings emitted a soft golden glow in the darkness, they walked all the way back to the mouth  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Heir of Slytherin 239 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">of the pipe. Gilderoy Lockhart was sitting there, humming placidly to himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘His memory’s gone,’ said Ron. ‘The Memory Charm backfired. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hit him instead of us. Hasn’t got a clue who he is, or where he is, or who we are. I told him to come and wait here. He’s a danger to himself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart peered good-naturedly up at them all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello,’ he said. ‘Odd sort of place, this, isn’t it? Do you live here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Ron, raising his eyebrows at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry bent down and looked up the long, dark pipe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you thought how we’re going to get back up this?’ he said to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron shook his head, but Fawkes the phoenix had swooped past Harry and was now fluttering in front of him, his beady eyes bright in the dark. He was waving his long golden tail feathers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked uncertainly at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He looks like he wants you to grab hold …’ said Ron, looking perplexed. ‘But you’re much too heavy for a bird to pull up there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fawkes,’ said Harry, ‘isn’t an ordinary bird.’ He turned quickly to the others. ‘We’ve got to hold on to each other. Ginny, grab Ron’s hand. Professor Lockhart –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He means you,’ said Ron sharply to Lockhart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You hold Ginny’s other hand.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tucked the sword and the Sorting Hat into his belt, Ron took hold of the back of Harry’s robes, and Harry reached out and took hold of Fawkes’s strangely hot tail feathers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">An extraordinary lightness seemed to spread through his whole body, and next second, with a whoosh, they were flying upwards through the pipe. Harry could hear Lockhart dangling below him, saying, ‘Amazing! Amazing! This is just like magic!’ The chill air was whipping through Harry’s hair, and before he’d stopped enjoying the ride, it was over – all four of them were hitting the wet floor of Moaning Myrtle’s bathroom, and as Lockhart straightened his hat, the sink that hid the pipe was sliding back into place. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Myrtle goggled at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re alive,’ she said blankly to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s no need to sound so disappointed,’ he said grimly, wiping flecks of blood and slime off his glasses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, well … I’d just been thinking. If you had died, you’d have </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>240 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">been welcome to share my toilet,’ said Myrtle, blushing silver. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Urgh!’ said Ron, as they left the bathroom for the dark, deserted corridor outside. ‘Harry! I think Myrtle’s got  <i class=\"calibre4\">fond</i> of you! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You’ve got competition, Ginny!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But tears were still flooding silently down Ginny’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where now?’ said Ron, with an anxious look at Ginny. Harry pointed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fawkes was leading the way, glowing gold along the corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They strode after him, and moments later, found themselves outside Professor McGonagall’s office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knocked and pushed the door open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER EIGHTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dobby’s Reward</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a moment, there was silence as Harry, Ron, Ginny and Lockhart stood in the doorway, covered in muck and slime and (in Harry’s case) blood. Then there was a scream. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ginny! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Mrs Weasley, who had been sitting crying in front of the fire. She leapt to her feet, closely followed by Mr Weasley, and both of them flung themselves on their daughter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, however, was looking past them. Professor Dumbledore was standing by the mantelpiece, beaming, next to Professor McGonagall, who was taking great, steadying gasps, clutching her chest. Fawkes went whooshing past Harry’s ear and settled on Dumbledore’s shoulder, just as Harry found himself and Ron being swept into Mrs Weasley’s tight embrace. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You saved her! You saved her!  <i class=\"calibre4\">How</i> did you do it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think we’d all like to know that,’ said Professor McGonagall weakly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley let go of Harry, who hesitated for a moment, then walked over to the desk and laid upon it the Sorting Hat, the ruby-encrusted sword and what remained of Riddle’s diary. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he started telling them everything. For nearly a quarter of an hour he spoke into the rapt silence: he told them about hearing the disembodied voice, how Hermione had finally realised that he was hearing a Basilisk in the pipes; how he and Ron had followed the spiders into the Forest, that Aragog had told them where the last victim of the Basilisk had died; how he had guessed that Moaning Myrtle had been the victim, and that the entrance to the Chamber of Secrets might be in her bathroom … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very well,’ Professor McGonagall prompted him, as he paused, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘so you found out where the entrance was – breaking a hundred school rules into pieces along the way, I might add – but how on </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>242 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">earth</i> did you all get out of there alive, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So Harry, his voice now growing hoarse from all this talking, told them about Fawkes’s timely arrival and about the Sorting Hat giving him the sword. But then he faltered. He had so far avoided mentioning Riddle’s diary – or Ginny. She was standing with her head against Mrs Weasley’s shoulder, and tears were still coursing silently down her cheeks. What if they expelled her? Harry thought in panic. Riddle’s diary didn’t work any more … How could they prove it had been he who’d made her do it all? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Instinctively, Harry looked at Dumbledore, who smiled faintly, the firelight glancing off his half-moon spectacles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What interests  <i class=\"calibre4\">me</i> most,’ said Dumbledore gently, ‘is how Lord Voldemort managed to enchant Ginny, when my sources tell me he is currently in hiding in the forests of Albania.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Relief – warm, sweeping, glorious relief – swept over Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘W-what’s that?’ said Mr Weasley in a stunned voice. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You Know</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Who? </i> En-enchant  <i class=\"calibre4\">Ginny? </i> But Ginny’s not … Ginny hasn’t been … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">has she?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was this diary,’ said Harry quickly, picking it up and showing it to Dumbledore. ‘Riddle wrote it when he was sixteen.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore took the diary from Harry and peered keenly down his long, crooked nose at its burnt and soggy pages. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Brilliant,’ he said softly. ‘Of course, he was probably the most brilliant student Hogwarts has ever seen.’ He turned around to the Weasleys, who were looking utterly bewildered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very few people know that Lord Voldemort was once called Tom Riddle. I taught him myself, fifty years ago, at Hogwarts. He disappeared after leaving the school … travelled far and wide … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">sank so deeply into the Dark Arts, consorted with the very worst of our kind, underwent so many dangerous, magical transformations, that when he resurfaced as Lord Voldemort, he was barely recognisable. Hardly anyone connected Lord Voldemort with the clever, handsome boy who was once Head Boy here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Ginny,’ said Mrs Weasley, ‘what’s our Ginny got to do with </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– with –  <i class=\"calibre4\">him? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘His d-diary!’ Ginny sobbed. ‘I’ve b-been writing in it, and he’s been w-writing back all year –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ginny! </i>’  said  Mr  Weasley,  flabbergasted. ‘Haven’t I taught you <i class=\"calibre4\">anything? </i> What have I always told you? Never trust anything that can think for itself  <i class=\"calibre4\">if you can’t see where it keeps its brain. </i> Why </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Reward 243 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">didn’t you show the diary to me, or your mother? A suspicious object like that, it was  <i class=\"calibre4\">clearly</i> full of Dark Magic!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I d-didn’t know,’ sobbed Ginny. ‘I found it inside one of the books Mum got me. I th-thought someone had just left it in there and forgotten about it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss Weasley should go up to the hospital wing straight away,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore interrupted in a firm voice. ‘This has been a terrible ordeal for her. There will be no punishment. Older and wiser wizards than she have been hoodwinked by Lord Voldemort.’ He strode over to the door and opened it. ‘Bed rest and perhaps a large, steaming mug of hot chocolate. I always find that cheers me up,’ he added, twinkling kindly down at her. ‘You will find that Madam Pomfrey is still awake. She’s just giving out Mandrake juice – I dare say the Basilisk’s victims will be waking up any moment.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So Hermione’s OK!’ said Ron brightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There has been no lasting harm done,’ said Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley led Ginny out, and Mr Weasley followed, still looking deeply shaken. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know, Minerva,’ Professor Dumbledore said thoughtfully to Professor McGonagall, ‘I think all this merits a good  <i class=\"calibre4\">feast. </i>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Might I ask you to go and alert the kitchens?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Professor McGonagall crisply, also moving to the door. ‘I’ll leave you to deal with Potter and Weasley, shall I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly,’ said Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She left, and Harry and Ron gazed uncertainly at Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What exactly had Professor McGonagall meant,  <i class=\"calibre4\">deal</i> with them? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Surely –  <i class=\"calibre4\">surely</i> – they weren’t about to be punished? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I seem to remember telling you both that I would have to expel you if you broke any more school rules,’ said Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron opened his mouth in horror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Which goes to show that the best of us must sometimes eat our words,’ Dumbledore went on, smiling. ‘You will both receive Special Awards for Services to the School and – let me see – yes, I think two hundred points apiece for Gryffindor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron went as brightly pink as Lockhart’s Valentine flowers and closed his mouth again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But one of us seems to be keeping mightily quiet about his part in this dangerous adventure,’ Dumbledore added. ‘Why so modest, Gilderoy?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry gave a start. He had completely forgotten about </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>244 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart. He turned and saw that Lockhart was standing in a corner of the room, still wearing his vague smile. When Dumbledore addressed him, Lockhart looked over his shoulder to see who he was talking to. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore,’ Ron said quickly, ‘there was an accident down in the Chamber of Secrets. Professor Lockhart –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Am I a Professor?’ said Lockhart in mild surprise. ‘Goodness. I expect I was hopeless, was I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He tried to do a Memory Charm and the wand backfired,’ Ron explained quietly to Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dear me,’ said Dumbledore, shaking his head, his long silver moustache quivering. ‘Impaled upon your own sword, Gilderoy!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sword?’ said Lockhart dimly. ‘Haven’t got a sword. That boy has, though.’ He pointed at Harry. ‘He’ll lend you one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Would you mind taking Professor Lockhart up to the hospital wing, too?’ Dumbledore said to Ron. ‘I’d like a few more words with Harry …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lockhart ambled out. Ron cast a curious look back at Dumbledore and Harry as he closed the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore crossed to one of the chairs by the fire. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit down, Harry,’ he said, and Harry sat, feeling unaccountably nervous. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘First of all, Harry, I want to thank you,’ said Dumbledore, eyes twinkling again. ‘You must have shown me real loyalty down in the Chamber. Nothing but that could have called Fawkes to you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stroked the phoenix, which had fluttered down onto his knee. Harry grinned awkwardly as Dumbledore watched him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And so you met Tom Riddle,’ said Dumbledore thoughtfully. ‘I imagine he was  <i class=\"calibre4\">most</i> interested in you …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Suddenly, something that was nagging at Harry came tumbling out of his mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore … Riddle said I’m like him. Strange like-nesses, he said …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Did</i> he, now?’ said Dumbledore, looking thoughtfully under his thick silver eyebrows at Harry. ‘And what do you think, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t think I’m like him!’ said Harry, more loudly than he’d intended. ‘I mean, I’m – I’m in  <i class=\"calibre4\">Gryffindor, </i> I’m …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he fell silent, a lurking doubt resurfacing in his mind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor,’ he started again after a moment, ‘the Sorting Hat </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Reward 245 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">told me I’d – I’d have done well in Slytherin. Everyone thought I was Slytherin’s heir for a while … because I can speak Parseltongue …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can speak Parseltongue, Harry,’ said Dumbledore calmly, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘because Lord Voldemort – who is the last remaining descendant of Salazar Slytherin – can speak Parseltongue. Unless I’m much mistaken, he transferred some of his own powers to you the night he gave you that scar. Not something he intended to do, I’m sure …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Voldemort put a bit of himself in  <i class=\"calibre4\">me? </i>’ Harry said, thunder-struck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It certainly seems so.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So I  <i class=\"calibre4\">should</i> be in Slytherin,’ Harry said, looking desperately into Dumbledore’s face. ‘The Sorting Hat could see Slytherin’s power in me, and it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Put you in Gryffindor,’ said Dumbledore calmly. ‘Listen to me, Harry. You happen to have many qualities Salazar Slytherin prized in his hand-picked students. His own very rare gift, Parseltongue </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… resourcefulness … determination … a certain disregard for rules,’ he added, his moustache quivering again. ‘Yet the Sorting Hat placed you in Gryffindor. You know why that was. Think.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It  only  put  me  in  Gryffindor,’  said  Harry  in  a  defeated  voice, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘because I asked not to go in Slytherin …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Exactly</i>,’ said Dumbledore, beaming once more. ‘Which makes you very  <i class=\"calibre4\">different</i> from Tom Riddle. It is our choices, Harry, that show what we truly are, far more than our abilities.’ Harry sat motionless in his chair, stunned. ‘If you want proof, Harry, that you belong in Gryffindor, I suggest you look more closely at  <i class=\"calibre4\">this. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore reached across to Professor McGonagall’s desk, picked up the blood-stained silver sword and handed it to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dully, Harry turned it over, the rubies blazing in the firelight. And then he saw the name engraved just below the hilt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Godric Gryffindor. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Only a true Gryffindor could have pulled that out of the Hat, Harry,’ said Dumbledore simply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a minute, neither of them spoke. Then Dumbledore pulled open one of the drawers in Professor McGonagall’s desk, and took out a quill and a bottle of ink. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What you need, Harry, is some food and sleep. I suggest you go down to the feast, while I write to Azkaban – we need our gamekeeper back. And I must draft an advertisement for the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>246 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Prophet, </i> too,’ he added thoughtfully. ‘We’ll be needing a new Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher. Dear me, we do seem to run through them, don’t we?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry got up and crossed to the door. He had just reached for the handle, however, when the door burst open so violently that it bounced back off the wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lucius Malfoy stood there, fury in his face. And cowering under his arm, heavily wrapped in bandages, was  <i class=\"calibre4\">Dobby. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good evening, Lucius,’ said Dumbledore pleasantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Malfoy almost knocked Harry over as he swept into the room. Dobby went scurrying in after him, crouching at the hem of his cloak, a look of abject terror on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So!’ said Lucius Malfoy, his cold eyes fixed on Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve come back. The governors suspended you, but you still saw fit to return to Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, you see, Lucius,’ said Dumbledore, smiling serenely, ‘the other eleven governors contacted me today. It was something like being caught in a hailstorm of owls, to tell the truth. They’d heard that Arthur Weasley’s daughter had been killed and wanted me back here at once. They seemed to think I was the best man for the job after all. Very strange tales they told me, too. Several of them seemed to think that you had threatened to curse their families if they didn’t agree to suspend me in the first place.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Malfoy went even paler than usual, but his eyes were still slits of fury. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So – have you stopped the attacks yet?’ he sneered. ‘Have you caught the culprit?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We have,’ said Dumbledore, with a smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Well? </i>’ said Mr Malfoy sharply. ‘Who is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The same person as last time, Lucius,’ said Dumbledore. ‘But this time, Lord Voldemort was acting through somebody else. By means of this diary.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He held up the small black book with the large hole through the centre, watching Mr Malfoy closely. Harry, however, was watching Dobby. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The elf was doing something very odd. His great eyes fixed meaningfully on Harry, he kept pointing at the diary, then at Mr Malfoy, and then hitting himself hard on the head with his fist. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see …’ said Mr Malfoy slowly to Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A clever plan,’ said Dumbledore in a level voice, still staring Mr </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Reward 247 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy straight in the eye. ‘Because if Harry here –’ Mr Malfoy shot Harry a swift, sharp look, ‘and his friend Ron hadn’t discovered this book, why – Ginny Weasley might have taken all the blame. No one would ever have been able to prove she hadn’t acted of her own free will …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Malfoy said nothing. His face was suddenly mask-like. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And imagine,’ Dumbledore went on, ‘what might have happened then … The Weasleys are one of our most prominent pure-blood families. Imagine the effect on Arthur Weasley and his Muggle Protection Act, if his own daughter was discovered attacking and killing Muggle-borns. Very fortunate the diary was discovered, and Riddle’s memories wiped from it. Who knows what the consequences might have been otherwise …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Malfoy forced himself to speak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very fortunate,’ he said stiffly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And still, behind his back, Dobby was pointing, first to the diary, then to Lucius Malfoy, then punching himself in the head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Harry suddenly understood. He nodded at Dobby, and Dobby backed into a corner, now twisting his ears in punishment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you want to know how Ginny got hold of that diary, Mr Malfoy?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lucius Malfoy rounded on him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How should I know how the stupid little girl got hold of it?’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because you gave it to her,’ said Harry. ‘In Flourish and Blotts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You picked up her old Transfiguration book, and slipped the diary inside it, didn’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He saw Mr Malfoy’s white hands clench and unclench. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Prove it,’ he hissed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, no one will be able to do that,’ said Dumbledore, smiling at Harry. ‘Not now Riddle has vanished from the book. On the other hand, I would advise you, Lucius, not to go giving out any more of Lord Voldemort’s old school things. If any more of them find their way into innocent hands, I think Arthur Weasley, for one, will make sure they are traced back to you …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lucius Malfoy stood for a moment, and Harry distinctly saw his right hand twitch as though he was longing to reach for his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Instead, he turned to his house-elf. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re going, Dobby!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He wrenched open the door, and as the elf came hurrying up to </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>248 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">him, he kicked him right through it. They could hear Dobby squealing with pain all the way along the corridor. Harry stood for a moment, thinking hard. Then it came to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore,’ he said hurriedly, ‘can I give that diary <i class=\"calibre4\">back</i> to Mr Malfoy, please?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly, Harry,’ said Dumbledore calmly. ‘But hurry. The feast, remember.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry grabbed the diary and dashed out of the office. He could hear Dobby’s squeals of pain receding around the corner. Quickly, wondering if this plan could possibly work, Harry took off one of his shoes, pulled off his slimy, filthy sock, and stuffed the diary into it. Then he ran down the dark corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He caught up with them at the top of the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mr Malfoy,’ he gasped, skidding to a halt, ‘I’ve got something for you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he forced the smelly sock into Lucius Malfoy’s hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What the –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Malfoy ripped the sock off the diary, threw it aside, then looked furiously from the ruined book to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll meet the same sticky end as your parents one of these days, Harry Potter,’ he said softly. ‘They were meddlesome fools, too.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned to go. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come, Dobby. I said,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Come! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Dobby didn’t move. He was holding up Harry’s disgusting, slimy sock, and looking at it as though it were a priceless treasure. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Master has given Dobby a sock,’ said the elf in wonderment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Master gave it to Dobby.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ spat Mr Malfoy. ‘What did you say?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dobby has got a sock,’ said Dobby in disbelief. ‘Master threw it, and Dobby caught it, and Dobby – Dobby is  <i class=\"calibre4\">free. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lucius Malfoy stood frozen, staring at the elf. Then he lunged at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve lost me my servant, boy!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Dobby shouted, ‘You shall not harm Harry Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud bang, and Mr Malfoy was thrown backwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He crashed down the stairs, three at a time, landing in a crumpled heap on the landing below. He got up, his face livid, and pulled out his wand, but Dobby raised a long threatening finger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You shall go now,’ he said fiercely, pointing down at Mr Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Reward 249 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You shall not touch Harry Potter. You shall go now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lucius Malfoy had no choice. With a last, incensed stare at the pair of them, he swung his cloak around him and hurried out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter freed Dobby!’ said the elf shrilly, gazing up at Harry, moonlight from the nearest window reflected in his orb-like eyes. ‘Harry Potter set Dobby free!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Least I could do, Dobby,’ said Harry, grinning. ‘Just promise never to try and save my life again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The elf’s ugly brown face split suddenly into a wide, toothy smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve just got one question, Dobby,’ said Harry, as Dobby pulled on Harry’s sock with shaking hands. ‘You told me all this had nothing to do with He Who Must Not Be Named, remember? Well –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was a clue, sir,’ said Dobby, his eyes widening, as though this was obvious. ‘Dobby was giving you a clue. The Dark Lord, before he changed his name, could be freely named, you see?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Harry weakly. ‘Well, I’d better go. There’s a feast, and my friend Hermione should be awake by now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby threw his arms around Harry’s middle and hugged him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry Potter is greater by far than Dobby knew!’ he sobbed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Farewell, Harry Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And with a final loud crack, Dobby disappeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had been to several Hogwarts feasts, but never one quite like this. Everybody was in their pyjamas, and the celebrations lasted all night. Harry didn’t know whether the best bit was Hermione running towards him, screaming, ‘You solved it! You solved it!’ or Justin hurrying over from the Hufflepuff table to wring his hand and apologise endlessly for suspecting him, or Hagrid turning up at half past three, cuffing Harry and Ron so hard on the shoulders that they were knocked into their plates of trifle, or his and Ron’s four hundred points securing Gryffindor the House Cup for the second year running, or Professor McGonagall standing up to tell them all that the exams had been cancelled as a school treat (‘Oh,  <i class=\"calibre4\">no! </i>’ said Hermione), or Dumbledore announcing that, unfortunately, Professor Lockhart would be unable to return next year, owing to the fact that he needed to go away and get his memory back. Quite a few of the teachers joined in the cheering that greeted this news. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>250 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shame,’ said Ron, helping himself to a jam doughnut. ‘He was starting to grow on me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rest of the summer term passed in a haze of blazing sunshine. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hogwarts was back to normal, with only a few, small differences: Defence Against the Dark Arts classes were cancelled (‘but we’ve had plenty of practice at that anyway,’ Ron told a disgruntled Hermione) and Lucius Malfoy had been sacked as a school governor. Draco was no longer strutting around the school as though he owned the place. On the contrary, he looked resentful and sulky. On the other hand, Ginny Weasley was perfectly happy again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Too soon, it was time for the journey home on the Hogwarts Express. Harry, Ron, Hermione, Fred, George and Ginny got a compartment to themselves. They made the most of the last few hours in which they were allowed to do magic before the holidays. They played Exploding Snap, set off the very last of Fred and George’s Filibuster Fireworks, and practised disarming each other by magic. Harry was getting very good at it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were almost at King’s Cross when Harry remembered something. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ginny – what did you see Percy doing, that he didn’t want you to tell anyone?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, that,’ said Ginny, giggling. ‘Well – Percy’s got a  <i class=\"calibre4\">girlfriend. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred dropped a stack of books on George’s head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s that Ravenclaw Prefect, Penelope Clearwater,’ said Ginny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s who he was writing to all last summer. He’s been meeting her all over the school in secret. I walked in on them kissing in an empty classroom one day. He was so upset when she was –  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you know – attacked. You won’t tease him, will you?’ she added anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wouldn’t dream of it,’ said Fred, who was looking as if his birthday had come early. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Definitely not,’ said George, sniggering. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hogwarts Express slowed and finally stopped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pulled out his quill and a bit of parchment and turned to Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is called a telephone number,’ he told Ron, scribbling it twice, tearing the parchment in two and handing it to them. ‘I told </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dobby’s Reward 251 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">your dad how to use a telephone last summer, he’ll know. Call me at the Dursleys, OK? I can’t stand another two months with only Dudley to talk to …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your aunt and uncle will be proud, though, won’t they?’ said Hermione, as they got off the train and joined the crowd throng-ing towards the enchanted barrier. ‘When they hear what you did this year?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Proud?’ said Harry. ‘Are you mad? All those times I could’ve died, and I didn’t manage it? They’ll be furious …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And together they walked back through the gateway to the Muggle world. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>\n<a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">J. K. (JOANNE KATHLEEN) ROWLING  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">has written fiction since she was a child. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Born in 1965, she grew up in Chepstow  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and wrote her first ‘book’ at the age of six  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">- a story about a rabbit called Rabbit. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She studied French and Classics at Exeter University, then moved to London to  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">work at Amnesty International, and then to Portugal to teach English as a foreign language, before settling in Edinburgh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The idea for Harry Potter occurred to her on the train from Manchester to London, where she says Harry Potter ‘just strolled into my head fully formed’, and by the time she had arrived at King’s Cross, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">many of the characters had taken shape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">During the next five years she outlined the plots for each book and began writing the first in the series,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry Potter and</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the Philosopher’s Stone, </i> which was first published by Bloomsbury in 1997. The  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">other Harry Potter titles:  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry Potter and</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the Chamber of Secrets, Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Prisoner of Azkaban, Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Goblet of Fire, </i> and  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Order of the Phoenix, </i> followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-2fbf83 twpub-64489a54c51f2eeb-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">J. K. Rowling has also written three other companion books,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Quidditch Through the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Ages, </i>  <i class=\"calibre4\">Fantastic Beasts and Where to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Find Them</i> and <i class=\"calibre4\"> The Tales of Beedle the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Bard, </i> in aid of Comic Relief. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/64489a54c51f2eeb/text/000004295": {
